INSERT INTO `hotels` (`id`, `name`, `slug`, `location`, `category`, `stars`, `description`, `description_en`, `description_ko`, `description_zh`, `facilities`, `primary_image`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(17, 'Manado Tateli Beach Resort', 'mercure-manado-tateli', 'Jalan Raya Tanawangko, Tateli Satu', 'resort', 4, '<p>Mercure Manado Tateli Beach Resort menawarkan kamar-kamar dengan TV kabel dan balkon pribadi yang menyuguhkan pemandangan Laut Sulawesi atau kolam renang hotel. Akomodasi ini memiliki restoran, ruang kebugaran, akses Wi-Fi gratis, dan tempat parkir.\r\n\r\nSetiap kamar di Mercure Manado Tateli Beach Resort dilengkapi dengan kamar mandi pribadi. Fasilitas di kamar meliputi fasilitas membuat teh/kopi, minibar, dan brankas. Jubah mandi dan sandal juga disediakan.\r\n\r\nAnda dapat bermain tenis atau bersantai di sauna. Berbagai kegiatan air yang ditawarkan mencakup snorkelling dan menyelam scuba.\r\n\r\nHidangan lokal, Barat, dan Asia disajikan di Kopi-O Restaurant. Berbagai minuman tersedia di Taman Laut Pool Bar.\r\n\r\nMercure Manado Tateli Beach Resort berjarak 30 menit berkendara dari Kota Manado. Bandara Sam Ratulangi dapat dicapai dalam waktu 45 menit. Pulau Bunaken berselang 1 jam naik perahu motor dari hotel.</p>', '<p>Mercure Manado Tateli Beach Resort offers rooms equipped with cable TV and private balconies overlooking the Sulawesi Sea or the hotel’s swimming pool. The property features a restaurant, fitness center, free Wi-Fi access, and parking facilities.</p><p>Each room at Mercure Manado Tateli Beach Resort includes a private bathroom. In-room amenities include tea/coffee making facilities, a minibar, and a safety deposit box. Bathrobes and slippers are also provided for guests’ comfort.</p><p>Guests can enjoy playing tennis or relaxing in the sauna. A variety of water activities are available, including snorkeling and scuba diving.</p><p>Local, Western, and Asian dishes are served at Kopi-O Restaurant. A selection of beverages is available at the Taman Laut Pool Bar.</p><p>Mercure Manado Tateli Beach Resort is located about a 30-minute drive from Manado City. Sam Ratulangi Airport can be reached within 45 minutes, while Bunaken Island is approximately a 1-hour motorboat ride from the resort.</p>', '<p>Mercure Manado Tateli Beach Resort는 케이블 TV와 술라웨시 바다 또는 호텔 수영장을 조망할 수 있는 전용 발코니를 갖춘 객실을 제공합니다. 리조트에는 레스토랑, 피트니스 센터, 무료 Wi-Fi, 주차 시설이 마련되어 있습니다.</p><p>각 객실에는 전용 욕실이 있으며, 커피/차 메이커, 미니바, 개인 금고 등의 편의시설이 구비되어 있습니다. 또한 목욕 가운과 슬리퍼도 제공됩니다.</p><p>투숙객은 테니스를 즐기거나 사우나에서 휴식을 취할 수 있습니다. 스노클링과 스쿠버 다이빙을 포함한 다양한 해양 액티비티도 이용 가능합니다.</p><p>Kopi-O Restaurant에서는 현지 요리, 서양식 및 아시아 요리를 제공합니다. Taman Laut Pool Bar에서는 다양한 음료를 즐길 수 있습니다.</p><p>Mercure Manado Tateli Beach Resort는 마나도 시내에서 차로 약 30분 거리에 위치해 있으며, 사무 라툴랑이 공항까지는 약 45분이 소요됩니다. 부나켄 섬까지는 리조트에서 모터보트로 약 1시간이 소요됩니다.</p>', '<p>Mercure Manado Tateli Beach Resort 提供配有有线电视和私人阳台的客房，客人可欣赏苏拉威西海或酒店泳池的景观。度假村设有餐厅、健身中心、免费 Wi-Fi 以及停车场。</p><p>每间客房均配有私人浴室。房内设施包括咖啡/茶冲泡设备、迷你吧以及保险箱，同时还提供浴袍和拖鞋以提升舒适度。</p><p>客人可以打网球或在桑拿中放松身心。酒店还提供多种水上活动，包括浮潜和水肺潜水。</p><p>Kopi-O Restaurant 提供当地、西式及亚洲美食，而 Taman Laut Pool Bar 则供应多种饮品。</p><p>Mercure Manado Tateli Beach Resort 距离万鸦老市区约30分钟车程，前往萨姆·拉图兰吉机场约需45分钟。从酒店乘坐快艇约1小时即可抵达布纳肯岛。</p>', '[\"Kolam renang outdoor\",\"WiFi gratis\",\"Antar-jemput bandara\",\"Tepi pantai\",\"Pusat kebugaran\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Bar\",\"Area pantai pribadi\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/pTFtp35DZYOiPJFc8vzp6pPMdJ4BVvVdraQdaz5T.webp', '2026-04-10 05:21:10', '2026-04-23 02:20:03'),
(18, 'Sintesa Peninsula Hotel Manado', 'sintesa-peninsula', 'Jl. Jend Sudirman, Gunung Wenang,', 'city_hotel', 5, '<p>Berlokasi strategis di jantung Kota Manado, Sintesa Peninsula Hotel Manado merupakan hotel bintang 5 yang didesain dengan mewah dan modern. Dengan menyuguhkan pemandangan kota Manado, penginapan ini merupakan pilihan yang tepat bagi kamu yang ingin melakukan perjalanan bisnis atau berlibur bersama keluarga. Koneksi WiFi bisa diakses di semua kamar dan area publik di hotel.</p><p>Beberapa kamar dilengkapi dengan balkon dan teras. Di dalam kamar, kamu bisa mendapatkan fasilitas pembuat kopi/teh, TV layar datar, meja tulis, dan lemari es mini. Selain itu, peralatan mandi gratis dan shower air panas atau bathtub disediakan di kamar mandi dalamnya.</p><p>Sarapan buffet dan menu a la carte tersedia selama 24 jam di Gardenia Restaurant yang ada di hotel. Kamu bisa memilih menikmati hidangan di area indoor atau di area dengan tempat duduk terbuka yang berlokasi di samping taman dan kolam renang hotel. Untuk hiburan tambahan, Club Deluxe menyajikan ruang karaoke lengkap dengan peralatannya yang mewah.</p><p>Sintesa Peninsula Hotel Manado juga menyediakan perawatan relaksasi di Fuji Spa dengan biaya tambahan. Sedangkan, pusat kebugaran dapat diakses secara gratis untuk tamu yang menginap. Fasilitas rapat dan jamuan makan di hotel ini dapat melayani hingga 1.200 tamu, serta dilengkapi dengan teknologi konferensi terbaru.</p><p>Dari hotel, Bandara Internasional Sam Ratulangi bisa ditempuh dengan 24 menit berkendara. Manado Town Square berjarak 2.55 km, sedangkan Pantai Malalayang berlokasi sejauh 6.53 km dari Sintesa Peninsula Hotel Manado</p>', '<p>Strategically located in the heart of Manado City, Sintesa Peninsula Hotel Manado is a 5-star hotel designed with luxury and modern elegance. Offering stunning views of Manado, this accommodation is an ideal choice for both business trips and family vacations. WiFi is available in all rooms and public areas of the hotel.</p><p>Some rooms feature a balcony and terrace. In each room, guests can enjoy facilities such as coffee/tea making facilities, a flat-screen TV, a work desk, and a mini refrigerator. The en-suite bathroom is equipped with free toiletries, as well as a hot shower or bathtub.</p><p>Buffet breakfast and à la carte menu are available 24 hours at the hotel’s Gardenia Restaurant. Guests can choose to dine indoors or in the open-air seating area located beside the hotel’s garden and swimming pool. For additional entertainment, Club Deluxe offers karaoke rooms equipped with luxurious facilities.</p><p>Sintesa Peninsula Hotel Manado also provides relaxing treatments at Fuji Spa for an additional charge, while the fitness center is available free of charge for in-house guests. The hotel’s meeting and banquet facilities can accommodate up to 1,200 guests and are equipped with the latest conference technology.</p><p>From the hotel, Sam Ratulangi International Airport can be reached within a 24-minute drive. Manado Town Square is located 2.55 km away, while Malalayang Beach is approximately 6.53 km from Sintesa Peninsula Hotel Manado.</p>', '<p>마나도 시 중심부에 위치한 Sintesa Peninsula Hotel Manado는 럭셔리하고 현대적인 디자인의 5성급 호텔입니다. 마나도 시내의 아름다운 전망을 제공하며, 비즈니스 여행과 가족 휴가 모두에 이상적인 숙소입니다. 호텔의 모든 객실과 공용 공간에서 Wi-Fi를 이용할 수 있습니다.</p><p>일부 객실에는 발코니와 테라스가 마련되어 있습니다. 객실 내에는 커피/차 메이커, 평면 TV, 업무용 책상, 미니 냉장고가 구비되어 있습니다. 또한 욕실에는 무료 세면도구와 함께 온수 샤워 또는 욕조가 제공됩니다.</p><p>호텔 내 Gardenia Restaurant에서는 24시간 동안 뷔페 조식과 일품요리(à la carte)를 제공합니다. 투숙객은 실내 또는 정원과 수영장 옆의 야외 좌석에서 식사를 즐길 수 있습니다. 추가적인 즐길 거리로, Club Deluxe에서는 고급 시설을 갖춘 노래방을 이용할 수 있습니다.</p><p>Sintesa Peninsula Hotel Manado는 추가 요금으로 Fuji Spa에서 편안한 스파 트리트먼트를 제공하며, 피트니스 센터는 투숙객에게 무료로 개방됩니다. 또한 최대 1,200명까지 수용 가능한 연회 및 회의 시설을 갖추고 있으며, 최신 회의 기술이 지원됩니다.</p><p>호텔에서 사무 라툴랑이 국제공항까지는 차량으로 약 24분이 소요됩니다. Manado Town Square는 약 2.55km, Malalayang 해변은 약 6.53km 거리에 위치해 있습니다.</p>', '<p>Sintesa Peninsula Hotel Manado 位于万鸦老市中心，是一家融合奢华与现代设计的五星级酒店。酒店可欣赏万鸦老城市景观，是商务出行及家庭度假的理想选择。酒店所有客房及公共区域均提供 WiFi。</p><p>部分客房设有阳台和露台。客房内配备咖啡/茶冲泡设施、平板电视、书桌以及迷你冰箱。每间客房均设有独立浴室，配备免费洗浴用品，以及热水淋浴或浴缸。</p><p>酒店内的 Gardenia Restaurant 提供24小时自助早餐及单点菜单。宾客可选择在室内用餐，或在位于花园与泳池旁的露天座位区享用美食。作为额外娱乐设施，Club Deluxe 提供设备齐全且豪华的卡拉OK包房。</p><p>Sintesa Peninsula Hotel Manado 还提供 Fuji Spa 放松护理服务（需额外付费），而健身中心则对住店客人免费开放。酒店的会议及宴会设施可容纳多达1,200位宾客，并配备先进的会议技术设备。</p><p>从酒店出发，驱车约24分钟即可到达萨姆·拉图兰吉国际机场。Manado Town Square 距离酒店约2.55公里，而 Malalayang 海滩距离约6.53公里</p>', '[\"Restoran\",\"Kolam Renang Indoor\",\"Kolam Renang Outdoor\",\"Menyelam\",\"Snorkeling\",\"Sauna\",\"Spa\",\"Ruang pijat\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/c7BD0uQz77NGxaVoOxYqcDid49TcMKJqmKPrzxlQ.webp', '2026-04-10 05:21:10', '2026-04-21 06:23:39'),
(19, 'Swiss-Belhotel Manado', 'swiss-belhotel-manado', 'Jl. Jendral Sudirman No.85-87', 'city_hotel', 4, '<p>Terletak di kawasan pusat bisnis kota Manado, <strong>Swiss-Belhotel Maleosan Manado</strong> menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang nyaman dengan perpaduan elegansi modern dan pelayanan berkualitas. Hotel ini menjadi pilihan ideal bagi wisatawan maupun pelaku perjalanan bisnis yang ingin menikmati kemudahan akses ke berbagai pusat aktivitas di kota Manado.</p><p>Salah satu daya tarik utama hotel ini adalah <strong>pemandangan panorama laut dan pegunungan</strong> yang dapat dinikmati dari beberapa area hotel dan kamar tertentu, menciptakan suasana menginap yang tenang dan menyegarkan. Untuk menunjang kenyamanan tamu, hotel juga menyediakan <strong>akses internet gratis</strong> serta <strong>layanan antar-jemput terjadwal ke pusat kota</strong> setiap hari.</p><p>Kamar-kamar di hotel ini dirancang <strong>luas, elegan, dan modern</strong>, memberikan kenyamanan maksimal bagi para tamu. Setiap kamar dilengkapi dengan berbagai fasilitas seperti <strong>AC, TV layar datar, area tempat duduk yang nyaman, serta berbagai fasilitas modern lainnya</strong> untuk memastikan pengalaman menginap yang menyenangkan.</p><p>Untuk relaksasi dan rekreasi, tamu dapat menikmati berbagai fasilitas hotel seperti <strong>kolam renang outdoor</strong> yang menyegarkan serta <strong>pusat kebugaran</strong> yang lengkap bagi tamu yang ingin tetap aktif selama menginap.</p><p>Dalam hal kuliner, hotel ini menawarkan berbagai pilihan bersantap yang menarik. <strong>Swiss Café</strong> menyajikan beragam hidangan lezat mulai dari masakan lokal hingga internasional, termasuk <strong>hidangan laut segar</strong> yang menjadi favorit para tamu. Sementara itu, <strong>Lounge Lobby Minahasa</strong> menjadi tempat yang sempurna untuk bersantai sambil menikmati <strong>koktail, minuman, dan makanan ringan</strong>, dengan <strong>pertunjukan musik live setiap malam</strong> yang menambah suasana hangat dan menyenangkan.</p><p>Lokasi hotel juga sangat strategis untuk menjelajahi berbagai destinasi populer di Manado. Tamu dapat mengunjungi <strong>Bunaken National Park</strong>, yang terkenal dengan keindahan bawah lautnya dan menjadi lokasi favorit untuk <strong>scuba diving dan snorkeling</strong>. Selain itu, <strong>Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong>, salah satu kuil tertua dan bersejarah di Manado, juga berada tidak jauh dari hotel.</p><p>Bagi tamu yang datang melalui jalur udara, hotel ini berjarak sekitar <strong>14 km atau sekitar 25–30 menit berkendara dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>. Hotel juga menyediakan <strong>area parkir gratis</strong> bagi tamu yang membawa kendaraan pribadi.</p><p>Dengan <strong>lokasi strategis di pusat kota, fasilitas lengkap, pemandangan indah, serta pelayanan yang ramah dan profesional</strong>, Swiss-Belhotel Maleosan Manado menjadi pilihan sempurna bagi tamu yang ingin menikmati pengalaman menginap yang nyaman dan berkelas di Manado.</p>', '<p>Located in the central business district of Manado, <strong>Swiss-Belhotel Maleosan Manado</strong> offers a comfortable stay with a blend of modern elegance and high-quality hospitality. The hotel is an excellent choice for both leisure and business travelers who want convenient access to the city’s main commercial and entertainment areas.</p><p>One of the hotel’s highlights is its <strong>panoramic views of the sea and surrounding mountains</strong>, which can be enjoyed from selected rooms and hotel areas, creating a relaxing and refreshing atmosphere. To enhance guests’ convenience, the hotel also provides <strong>complimentary internet access</strong> and <strong>daily scheduled shuttle service to the city center</strong>.</p><p>The hotel’s rooms are <strong>spacious, stylish, and thoughtfully designed</strong>, offering a comfortable environment for guests to relax. Each room is equipped with modern amenities including <strong>air conditioning, a flat-screen TV, a comfortable seating area, and other essential facilities</strong> to ensure a pleasant stay.</p><p>For relaxation and recreation, guests can enjoy the hotel’s facilities such as an <strong>outdoor swimming pool</strong> and a <strong>fully equipped fitness center</strong>, perfect for staying active while traveling.</p><p>When it comes to dining, the hotel offers delightful culinary experiences. <strong>Swiss Café</strong> serves a variety of delicious dishes ranging from <strong>local Indonesian cuisine to international favorites</strong>, including <strong>fresh seafood specialties</strong>. Guests can also unwind at the <strong>Lobby Lounge Minahasa</strong>, where <strong>cocktails, beverages, and light snacks</strong> are served while enjoying <strong>live music performances every evening</strong>.</p><p>The hotel’s strategic location also makes it easy to explore nearby attractions. Guests can visit <strong>Bunaken National Park</strong>, famous for its spectacular marine biodiversity and a popular destination for <strong>scuba diving and snorkeling</strong>. Another nearby attraction is <strong>Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong>, one of the oldest and most historic temples in the city.</p><p>For travelers arriving by air, the hotel is located about <strong>14 km (approximately 25–30 minutes by car)</strong> from <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>. The hotel also provides <strong>free parking facilities</strong> for guests with private vehicles.</p><p>With its <strong>strategic city-center location, complete facilities, beautiful views, and warm professional service</strong>, Swiss-Belhotel Maleosan Manado is an ideal choice for travelers seeking a comfortable and memorable stay in Manado. ✨</p>', '<p>마나도 중심 비즈니스 지구에 위치한 Swiss-Belhotel Maleosan Manado는 현대적인 우아함과 수준 높은 서비스를 결합한 편안한 숙박 경험을 제공합니다. 이 호텔은 마나도 내 주요 활동 중심지로의 접근성이 뛰어나 관광객과 비즈니스 여행객 모두에게 이상적인 선택입니다.</p><p>이 호텔의 주요 매력 중 하나는 일부 객실과 호텔 구역에서 감상할 수 있는 바다와 산의 파노라마 전망으로, 평온하고 상쾌한 분위기를 제공합니다. 또한 투숙객의 편의를 위해 무료 인터넷과 매일 도심으로 운행되는 셔틀 서비스를 제공합니다.</p><p>객실은 넓고 우아하며 현대적인 디자인으로 설계되어 최대의 편안함을 제공합니다. 각 객실에는 에어컨, 평면 TV, 편안한 휴식 공간 등 다양한 현대식 편의시설이 갖추어져 있어 쾌적한 숙박을 보장합니다.</p><p>휴식과 레저를 위해 투숙객은 상쾌한 야외 수영장과 완비된 피트니스 센터를 이용할 수 있어 숙박 중에도 활기찬 시간을 보낼 수 있습니다.</p><p>미식 경험 또한 다양하게 즐길 수 있습니다. Swiss Café에서는 현지 요리부터 세계 각국의 요리까지 다양한 메뉴를 제공하며, 특히 신선한 해산물 요리가 많은 고객들에게 인기가 있습니다. Lobby Minahasa Lounge는 칵테일과 음료, 가벼운 스낵을 즐기며 휴식을 취하기에 완벽한 장소이며, 매일 밤 라이브 음악 공연이 분위기를 더욱 따뜻하고 즐겁게 만들어 줍니다.</p><p>호텔의 위치는 마나도의 인기 관광지를 탐방하기에도 매우 편리합니다. 아름다운 해양 생태계로 유명한 부나켄 국립공원은 스쿠버 다이빙과 스노클링을 즐기기에 최적의 장소입니다. 또한 마나도에서 가장 오래되고 역사적인 사원 중 하나인 반힌 키옹 사원도 호텔에서 가까운 거리에 위치해 있습니다.</p><p>항공편으로 방문하는 고객의 경우, 호텔은 사무 라툴랑이 국제공항에서 약 14km(차로 약 25~30분 거리)에 위치해 있어 접근성이 매우 뛰어납니다. 또한 자가용을 이용하는 고객을 위해 무료 주차 공간도 제공됩니다.</p><p>전략적인 위치, 완비된 시설, 아름다운 전망, 그리고 친절하고 전문적인 서비스를 갖춘 Swiss-Belhotel Maleosan Manado는 마나도에서 편안하고 품격 있는 숙박을 원하는 고객에게 완벽한 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>Swiss-Belhotel Maleosan Manado 位于万鸦老市中心商业区，为宾客提供融合现代优雅与高品质服务的舒适住宿体验。酒店地理位置优越，方便前往城市各大活动中心，是商务出行及休闲旅游的理想之选。</p><p>酒店的一大亮点是从部分客房及公共区域可欣赏到壮丽的海景与山景全景，为宾客营造宁静而清新的入住氛围。为提升入住体验，酒店还提供免费网络服务以及每日定时往返市中心的班车服务。</p><p>客房设计宽敞、优雅且现代，为宾客带来最大的舒适感。每间客房均配备空调、平板电视、舒适的休息区以及多种现代化设施，确保宾客拥有愉快的入住体验。</p><p>在休闲娱乐方面，宾客可使用酒店的多种设施，包括清爽的室外游泳池以及设备齐全的健身中心，让宾客在入住期间保持活力。</p><p>在餐饮方面，酒店提供丰富多样的用餐选择。Swiss Café 提供从本地美食到国际料理的多种菜品，其中新鲜海鲜尤为受欢迎。Lobby Minahasa Lounge 是放松身心的理想场所，宾客可在此享用鸡尾酒、饮品及小吃，每晚还有现场音乐表演，营造温馨愉悦的氛围。</p><p>酒店地理位置便利，方便宾客前往万鸦老的热门景点。布纳肯国家公园以其美丽的海底景观而闻名，是潜水和浮潜爱好者的理想目的地。此外，万鸦老历史悠久的寺庙之一——Ban Hin Kiong 寺也距离酒店不远。</p><p>对于乘飞机抵达的宾客，酒店距离萨姆·拉图兰吉国际机场约14公里，车程约25至30分钟。酒店还为自驾宾客提供免费停车场。</p><p>凭借优越的地理位置、完善的设施、优美的景观以及热情专业的服务，Swiss-Belhotel Maleosan Manado 是在万鸦老享受舒适与高品质住宿体验的理想选择。</p>', '[\"Kolam renang outdoor\",\"WiFi gratis\",\"Antar-jemput bandara\",\"Pusat kebugaran\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Spa & pusat kesehatan\",\"Pembuat teh\\/kopi di semua kamar\",\"Bar\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/JFd5bZFFNKIIoYHmTAJdD5ZOmOHeWSURJlWi659F.webp', '2026-04-10 05:21:10', '2026-04-21 06:24:00'),
(20, 'Manado Quality Hotel', 'manado-quality-hotel', 'Jl. Piere Tendean No.88-89', 'city_hotel', 3, '<p>Terletak di pusat kota Manado, <strong>Manado Quality Hotel</strong> menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang nyaman dengan pelayanan berkualitas tinggi, cocok untuk perjalanan bisnis maupun liburan. Hotel ini dikenal dengan standar pelayanan yang baik, fasilitas lengkap, serta suasana yang hangat sehingga memberikan pengalaman menginap yang menyenangkan bagi setiap tamu.</p><p>Hotel ini dilengkapi dengan berbagai fasilitas untuk menunjang kenyamanan tamu, termasuk <strong>pusat kebugaran yang lengkap, restoran, dan bar</strong> yang nyaman untuk bersantai setelah beraktivitas seharian. Dengan <strong>resepsionis 24 jam, layanan kamar, transfer bandara, serta WiFi gratis di seluruh area hotel</strong>, tamu dapat menikmati pelayanan yang praktis dan efisien selama menginap.</p><p>Setiap kamar dirancang dengan konsep <strong>modern, luas, dan nyaman</strong>. Kamar dilengkapi dengan <strong>AC, area tempat duduk, TV layar datar dengan saluran kabel, brankas pribadi, kulkas, serta ketel listrik</strong> untuk menambah kenyamanan tamu. Kamar mandi pribadi juga tersedia di setiap kamar, dilengkapi dengan <strong>bidet, perlengkapan mandi gratis, serta pengering rambut</strong>. Beberapa kamar bahkan menawarkan <strong>pemandangan laut yang indah</strong>, memberikan suasana menginap yang lebih menyenangkan.</p><p>Setiap pagi, tamu dapat menikmati pilihan <strong>sarapan prasmanan, sarapan ala Amerika, atau sarapan Asia</strong>, yang disiapkan untuk memulai hari dengan penuh energi.</p><p>Lokasi hotel yang strategis juga memudahkan tamu untuk menjelajahi berbagai destinasi menarik di Manado. <strong>Megamas Beach</strong> dapat dicapai dengan berjalan kaki sekitar <strong>17 menit</strong>, sementara <strong>Manado Harbor</strong> berjarak sekitar <strong>3,9 km</strong> dari hotel. Ikon kota <strong>Soekarno Bridge</strong> juga berada sekitar <strong>3,8 km</strong>, dan <strong>North Sulawesi State Museum</strong> berjarak sekitar <strong>3,9 km</strong> dari hotel. Bagi pecinta wisata alam, <strong>Mount Lokon</strong> yang terkenal berada sekitar <strong>23 km</strong> dari hotel.</p><p>Untuk tamu yang datang melalui jalur udara, hotel ini berjarak sekitar <strong>18 km atau sekitar 30 menit perjalanan dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, sehingga mudah diakses dari bandara.</p><p>Dengan <strong>pelayanan berkualitas, fasilitas lengkap, serta lokasi strategis di pusat kota</strong>, Manado Quality Hotel menjadi pilihan ideal bagi wisatawan yang mencari kenyamanan, kemudahan akses, dan pengalaman menginap yang menyenangkan di Manado.</p>', '<p>Located in the heart of Manado, <strong>Manado Quality Hotel</strong> offers a comfortable stay with high-quality service, making it a great choice for both business and leisure travelers. The hotel is well known for its reliable hospitality standards, modern facilities, and welcoming atmosphere, ensuring a pleasant and memorable stay for every guest.</p><p>The hotel features a variety of facilities designed to enhance guests’ comfort, including a <strong>fully equipped fitness center, a restaurant, and a cozy bar</strong> where guests can relax after a busy day. With <strong>a 24-hour front desk, room service, airport transfer, and complimentary WiFi throughout the property</strong>, guests can enjoy convenience and attentive service during their stay.</p><p>Each room is designed with a <strong>modern, spacious, and comfortable concept</strong>. Rooms are equipped with <strong>air conditioning, a seating area, a flat-screen TV with cable channels, a personal safe, a refrigerator, and an electric kettle</strong> for added convenience. The private bathrooms include <strong>a bidet, complimentary toiletries, and a hairdryer</strong>. Selected rooms also offer <strong>beautiful sea views</strong>, creating a relaxing atmosphere during your stay.</p><p>Guests can start their day with a delicious selection of <strong>buffet, American, or Asian breakfast</strong> options served at the hotel.</p><p>The hotel’s strategic location makes it easy to explore several attractions around Manado. <strong>Megamas Beach</strong> is about a <strong>17-minute walk</strong> from the hotel, while <strong>Manado Harbor</strong> is approximately <strong>3.9 km away</strong>. The iconic <strong>Soekarno Bridge</strong> is around <strong>3.8 km</strong> from the property, and <strong>North Sulawesi State Museum</strong> is about <strong>3.9 km away</strong>. For nature lovers, the famous <strong>Mount Lokon</strong> is located approximately <strong>23 km from the hotel</strong>.</p><p>For travelers arriving by air, the hotel is conveniently located about <strong>18 km (around 30 minutes by car)</strong> from <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, the main airport serving Manado.</p><p>With its <strong>quality service, comfortable facilities, and strategic location</strong>, Manado Quality Hotel is an excellent choice for travelers seeking convenience, comfort, and a pleasant stay in the vibrant city of Manado. ✨</p>', '<p>마나도 중심부에 위치한 Manado Quality Hotel은 편안한 숙박과 높은 수준의 서비스를 제공하며, 비즈니스 여행과 휴가 모두에 적합합니다. 이 호텔은 우수한 서비스 기준, 완비된 시설, 따뜻한 분위기로 모든 투숙객에게 쾌적한 숙박 경험을 제공합니다.</p><p>호텔은 다양한 편의시설을 갖추고 있으며, 완비된 피트니스 센터, 레스토랑, 그리고 하루 일정을 마친 후 휴식을 취할 수 있는 아늑한 바가 마련되어 있습니다. 또한 24시간 프런트 데스크, 룸서비스, 공항 셔틀 서비스, 전 구역 무료 Wi-Fi를 제공하여 편리하고 효율적인 서비스를 제공합니다.</p><p>각 객실은 현대적이고 넓으며 편안하게 설계되어 있습니다. 객실에는 에어컨, 휴식 공간, 케이블 채널이 제공되는 평면 TV, 개인 금고, 냉장고, 전기 주전자가 구비되어 있습니다. 전용 욕실에는 비데, 무료 세면도구, 헤어드라이어가 제공됩니다. 일부 객실에서는 아름다운 바다 전망을 감상할 수 있어 더욱 쾌적한 숙박을 제공합니다.</p><p>매일 아침 투숙객은 뷔페식 조식, 미국식 조식 또는 아시아식 조식 중에서 선택하여 즐길 수 있습니다.</p><p>호텔의 전략적인 위치는 마나도의 주요 관광지로 이동하기에 매우 편리합니다. 메가마스 해변까지는 도보 약 17분, 마나도 항구까지는 약 3.9km 거리에 있습니다. 도시의 랜드마크인 소에카르노 다리는 약 3.8km, 북술라웨시 주립 박물관은 약 3.9km 거리에 위치해 있습니다. 자연을 사랑하는 여행객에게 인기 있는 로콘 산은 약 23km 떨어져 있습니다.</p><p>항공으로 방문하는 투숙객의 경우, 호텔은 사무 라툴랑이 국제공항에서 약 18km(차로 약 30분 거리)에 위치해 있어 접근성이 뛰어납니다.</p><p>우수한 서비스, 완비된 시설, 그리고 마나도 중심부의 전략적인 위치를 갖춘 Manado Quality Hotel은 편안함과 편리함, 그리고 만족스러운 숙박 경험을 원하는 여행객에게 이상적인 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>Manado Quality Hotel 位于万鸦老市中心，为宾客提供舒适的住宿体验和高品质的服务，非常适合商务出行和休闲度假。酒店以优质的服务标准、完善的设施以及温馨的氛围而闻名，为每一位宾客带来愉快的入住体验。</p><p>酒店配备多种设施以满足宾客需求，包括设备齐全的健身中心、餐厅以及供客人放松的舒适酒吧。酒店还提供24小时前台服务、客房服务、机场接送服务以及覆盖全酒店的免费 Wi-Fi，让宾客在入住期间享受便捷高效的服务。</p><p>每间客房均采用现代化设计，空间宽敞舒适，配备空调、休息区、带有线频道的平板电视、私人保险箱、冰箱以及电热水壶。每间客房均设有私人浴室，配有坐浴盆、免费洗浴用品及吹风机。部分客房还可欣赏美丽的海景，让入住体验更加惬意。</p><p>每天早晨，宾客可选择享用自助早餐、美式早餐或亚洲风味早餐，为新的一天注入满满活力。</p><p>酒店地理位置优越，方便宾客前往万鸦老的各大景点。Megamas 海滩步行约17分钟可达，万鸦老港口距离酒店约3.9公里。城市地标索加诺大桥距离约3.8公里，北苏拉威西州博物馆距离约3.9公里。著名的洛孔山距离酒店约23公里，是自然爱好者的理想去处。</p><p>对于乘飞机抵达的宾客，酒店距离萨姆·拉图兰吉国际机场约18公里，车程约30分钟，交通十分便利。</p><p>凭借优质的服务、完善的设施以及位于市中心的优越位置，Manado Quality Hotel 是在万鸦老寻求舒适、便利与愉快住宿体验的理想之选</p>', '[\"WiFi gratis\",\"Antar-jemput bandara\",\"Pusat kebugaran\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Restoran\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Fasilitas tamu difabel\",\"Bar\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/g2B12c8pLQ9uv34U4CHlwuObeD25bBiiA18AOua2.jpg', '2026-04-10 05:21:10', '2026-04-21 06:13:05'),
(21, 'Novotel Manado Golf Resort & Convention Center', 'novotel-manado', 'Grand Kawanua City', 'resort', 4, '<p>Novotel Manado Golf Resort &amp; Convention Center merupakan hotel bintang 4 yang menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang nyaman dengan suasana resort yang tenang, cocok untuk wisatawan maupun pelaku perjalanan bisnis. Berlokasi strategis, hotel ini hanya sekitar 15 menit berkendara dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport, sehingga sangat mudah dijangkau bagi tamu yang datang melalui jalur udara.</p><p>Hotel ini dilengkapi dengan berbagai fasilitas premium untuk memberikan pengalaman menginap yang menyenangkan. Para tamu dapat menikmati perawatan spa yang memanjakan, serta lapangan golf yang menjadi daya tarik utama hotel ini. Selain itu tersedia juga kolam renang outdoor, akses internet kabel gratis, serta layanan kamar 24 jam untuk menambah kenyamanan selama menginap.</p><p>Kamar-kamar di hotel ini dirancang dengan konsep modern, luas, dan nyaman. Setiap kamar dilengkapi dengan AC, TV layar datar, minibar, serta brankas pribadi. Untuk tipe suite, tersedia ruang tamu terpisah dan dapur kecil (kitchenette) yang memberikan ruang lebih bagi tamu yang menginginkan kenyamanan ekstra. Kamar mandi dalam setiap kamar dilengkapi dengan shower atau bathtub serta perlengkapan mandi yang lengkap.</p><p>Lokasi hotel juga memudahkan tamu untuk mengunjungi berbagai destinasi menarik di sekitar Manado. Kawasan Manado Town Square dan Mega Mall Manado di area Boulevard dapat dicapai sekitar 30 menit berkendara, menawarkan berbagai pilihan belanja, restoran, dan hiburan. Sementara itu, Manado Bay yang menjadi titik keberangkatan kapal menuju Bunaken Island dapat dicapai sekitar 35 menit perjalanan. Bagi pecinta alam, Lake Tondano juga dapat dikunjungi dengan perjalanan sekitar 1 jam 30 menit dari hotel.</p><p>WiFi gratis tersedia di area publik hotel. Tamu juga dapat mengatur wisata harian dan penyewaan mobil melalui meja layanan tur. Setelah berolahraga di pusat kebugaran, tamu dapat bersantai di sauna atau hot tub yang tersedia di hotel.</p><p>Untuk pengalaman kuliner, restoran The Square menghadirkan konsep interactive open kitchen yang menyajikan berbagai hidangan internasional dalam bentuk buffet. Pilihan bersantap lainnya termasuk Wasabi Japanese Restaurant yang menyajikan hidangan Jepang autentik, serta H2O Pool Bar yang menawarkan berbagai minuman segar di tepi kolam renang. Tamu juga dapat bersantai sambil menikmati minuman di Water Hole Lounge Bar.</p><p>Dengan fasilitas resort yang lengkap, lokasi strategis dekat bandara, serta berbagai pilihan rekreasi dan kuliner, Novotel Manado Golf Resort &amp; Convention Center menjadi pilihan ideal bagi tamu yang ingin menikmati pengalaman menginap yang nyaman dan berkelas di Manado.&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Novotel Manado Golf Resort &amp; Convention Center</strong> is a 4-star hotel that offers a comfortable stay with a peaceful resort atmosphere, making it an excellent choice for both leisure travelers and business guests. Conveniently located, the hotel is only about <strong>15 minutes’ drive from Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, providing easy access for travelers arriving by air.</p><p>The hotel features a range of premium facilities designed to enhance guests’ experience. Visitors can enjoy relaxing <strong>spa treatments</strong> and access to the <strong>golf course</strong>, which is one of the resort’s main attractions. Additional amenities include an <strong>outdoor swimming pool</strong>, <strong>free wired internet access</strong>, and <strong>24-hour room service</strong>, ensuring a pleasant and convenient stay.</p><p>The rooms are designed with a <strong>modern, spacious, and comfortable concept</strong>. Each room is equipped with <strong>air conditioning, a flat-screen TV, a minibar, and a personal safe</strong>. For guests seeking extra space and comfort, the suites feature a <strong>separate living room and a small kitchenette</strong>. All rooms also include a private bathroom fitted with <strong>a shower or bathtub along with complete bathroom amenities</strong>.</p><p>The hotel’s location also provides easy access to several attractions around Manado. The popular shopping and entertainment area around <strong>Manado Town Square</strong> and <strong>Mega Mall Manado</strong> along Boulevard can be reached in about <strong>30 minutes by car</strong>. Meanwhile, <strong>Manado Bay</strong>, where boats depart for <strong>Bunaken Island</strong>, is approximately <strong>35 minutes away</strong>. Nature lovers can also visit <strong>Lake Tondano</strong>, which is about <strong>1 hour and 30 minutes’ drive</strong> from the hotel.</p><p>Free WiFi is available in the hotel’s public areas. Guests can also arrange <strong>day trips and car rentals</strong> through the tour desk. After a workout at the fitness center, guests can relax and unwind in the <strong>sauna or hot tub</strong>.</p><p>For dining experiences, <strong>The Square Restaurant</strong> features an <strong>interactive open-kitchen concept</strong>, offering a variety of international buffet dishes. Other dining options include <strong>Wasabi Japanese Restaurant</strong>, which serves authentic Japanese cuisine, and <strong>H2O Pool Bar</strong>, where guests can enjoy refreshing drinks by the pool. Guests can also relax with beverages at the <strong>Water Hole Lounge Bar</strong>.</p><p>With its <strong>complete resort facilities, convenient location near the airport, and various recreational and dining options</strong>, Novotel Manado Golf Resort &amp; Convention Center is an ideal choice for travelers looking to enjoy a comfortable and upscale stay in Manado. ✨</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Novotel Manado Golf Resort &amp; Convention Center는 편안한 숙박과 평온한 리조트 분위기를 제공하는 4성급 호텔로, 관광객과 비즈니스 여행객 모두에게 적합합니다. 전략적인 위치에 자리한 이 호텔은 사무 라툴랑이 국제공항에서 차로 약 15분 거리에 있어 항공으로 도착하는 고객들에게 매우 편리합니다.</p><p>호텔은 다양한 프리미엄 시설을 갖추고 있어 쾌적한 숙박 경험을 제공합니다. 투숙객은 편안한 스파 트리트먼트를 즐길 수 있으며, 호텔의 주요 매력인 골프 코스를 이용할 수 있습니다. 또한 야외 수영장, 무료 유선 인터넷, 24시간 룸서비스도 제공됩니다.</p><p>객실은 현대적인 디자인으로 넓고 편안하게 설계되어 있으며, 에어컨, 평면 TV, 미니바, 개인 금고가 갖추어져 있습니다. 스위트 객실의 경우 별도의 거실과 간이 주방(키친넷)이 마련되어 있어 더욱 넉넉한 공간과 편안함을 제공합니다. 각 객실의 욕실에는 샤워 시설 또는 욕조와 함께 다양한 욕실용품이 구비되어 있습니다.</p><p>호텔의 위치는 마나도 주변 관광지로의 접근도 용이하게 합니다. 마나도 타운 스퀘어 및 메가 몰 마나도(불르바르 지역)는 차량으로 약 30분 거리에 있으며, 다양한 쇼핑, 레스토랑, 엔터테인먼트를 즐길 수 있습니다. 또한 부나켄 섬으로 향하는 배가 출발하는 마나도 만은 약 35분 거리에 있습니다. 자연을 사랑하는 여행객이라면 호텔에서 약 1시간 30분 거리에 있는 톤다노 호수도 방문할 수 있습니다.</p><p>호텔 공용 구역에서는 무료 Wi-Fi가 제공됩니다. 투숙객은 투어 데스크를 통해 일일 관광 일정이나 차량 렌탈을 예약할 수 있습니다. 피트니스 센터에서 운동을 한 후에는 사우나 또는 온수 욕조에서 휴식을 취할 수 있습니다.</p><p>미식 경험을 위해 The Square 레스토랑에서는 인터랙티브 오픈 키친 콘셉트로 다양한 세계 요리를 뷔페 형식으로 제공합니다. 또한 Wasabi Japanese Restaurant에서는 정통 일본 요리를 즐길 수 있으며, H2O Pool Bar에서는 수영장 옆에서 다양한 음료를 즐길 수 있습니다. Water Hole Lounge Bar에서는 편안한 분위기에서 음료와 함께 휴식을 취할 수 있습니다.</p><p>완벽한 리조트 시설, 공항과 가까운 편리한 위치, 다양한 레저 및 미식 옵션을 갖춘 Novotel Manado Golf Resort &amp; Convention Center는 마나도에서 편안하고 품격 있는 숙박을 원하는 고객에게 이상적인 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>Novotel Manado Golf Resort &amp; Convention Center 是一家四星级酒店，提供舒适的住宿体验与宁静的度假氛围，非常适合休闲旅游及商务出行。酒店地理位置优越，距离萨姆·拉图兰吉国际机场仅约15分钟车程，方便乘飞机抵达的宾客。</p><p>酒店配备多种高端设施，为宾客带来愉悦的入住体验。客人可以享受放松身心的水疗护理，同时酒店还设有高尔夫球场，是其主要特色之一。此外，酒店还提供室外游泳池、免费有线网络以及24小时客房服务。</p><p>客房设计现代、宽敞且舒适，配备空调、平板电视、迷你吧以及私人保险箱。套房类型还设有独立客厅和小厨房（简易厨房），为追求更高舒适度的宾客提供更多空间。每间客房均配有带淋浴或浴缸的私人浴室，以及齐全的洗浴用品。</p><p>酒店地理位置便利，方便宾客前往万鸦老的各大景点。位于 Boulevard 区域的 Manado Town Square 和 Mega Mall Manado 距离酒店约30分钟车程，提供丰富的购物、餐饮和娱乐选择。万鸦老湾（Manado Bay）作为前往布纳肯岛的出发点，距离酒店约35分钟车程。对于热爱自然的游客，通往托纳诺湖（Lake Tondano）约需1小时30分钟车程。</p><p>酒店公共区域提供免费 Wi-Fi。宾客还可通过旅游服务台安排一日游或租车服务。在健身中心锻炼后，客人还可以在酒店的桑拿或热水浴池中放松身心。</p><p>在餐饮方面，The Square 餐厅采用互动式开放厨房理念，以自助餐形式提供多种国际美食。Wasabi Japanese Restaurant 提供正宗日本料理，而 H2O Pool Bar 则在泳池边供应各类清爽饮品。Water Hole Lounge Bar 是放松小憩、享用饮品的理想场所。</p><p>凭借完善的度假设施、靠近机场的优越位置以及丰富的休闲与餐饮选择，Novotel Manado Golf Resort &amp; Convention Center 是在万鸦老享受舒适且高品质住宿体验的理想之选</p>', '[\"Kolam renang outdoor\",\"Antar-jemput bandara\",\"Pusat kebugaran\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Spa & pusat kesehatan\",\"Pembuat teh\\/kopi di semua kamar\",\"Bar\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/aVRScg4iTaOmvH7lQTyHVy4mAnrtvSJXUVamLLKS.jpg', '2026-04-10 05:21:10', '2026-04-20 08:53:01'),
(22, 'Grand Whiz Manado', 'grand-whiz-manado', 'Megamas Area', 'city_hotel', 4, '<p>Terletak di kawasan <strong>Megamas yang dinamis di kota Manado</strong>, <strong>Grand Whiz Megamas Manado</strong> menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang nyaman dan modern, sangat cocok untuk perjalanan bisnis maupun liburan. Hotel bintang 4 ini berada hanya <strong>3 menit berjalan kaki dari Megamas Beach</strong>, kawasan tepi laut yang populer dengan pemandangan laut yang indah, berbagai restoran, kafe, serta tempat hiburan yang membuat suasana Manado terasa hidup dan menyenangkan.</p><p>Hotel ini memadukan desain modern dengan pelayanan yang hangat untuk memastikan setiap tamu mendapatkan pengalaman menginap yang menyenangkan. Berbagai fasilitas tersedia untuk menunjang kenyamanan tamu, seperti <strong>resepsionis 24 jam</strong>, <strong>layanan concierge</strong>, <strong>transfer bandara</strong>, <strong>layanan kamar</strong>, serta <strong>WiFi gratis di seluruh area hotel</strong>.</p><p>Untuk urusan kuliner, restoran di hotel menyajikan beragam hidangan lezat mulai dari <strong>masakan Indonesia, hidangan khas lokal Manado, hingga menu Asia</strong>, yang disiapkan dengan cita rasa autentik sehingga memberikan pengalaman bersantap yang memuaskan bagi para tamu.</p><p>Lokasi hotel yang strategis juga memudahkan tamu untuk menjelajahi berbagai destinasi menarik di sekitar kota. <strong>Manado Harbor</strong> dapat dicapai dalam jarak sekitar <strong>1,8 km</strong>, sementara ikon kota <strong>Soekarno Bridge</strong> berada sekitar <strong>2,1 km</strong> dari hotel dan menawarkan pemandangan kota serta laut yang indah. Bagi pecinta wisata alam dan petualangan, <strong>Mount Lokon</strong> yang terkenal berada sekitar <strong>25 km</strong> dari hotel.</p><p>Bagi tamu yang datang melalui jalur udara, hotel ini berjarak sekitar <strong>18 km dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, atau sekitar <strong>30 menit perjalanan dengan kendaraan</strong>, sehingga memudahkan akses menuju dan dari bandara.</p><p>Dengan <strong>lokasi yang sangat strategis, fasilitas modern, serta suasana yang nyaman</strong>, Grand Whiz Megamas Manado menjadi pilihan ideal bagi wisatawan yang ingin menikmati pengalaman menginap yang menyenangkan di pusat kota Manado, dekat dengan pantai, pusat kuliner, dan berbagai tempat hiburan.</p>', '<p>Strategically located in the vibrant <strong>Megamas district of Manado</strong>, <strong>Grand Whiz Megamas Manado</strong> offers a stylish and comfortable stay, perfect for both business and leisure travelers. This 4-star hotel is just a <strong>3-minute walk from Megamas Beach</strong>, a lively waterfront area known for its beautiful sea views, restaurants, cafés, and entertainment spots, making it an ideal place to relax and enjoy Manado’s coastal atmosphere.</p><p>The hotel combines modern design with warm hospitality to ensure a pleasant and convenient stay. Guests can enjoy a range of services and facilities, including a <strong>24-hour front desk</strong>, <strong>concierge service</strong>, <strong>airport transfer</strong>, <strong>room service</strong>, and <strong>complimentary WiFi throughout the property</strong>. Its comfortable environment and attentive service make it a great base for exploring the city.</p><p>At the hotel’s restaurant, guests can indulge in a variety of delicious cuisines, featuring <strong>Indonesian, local Manadonese, and Asian dishes</strong>, carefully prepared to deliver authentic flavors and satisfying dining experiences.</p><p>Thanks to its prime location, the hotel provides easy access to several well-known attractions in the area. <strong>Manado Harbor</strong> is located about <strong>1.8 km</strong> from the hotel, while the iconic <strong>Soekarno Bridge</strong> is approximately <strong>2.1 km away</strong>, offering scenic views of the city and coastline. For nature lovers, the famous <strong>Mount Lokon</strong> is about <strong>25 km</strong> from the hotel and is a popular destination for hiking and adventure.</p><p>For travelers arriving by air, the hotel is conveniently located about <strong>18 km from Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, which can typically be reached in <strong>around 30 minutes by car</strong>, depending on traffic.</p><p>With its <strong>excellent location, modern comfort, and easy access to Manado’s main attractions</strong>, Grand Whiz Megamas Manado is a wonderful choice for guests seeking a relaxing stay in the heart of the city while staying close to the beach, dining spots, and entertainment areas. ✨</p>', '<p>마나도의 활기찬 메가마스 지역에 위치한 Grand Whiz Megamas Manado는 편안하고 현대적인 숙박 경험을 제공하며, 비즈니스 여행과 휴가 모두에 이상적인 선택입니다. 이 4성급 호텔은 아름다운 바다 전망과 다양한 레스토랑, 카페, 엔터테인먼트 시설로 유명한 메가마스 해변에서 도보로 단 3분 거리에 위치해 있어, 마나도의 활기차고 즐거운 분위기를 만끽할 수 있습니다.</p><p>호텔은 현대적인 디자인과 따뜻한 서비스를 조화롭게 결합하여 모든 투숙객이 편안한 숙박을 즐길 수 있도록 합니다. 또한 24시간 프런트 데스크, 컨시어지 서비스, 공항 셔틀, 룸서비스, 전 구역 무료 Wi-Fi 등 다양한 편의시설을 제공합니다.</p><p>호텔 내 레스토랑에서는 인도네시아 요리, 마나도 지역 특선 요리, 아시아 요리 등 다양한 메뉴를 선보이며, 정통의 맛으로 고객에게 만족스러운 미식 경험을 제공합니다.</p><p>호텔의 전략적인 위치 덕분에 주변 관광지로의 이동도 매우 편리합니다. 마나도 항구는 약 1.8km 거리에 있으며, 도시의 랜드마크인 소에카르노 다리는 약 2.1km 떨어져 있어 아름다운 도시와 바다 전망을 감상할 수 있습니다. 또한 자연과 모험을 즐기는 여행객에게 인기 있는 로콘 산은 호텔에서 약 25km 거리에 위치해 있습니다.</p><p>항공편으로 방문하는 투숙객의 경우, 호텔은 사무 라툴랑이 국제공항에서 약 18km(차량으로 약 30분 거리)에 위치해 있어 접근성이 뛰어납니다.</p><p>전략적인 위치, 현대적인 시설, 그리고 편안한 분위기를 갖춘 Grand Whiz Megamas Manado는 마나도 중심에서 해변, 미식, 그리고 다양한 엔터테인먼트를 가까이에서 즐기고자 하는 여행객에게 이상적인 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>Grand Whiz Megamas Manado 位于万鸦老市充满活力的 Megamas 区域，为宾客提供舒适而现代的住宿体验，非常适合商务出行和休闲度假。这家四星级酒店距离风景优美、拥有众多餐厅、咖啡馆及娱乐场所的 Megamas 海滩仅需步行约3分钟，让您轻松感受万鸦老充满活力与魅力的氛围。</p><p>酒店将现代设计与热情服务相结合，确保每位宾客都能享受到愉快的入住体验。酒店提供多种设施与服务，包括24小时前台、礼宾服务、机场接送、客房服务以及覆盖全酒店的免费Wi-Fi。</p><p>在餐饮方面，酒店内餐厅提供丰富多样的美食选择，包括印尼菜、万鸦老特色美食以及亚洲料理，均以地道风味精心烹制，为宾客带来令人满意的用餐体验。</p><p>酒店地理位置优越，方便宾客探索周边景点。万鸦老港口距离酒店约1.8公里，而城市地标索加诺大桥距离约2.1公里，可欣赏迷人的城市与海景。对于喜爱自然与探险的游客来说，著名的洛孔山距离酒店约25公里。</p><p>对于乘飞机抵达的宾客，酒店距离萨姆·拉图兰吉国际机场约18公里，车程约30分钟，交通十分便利。</p><p>凭借优越的地理位置、现代化设施以及舒适的环境，Grand Whiz Megamas Manado 是希望在万鸦老市中心享受愉快住宿体验、靠近海滩、美食和娱乐设施的理想之选</p>', '[\"WiFi gratis\",\"Antar-jemput bandara\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Parkir di lokasi\",\"Restoran\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/oyBWxQJJ5G63fSbEv1tiee7LempeXMWK5gmdgOCB.jpg', '2026-04-10 05:21:10', '2026-04-20 08:47:46'),
(23, 'Gran Puri Hotel Manado', 'gran-puri-hotel', 'Manado', 'city_hotel', 4, '<p>Terletak strategis di pusat kota Manado, Hotel Gran Puri Manado menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang nyaman dengan sentuhan elegan, cocok untuk perjalanan bisnis maupun liburan. Hotel ini hanya berjarak sekitar 2,4 km dari Megamas Beach, kawasan populer yang terkenal dengan pemandangan laut, pusat kuliner, dan tempat bersantai di tepi pantai.</p><p>Hotel ini menghadirkan berbagai fasilitas untuk menunjang kenyamanan tamu, termasuk kolam renang outdoor yang menyegarkan, area parkir pribadi gratis, serta bar yang nyaman untuk menikmati minuman setelah beraktivitas seharian. Dengan layanan resepsionis 24 jam, fasilitas ATM, restoran di dalam hotel, layanan kamar, serta WiFi gratis di seluruh area, setiap kebutuhan Anda selama menginap dapat terpenuhi dengan mudah.</p><p>Setiap kamar dirancang untuk memberikan kenyamanan maksimal. Kamar dilengkapi dengan AC, TV layar datar dengan saluran kabel, kulkas, ketel listrik, serta meja kerja yang cocok bagi tamu yang sedang dalam perjalanan bisnis. Kamar mandi pribadi tersedia di setiap unit, dilengkapi bathtub, perlengkapan mandi gratis, pengering rambut, dan handuk bersih untuk menambah kenyamanan selama menginap.</p><p>Lokasi hotel juga sangat strategis untuk menjelajahi berbagai destinasi di Manado. Manado Harbor dapat dicapai dalam jarak sekitar 5,3 km, sementara Mount Lokon yang terkenal berada sekitar 22 km dari hotel, cocok bagi wisatawan yang ingin menikmati wisata alam dan petualangan.</p><p>Bagi tamu yang datang melalui jalur udara, hotel ini berjarak sekitar <strong>20 km atau sekitar 30–35 menit perjalanan</strong> dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport, bandara utama yang melayani penerbangan domestik dan internasional ke Manado.</p><p>Dengan lokasi strategis, fasilitas lengkap, dan suasana yang nyaman, Hotel Gran Puri Manado menjadi pilihan ideal bagi Anda yang ingin menikmati pengalaman menginap yang menyenangkan di kota Manado.</p>', '<p>Strategically located in the heart of Manado, <strong>Hotel Gran Puri Manado</strong> offers a comfortable stay with a touch of elegance, making it an excellent choice for both business and leisure travelers. The hotel is situated just about 2.4 km from <strong>Megamas Beach</strong>, a popular waterfront area known for its beautiful sea views, lively dining spots, and relaxing seaside atmosphere.</p><p>The hotel provides a range of facilities designed to enhance guests’ comfort, including a refreshing outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, and a cozy bar where guests can unwind after a busy day. With a 24-hour front desk, ATM facilities, an on-site restaurant, room service, and complimentary WiFi available throughout the property, every need during your stay is well taken care of.</p><p>Each room is thoughtfully designed to ensure maximum comfort. Rooms are equipped with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with cable channels, a refrigerator, an electric kettle, and a work desk—ideal for guests traveling for business. Every unit also features a private bathroom complete with a bathtub, complimentary toiletries, a hairdryer, and fresh towels to make your stay even more relaxing.</p><p>The hotel’s location also makes it easy to explore many of Manado’s attractions. <strong>Manado Harbor</strong> is approximately 5.3 km away, while the well-known <strong>Mount Lokon</strong> is located about 22 km from the property, perfect for travelers interested in nature and adventure.</p><p>For guests arriving by air, the hotel is located around <strong>20 km (approximately 30–35 minutes by car)</strong> from <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, the main airport serving both domestic and international flights to Manado.</p><p>With its strategic location, complete facilities, and welcoming atmosphere, <strong>Hotel Gran Puri Manado</strong> is an ideal choice for travelers looking to enjoy a pleasant and convenient stay in the vibrant city of Manado. ✨</p>', '<p>마나도 중심부에 전략적으로 위치한 <strong>Hotel Gran Puri Manado</strong>는 우아한 분위기와 함께 편안한 숙박 경험을 제공하며, 비즈니스 여행과 휴가 모두에 적합합니다. 이 호텔은 바다 전망과 다양한 먹거리, 해변에서의 휴식을 즐길 수 있는 인기 지역인 Megamas Beach에서 약 2.4km 거리에 있습니다.</p><p>호텔은 야외 수영장, 무료 전용 주차장, 하루 일과 후 휴식을 취할 수 있는 아늑한 바 등 다양한 편의시설을 제공합니다. 또한 24시간 프런트 데스크, ATM 시설, 호텔 내 레스토랑, 룸서비스, 전 구역 무료 Wi-Fi를 갖추고 있어 투숙객의 모든 요구를 편리하게 충족시켜 줍니다.</p><p>각 객실은 최대한의 편안함을 위해 설계되었으며, 에어컨, 케이블 채널이 제공되는 평면 TV, 냉장고, 전기 주전자, 업무용 책상이 구비되어 있어 비즈니스 여행객에게도 적합합니다. 모든 객실에는 욕조, 무료 세면도구, 헤어드라이어, 깨끗한 수건이 제공되는 전용 욕실이 마련되어 있습니다.</p><p>호텔의 위치는 마나도의 다양한 관광지를 탐험하기에도 매우 편리합니다. Manado Harbor는 약 5.3km 거리에 있으며, 유명한 Mount Lokon은 약 22km 거리에 있어 자연과 모험을 즐기기에 좋습니다.</p><p>항공편으로 도착하는 투숙객의 경우, 호텔은 Sam Ratulangi International Airport에서 약 20km, 차량으로 약 30~35분 거리에 위치해 있습니다.</p><p>전략적인 위치와 완벽한 시설, 그리고 편안한 분위기를 갖춘 Hotel Gran Puri Manado는 마나도에서 즐거운 숙박 경험을 원하는 분들에게 이상적인 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>位于万鸦老市中心的 <strong>Hotel Gran Puri Manado</strong> 地理位置优越，提供舒适且优雅的住宿体验，非常适合商务出行和休闲度假。酒店距离著名的 Megamas Beach 约 2.4 公里，该地区以海景、美食中心以及海边休闲场所而闻名。</p><p>酒店提供多种设施以提升住客的舒适度，包括清爽的室外游泳池、免费私人停车场，以及一个舒适的酒吧，方便客人在忙碌一天后放松身心。此外，酒店还设有24小时前台服务、ATM设施、内部餐厅、客房服务以及覆盖全区域的免费Wi-Fi，确保您的需求都能得到满足。</p><p>每间客房均精心设计，以提供最大的舒适度。客房配备空调、带有有线频道的平板电视、冰箱、电热水壶以及办公桌，非常适合商务旅客。每间客房还设有私人浴室，配有浴缸、免费洗浴用品、吹风机以及干净的毛巾。</p><p>酒店地理位置优越，方便客人探索万鸦老的各大景点。Manado Harbor 距离酒店约 5.3 公里，而著名的 Mount Lokon 距离约 22 公里，非常适合喜爱自然风光与探险的游客。</p><p>对于乘坐飞机抵达的旅客，酒店距离 Sam Ratulangi International Airport 约 20 公里，车程约 30–35 分钟，是通往万鸦老的主要国内及国际机场。</p><p>凭借其优越的地理位置、完善的设施以及舒适的环境，Hotel Gran Puri Manado 是您在万鸦老享受愉快住宿体验的理想选择。</p>', '[\"Kolam renang outdoor\",\"WiFi gratis\",\"Antar-jemput bandara\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Spa & pusat kesehatan\",\"Restoran\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Bar\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/LvEjxV06c6IOayULElCWFErVZnJOr2Fu8cgF3RN3.jpg', '2026-04-10 05:21:10', '2026-04-21 02:55:08'),
(24, 'Lion Hotel & Plaza Manado', 'lion-hotel-plaza', 'Manado', 'city_hotel', 4, '<p><strong>Lion Hotel &amp; Plaza Manado</strong> menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang nyaman dan bergaya di pusat kota Manado. Hotel ini dilengkapi dengan kolam renang outdoor, pusat kebugaran yang lengkap, taman yang menenangkan, serta area lounge bersama untuk bersantai. Lokasinya hanya sekitar 17 menit berjalan kaki dari Pantai Megamas, dan hotel juga memiliki bar yang nyaman untuk menikmati berbagai minuman segar.</p><p>Dirancang untuk wisatawan maupun pelaku bisnis, hotel ini menyediakan layanan resepsionis 24 jam, layanan antar-jemput bandara, layanan kamar, serta WiFi gratis yang tersedia di seluruh area hotel.</p><p>Setiap kamar di Lion Hotel &amp; Plaza Manado dirancang dengan memperhatikan kenyamanan dan kemudahan. Kamar dilengkapi dengan AC, area tempat duduk, TV layar datar dengan saluran satelit, brankas, serta kamar mandi pribadi yang dilengkapi shower, perlengkapan mandi gratis, dan sandal. Setiap kamar juga menyediakan ketel listrik, sementara beberapa kamar tertentu memiliki balkon pribadi atau pemandangan kota yang indah. Seprai dan handuk bersih juga disediakan di semua kamar.</p><p>Setiap pagi, tamu dapat menikmati sarapan prasmanan yang lezat di hotel. Restoran di dalam hotel menyajikan berbagai hidangan Indonesia, Asia, dan Eropa, dengan pilihan menu vegetarian dan halal yang tersedia berdasarkan permintaan.</p><p>Hotel ini juga memiliki lokasi yang strategis, hanya sekitar 3,9 km dari Pelabuhan Manado dan 24 km dari Gunung Lokon, sehingga menjadi tempat yang ideal sebagai titik awal untuk menjelajahi berbagai destinasi menarik di Manado.</p>', '<p><strong>Lion Hotel &amp; Plaza Manado</strong> offers a comfortable and stylish stay in the heart of Manado, featuring an outdoor swimming pool, a fully equipped fitness center, a relaxing garden, and a shared lounge for guests to unwind. Located just a <strong>17-minute walk from Megamas Beach</strong>, the hotel also features a welcoming bar for guests to enjoy refreshing drinks.</p><p>Designed for both leisure and business travelers, the property provides a <strong>24-hour front desk</strong>, <strong>airport transfer service</strong>, <strong>room service</strong>, and <strong>complimentary WiFi throughout the hotel</strong>.</p><p>Each room at Lion Hotel &amp; Plaza Manado is thoughtfully designed for comfort and convenience. Rooms are equipped with <strong>air conditioning</strong>, a <strong>seating area</strong>, a <strong>flat-screen TV with satellite channels</strong>, a <strong>safety deposit box</strong>, and a <strong>private bathroom</strong> complete with a shower, complimentary toiletries, and slippers. Guests will also find an <strong>electric kettle</strong> in every room, while selected rooms feature a <strong>private balcony</strong> or <strong>beautiful city views</strong>. Fresh <strong>bed linen and towels</strong> are provided in all rooms.</p><p>Every morning, guests can enjoy a <strong>delicious buffet breakfast</strong> at the hotel. The on-site restaurant serves a variety of <strong>Indonesian, Asian, and European cuisines</strong>, with <strong>vegetarian and halal options available upon request</strong>.</p><p>The hotel is conveniently located <strong>3.9 km from Manado Harbor</strong> and <strong>24 km from Mount Lokon</strong>, making it a great base for exploring the attractions of Manado.</p>', '<p>Lion Hotel &amp; Plaza Manado는 마나도 중심부에 위치한 편안하고 세련된 숙박 경험을 제공합니다. 호텔에는 야외 수영장, 완비된 피트니스 센터, 편안한 정원, 그리고 휴식을 위한 공용 라운지 공간이 마련되어 있습니다. 또한 메가마스 해변까지 도보로 약 17분 거리에 있으며, 다양한 음료를 즐길 수 있는 아늑한 바도 운영하고 있습니다.</p><p>이 호텔은 관광객과 비즈니스 여행객 모두를 위해 설계되었으며, 24시간 프런트 데스크, 공항 셔틀 서비스, 룸서비스, 전 구역 무료 Wi-Fi를 제공합니다.</p><p>각 객실은 편안함과 편의성을 고려하여 설계되었으며, 에어컨, 휴식 공간, 위성 채널이 제공되는 평면 TV, 금고, 샤워 시설, 무료 세면도구 및 슬리퍼가 구비된 전용 욕실이 포함되어 있습니다. 모든 객실에는 전기 주전자가 제공되며, 일부 객실에는 전용 발코니 또는 아름다운 도시 전망이 있습니다. 깨끗한 침대 린넨과 수건도 제공됩니다.</p><p>매일 아침 호텔에서는 맛있는 뷔페식 조식을 즐길 수 있습니다. 호텔 내 레스토랑에서는 인도네시아, 아시아, 유럽 요리를 제공하며, 요청 시 채식 및 할랄 메뉴도 준비됩니다.</p><p>호텔은 전략적인 위치에 자리 잡고 있어 마나도 항구까지 약 3.9km, 로콘 산까지 약 24km 거리에 위치해 있으며, 마나도의 다양한 관광지를 탐험하기에 이상적인 출발점입니다.</p>', '<p>Lion Hotel &amp; Plaza Manado 位于万鸦老市中心，为客人提供舒适且时尚的住宿体验。酒店配备室外游泳池、设备齐全的健身中心、宁静的花园以及公共休息区，供客人放松身心。酒店距离 Megamas 海滩步行约17分钟，同时还设有舒适的酒吧，可享用各种清爽饮品。</p><p>酒店专为游客和商务人士设计，提供24小时前台服务、机场接送服务、客房服务以及覆盖全酒店的免费Wi-Fi。</p><p>每间客房都以舒适和便利为设计重点，配备空调、休息区、带卫星频道的平板电视、保险箱以及带淋浴、免费洗浴用品和拖鞋的私人浴室。所有客房均配有电热水壶，部分客房还设有私人阳台或可欣赏美丽的城市景观。酒店为所有客人提供干净的床单和毛巾。</p><p>每天早晨，客人可以在酒店享用美味的自助早餐。酒店内的餐厅提供印尼、亚洲及欧洲美食，并可根据需求提供素食和清真餐点。</p><p>酒店地理位置优越，距离万鸦老港约3.9公里，距离洛孔山约24公里，是探索万鸦老各大景点的理想出发点</p>', '[\"Kolam renang outdoor\",\"WiFi gratis\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Spa & pusat kesehatan\",\"Restoran\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Bar\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/eNkpVimpY0ei3Q1aegcw4Fl8toeOQfxE7Lt2J0o8.jpg', '2026-04-10 05:21:10', '2026-04-20 08:44:48'),
(26, 'Luwansa Hotel & Convention Center Manado', 'luwansa-hotel', 'Manado', 'city_hotel', 4, 'A massive hub of luxury, Luwansa Hotel & Convention Center Manado has it all for premium events and luxurious high-altitude stays.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1629140727571-9b5c6f6267b4?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop', '2026-04-10 05:21:10', '2026-04-10 05:21:10');
INSERT INTO `hotels` (`id`, `name`, `slug`, `location`, `category`, `stars`, `description`, `description_en`, `description_ko`, `description_zh`, `facilities`, `primary_image`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(27, 'Siladen Resort & Spa', 'siladen-resort', 'Siladen Island', 'resort', 4, '<p>Terletak di pulau tropis yang indah di kawasan <strong>Bunaken National Park</strong>, <strong>Siladen Resort &amp; Spa</strong> menawarkan pengalaman menginap eksklusif yang memadukan kemewahan, ketenangan, dan keindahan alam bawah laut yang luar biasa. Resort ini berada di <strong>Siladen Island</strong>, sebuah pulau kecil yang terkenal dengan pantai pasir putih dan perairan jernih yang kaya akan kehidupan laut.</p><p>Resort ini memiliki <strong>kolam renang yang unik, termasuk kolam air asin</strong>, yang memberikan pengalaman berenang yang berbeda. Para tamu juga dapat menikmati <strong>pantai pribadi eksklusif</strong>, tempat yang sempurna untuk bersantai sambil menikmati panorama laut tropis. Bagi pecinta aktivitas laut, resort ini menawarkan berbagai kegiatan menarik seperti <strong>snorkeling dan diving</strong>, yang memungkinkan Anda menjelajahi keindahan terumbu karang dan beragam biota laut yang menjadi ciri khas Bunaken.</p><p>Untuk relaksasi, tamu dapat memanjakan diri di <strong>spa dan ruang pijat</strong>, tempat yang ideal untuk menyegarkan tubuh dan pikiran setelah seharian beraktivitas. Bagi yang menyukai olahraga, resort juga menyediakan <strong>peralatan olahraga air dan fasilitas memancing</strong>, memberikan pengalaman liburan yang aktif sekaligus menyenangkan.</p><p>Dalam hal kuliner, restoran resort menyajikan berbagai pilihan hidangan lezat yang dapat dinikmati sepanjang hari. Tamu juga dapat menikmati <strong>layanan kamar</strong> jika ingin bersantap dengan suasana lebih privat di villa mereka. Saat matahari terbenam, bar resort menjadi tempat sempurna untuk bersantai sambil menikmati minuman favorit.</p><p>Fasilitas tambahan seperti <strong>area barbekyu, taman tropis yang indah, layanan penukaran mata uang, penitipan bagasi, serta layanan laundry</strong> juga tersedia untuk memastikan kenyamanan tamu selama menginap. Staf resepsionis yang ramah dan profesional bahkan dapat berkomunikasi dalam <strong>hingga 8 bahasa</strong>, termasuk Bahasa Indonesia, sehingga memberikan pelayanan yang hangat bagi tamu dari berbagai negara.</p><p>Dengan lokasi yang luar biasa di jantung Bunaken, pemandangan laut yang menakjubkan, serta fasilitas kelas dunia, Siladen Resort &amp; Spa adalah pilihan sempurna bagi wisatawan yang ingin merasakan <strong>liburan tropis yang mewah dan tak terlupakan di Sulawesi Utara</strong>.</p>', '<p>Located on a stunning tropical island within <strong>Bunaken National Park</strong>, <strong>Siladen Resort &amp; Spa</strong> offers an exclusive retreat that blends luxury, tranquility, and breathtaking marine biodiversity. The resort is situated on <strong>Siladen Island</strong>, a beautiful island known for its white sandy beaches and crystal-clear waters.</p><p>The resort features a <strong>unique swimming pool, including a saltwater pool</strong>, providing guests with a refreshing and distinctive swimming experience. Guests can also relax on the resort’s <strong>private beach</strong>, the perfect place to unwind while enjoying panoramic views of the tropical sea.</p><p>For ocean lovers, Siladen Resort &amp; Spa offers a wide range of activities such as <strong>snorkeling and diving</strong>, allowing guests to explore the vibrant coral reefs and extraordinary marine life that make Bunaken famous worldwide.</p><p>To rejuvenate the body and mind, guests can indulge in the resort’s <strong>spa and massage facilities</strong>, ideal for relaxation after a day of adventure. For more active guests, the resort also provides <strong>water sports equipment and fishing activities</strong>.</p><p>Dining at the resort is equally delightful. The on-site restaurant offers a variety of delicious dishes throughout the day. Guests may also enjoy meals in the comfort of their villa through <strong>in-room dining service</strong>. In the evening, the resort’s <strong>bar</strong> is the perfect place to unwind with a refreshing drink while enjoying the tropical atmosphere.</p><p>Additional facilities include <strong>barbecue areas, a tropical garden, currency exchange services, luggage storage, and laundry services</strong>. The friendly reception staff speak <strong>up to eight languages</strong>, including Indonesian, ensuring warm and attentive service for international guests.</p><p>With its spectacular location in the heart of Bunaken, pristine beaches, and world-class facilities, Siladen Resort &amp; Spa is the perfect destination for travelers seeking a <strong>luxurious and unforgettable tropical escape in North Sulawesi</strong>.</p>', '<p><strong>Siladen Resort &amp; Spa</strong>는 아름다운 열대 섬 **Siladen Island**에 위치한 럭셔리 리조트로, **Bunaken National Park**의 환상적인 자연환경 속에서 특별한 휴식을 제공합니다. 이곳은 하얀 모래 해변과 맑은 바다로 유명한 지역으로, 세계적인 다이빙 명소로도 잘 알려져 있습니다.</p><p>리조트에는 <strong>소금물 수영장을 포함한 수영장 시설</strong>이 마련되어 있어 색다른 수영 경험을 제공합니다. 또한 투숙객은 리조트의 <strong>전용 해변</strong>에서 여유롭게 휴식을 취하며 아름다운 바다 전망을 즐길 수 있습니다.</p><p>해양 활동을 좋아하는 여행객을 위해 <strong>스노클링과 다이빙 프로그램</strong>이 마련되어 있으며, 이곳에서 다채로운 산호초와 다양한 해양 생물을 가까이에서 만날 수 있습니다.</p><p>하루의 활동 후에는 <strong>스파와 마사지 시설</strong>에서 몸과 마음을 편안하게 회복할 수 있습니다. 또한 리조트에서는 <strong>수상 스포츠 장비와 낚시 활동</strong>도 제공되어 더욱 즐거운 휴가를 보낼 수 있습니다.</p><p>리조트 레스토랑에서는 다양한 요리를 즐길 수 있으며, <strong>룸서비스</strong>를 통해 객실에서도 편안하게 식사를 할 수 있습니다. 저녁에는 <strong>바</strong>에서 좋아하는 음료를 마시며 여유로운 시간을 보내기에 좋습니다.</p><p>이 외에도 <strong>바비큐 시설, 아름다운 정원, 환전 서비스, 수하물 보관, 세탁 서비스</strong> 등이 제공됩니다. 리셉션 직원은 <strong>최대 8개 언어</strong>로 소통이 가능하여 전 세계 여행객에게 편안한 서비스를 제공합니다.</p>', '<p><strong>Siladen Resort &amp; Spa</strong> 位于美丽的 <strong>Siladen Island</strong>，坐落在著名的 <strong>Bunaken National Park</strong> 内，是一处融合奢华、宁静与自然之美的度假胜地。这里拥有洁白的沙滩和清澈的海水，是世界知名的潜水与海洋生态天堂。</p><p>度假村设有 <strong>游泳池，包括独特的海水泳池</strong>，为客人提供清爽而特别的游泳体验。客人还可以在度假村的 <strong>私人海滩</strong> 放松身心，欣赏壮丽的热带海景。</p><p>对于喜欢海洋活动的旅客，度假村提供 <strong>浮潜和潜水</strong> 项目，让客人能够探索色彩斑斓的珊瑚礁以及丰富多样的海洋生物。</p><p>在忙碌的一天结束后，客人可以前往 <strong>Spa 和按摩中心</strong> 放松身心。度假村还提供 <strong>水上运动设备和钓鱼活动</strong>，让旅客享受更加丰富多彩的度假体验。</p><p>度假村内的餐厅提供多种美味佳肴，客人也可以通过 <strong>客房送餐服务</strong> 在私人空间中享用美食。晚上，度假村的 <strong>酒吧</strong> 是放松并享用饮品的理想场所。</p><p>此外，度假村还提供 <strong>烧烤设施、热带花园、货币兑换服务、行李寄存以及洗衣服务</strong>。前台工作人员可使用 <strong>多达8种语言</strong> 为客人提供服务，为来自世界各地的旅客带来贴心而专业的体验。</p><p>凭借绝美的自然环境、一流的设施以及世界级的海洋生态资源，Siladen Resort &amp; Spa 是体验 <strong>北苏拉威西奢华热带度假的理想之选</strong>。</p>', '[\"Restoran\",\"Kolam Renang Outdoor\",\"Area pantai pribadi\",\"Menyelam\",\"Snorkeling\",\"Spa\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/Kv36IFl5lX0kLjnFNSY6MnX93x62bDNErzYCrhTt.webp', '2026-04-10 05:21:10', '2026-04-25 03:15:05'),
(28, 'Yama Resort Tondano', 'yama-resort-tondano', 'Tondano', 'resort', 4, '<p><strong>Yama Resort Indonesia</strong> menghadirkan pengalaman menginap yang tenang dan mewah di kawasan <strong>Tondano, Sulawesi Utara</strong>, dikelilingi pemandangan alam yang indah dan udara pegunungan yang segar.</p><p>Resor bintang 4 ini menawarkan berbagai fasilitas lengkap untuk kenyamanan tamu, termasuk <strong>taman yang luas, lounge bersama, teras santai, bar, serta layanan kamar dan resepsionis 24 jam</strong>. Para tamu juga dapat menikmati <strong>kolam renang outdoor, hot tub, karaoke, klub anak-anak</strong>, serta pengalaman relaksasi khas Jepang di <strong>Onsen (pemandian air panas)</strong> yang menenangkan.</p><p>Setiap kamar dirancang dengan nyaman dan modern, dilengkapi dengan <strong>AC, TV layar datar dengan saluran satelit, ketel listrik, shower, amenitas kamar mandi gratis, lemari pakaian, seprai, dan handuk</strong>.</p><p>Untuk aktivitas santai, tamu dapat bermain <strong>tenis meja</strong> atau menjelajahi area sekitar dengan <strong>layanan rental sepeda</strong> yang tersedia di resort.</p><p>📍 Lokasi Yama Resort juga sangat strategis:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e4129e55a326edc96bf77d81f34e8139c\">Sekitar <strong>34 km dari Manado Port</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e98deefbdf5e481376fc7926d449629da\">Sekitar <strong>14 km dari Gunung Lokon</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb4853fce97565a75eb8a8c6604b531c9\">Sekitar <strong>40 km dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec28ea2ec583394f6adfa43e62f6ca23a\">Sekitar <strong>35 km dari Manado City</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"eac8c1f0de297ec9afad7a8064ab81ded\">Sekitar <strong>15 km dari Tomohon City</strong></li></ul><p>Yama Resort Indonesia adalah pilihan sempurna bagi Anda yang ingin menikmati <strong>ketenangan alam, relaksasi, dan pengalaman menginap yang unik di Sulawesi Utara</strong>.</p>', '<p><strong>Yama Resort Indonesia</strong> offers a peaceful and luxurious stay in <strong>Tondano, North Sulawesi</strong>, surrounded by beautiful natural scenery and refreshing mountain air.</p><p>This <strong>4-star resort</strong> features a variety of facilities designed for comfort and relaxation, including a <strong>lush garden, shared lounge, terrace, bar, 24-hour front desk, and room service</strong>. Guests can also enjoy an <strong>outdoor swimming pool, hot tub, karaoke, kids’ club</strong>, and a unique relaxing experience at the <strong>Onsen (Japanese-style hot spring bath)</strong>.</p><p>Each guest room is thoughtfully designed and equipped with <strong>air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, electric kettle, shower, complimentary toiletries, wardrobe, bed linen, and towels</strong>.</p><p>For leisure activities, guests can play <strong>table tennis</strong> or explore the surrounding area using the <strong>bicycle rental service</strong> available at the resort.</p><p>📍 Yama Resort is conveniently located:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e8249a1ec56747b77d00eca44f46bd23b\">Around <strong>34 km from Manado Port</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee35a4ffbf1388df748800cb7652c4117\">Around <strong>14 km from Mount Lokon</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e64fa4f933c2396fea73b53af5475c39b\">Around <strong>40 km from Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebe75f748d338d96e915668fcddfc4d18\">Around <strong>35 km from Manado City</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecfaa346e6bc890ca0cc647ae601c23be\">Around <strong>15 km from Tomohon City</strong></li></ul><p>Yama Resort Indonesia is the perfect destination for travelers seeking <strong>relaxation, nature, and a unique resort experience in North Sulawesi</strong>.</p>', '<p>**야마 리조트 인도네시아 (Yama Resort Indonesia)**는 북술라웨시 <strong>톤다노(Tondano)</strong> 지역에 위치한 평화롭고 고급스러운 리조트로, 아름다운 자연 경관과 상쾌한 산 공기를 즐길 수 있습니다.</p><p>이 <strong>4성급 리조트</strong>는 편안한 휴식을 위한 다양한 시설을 제공합니다. 넓은 <strong>정원, 공용 라운지, 테라스, 바</strong>, 그리고 <strong>24시간 프런트 데스크와 룸서비스</strong>가 준비되어 있습니다. 또한 <strong>야외 수영장, 온수 욕조, 노래방, 키즈 클럽</strong>을 이용할 수 있으며, 일본식 온천인 **온센(Onsen)**에서 특별한 휴식을 경험하실 수 있습니다.</p><p>모든 객실에는 <strong>에어컨, 위성 채널이 제공되는 평면 TV, 전기 주전자, 샤워 시설, 무료 욕실 어메니티, 옷장, 침구 및 수건</strong>이 마련되어 있습니다.</p><p>리조트에서는 <strong>탁구</strong>를 즐길 수 있으며, 주변 지역을 탐험할 수 있는 <strong>자전거 대여 서비스</strong>도 제공합니다.</p><p>📍 주요 위치 거리:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"effe2ef7f4ef8929275eb1ceb0dc97cee\"><strong>마나도 항구</strong>까지 약 <strong>34km</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebc8359bb259d323a1067e3444622a13c\">**로콘 화산(Mount Lokon)**까지 약 <strong>14km</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2cf66b3c8877a392d374d9f53a4f9973\"><strong>사무 라툴랑이 국제공항</strong>까지 약 <strong>40km</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebfc0639b2bc2dad345698d86196f201d\"><strong>마나도 시내</strong>까지 약 <strong>35km</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e24de70448e1767169c1bf552efc35f60\"><strong>토모혼 시내</strong>까지 약 <strong>15km</strong></li></ul><p>Yama Resort Indonesia는 <strong>자연 속에서의 휴식과 특별한 리조트 경험</strong>을 원하는 여행객들에게 완벽한 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>**Yama Resort Indonesia（雅玛度假酒店）**位于印度尼西亚北苏拉威西 **Tondano（通达诺）**地区，周围环绕着优美的自然风景和清新的山间空气，为客人提供宁静而舒适的度假体验。</p><p>这家 <strong>四星级度假酒店</strong>提供完善的设施，包括 <strong>花园、公共休息室、露台、酒吧、24小时前台服务以及客房服务</strong>。客人还可以享受 <strong>室外游泳池、热水浴池、卡拉OK、儿童俱乐部</strong>，以及放松身心的 **Onsen（日式温泉浴）**体验。</p><p>所有客房均配备 <strong>空调、带卫星频道的平板电视、电热水壶、淋浴、免费洗浴用品、衣柜、床单和毛巾</strong>，为客人提供舒适便利的住宿环境。</p><p>酒店还提供 <strong>乒乓球娱乐设施</strong>，并可租借 <strong>自行车</strong>，方便客人探索周边地区。</p><p>📍 酒店地理位置便利：</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e9e5e3d54643e49aa3b1cb4edbd4c4f31\">距离 <strong>Manado Port（马纳多港口）</strong> 约 <strong>34公里</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e47c661519bdbe0383399c420de96910e\">距离 <strong>Lokon火山（Gunung Lokon）</strong> 约 <strong>14公里</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e503ca71845f5ad4e9f52c995b44161e1\">距离 <strong>Sam Ratulangi国际机场</strong> 约 <strong>40公里</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e63bce84ca58aa586b960eac451099c37\">距离 <strong>Manado市中心</strong> 约 <strong>35公里</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecb2a79465cb1d8fa66f3395716ea4d93\">距离 <strong>Tomohon市中心</strong> 约 <strong>15公里</strong></li></ul><p>Yama Resort Indonesia 是希望在 <strong>北苏拉威西享受自然、放松身心并体验独特度假氛围</strong>旅客的理想选择。</p>', '[\"Kolam renang outdoor\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Restoran\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Bar\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/GEMM5XIs0hnmoxwG1gJ7OsHFXQKv7Bzjg53P82RX.jpg', '2026-04-10 05:21:10', '2026-04-21 06:36:20'),
(29, 'Grand Master Villa Tomohon', 'grand-master-tomohon', 'Tomohon', 'resort', 3, '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Grand Master Villa Tomohon adalah akomodasi nyaman yang terletak di kota Tomohon, dikelilingi oleh udara pegunungan yang sejuk dan pemandangan alam yang indah. Villa ini menawarkan suasana damai dan fasilitas yang nyaman, menjadikannya ideal untuk liburan keluarga, pasangan, atau perjalanan bersama teman. Dengan lokasinya yang strategis, para tamu dapat dengan mudah menjelajahi berbagai objek wisata alam dan tempat kuliner lokal di Tomohon.<br><br>Grand Master Villa Tomohon adalah akomodasi nyaman yang terletak di kota Tomohon, dikelilingi oleh udara pegunungan yang sejuk dan pemandangan alam yang indah. Villa ini menawarkan suasana damai dan fasilitas yang nyaman, menjadikannya ideal untuk liburan keluarga, pasangan, atau perjalanan bersama teman. Dengan lokasinya yang strategis, para tamu dapat dengan mudah menjelajahi berbagai objek wisata alam dan tempat kuliner lokal di Tomohon.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Grand Master Villa Tomohon is a luxurious hotel in Tomohon, surrounded by cool mountain air and stunning natural landscape. The villa has a relaxing ambiance and excellent amenities, making it suitable for family vacations, couples, or outings with friends. With its excellent position, tourists may easily discover Tomohon\'s natural features and local culinary destinations.<br><br>Grand Master Villa Tomohon is a luxurious hotel in Tomohon, surrounded by cool mountain air and stunning natural landscape. The villa has a relaxing ambiance and excellent amenities, making it suitable for family vacations, couples, or outings with friends. With its excellent position, tourists may easily discover Tomohon\'s natural features and local culinary destinations.</p>', '<p>그랜드 마스터 빌라 토모혼은 토모혼 시내에 위치한 편안한 숙소로, 시원한 산 공기와 아름다운 자연 경관으로 둘러싸여 있습니다. 평화로운 분위기와 편안한 편의시설을 갖춘 이 빌라는 가족 휴가, 커플 여행, 친구들과의 여행에 이상적입니다. 편리한 위치 덕분에 토모혼의 다양한 자연 명소와 맛있는 음식을 쉽게 즐길 수 있습니다.\r\n\r\n그랜드 마스터 빌라 토모혼은 토모혼 시내에 위치한 편안한 숙소로, 시원한 산 공기와 아름다운 자연 경관으로 둘러싸여 있습니다. 평화로운 분위기와 편안한 편의시설을 갖춘 이 빌라는 가족 휴가, 커플 여행, 친구들과의 여행에 이상적입니다. 편리한 위치 덕분에 토모혼의 다양한 자연 명소와 맛있는 음식을 쉽게 즐길 수 있습니다.</p>', '<p>托莫洪大师别墅 (Grand Master Villa Tomohon) 坐落于托莫洪市，四周环绕着凉爽的山间空气和秀丽的自然风光，是一处舒适的下榻之所。别墅环境静谧，设施齐全，是家庭度假、情侣出游或朋友结伴旅行的理想之选。别墅地理位置优越，方便客人轻松探索托莫洪的众多自然景点和当地美食。\r\n\r\n托莫洪大师别墅 (Grand Master Villa Tomohon) 坐落于托莫洪市，四周环绕着凉爽的山间空气和秀丽的自然风光，是一处舒适的下榻之所。别墅环境静谧，设施齐全，是家庭度假、情侣出游或朋友结伴旅行的理想之选。别墅地理位置优越，方便客人轻松探索托莫洪的众多自然景点和当地美食。</p>', '[\"AC\",\"Swimming pool\",\"Family room\",\"Pool Bar\",\"Breakfast\",\"Cafe\",\"Free Wifi\",\"Karoke\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/HWVtT0KKbF5wu1hyWunkrUjLwC8oKZJYeB2p9yEh.webp', '2026-04-10 05:21:11', '2026-04-20 02:53:59'),
(30, 'Jhoanie Hotel Tomohon', 'jhoanie-hotel-tomohon', 'Tomohon', 'city_hotel', 3, '<p><strong>Jhoanie Hotel</strong> merupakan salah satu pilihan akomodasi yang menarik di Tomohon (Manado) dan menjadi pilihan cerdas bagi para wisatawan. Baik Anda bepergian untuk bisnis maupun liburan, nikmati perjalanan Anda secara maksimal dengan menginap di Jhoanie Hotel.</p><p>Jhoanie Hotel menawarkan berbagai fasilitas di dalam properti untuk memenuhi kebutuhan para tamu, bahkan yang paling selektif sekalipun. Tetap terhubung dengan mudah melalui Wi-Fi gratis yang tersedia di seluruh area hotel. Jika Anda membutuhkan transportasi dari atau ke bandara, pihak hotel dapat mengaturnya sebelum tanggal check-in Anda. Menjelajahi Manado juga menjadi lebih mudah dengan layanan penyewaan mobil yang tersedia di hotel.</p><p>Bagi Anda yang datang dengan kendaraan pribadi, hotel ini menyediakan area parkir gratis di lokasi. Hotel juga menyediakan layanan resepsionis seperti penitipan bagasi dan kotak penyimpanan aman untuk kenyamanan tamu. Menginap lebih lama atau membutuhkan pakaian bersih? Layanan dry cleaning dan laundry yang tersedia akan menjaga pakaian Anda tetap bersih dan siap digunakan. Untuk hari-hari santai, fasilitas dalam kamar seperti layanan kamar dan housekeeping harian memungkinkan Anda menikmati waktu istirahat dengan maksimal.</p><p>Merokok hanya diperbolehkan di area tertentu demi kesehatan dan kenyamanan semua tamu serta staf. Dengan berbagai fasilitas yang tersedia, kamar di Jhoanie Hotel menjamin kenyamanan bagi setiap tamu. Beberapa kamar dilengkapi dengan pendingin ruangan (AC) untuk kenyamanan Anda. Hiburan dalam kamar seperti koran harian, televisi, dan TV kabel tersedia di beberapa kamar tertentu. Hotel juga menyediakan kulkas di beberapa kamar bila diperlukan. Selain itu, perlengkapan mandi juga tersedia di beberapa kamar mandi untuk kenyamanan Anda.</p>', '<p>Jhoanie Hotel is a distinctive addition to Tomohon (Manado) and an excellent alternative for travelers. Whether you\'re traveling for business or pleasure, make the most of your trip by staying at Jhoanie Hotel.</p><p>Jhoanie Hotel has several on-site amenities to please even the most sophisticated guest. Stay in touch with your contacts at all times thanks to the free Wi-Fi available during your stay. If you require transportation from or to the airport, the hotel can arrange it before your check-in date. The hotel\'s car rental service makes it even easier to explore Manado.</p><p>If you intend on arriving by car, you\'ll appreciate the hotel\'s free on-site parking. For the convenience of its visitors, the hotel offers front-desk facilities such as luggage storage and safety deposit lockers. Are you staying for an extended period of time, or do you simply need clean clothes? The hotel offers dry cleaning and laundry services to keep your favorite travel outfits clean and available. For relaxed days and nights, in-room amenities such as room service and daily housekeeping allow you to make the most of your accommodations.</p><p>To ensure the health and well-being of all visitors and workers, smoking is only permitted in designated places. Jhoanie Hotel\'s guestrooms are equipped with convenient conveniences, ensuring a comfortable stay for all tourists. Some rooms at Jhoanie Hotel have air conditioning for your comfort. In some selected rooms, visitors can enjoy in-room entertainment such as a daily newspaper, television, and cable TV. In addition, the hotel provides a refrigerator in select rooms for those who require one. Jhoanie Hotel also offers amenities in several of its bathrooms for your convenience.</p>', '<p>조아니 호텔은 토모혼(마나도)에서 매력적인 숙박 시설 중 하나이며 여행객에게 현명한 선택입니다. 비즈니스 여행이든 휴가 여행이든, 조아니 호텔에 머무르며 최고의 여행을 경험해 보세요.\r\n\r\n조아니 호텔은 가장 까다로운 고객의 요구까지 충족할 수 있는 다양한 편의 시설을 제공합니다. 호텔 전역에서 무료 Wi-Fi를 이용하여 편리하게 인터넷에 접속할 수 있습니다. 공항 교통편이 필요하신 경우, 체크인 전에 호텔에서 예약해 드립니다. 호텔의 렌터카 서비스를 이용하면 마나도를 더욱 편리하게 둘러볼 수 있습니다.\r\n\r\n자가용을 이용하시는 고객을 위해 호텔 내 무료 주차장을 제공합니다. 또한, 프런트 데스크에서 수하물 보관소와 안전 금고를 이용하실 수 있습니다. 장기 투숙 또는 새 옷이 필요하신가요? 드라이클리닝 및 세탁 서비스를 통해 옷을 깨끗하게 보관하고 언제든 입을 수 있습니다. 편안한 휴식을 위해 룸서비스와 객실 청소 서비스를 제공합니다.\r\n\r\n모든 투숙객과 직원의 건강과 편안함을 위해 흡연은 지정된 구역에서만 허용됩니다. 조아니 호텔의 객실은 다양한 편의 시설을 갖추고 있어 모든 투숙객에게 편안한 숙박을 보장합니다. 일부 객실에는 에어컨이 설치되어 있어 더욱 쾌적한 환경을 제공합니다. 일부 객실에서는 일간 신문, 텔레비전, 케이블 TV 등의 객실 내 엔터테인먼트를 즐기실 수 있습니다. 또한, 필요시 이용할 수 있도록 일부 객실에는 냉장고가 마련되어 있습니다. 욕실에는 세면도구도 비치되어 있습니다.</p>', '<p>乔尼酒店 (Jhoanie Hotel) 是托莫洪 (万鸦老) 地区极具吸引力的住宿选择之一，也是旅行者的明智之选。无论您是商务出行还是休闲度假，入住乔尼酒店都能让您的旅程更加精彩。\r\n\r\n乔尼酒店提供各种便利设施，即使是最挑剔的客人也能找到心仪之选。酒店各处均提供免费无线网络，让您随时保持在线。如果您需要往返机场的接送服务，酒店可在您入住前为您安排。此外，酒店还提供租车服务，方便您探索万鸦老。\r\n\r\n如果您自驾前来，酒店提供免费停车位。酒店前台还提供行李寄存和保险箱等便利服务。如果您需要延长入住时间或清洗衣物，酒店提供干洗和洗衣服务，确保您的衣物洁净如新。客房内提供客房送餐服务和每日客房清洁服务，让您尽享舒适惬意的假期。\r\n\r\n为了所有客人和员工的健康与舒适，酒店仅允许在指定区域吸烟。乔尼酒店的客房设施齐全，确保每位宾客都能享受舒适的住宿体验。部分客房配备空调，为您带来舒适的睡眠环境。部分客房还提供室内娱乐设施，例如每日报纸、电视和有线电视。酒店还可根据需求在部分客房内提供冰箱。此外，部分浴室还提供洗浴用品，方便您的使用。</p>', '[\"AC\",\"Heater\",\"Smoke-free area\",\"Swimming pool\",\"Rooftop terrace\",\"Restaurant for breakfast\",\"Aerobics\",\"Billiards\",\"Pool\",\"Snooker\",\"Mini Market\",\"free WiFi\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/OAmHECxxjpmPLS8amIuBoPfuCJ1KhH3bVBx3sdcQ.webp', '2026-04-10 05:21:11', '2026-04-24 03:18:21'),
(31, 'Villa Emitta Hotel Tomohon', 'villa-emitta-tomohon', 'Tomohon', 'boutique', 3, '<p><strong>Villa Emitta Hotel Tomohon</strong> menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang menenangkan dengan suasana pegunungan yang sejuk khas Tomohon. Dikelilingi oleh pemandangan alam yang indah, hotel ini memiliki kamar modern yang luas, kolam renang outdoor, serta taman hijau yang asri.</p><p>Suasana yang tenang serta lokasi yang strategis menjadikannya tempat yang sempurna untuk bersantai sambil menikmati keindahan Tomohon dan sekitarnya.</p>', '<p>Villa Emitta Hotel Tomohon provides a pleasant stay in the lovely mountain environment of Tomohon. Surrounded by stunning natural setting, the hotel offers big modern rooms, an outdoor swimming pool, and lush green gardens. Its tranquil atmosphere and handy location make it an ideal place to relax while exploring Tomohon and its surrounds.<br>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>토모혼에 위치한 빌라 에미타 호텔은 토모혼 특유의 시원한 산속 분위기 속에서 편안한 휴식을 선사합니다. 아름다운 자연 경관으로 둘러싸인 이 호텔은 넓고 현대적인 객실, 야외 수영장, 그리고 울창한 정원을 자랑합니다.\r\n\r\n고요한 분위기와 최적의 위치 덕분에 토모혼과 그 주변 지역의 아름다움을 만끽하며 휴식을 취하기에 더할 나위 없이 좋은 곳입니다.</p>', '<p>托莫洪埃米塔别墅酒店 (Villa Emitta Hotel Tomohon) 坐落在托莫洪凉爽宜人的山间，为您提供轻松惬意的住宿体验。酒店四周环绕着美丽的自然风光，拥有宽敞现代的客房、室外游泳池和郁郁葱葱的花园。\r\n\r\n宁静的氛围和优越的地理位置，使这里成为您放松身心、欣赏托莫洪及其周边美景的理想之所</p>', '[\"AC\",\"Family room\",\"Smoke-free area\",\"Smoking area\",\"TV\",\"Children\'s play area\",\"Wifi\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/mRU2I7Y6clRIN6bTn9HCdfelk5k982mLYdW0wEop.webp', '2026-04-10 05:21:11', '2026-04-20 03:25:14'),
(32, 'Cocotinos Manado', 'cocotinos-manado', 'Manado', 'resort', 3, '<p>Selamat datang di Cocotinos Manado, tempat pelarian intim Anda ke jantung Sulawesi Utara! Terletak di sepanjang Teluk Wori dengan pemandangan Taman Laut Nasional Bunaken yang menakjubkan, resor selam butik kami menawarkan perpaduan tak tertandingi antara petualangan bawah laut kelas dunia dan ketenangan tropis yang damai.\r\n\r\nBenamkan diri Anda dalam kehidupan laut yang semarak di dinding Bunaken yang terkenal dan jelajahi keajaiban makro unik dari lokasi penyelaman \"muck\" Manado. Di luar pelukan samudra, temukan kekayaan budaya dan lanskap menakjubkan Dataran Tinggi Minahasa.\r\n\r\n\r\nDi Cocotinos, Anda akan mendapatkan layanan hangat dan personal, hidangan lokal dan internasional yang lezat, serta matahari terbenam spektakuler yang mewarnai langit. Baik Anda se orang penyelam yang bersemangat, pencinta alam, atau sekadar mencari tempat peristirahatan yang damai, perjalanan Indonesia Anda yang tak terlupakan dimulai di sini.</p>', '<p>Welcome to Cocotinos Manado, your cozy getaway in the heart of North Sulawesi! Nestled in Wori Bay, with breathtaking views of Bunaken National Marine Park, our boutique dive resort provides an unrivaled combination of world-class underwater thrills and quiet tropical solitude.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Immerse yourself in the vivid marine life of Bunaken\'s famed walls, and discover the unique macro wonders of Manado\'s \"muck\" diving locations. Beyond the ocean\'s embrace, explore the Minahasa Highlands\' rich culture and breathtaking vistas.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Cocotinos offers warm, individualized service, wonderful local and international cuisine, and stunning sunsets that color the sky. Whether you\'re an avid diver, a nature lover, or simply looking for a calm getaway, your unique Indonesian adventure begins here.</p>', '<p>북술라웨시의 중심부에 위치한 아늑한 휴양지, 코코티노스 마나도에 오신 것을 환영합니다! 숨 막히도록 아름다운 부나켄 국립해양공원이 내려다보이는 워리 만에 자리 잡은 저희 부티크 다이빙 리조트는 세계 최고 수준의 수중 모험과 평화로운 열대 분위기를 완벽하게 조화시킨 곳입니다. 부나켄의 유명한 해저 절벽에서 활기 넘치는 해양 생물을 만끽하고, 마나도의 \"머크\" 다이빙 포인트에서 독특한 미확인 생물들을 관찰해 보세요. 바다 너머로는 미나하사 고원의 풍부한 문화와 아름다운 풍경이 펼쳐집니다. 코코티노스에서는 따뜻하고 세심한 서비스, 맛있는 현지 및 세계 각국의 요리, 그리고 하늘을 물들이는 환상적인 일몰을 경험하실 수 있습니다. 열정적인 다이버, 자연 애호가, 혹은 그저 평화로운 휴식을 찾는 분이든, 잊지 못할 인도네시아 여행은 바로 여기에서 시작됩니다</p>', '<p>欢迎来到科科蒂诺斯万鸦老度假村，您在北苏拉威西岛中心地带的私密休憩之所！度假村坐落于沃里湾畔，俯瞰着令人叹为观止的布纳肯国家海洋公园，为您打造世界一流的水下探险与宁静祥和的热带风情完美融合的度假体验。您可以潜入布纳肯著名峭壁附近生机勃勃的海洋生物群落，探索万鸦老“微距”潜水点的独特微观世界。除了精彩的海洋之旅，您还可以探索米纳哈萨高地丰富的文化和壮丽的自然景观。在科科蒂诺斯，您将享受到热情周到的个性化服务、品尝到美味的当地和国际佳肴，以及欣赏到令人叹为观止的日落美景。无论您是潜水爱好者、自然爱好者，还是仅仅寻求一处静谧的休憩之所，您难忘的印尼之旅都将从这里启程</p>', '[\"TV\",\"AC\",\"Smoke-free area\",\"Smoking area\",\"Park\",\"Outdoor swimming pool\",\"Spa\",\"Bar\",\"Breakfast\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/ZFsNccfcqzWD4bBiqyyPVKNd8QZBLou5wOUdRORM.jpg', '2026-04-10 05:21:11', '2026-04-20 08:15:09'),
(33, 'Ibis Hotel Manado', 'ibis-hotel-manado', 'Jl. Pierre Tendean Boulevard No.85', 'city_hotel', 3, '<p>Terletak di kawasan strategis pusat bisnis dan komersial kota, Ibis Manado City Center Boulevard menghadirkan pengalaman menginap modern dengan standar internasional yang konsisten. Hotel ini sangat cocok bagi wisatawan maupun pelaku perjalanan bisnis yang menginginkan kenyamanan, efisiensi, dan akses mudah ke berbagai pusat aktivitas di Manado.</p><p>Dengan desain kontemporer yang simpel dan stylish, setiap kamar dirancang untuk memberikan kenyamanan maksimal. Fasilitas kamar meliputi AC, tempat tidur berkualitas tinggi khas ibis, TV layar datar, WiFi gratis berkecepatan tinggi, meja kerja ergonomis, serta kamar mandi modern dengan shower dan perlengkapan mandi lengkap.</p><p>Hotel ini juga menawarkan berbagai fasilitas penunjang, seperti restoran yang menyajikan menu lokal dan internasional, bar/lounge untuk bersantai, ruang meeting untuk kebutuhan bisnis, serta layanan resepsionis 24 jam yang siap membantu kapan saja. Suasana hotel yang bersih, modern, dan efisien memberikan pengalaman menginap yang menyenangkan.</p><p>Berlokasi di area Boulevard yang terkenal, hotel ini memberikan akses mudah ke berbagai destinasi populer seperti Megamas Manado yang ramai dengan pusat kuliner dan hiburan, serta Manado Town Square sebagai salah satu pusat perbelanjaan terbesar di kota.</p><p>Bagi pecinta wisata bahari, hotel ini juga menjadi titik awal yang ideal untuk menjelajahi Bunaken National Park yang terkenal dengan keindahan bawah lautnya. Sementara itu, Sam Ratulangi International Airport dapat dicapai dalam waktu sekitar 30–40 menit perjalanan.</p><p>Dengan lokasi premium, fasilitas lengkap, dan kualitas layanan bertaraf internasional, Ibis Hotel Manado menjadi pilihan tepat bagi Anda yang menginginkan pengalaman menginap yang praktis, nyaman, dan terpercaya.</p>', '<p>Strategically located in the heart of Manado’s business and commercial district, Ibis Manado City Center Boulevard offers a modern stay experience with consistent international standards. It is an excellent choice for both leisure and business travelers seeking comfort, efficiency, and easy access to the city’s main attractions.</p><p>Featuring a contemporary and stylish design, each room is thoughtfully designed for maximum comfort. Room amenities include air conditioning, signature ibis bedding, a flat-screen TV, high-speed free WiFi, an ergonomic work desk, and a modern bathroom with a shower and complete toiletries.</p><p>The hotel also provides a range of facilities, including a restaurant serving local and international cuisine, a bar/lounge for relaxation, meeting rooms for business needs, and a 24-hour front desk service. The clean, modern, and efficient environment ensures a pleasant stay.</p><p>Located in the vibrant Boulevard area, the hotel offers easy access to popular destinations such as Megamas Manado, known for its dining and entertainment scene, and Manado Town Square, one of the city’s main shopping hubs.</p><p>For nature enthusiasts, the hotel also serves as a convenient base to explore Bunaken National Park, famous for its stunning marine biodiversity. Meanwhile, Sam Ratulangi International Airport is approximately a 30–40 minute drive away.</p><p>With its prime location, complete facilities, and trusted international service quality, Ibis Hotel Manado is the perfect choice for a practical, comfortable, and reliable stay.</p>', '<p>마나도의 비즈니스 및 상업 중심지에 위치한 Ibis Manado City Center Boulevard는 국제적인 기준의 현대적인 숙박 경험을 제공합니다. 편안함과 효율성, 그리고 뛰어난 접근성을 원하는 관광객과 비즈니스 여행객 모두에게 적합한 호텔입니다.</p><p>모던하고 세련된 디자인의 객실은 에어컨, ibis 시그니처 침대, 평면 TV, 고속 무료 Wi-Fi, 업무용 책상, 샤워 시설과 어메니티가 갖춰진 욕실을 포함하여 최상의 편안함을 제공합니다.</p><p>호텔은 레스토랑, 바/라운지, 미팅룸, 24시간 프런트 데스크 등 다양한 시설을 제공하며, 깔끔하고 효율적인 환경으로 쾌적한 숙박을 보장합니다.</p><p>호텔은 Megamas Manado 및 Manado Town Square과 가까워 쇼핑과 식사를 즐기기에 매우 편리합니다.</p><p>또한 Bunaken National Park과 같은 자연 관광지로의 접근도 용이하며, Sam Ratulangi International Airport까지는 약 30~40분 정도 소요됩니다.</p><p>최적의 위치와 완벽한 시설, 그리고 신뢰할 수 있는 서비스 품질을 갖춘 Ibis Hotel Manado는 실용적이고 편안한 숙박을 원하는 분들에게 최고의 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>位于万鸦老商业与商务中心核心地段的 Ibis Manado City Center Boulevard，以国际标准为基础，提供现代化且舒适的住宿体验。无论是商务出行还是休闲旅游，这里都是理想之选。</p><p>酒店采用时尚现代的设计风格，每间客房均配备空调、ibis特色舒适床品、平板电视、高速免费WiFi、办公桌以及带淋浴和齐全洗浴用品的现代化浴室。</p><p>酒店设施完善，包括提供本地及国际美食的餐厅、休闲酒吧/休息区、会议室以及24小时前台服务，为宾客带来便利与舒适。</p><p>酒店位于热闹的 Boulevard 区域，方便前往 Megamas Manado 美食娱乐区，以及 Manado Town Square 购物中心。</p><p>同时，酒店也是前往著名海洋旅游胜地 Bunaken National Park 的理想出发点。距离 Sam Ratulangi International Airport 约30–40分钟车程。</p><p>凭借优越的地理位置、完善的设施以及可靠的国际服务品质，Ibis Hotel Manado 是追求高性价比与舒适体验旅客的理想选择。</p>', '[\"Sarapan\",\"Restoran\",\"Parkir gratis di tempat\",\"WiFi gratis\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Pemandangan\",\"Fasilitas BBQ\",\"AC\",\"Shower\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/EjlHpDG24hAIwFV21NLKDDCjSZ6snQP5TaOIUwW8.jpg', '2026-04-10 05:21:11', '2026-04-21 07:03:50'),
(34, 'Casa de Wanea Hotel & Resto', 'casa-de-wanea', 'Jl. Sam Ratulangi No. 90 - 92 Tanjung Batu, Wanea', 'city_hotel', 3, '<p>Terletak di kawasan Wanea yang strategis dan nyaman, Casa de Wanea Hotel &amp; Resto Manado menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang hangat dengan nuansa homey yang menenangkan. Hotel ini cocok bagi wisatawan maupun pelaku perjalanan bisnis yang mencari akomodasi praktis dengan suasana santai namun tetap dekat dengan pusat kota.</p><p>Mengusung konsep sederhana namun elegan, hotel ini menghadirkan kamar-kamar yang bersih dan nyaman, dilengkapi dengan AC, TV layar datar, WiFi gratis, serta kamar mandi pribadi dengan perlengkapan mandi lengkap. Beberapa kamar juga memiliki area duduk yang memberikan kenyamanan ekstra untuk bersantai.</p><p>Salah satu daya tarik utama hotel ini adalah restoran yang menyajikan berbagai hidangan lezat, mulai dari masakan lokal khas Manado hingga menu favorit internasional. Suasana restoran yang cozy menjadikannya tempat yang sempurna untuk bersantap bersama keluarga maupun rekan bisnis.</p><p>Untuk menunjang kenyamanan tamu, hotel ini juga menyediakan layanan resepsionis 24 jam, area parkir, serta layanan kamar. Lingkungan hotel yang tenang membuatnya ideal untuk beristirahat setelah beraktivitas seharian di kota.</p><p>Lokasi hotel memberikan akses mudah ke berbagai destinasi populer, seperti Manado Town Square dan kawasan Megamas Manado yang terkenal dengan kuliner dan hiburannya. Selain itu, akses menuju Bunaken National Park juga cukup mudah bagi pecinta wisata bahari.</p><p>Hotel ini berjarak sekitar 30–40 menit perjalanan dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport, menjadikannya pilihan yang praktis dan mudah dijangkau.</p><p>Dengan kombinasi suasana yang nyaman, pelayanan ramah, dan lokasi strategis, Casa de Wanea Hotel &amp; Resto Manado menjadi pilihan tepat untuk pengalaman menginap yang santai dan menyenangkan</p>', '<p>Located in the strategic and comfortable Wanea area, Casa de Wanea Hotel &amp; Resto Manado offers a warm and homey stay experience. It is an excellent choice for both leisure and business travelers looking for practical accommodation with a relaxed atmosphere while remaining close to the city center.</p><p>Featuring a simple yet elegant concept, the hotel provides clean and comfortable rooms equipped with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV, free WiFi, and a private bathroom with complete amenities. Some rooms also include a seating area for added comfort.</p><p>One of the hotel’s highlights is its restaurant, serving a variety of delicious dishes ranging from local Manado specialties to international favorites. The cozy dining atmosphere makes it a perfect place for meals with family or business partners.</p><p>To ensure guests’ convenience, the hotel offers a 24-hour front desk, parking area, and room service. Its quiet environment makes it ideal for relaxing after a busy day in the city.</p><p>The hotel’s location allows easy access to popular destinations such as Manado Town Square and Megamas Manado, known for dining and entertainment. It also provides convenient access to Bunaken National Park for marine tourism lovers.</p><p>The hotel is approximately 30–40 minutes from Sam Ratulangi International Airport, making it easily accessible for travelers.</p><p>With its cozy ambiance, friendly service, and strategic location, Casa de Wanea Hotel &amp; Resto Manado is an ideal choice for a relaxing and enjoyable stay.</p>', '<p>와네아 지역의 편리한 위치에 자리한 Casa de Wanea Hotel &amp; Resto Manado는 따뜻하고 아늑한 분위기의 숙박 경험을 제공합니다. 도심과 가까우면서도 편안한 휴식을 원하는 관광객과 비즈니스 여행객 모두에게 적합한 호텔입니다.</p><p>심플하면서도 세련된 디자인의 객실은 에어컨, 평면 TV, 무료 Wi-Fi, 그리고 어메니티가 갖춰진 전용 욕실을 제공하여 편안한 숙박을 보장합니다. 일부 객실에는 휴식 공간도 마련되어 있어 더욱 여유로운 시간을 보낼 수 있습니다.</p><p>호텔의 레스토랑은 마나도 전통 요리부터 다양한 국제 요리까지 제공하며, 아늑한 분위기 속에서 식사를 즐길 수 있는 매력적인 공간입니다.</p><p>또한 24시간 프런트 데스크, 주차 공간, 룸서비스 등 다양한 편의시설이 제공되며, 조용한 환경은 하루 일정을 마친 후 휴식을 취하기에 적합합니다.</p><p>호텔은 Manado Town Square 및 Megamas Manado과 가까워 쇼핑과 식사를 즐기기에 편리합니다. 또한 Bunaken National Park도 쉽게 방문할 수 있습니다.</p><p>Sam Ratulangi International Airport까지는 약 30~40분이 소요됩니다.</p><p>아늑한 분위기와 친절한 서비스, 그리고 편리한 위치를 갖춘 Casa de Wanea Hotel &amp; Resto Manado는 편안한 휴식을 원하는 분들에게 최고의 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>位于万鸦老 Wanea 区的 Casa de Wanea Hotel &amp; Resto Manado，以温馨舒适的居家氛围为特色，为宾客提供轻松愉快的住宿体验。无论是商务出行还是休闲旅游，这里都是理想的选择。</p><p>酒店采用简约优雅的设计风格，客房干净舒适，配备空调、平板电视、免费WiFi以及带齐全洗浴用品的独立浴室。部分房型还设有休息区，为宾客提供更多放松空间。</p><p>酒店内的餐厅是其亮点之一，提供多种美味佳肴，包括万鸦老特色美食和国际菜肴。温馨的用餐环境非常适合家庭聚餐或商务会面。</p><p>酒店还提供24小时前台服务、停车场及客房服务，安静的环境让宾客在忙碌一天后能够充分休息。</p><p>酒店地理位置优越，方便前往 Manado Town Square 和 Megamas Manado 等热门区域。同时，也可轻松前往著名的 Bunaken National Park。</p><p>酒店距离 Sam Ratulangi International Airport 约30–40分钟车程，交通便利。</p><p>凭借温馨的氛围、贴心的服务以及优越的地理位置，Casa de Wanea Hotel &amp; Resto Manado 是放松身心、享受旅程的理想之选。</p>', '[\"WiFi gratis\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Restoran\",\"Fasilitas tamu difabel\",\"Bar\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/0E1QO3kWbWCGrYWQRlxxSvTecTj4xFP8CEJJ1Wsq.jpg', '2026-04-10 05:21:11', '2026-04-21 06:12:13'),
(35, 'Genio Hotel Manado', 'genio-hotel-manado', 'Manado', 'city_hotel', 3, '<p>Genio Hotel Manado adalah hotel budget modern yang terletak di pusat kota Manado. Hotel ini menawarkan akomodasi yang nyaman dengan fasilitas seperti kamar ber-AC, Wi-Fi gratis, restoran, bar, serta layanan resepsionis 24 jam. Lokasinya yang strategis memberikan akses mudah ke berbagai tempat penting di kota, termasuk Manado Harbor dan area perbelanjaan, sehingga cocok untuk wisatawan bisnis maupun liburan. Hotel ini berjarak sekitar 12 km dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport, dengan waktu tempuh sekitar 25–30 menit menggunakan mobil.</p>', '<p>Genio Hotel Manado is a modern budget hotel located in the center of Manado. The hotel offers comfortable accommodation with facilities such as air-conditioned rooms, free Wi-Fi, a restaurant, a bar, and a 24-hour front desk service. Its strategic location provides easy access to important places in the city, including Manado Harbor and shopping areas, making it suitable for both business and leisure travelers. The hotel is located about 12 km from Sam Ratulangi International Airport, which takes approximately 25–30 minutes by car.</p>', '<p>Genio Hotel Manado는 마나도 도심에 위치한 현대적인 저가 호텔입니다. 이 호텔은 에어컨이 완비된 객실, 무료 Wi-Fi, 레스토랑, 바, 24시간 프런트 데스크 서비스를 제공하여 편안한 숙박을 제공합니다. 전략적인 위치 덕분에 Manado Harbor 및 쇼핑 지역 등 주요 장소로의 접근이 용이하여 비즈니스 및 관광 여행객 모두에게 적합합니다. 호텔은 Sam Ratulangi International Airport에서 약 12km 떨어져 있으며, 차량으로 약 25~30분 정도 소요됩니다.</p>', '<p>Genio Hotel Manado 是一家位于万鸦老市中心的现代经济型酒店。酒店提供舒适的住宿环境，配备空调客房、免费Wi-Fi、餐厅、酒吧以及24小时前台服务。其优越的地理位置使客人能够轻松前往城市的重要地点，包括 Manado Harbor 和各大购物区，非常适合商务和休闲旅客。酒店距离 Sam Ratulangi International Airport 约12公里，车程约25–30分钟。</p>', '[\"WiFi\",\"Parkir\",\"AC\",\"tiket CLEAN\",\"Resepsionis 24 Jam\",\"Lift\",\"Restoran\",\"Ruang Tamu\",\"Penyimpanan Barang\",\"Fasilitas Rapat\",\"Bukti Vaksin Covid-19\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/MpzWvyFnp2F9nVvVHlKfTCGqD9p4Kx51TMti6WiV.webp', '2026-04-10 05:21:11', '2026-04-21 05:39:52'),
(37, 'Whiz Prime Hotel Manado', 'whiz-prime-manado', 'Manado', 'city_hotel', 3, '<p>Terletak di jantung kota Manado yang dinamis, Whiz Prime Hotel Manado menawarkan pengalaman menginap modern dengan sentuhan gaya hidup urban yang praktis dan nyaman. Hotel ini menjadi pilihan tepat bagi wisatawan maupun pelaku bisnis yang menginginkan akomodasi stylish dengan harga terjangkau serta akses mudah ke berbagai pusat aktivitas kota.</p><p>Dengan desain interior yang minimalis dan modern, hotel ini menghadirkan suasana yang segar dan efisien. Setiap kamar dirancang untuk memberikan kenyamanan maksimal, dilengkapi dengan AC, TV layar datar, WiFi gratis, meja kerja ergonomis, serta kamar mandi pribadi dengan perlengkapan mandi lengkap.</p><p>Untuk menunjang kenyamanan tamu, hotel ini menyediakan berbagai fasilitas seperti restoran dengan pilihan menu lokal dan internasional, ruang meeting untuk keperluan bisnis, layanan resepsionis 24 jam, serta area parkir yang aman. Suasana hotel yang bersih dan tertata menjadikan pengalaman menginap semakin menyenangkan.</p><p>Lokasinya yang strategis memudahkan akses ke berbagai destinasi populer di Manado. Kawasan Megamas Manado yang terkenal dengan pusat hiburan dan kuliner dapat dijangkau dengan mudah. Selain itu, Manado Town Square sebagai pusat perbelanjaan favorit juga berada tidak jauh dari hotel.</p><p>Bagi wisatawan yang ingin menjelajahi keindahan alam, hotel ini juga memberikan akses yang cukup mudah menuju Bunaken National Park yang terkenal dengan keindahan bawah lautnya. Sementara itu, Sam Ratulangi International Airport dapat dicapai dalam waktu sekitar 30 menit perjalanan.</p><p>Dengan kombinasi lokasi strategis, desain modern, dan fasilitas lengkap, Whiz Prime Hotel Manado menjadi pilihan ideal bagi Anda yang mencari pengalaman menginap praktis, nyaman, dan bernilai tinggi di kota Manado.</p>', '<p>Strategically located in the vibrant heart of Manado, Whiz Prime Hotel Manado offers a modern stay experience with a practical and stylish urban lifestyle concept. It is an ideal choice for both leisure and business travelers seeking affordable yet comfortable accommodation with easy access to the city’s main attractions.</p><p>Featuring a minimalist and contemporary design, the hotel creates a fresh and efficient atmosphere. Each room is thoughtfully designed for maximum comfort, equipped with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV, free WiFi, an ergonomic work desk, and a private bathroom with complete amenities.</p><p>To enhance guests’ convenience, the hotel provides facilities such as a restaurant serving local and international dishes, meeting rooms for business needs, a 24-hour front desk, and secure parking areas. The clean and well-organized environment ensures a pleasant stay.</p><p>Its strategic location allows easy access to popular destinations in Manado. The lively Megamas Manado area, known for entertainment and dining, is within easy reach. Additionally, Manado Town Square, a favorite shopping destination, is located nearby.</p><p>For nature lovers, the hotel also provides convenient access to Bunaken National Park, famous for its stunning marine biodiversity. Meanwhile, Sam Ratulangi International Airport is approximately a 30-minute drive away.</p><p>With its strategic location, modern design, and complete facilities, Whiz Prime Hotel Manado is the perfect choice for those seeking a practical, comfortable, and value-for-money stay in Manado.</p>', '<p>마나도의 중심부에 위치한 Whiz Prime Hotel Manado는 현대적이고 실용적인 도시 라이프스타일을 반영한 편안한 숙박 경험을 제공합니다. 합리적인 가격과 뛰어난 접근성을 갖춘 이 호텔은 관광객과 비즈니스 여행객 모두에게 이상적인 선택입니다.</p><p>미니멀하고 세련된 인테리어 디자인으로 깔끔하고 효율적인 분위기를 자아내며, 모든 객실은 에어컨, 평면 TV, 무료 Wi-Fi, 업무용 책상, 그리고 어메니티가 완비된 전용 욕실을 갖추고 있어 편안함을 제공합니다.</p><p>호텔은 레스토랑, 미팅룸, 24시간 프런트 데스크, 안전한 주차 공간 등 다양한 편의시설을 제공하여 투숙객의 만족도를 높입니다. 청결하고 정돈된 환경 또한 큰 장점입니다.</p><p>호텔은 Megamas Manado 및 Manado Town Square과 가까워 쇼핑과 식사를 즐기기에 편리합니다. 또한 아름다운 해양 생태계로 유명한 Bunaken National Park도 쉽게 방문할 수 있습니다.</p><p>Sam Ratulangi International Airport까지는 차량으로 약 30분 정도 소요됩니다.</p><p>전략적인 위치와 현대적인 시설을 갖춘 Whiz Prime Hotel Manado는 실용적이고 편안한 숙박을 원하는 분들에게 최고의 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>位于万鸦老市中心的 Whiz Prime Hotel Manado，以现代简约的城市风格为特色，提供舒适且高性价比的住宿体验。无论是商务出行还是休闲旅游，这里都是理想之选。</p><p>酒店采用现代极简设计风格，营造出清新高效的环境。每间客房均配备空调、平板电视、免费WiFi、办公桌以及带齐全洗浴用品的独立浴室，确保宾客的舒适体验。</p><p>酒店提供完善的设施，包括供应本地及国际美食的餐厅、会议室、24小时前台服务以及安全的停车区域，为宾客带来便利与安心。</p><p>酒店地理位置优越，靠近 Megamas Manado 娱乐与美食区，同时也临近 Manado Town Square 购物中心。对于喜爱自然的游客，还可轻松前往著名的 Bunaken National Park。</p><p>此外，酒店距离 Sam Ratulangi International Airport 约30分钟车程，交通十分便利。</p><p>凭借优越的地理位置、现代化设施以及舒适环境，Whiz Prime Hotel Manado 是追求实用与品质住宿体验旅客的理想选择。</p>', '[\"WiFi\",\"Parkir\",\"AC\",\"Resepsionis 24 Jam\",\"Lift\",\"Restoran\",\"Penyimpanan Barang\",\"Fasilitas Rapat\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/fpq4d0JTXsuVUqtLs2u4Ng9otN4l2oeOauN5uC33.webp', '2026-04-10 05:21:11', '2026-04-21 03:35:53'),
(38, 'Formosa Hotel Manado', 'formosa-hotel-manado', 'Manado', 'city_hotel', 3, '<p>Terletak di kawasan strategis tepi Teluk Manado, Hotel Formosa Manado menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang sederhana namun penuh kenyamanan dengan panorama laut yang memikat. Hotel ini menjadi pilihan ideal bagi wisatawan maupun pelaku perjalanan bisnis yang mencari akomodasi terjangkau dengan lokasi yang sangat menguntungkan.</p><p>Menghadap langsung ke laut, beberapa kamar di hotel ini menghadirkan pemandangan indah yang menenangkan, terutama saat matahari terbenam. Suasana ini menciptakan pengalaman menginap yang hangat dan berkesan, jauh dari hiruk pikuk, namun tetap dekat dengan pusat aktivitas kota. Lokasinya yang berada di kawasan Bahu membuat hotel ini hanya berjarak sekitar 100 meter dari pusat perbelanjaan dan tidak jauh dari kawasan kuliner populer di Manado.</p><p>Hotel ini menyediakan berbagai fasilitas dasar yang menunjang kenyamanan tamu, seperti WiFi gratis, layanan kamar, restoran dengan sarapan harian, serta area parkir. Selain itu, tersedia juga layanan transportasi bandara dan concierge untuk membantu kebutuhan perjalanan Anda selama di Manado.</p><p>Setiap kamar dirancang dengan konsep simpel namun fungsional. Dilengkapi dengan AC, TV kabel layar datar, meja kerja, serta kamar mandi pribadi, hotel ini cocok bagi tamu yang mengutamakan efisiensi dan kenyamanan dalam satu paket. Beberapa tipe kamar juga dilengkapi fasilitas tambahan seperti area duduk dan mini kulkas untuk menunjang kebutuhan menginap yang lebih lama.</p><p>Keunggulan lain dari hotel ini adalah aksesnya yang mudah ke berbagai destinasi menarik di Manado. Anda dapat dengan cepat mencapai kawasan Boulevard yang terkenal dengan deretan kafe dan restoran, atau mengunjungi Jembatan Soekarno yang menjadi ikon kota. Selain itu, Pelabuhan Manado yang menjadi pintu menuju destinasi wisata bahari seperti Bunaken juga dapat dijangkau dengan mudah dari hotel.</p><p>Bagi wisatawan yang datang melalui jalur udara, hotel ini berjarak sekitar 15–18 km dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport, sehingga cukup mudah diakses dengan waktu tempuh sekitar 30 menit perjalanan.</p><p>Meskipun tergolong hotel bintang tiga, Hotel Formosa Manado tetap menawarkan nilai lebih melalui lokasinya yang strategis, pemandangan laut yang indah, serta suasana yang nyaman untuk beristirahat. Dengan harga yang relatif terjangkau, hotel ini menjadi pilihan tepat bagi Anda yang ingin menikmati keindahan Kota Manado tanpa harus mengeluarkan biaya besar.</p>', '<p>Strategically located along the scenic coastline of Manado Bay, Hotel Formosa Manado offers a simple yet comfortable stay complemented by captivating ocean views. This hotel is an ideal choice for both tourists and business travelers seeking affordable accommodation with a highly convenient location.</p><p>Facing directly toward the sea, several rooms provide calming and picturesque views, especially during sunset. The peaceful atmosphere creates a warm and memorable stay, away from the hustle and bustle while still being close to the city’s main attractions. Situated in the Bahu area, the hotel is only about 100 meters from shopping centers and within close proximity to Manado’s popular culinary spots.</p><p>The hotel features essential facilities to ensure guests’ comfort, including free WiFi, room service, a restaurant serving daily breakfast, and a parking area. In addition, airport transfer and concierge services are available to assist with your travel needs while in Manado.</p><p>Each room is designed with a simple yet functional concept, equipped with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with cable channels, a work desk, and a private bathroom. This makes it especially suitable for guests who value efficiency and comfort in one package. Some room types also include additional amenities such as a seating area and a mini refrigerator, ideal for longer stays.</p><p>Another advantage of this hotel is its easy access to various attractions in Manado. Guests can quickly reach the Boulevard Area Manado, known for its rows of cafés and restaurants, or visit the iconic Soekarno Bridge Manado. Additionally, Manado Harbor, the gateway to marine tourism destinations such as Bunaken National Park, is also easily accessible from the hotel.</p><p>For travelers arriving by air, the hotel is located approximately 15–18 km from Sam Ratulangi International Airport, with an estimated travel time of around 30 minutes.</p><p>Although categorized as a three-star hotel, Hotel Formosa Manado offers great value through its strategic location, beautiful sea views, and comfortable atmosphere. With its affordable rates, it is the perfect choice for those who wish to enjoy the beauty of Manado without spending excessively.</p>', '<p>마나도 만 해안의 전략적인 위치에 자리한 Hotel Formosa Manado는 매력적인 바다 전망과 함께 심플하지만 편안한 숙박 경험을 제공합니다. 이 호텔은 합리적인 가격과 뛰어난 입지를 갖춘 숙소를 찾는 관광객과 비즈니스 여행객 모두에게 이상적인 선택입니다.</p><p>바다를 바로 마주한 일부 객실에서는 특히 일몰 시간에 아름답고 평온한 풍경을 감상할 수 있습니다. 이러한 분위기는 도심의 번잡함에서 벗어나면서도 주요 활동 지역과 가까운 특별한 휴식 경험을 선사합니다. Bahu 지역에 위치한 이 호텔은 쇼핑센터에서 약 100m 거리에 있으며, 마나도의 인기 있는 미식 지역과도 가깝습니다.</p><p>호텔은 무료 Wi-Fi, 룸서비스, 조식이 제공되는 레스토랑, 주차 공간 등 기본적인 편의시설을 갖추고 있습니다. 또한 공항 교통 서비스와 컨시어지 서비스도 제공되어 여행 중 필요한 다양한 편의를 지원합니다.</p><p>각 객실은 심플하면서도 기능적으로 설계되어 있으며, 에어컨, 케이블 채널이 제공되는 평면 TV, 업무용 책상, 전용 욕실이 구비되어 있어 효율성과 편안함을 동시에 제공합니다. 일부 객실에는 휴식 공간과 미니 냉장고가 추가로 마련되어 장기 투숙에도 적합합니다.</p><p>호텔은 마나도의 주요 관광지로의 접근성도 뛰어납니다. Boulevard Area Manado의 카페와 레스토랑 거리, 도시의 상징인 Soekarno Bridge Manado 등을 쉽게 방문할 수 있습니다. 또한 Manado Harbor을 통해 Bunaken National Park 같은 해양 관광지로 이동하기에도 편리합니다.</p><p>항공편을 이용하는 여행객의 경우, 호텔은 Sam Ratulangi International Airport에서 약 15~18km, 차량으로 약 30분 거리에 위치해 있어 접근성이 좋습니다.</p><p>3성급 호텔로 분류되는 Hotel Formosa Manado는 전략적인 위치, 아름다운 바다 전망, 그리고 편안한 분위기를 통해 뛰어난 가성비를 제공합니다. 합리적인 가격으로 마나도의 매력을 즐기고 싶은 분들에게 최적의 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>位于万鸦老湾沿岸黄金地段的 Hotel Formosa Manado，以迷人的海景和舒适简约的住宿体验而著称。对于寻找价格实惠且位置优越的游客和商务旅客来说，这里是一个理想的选择。</p><p>部分客房可直接面朝大海，尤其在日落时分，可以欣赏到宁静而迷人的景色，为入住体验增添温馨与难忘的氛围。酒店位于 Bahu 区，距离购物中心约 100 米，同时也靠近万鸦老著名的美食区域。</p><p>酒店提供多种基础设施，包括免费 Wi-Fi、客房服务、提供每日早餐的餐厅以及停车场。此外，还设有机场接送服务和礼宾服务，为您的旅程提供更多便利。</p><p>每间客房均采用简约而实用的设计，配备空调、有线频道平板电视、办公桌以及独立浴室，非常适合注重效率与舒适的旅客。部分房型还提供休息区和迷你冰箱，方便长期入住。</p><p>酒店地理位置优越，方便前往万鸦老多个热门景点。您可以轻松抵达著名的 Boulevard Area Manado，这里汇聚了众多咖啡馆和餐厅；或参观城市地标 Soekarno Bridge Manado。此外，通过 Manado Harbor 还可以前往著名的海洋旅游胜地 Bunaken National Park。</p><p>对于乘飞机抵达的旅客，酒店距离 Sam Ratulangi International Airport 约 15–18 公里，车程约 30 分钟，交通十分便利。</p><p>作为一家三星级酒店，Hotel Formosa Manado 以其优越的地理位置、优美的海景以及舒适的环境，为宾客提供高性价比的住宿选择。对于希望以合理预算体验万鸦老魅力的旅客来说，这里是理想之选</p>', '[\"Area parkir\",\"Internet Kecepatan Tinggi Gratis (Wi-Fi)\",\"Kolam renang\",\"Kedai kopi\",\"Pantai\",\"Transportasi bandara\",\"Layanan pijat\",\"Layanan concierge\",\"AC\",\"Bathtub\\/shower\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/7OonXmPOqgWpXZxjpjKYnIYmsvZGx0F041K7yMXu.webp', '2026-04-10 05:21:11', '2026-04-21 07:11:01');
INSERT INTO `hotels` (`id`, `name`, `slug`, `location`, `category`, `stars`, `description`, `description_en`, `description_ko`, `description_zh`, `facilities`, `primary_image`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(56, 'Bobocabin Bunaken Hills', 'bobocabin-bunaken-hills-WWbGQZ', 'Jl,Molas-Tongkaina', 'resort', 3, '<p>Terletak di kawasan perbukitan yang tenang dengan pemandangan alam yang menakjubkan, <strong>Bobocabin Bunaken Hills, Manado</strong> menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang unik dengan konsep <strong>smart cabin modern</strong> yang memadukan teknologi, kenyamanan, dan keindahan alam. Resort bintang 4 ini menjadi pilihan ideal bagi wisatawan yang ingin menikmati suasana relaksasi jauh dari keramaian kota, namun tetap dekat dengan berbagai destinasi utama di Manado.</p><p>Akomodasi ini dilengkapi dengan <strong>taman yang asri dan area teras</strong> yang memungkinkan tamu menikmati panorama kota Manado dan perbukitan di sekitarnya. Dengan konsep kabin modern yang minimalis namun fungsional, Bobocabin memberikan pengalaman menginap yang berbeda dan nyaman bagi para tamu.</p><p>Setiap kabin dirancang dengan fasilitas modern, dilengkapi dengan <strong>kamar mandi pribadi, bidet, pengering rambut, serta desain interior yang nyaman</strong>. Beberapa unit juga menawarkan <strong>pemandangan kota Manado yang indah</strong>, terutama pada malam hari ketika lampu kota terlihat dari ketinggian.</p><p>Untuk memberikan kenyamanan maksimal, resort ini menyediakan <strong>WiFi gratis di seluruh area, layanan kamar, resepsionis 24 jam, serta layanan transfer bandara</strong> bagi para tamu.</p><p>Lokasinya juga cukup strategis untuk menjelajahi berbagai destinasi wisata di Manado. <strong>Manado Harbor</strong> berjarak sekitar <strong>8,7 km</strong>, sementara <strong>Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong> dan <strong>Soekarno Bridge</strong> dapat dicapai dalam jarak sekitar <strong>8 km</strong>. Selain itu, <strong>North Sulawesi State Museum</strong> berada sekitar <strong>10 km dari resort</strong>, dan destinasi alam terkenal <strong>Mount Lokon</strong> berjarak sekitar <strong>35 km</strong>.</p><p>Dari resort ini, tamu dapat mencapai <strong>pusat kota Manado dalam waktu sekitar 15–20 menit berkendara (sekitar 9 km)</strong>. Sementara itu, bagi tamu yang datang melalui jalur udara, resort ini berjarak sekitar <strong>19 km atau sekitar 35–40 menit perjalanan dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>.</p><p>Dengan <strong>konsep kabin modern, suasana alam yang tenang, serta pemandangan kota dari perbukitan</strong>, Bobocabin Bunaken Hills Manado menjadi pilihan sempurna bagi wisatawan yang mencari pengalaman menginap yang unik dan berbeda di Manado. ✨</p>', '<p>Nestled in the peaceful hills overlooking Manado, <strong>Bobocabin Bunaken Hills, Manado</strong> offers a unique stay experience with its <strong>modern smart cabin concept</strong>, combining technology, comfort, and beautiful natural surroundings. This 4-star accommodation is ideal for travelers seeking relaxation away from the busy city while still being close to Manado’s main attractions.</p><p>The property features <strong>lush gardens and relaxing terrace areas</strong> where guests can enjoy scenic views of Manado city and the surrounding hills. Designed with a <strong>minimalist yet functional cabin concept</strong>, Bobocabin provides a distinctive and comfortable stay experience.</p><p>Each cabin is thoughtfully designed with modern amenities including a <strong>private bathroom, bidet, hairdryer, and cozy interior design</strong>. Some units also offer <strong>beautiful city views</strong>, especially at night when the lights of Manado create a stunning panorama from the hills.</p><p>To ensure a pleasant stay, the resort provides <strong>free WiFi throughout the property, room service, a 24-hour front desk, and airport transfer services</strong>.</p><p>The location also offers convenient access to several attractions around Manado. <strong>Manado Harbor</strong> is about <strong>8.7 km away</strong>, while <strong>Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong> and <strong>Soekarno Bridge</strong> are approximately <strong>8 km away</strong>. <strong>North Sulawesi State Museum</strong> is located about <strong>10 km from the resort</strong>, and the famous <strong>Mount Lokon</strong> is around <strong>35 km away</strong>.</p><p>The <strong>Manado city center</strong> can be reached in about <strong>15–20 minutes by car (approximately 9 km)</strong>. For air travelers, the resort is located about <strong>19 km (around 35–40 minutes by car)</strong> from <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>.</p><p>With its <strong>modern cabin concept, peaceful hilltop setting, and stunning city views</strong>, Bobocabin Bunaken Hills Manado offers a unique and memorable stay experience in Manado. ✨</p>', '<p>마나도 언덕 지역에 위치한 <strong>Bobocabin Bunaken Hills, Manado</strong>는 자연 속에서 편안한 휴식을 즐길 수 있는 <strong>스마트 캐빈 콘셉트의 4성급 숙소</strong>입니다.</p><p>리조트는 <strong>아름다운 정원과 테라스</strong>를 갖추고 있어 마나도 시내와 주변 언덕의 멋진 전망을 감상할 수 있습니다. 현대적인 미니멀 디자인의 캐빈은 <strong>편안함과 기능성을 동시에 제공</strong>합니다.</p><p>객실에는 <strong>전용 욕실, 비데, 헤어드라이어</strong> 등의 편의시설이 마련되어 있으며 일부 객실에서는 <strong>마나도 시내의 아름다운 야경</strong>을 감상할 수 있습니다.</p><p>호텔은 <strong>무료 Wi-Fi, 24시간 프런트 데스크, 룸서비스, 공항 셔틀 서비스</strong>를 제공하여 편리한 숙박을 지원합니다.</p><p>호텔은 **Manado Harbor**에서 약 <strong>8.7km</strong>, <strong>Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong> 및 **Soekarno Bridge**에서 약 <strong>8km</strong> 거리에 있습니다. 또한 **North Sulawesi State Museum**은 약 <strong>10km</strong>, **Mount Lokon**은 약 <strong>35km</strong> 떨어져 있습니다.</p><p>마나도 시내 중심까지는 약 <strong>9km (차로 약 15~20분)</strong> 거리이며, **Sam Ratulangi International Airport**까지는 약 <strong>19km (차로 약 35~40분)</strong> 거리입니다.</p>', '<p>位于万鸦老山丘地区的 <strong>Bobocabin Bunaken Hills, Manado</strong> 是一家采用 <strong>智能小木屋概念（Smart Cabin）</strong> 的四星级度假住宿，为客人提供融合自然与现代科技的独特住宿体验。</p><p>酒店拥有 <strong>美丽的花园和观景露台</strong>，客人可以在这里欣赏万鸦老城市以及周围山丘的壮丽景色。简约现代的设计让客人既能享受自然环境，又能拥有舒适便利的住宿体验。</p><p>每间客房均配备 <strong>私人浴室、坐浴盆（Bidet）、吹风机</strong> 等设施。部分客房还可以欣赏 <strong>万鸦老城市的美丽景观，尤其是夜晚的城市灯光</strong>。</p><p>酒店提供 <strong>全区域免费Wi-Fi、24小时前台服务、客房服务以及机场接送服务</strong>，确保客人的入住更加方便。</p><p>酒店距离 <strong>Manado Harbor</strong> 约 <strong>8.7公里</strong>，距离 <strong>Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong> 和 <strong>Soekarno Bridge</strong> 约 <strong>8公里</strong>。此外，酒店距离 <strong>North Sulawesi State Museum</strong> 约 <strong>10公里</strong>，距离著名的 <strong>Mount Lokon</strong> 约 <strong>35公里</strong>。</p><p>酒店距离 <strong>万鸦老市中心约9公里（车程约15–20分钟）</strong>，距离 <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong> 约 <strong>19公里（车程约35–40分钟）</strong>，交通便利。</p>', '[\"WiFi gratis\",\"Antar-jemput bandara\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Kamar keluarga\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/aFiSkZ8HCYmsQm1UHlPqvh4sMquAL56rg3lKME4M.jpg', '2026-04-20 09:45:31', '2026-04-21 06:11:51'),
(57, 'Aston Manado Hotel', 'aston-manado-hotel-CacMmm', 'Manado', 'city_hotel', 4, '<p>Terletak strategis di jantung kota <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>Aston Manado Hotel</strong> menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang nyaman dengan akses mudah ke berbagai destinasi wisata dan pusat aktivitas kota. Hotel ini hanya berjarak sekitar <strong>13 menit berjalan kaki dari Pantai Megamas</strong>, menjadikannya pilihan ideal bagi wisatawan yang ingin menikmati keindahan pantai sekaligus suasana perkotaan.</p><p>Hotel ini menyediakan berbagai fasilitas modern untuk menunjang kenyamanan tamu, termasuk <strong>pusat kebugaran lengkap, layanan pijat relaksasi, bar yang nyaman, serta area parkir pribadi gratis</strong>. Tamu juga dapat menikmati <strong>WiFi gratis di seluruh area hotel</strong>, layanan kamar, serta <strong>resepsionis 24 jam</strong> yang siap membantu kebutuhan Anda. Untuk kemudahan perjalanan, hotel juga menyediakan <strong>layanan antar-jemput bandara</strong> menuju <strong>Bandara Sam Ratulangi</strong> yang berjarak sekitar <strong>14 km</strong> dari hotel.</p><p>Setiap kamar dirancang dengan nyaman dan dilengkapi dengan <strong>AC, TV, kamar mandi pribadi, serta brankas</strong> untuk menyimpan barang berharga. Beberapa tipe kamar juga memiliki <strong>area tempat duduk</strong> yang luas untuk bersantai.</p><p>Di pagi hari, tamu dapat menikmati <strong>sarapan prasmanan</strong> yang lezat. Restoran hotel menyajikan berbagai pilihan <strong>hidangan khas Indonesia dan masakan internasional</strong>, cocok untuk berbagai selera.</p><p>Lokasi hotel juga sangat dekat dengan berbagai tempat menarik di kota Manado, seperti:</p><ul><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"ea5edfc4a596959a12246c36049116cfa\"><strong>Pelabuhan Manado</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e25dfbb5e953ea457eb4b5583c8dd2d40\"><strong>Museum Negeri Provinsi Sulawesi Utara</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"ebd313df5eaacd3db4ff77d0494b68f1f\"><strong>Kelenteng Ban Hin Kiong</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2201080f31ea89744ce49cddc74cd4b0\">sekitar <strong>12 menit berjalan kaki ke Jembatan Soekarno</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e1257be091a8f184b8895060a55eb23b2\">sekitar <strong>7,2 km dari Patung Yesus Memberkati</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee48b966174a98d5e3bb9ebeaeec41145\">sekitar <strong>26 km dari Gunung Lokon</strong></li></ul><p>Dengan lokasi strategis, fasilitas lengkap, serta pelayanan ramah, <strong>Aston Manado Hotel</strong> menjadi pilihan sempurna bagi wisatawan bisnis maupun liburan yang ingin menikmati keindahan Manado dengan kenyamanan maksimal.</p>', '<p>Located in the vibrant city of <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>Aston Manado Hotel</strong> offers a comfortable and convenient stay with easy access to the city’s top attractions and business districts. The hotel is only <strong>a 13-minute walk from Megamas Beach</strong>, making it an ideal choice for travelers who want to enjoy both the seaside atmosphere and city lifestyle.</p><p>Guests can enjoy a wide range of modern facilities including a <strong>fully equipped fitness center, relaxing massage services, a cozy bar, and free private parking</strong>. The hotel also provides <strong>complimentary WiFi throughout the property</strong>, <strong>24-hour front desk service</strong>, <strong>room service</strong>, and convenient <strong>airport transfer services</strong> to <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, located approximately <strong>14 km away</strong>.</p><p>Each room is designed for comfort and equipped with <strong>air conditioning, a TV, private bathroom, and a safety deposit box</strong>. Selected rooms also feature a <strong>spacious seating area</strong>, perfect for relaxation.</p><p>Guests can start their day with a <strong>delicious buffet breakfast</strong>, while the hotel restaurant serves a variety of <strong>Indonesian specialties and international cuisine</strong>.</p><p>The hotel is also conveniently located near several popular attractions, including:</p><ul><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e34ea357c7d07e0d8c5610ed8ea780a2c\"><strong>Manado Harbor</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e9f22f2a02d4e765f5d1860990da2c834\"><strong>North Sulawesi State Museum</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e98db386f618412db983c1e06f231d572\"><strong>Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e313fea46060981694cc5251e0e0dfc48\"><strong>12-minute walk to Soekarno Bridge</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e0439f3d026064e36b1794d52bb6fe28e\"><strong>7.2 km from Christ Blessing Statue</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"ea68e95a83ebf35972766cbd1217837a5\"><strong>26 km from Mount Lokon</strong></li></ul><p>With its strategic location, modern amenities, and warm hospitality, <strong>Aston Manado Hotel</strong> is an excellent choice for both business and leisure travelers visiting Manado.</p>', '<p>북술라웨시의 아름다운 도시 <strong>마나도</strong> 중심에 위치한 <strong>Aston Manado Hotel</strong>은 편안함과 편리함을 동시에 제공하는 호텔입니다. 호텔은 **메가마스 해변**에서 도보 약 <strong>13분 거리</strong>에 있어 해변과 도심을 함께 즐기기에 이상적인 위치에 있습니다.</p><p>호텔에는 <strong>피트니스 센터, 마사지 서비스, 바, 무료 전용 주차장</strong> 등 다양한 시설이 마련되어 있습니다. 또한 <strong>전 구역 무료 Wi-Fi</strong>, <strong>24시간 프런트 데스크</strong>, <strong>룸서비스</strong>, 그리고 <strong>공항 셔틀 서비스</strong>가 제공됩니다. 호텔은 **사무 라툴랑이 국제공항**에서 약 <strong>14km</strong> 거리에 있습니다.</p><p>모든 객실에는 <strong>에어컨, TV, 전용 욕실, 금고</strong>가 마련되어 있으며, 일부 객실에는 <strong>편안한 휴식을 위한 좌석 공간</strong>도 제공됩니다.</p><p>아침에는 <strong>뷔페식 조식</strong>을 즐길 수 있으며, 호텔 레스토랑에서는 <strong>인도네시아 요리와 세계 각국의 요리</strong>를 제공합니다.</p><p>호텔 인근에는 다음과 같은 명소들이 있습니다:</p><ul><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"ea4c545a5451c2bd94d7ac1cf5962d6bb\"><strong>마나도 항구</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e4da292d5b135dbfe2c8cd79161e79611\"><strong>북술라웨시 주립 박물관</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e8b11091b4af9c540828ef54319f9fa24\"><strong>반힌키옹 사원</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e53135b8fffd849a17307596b4fe7fcbb\">도보 약 <strong>12분 거리의 수카르노 다리</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e02e2bda2aa33ff3c7c6d1f6d171068f2\">약 <strong>7.2km 거리의 예수 축복 동상</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb2d3a7420f56db5e96231d7548992779\">약 <strong>26km 거리의 로콘 산</strong></li></ul><p>편리한 위치와 완벽한 시설을 갖춘 <strong>Aston Manado Hotel</strong>은 비즈니스 여행객과 관광객 모두에게 최고의 숙박 선택이 될 것입니다.</p>', '<p>位于印度尼西亚北苏拉威西省首府 <strong>万鸦老</strong> 市中心的 <strong>Aston Manado Hotel</strong> 为旅客提供舒适便捷的住宿体验。酒店距离 <strong>Megamas 海滩</strong> 仅需 <strong>步行约13分钟</strong>，是想要同时享受海滨风景和城市生活的理想选择。</p><p>酒店配备完善的设施，包括 <strong>健身中心、按摩服务、酒吧以及免费私人停车场</strong>。酒店全区域提供 <strong>免费 Wi-Fi</strong>，并设有 <strong>24小时前台服务、客房服务以及机场接送服务</strong>。酒店距离 <strong>Sam Ratulangi 国际机场</strong> 约 <strong>14公里</strong>。</p><p>所有客房均配备 <strong>空调、电视、私人浴室以及保险箱</strong>，部分客房还设有 <strong>舒适的休息区</strong>，让您在旅途中也能轻松放松。</p><p>每天早晨，宾客可以享用 <strong>自助早餐</strong>。酒店餐厅供应丰富的 <strong>印尼特色美食以及国际料理</strong>，满足不同客人的口味需求。</p><p>酒店附近的热门景点包括：</p><ul><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"efbc6a324915a1dd08d8a89e9ef0a15a7\"><strong>万鸦老港口</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e0570f28d6d52eecce5794bcafd229e42\"><strong>北苏拉威西州博物馆</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e424b120c16d299628852c4b86dfae650\"><strong>Ban Hin Kiong 寺庙</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e508f714deaadd876a5f65987664e39b3\">步行 <strong>12分钟</strong> 可到达 <strong>苏加诺大桥</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec99481b4e5449fa8e9232a59e98557a9\">距离 <strong>耶稣祝福雕像</strong> 约 <strong>7.2公里</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef97fdb43cde9c25204c294f508fdc63e\">距离 <strong>洛孔火山</strong> 约 <strong>26公里</strong></li></ul><p>凭借优越的地理位置、完善的设施以及热情周到的服务，<strong>Aston Manado Hotel</strong> 是商务出行和休闲旅游旅客的理想住宿选择。</p>', '[\"WiFi gratis\",\"Antar-jemput bandara\",\"Pusat kebugaran\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Restoran\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Bar\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/lXQy1f7AC7DApYttYVfUnLUgd7OnoLdbh8bYJPbF.jpg', '2026-04-21 06:59:57', '2026-04-21 06:59:57'),
(58, 'Top Hotel Manado by Gran Puri', 'top-hotel-manado-by-gran-puri-gObt1Q', 'Manado', 'city_hotel', 3, '<p>Terletak di pusat kota <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>Top Hotel Manado by Gran Puri</strong> menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang nyaman dengan pemandangan kota yang indah. Lokasinya yang strategis memudahkan tamu untuk menjelajahi berbagai destinasi menarik, pusat bisnis, serta tempat wisata populer di kota Manado.</p><p>Hotel ini menyediakan berbagai fasilitas untuk kenyamanan tamu, termasuk <strong>resepsionis 24 jam, layanan kamar, serta akses WiFi gratis di seluruh area hotel</strong>. Tamu juga dapat menikmati <strong>restoran yang menyajikan hidangan khas Indonesia yang lezat</strong>, serta <strong>parkir pribadi gratis</strong> bagi yang membawa kendaraan.</p><p>Setiap kamar dirancang dengan nyaman dan dilengkapi dengan berbagai fasilitas modern seperti <strong>AC, TV layar datar dengan saluran satelit, ketel listrik, serta meja kerja</strong>. Kamar mandi pribadi dilengkapi dengan <strong>shower, sandal kamar, serta perlengkapan mandi gratis</strong>, sementara <strong>seprai yang bersih dan nyaman</strong> memastikan pengalaman menginap yang menyenangkan.</p><p>Hotel ini juga berada dekat dengan berbagai tempat menarik di Manado, antara lain:</p><ul><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e41d62c1d8e38b35b2c95570fb33f89af\"><strong>Pelabuhan Manado</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e7878a9e79d78e216650bc6cff2099382\"><strong>Museum Negeri Provinsi Sulawesi Utara</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"ec92a6197f695ea4726664280b703a129\"><strong>Kelenteng Ban Hin Kiong</strong></li></ul><p>Bagi tamu yang datang melalui udara, <strong>Bandara Sam Ratulangi</strong> dapat dicapai dengan perjalanan sekitar <strong>13 km</strong> dari hotel.</p><p>Dengan lokasi strategis, fasilitas lengkap, serta pelayanan ramah, <strong>Top Hotel Manado by Gran Puri</strong> menjadi pilihan ideal bagi wisatawan bisnis maupun liburan yang berkunjung ke Manado.</p>', '<p>Located in the vibrant city of <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>Top Hotel Manado by Gran Puri</strong> offers a comfortable stay with beautiful city views and easy access to many of Manado’s attractions and business areas.</p><p>The hotel provides convenient facilities including a <strong>24-hour front desk, room service, and complimentary WiFi throughout the property</strong>. Guests can also enjoy <strong>an on-site restaurant serving delicious Indonesian cuisine</strong>, as well as <strong>free private parking</strong> for those traveling by car.</p><p>Each room is thoughtfully designed for comfort and equipped with <strong>air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, an electric kettle, and a work desk</strong>. The <strong>private bathroom</strong> features a <strong>shower, slippers, and complimentary toiletries</strong>, while <strong>clean and comfortable bed linens</strong> ensure a relaxing stay.</p><p>The hotel is also located close to several popular attractions in Manado, including:</p><ul><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"ef3ffefff93d987d2e5803d1befef1d07\"><strong>Manado Harbor</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e2024d9cde5ac317c0ae3985e9da3e1d3\"><strong>North Sulawesi State Museum</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e8d3821fdc2d2065a014626eb836d9e78\"><strong>Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong></li></ul><p>For travelers arriving by air, <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong> is conveniently located about <strong>13 km</strong> from the hotel.</p><p>With its strategic location, comfortable rooms, and friendly service, <strong>Top Hotel Manado by Gran Puri</strong> is an excellent choice for both business and leisure travelers visiting Manado.</p>', '<p>북술라웨시의 아름다운 도시 **마나도**에 위치한 <strong>Top Hotel Manado by Gran Puri</strong>는 멋진 도시 전망과 편안한 숙박을 제공하는 호텔입니다. 호텔은 마나도의 주요 관광지와 비즈니스 지역으로 이동하기에 편리한 위치에 자리하고 있습니다.</p><p>호텔에서는 <strong>24시간 프런트 데스크 서비스, 룸서비스, 전 구역 무료 Wi-Fi</strong> 등 다양한 편의시설을 제공합니다. 또한 <strong>인도네시아 요리를 제공하는 레스토랑</strong>과 <strong>무료 전용 주차장</strong>도 이용하실 수 있습니다.</p><p>객실에는 <strong>에어컨, 위성 채널이 포함된 평면 TV, 전기 주전자, 업무용 책상</strong>이 구비되어 있습니다. 모든 객실에는 <strong>샤워 시설이 있는 전용 욕실, 슬리퍼, 무료 세면도구</strong>가 제공되며 <strong>편안한 침구</strong>가 준비되어 있어 쾌적한 휴식을 즐길 수 있습니다.</p><p>호텔 근처에는 다음과 같은 인기 명소들이 있습니다:</p><ul><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e5bd290911158cd37678a70032315d568\"><strong>마나도 항구</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e8ef580674f2760a433eee51727513eb4\"><strong>북술라웨시 주립 박물관</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e5004f13e916541ee0f2f2ab9dea3d664\"><strong>반힌키옹 사원</strong></li></ul><p>또한 **사무 라툴랑이 국제공항**까지 약 <strong>13km</strong> 거리에 있어 이동이 편리합니다.</p><p>편리한 위치와 쾌적한 객실, 친절한 서비스를 제공하는 <strong>Top Hotel Manado by Gran Puri</strong>는 마나도를 방문하는 여행객들에게 이상적인 숙박 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>位于印度尼西亚北苏拉威西省首府 <strong>万鸦老</strong> 的 <strong>Top Hotel Manado by Gran Puri</strong> 为旅客提供舒适的住宿环境以及迷人的城市景观。酒店地理位置优越，方便前往万鸦老的主要景点和商业区域。</p><p>酒店提供多种便利设施，包括 <strong>24小时前台服务、客房服务以及全区域免费 Wi-Fi</strong>。酒店内设有 <strong>供应印尼特色美食的餐厅</strong>，并为自驾旅客提供 <strong>免费私人停车场</strong>。</p><p>所有客房均配备 <strong>空调、卫星频道平板电视、电热水壶以及办公桌</strong>。客房内设有 <strong>带淋浴的私人浴室、拖鞋以及免费洗浴用品</strong>，并提供 <strong>干净舒适的床上用品</strong>，让您的住宿更加轻松愉快。</p><p>酒店附近的热门景点包括：</p><ul><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"edb0cfa26e4dcadfdb560ee2112dbb23b\"><strong>万鸦老港口</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"ed7f132f49b17dd621860867d7072c6e2\"><strong>北苏拉威西州博物馆</strong></li><li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e259b0be88685fa7dd1f36cbdda02b4bd\"><strong>Ban Hin Kiong 寺庙</strong></li></ul><p>酒店距离 <strong>Sam Ratulangi 国际机场</strong> 约 <strong>13公里</strong>，交通十分便利。</p><p>凭借优越的地理位置、舒适的客房设施以及贴心的服务，<strong>Top Hotel Manado by Gran Puri</strong> 是商务与休闲旅客在万鸦老的理想住宿选择。</p>', '[\"WiFi gratis\",\"Antar-jemput bandara\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Restoran\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/xeefuZ7gt3CQVG8AcAZpml88l6mRtsGErkysJIkb.jpg', '2026-04-21 07:27:06', '2026-04-21 07:40:46'),
(59, 'Aryaduta Hotel Manado', 'aryaduta-hotel-manado-ZJNURu', 'Manado', 'city_hotel', 4, '<p>Terletak di sepanjang kawasan <strong>Boulevard Manado</strong> yang terkenal, <strong>Hotel Aryaduta Manado</strong> menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang mewah dengan pemandangan laut yang memukau dan akses langsung ke berbagai fasilitas kota. Hotel ini terhubung langsung dengan <strong>Rumah Sakit Siloam Manado</strong> serta sebuah pusat perbelanjaan modern 4 lantai, memberikan kenyamanan maksimal bagi para tamu.</p><p>Salah satu daya tarik utama hotel ini adalah <strong>kolam renang infinity outdoor</strong> yang spektakuler. Dari tepi kolam, air tampak seolah <strong>menyatu dengan cakrawala Laut Sulawesi</strong>, menciptakan pemandangan yang menenangkan dan sangat Instagramable. Tamu dapat berenang sambil menikmati panorama laut luas yang indah.</p><p>Untuk menjaga kebugaran selama menginap, tamu dapat memanfaatkan <strong>pusat kebugaran lengkap</strong>, atau memanjakan diri dengan <strong>perawatan relaksasi di pusat spa dan layanan pijat</strong>.</p><p>Menghadap langsung ke <strong>Laut Sulawesi</strong> serta panorama pegunungan seperti <strong>Gunung Klabat</strong>, hotel ini berada tepat di pusat kota <strong>Manado</strong>. Lokasinya juga sangat strategis dengan jarak sekitar <strong>30 menit berkendara dari Bandara Internasional Sam Ratulangi</strong>.</p><p>Semua kamar di hotel ini dirancang luas dan nyaman, dilengkapi dengan <strong>AC, TV satelit, minibar, serta sofa</strong> untuk bersantai. Kamar mandi pribadi menyediakan <strong>shower air panas, bathtub, serta pengering rambut</strong>, memberikan kenyamanan ekstra bagi para tamu.</p><p>Hotel ini juga menyediakan <strong>ruang pertemuan untuk acara bisnis atau konferensi</strong>, serta berbagai layanan tambahan seperti <strong>penyewaan mobil dan layanan kamar 24 jam</strong>.</p><p>Untuk pengalaman kuliner, <strong>Cakrawala Coffee Shop</strong> menyajikan <strong>sarapan prasmanan internasional</strong> dengan berbagai pilihan menu lezat. Sementara itu, <strong>Lobby Lounge</strong> menawarkan suasana santai untuk menikmati <strong>minuman ringan dan koktail</strong>, ditemani <strong>alunan musik jazz live</strong> yang menambah kehangatan suasana malam di hotel.</p><p>Dengan pemandangan laut yang spektakuler, fasilitas lengkap, dan lokasi premium di pusat kota, <strong>Hotel Aryaduta Manado</strong> menjadi pilihan ideal bagi wisatawan bisnis maupun liburan yang ingin menikmati kenyamanan dan keindahan Manado.</p>', '<p>Located along the famous <strong>Manado Boulevard</strong>, <strong>Aryaduta Manado</strong> offers a luxurious stay with breathtaking ocean views and convenient access to city facilities. The hotel is directly connected to <strong>Siloam Hospital Manado</strong> and a modern four-story shopping center, providing extra comfort and convenience for guests.</p><p>One of the hotel’s most remarkable highlights is its <strong>stunning outdoor infinity swimming pool</strong>. From the edge of the pool, the water appears to <strong>blend seamlessly with the horizon of the Sulawesi Sea</strong>, creating a spectacular visual effect where the pool seems to merge with the ocean. It’s the perfect spot to relax, swim, and enjoy panoramic sea views.</p><p>Guests can stay active at the <strong>fully equipped fitness center</strong>, or unwind with a relaxing <strong>spa treatment and massage service</strong>.</p><p>Overlooking the beautiful <strong>Sulawesi Sea</strong> and the majestic <strong>Mount Klabat</strong>, the hotel is located in the heart of <strong>Manado</strong>. It is also conveniently situated about <strong>30 minutes by car from Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>.</p><p>All rooms are spacious and air-conditioned, featuring <strong>satellite TV, a minibar, and a comfortable sofa seating area</strong>. The <strong>en-suite bathrooms</strong> are equipped with <strong>hot showers, bathtubs, and hairdryers</strong>, ensuring a relaxing stay.</p><p>The hotel also features <strong>meeting rooms for business events and conferences</strong>, along with services such as <strong>car rental and 24-hour room service</strong>.</p><p>For dining, <strong>Cakrawala Coffee Shop</strong> serves a delicious <strong>international buffet breakfast</strong> with a wide variety of dishes. Meanwhile, the <strong>Lobby Lounge</strong> offers a relaxing atmosphere where guests can enjoy <strong>light refreshments and cocktails accompanied by live jazz music</strong>.</p><p>With its spectacular ocean views, elegant facilities, and prime location in Manado, <strong>Aryaduta Manado</strong> is the perfect choice for both business and leisure travelers.</p>', '<p>유명한 **마나도 블러바드**에 위치한 <strong>아리아두타 마나도 호텔</strong>은 아름다운 바다 전망과 편리한 위치를 자랑하는 럭셔리 호텔입니다. 호텔은 <strong>실로암 병원 마나도</strong> 및 4층 규모의 쇼핑센터와 직접 연결되어 있어 더욱 편리한 숙박을 제공합니다.</p><p>호텔의 가장 큰 매력 중 하나는 <strong>야외 인피니티 수영장</strong>입니다. 수영장 가장자리에서 바라보면 물이 마치 <strong>술라웨시 바다와 하나로 이어지는 것처럼 보이며</strong>, 수평선과 자연스럽게 연결된 환상적인 풍경을 감상할 수 있습니다.</p><p>호텔에는 <strong>피트니스 센터</strong>가 마련되어 있으며, <strong>스파와 마사지 서비스</strong>를 통해 편안한 휴식을 즐길 수 있습니다.</p><p>호텔은 **술라웨시 바다**와 **클라밧 산**의 아름다운 전망을 자랑하며 <strong>마나도</strong> 중심부에 위치해 있습니다. 또한 **사무 라툴랑이 국제공항**까지 차량으로 약 <strong>30분 거리</strong>입니다.</p><p>모든 객실은 넓고 쾌적하며 <strong>에어컨, 위성 TV, 미니바, 소파</strong>가 갖춰져 있습니다. 전용 욕실에는 <strong>온수 샤워, 욕조, 헤어드라이어</strong>가 마련되어 있습니다.</p><p>호텔에는 <strong>회의실</strong>, <strong>렌터카 서비스</strong>, <strong>24시간 룸서비스</strong>도 제공됩니다.</p><p>식사는 <strong>Cakrawala Coffee Shop</strong>에서 제공되는 <strong>세계 각국의 뷔페식 아침 식사</strong>를 즐길 수 있습니다. 또한 <strong>Lobby Lounge</strong>에서는 <strong>라이브 재즈 음악과 함께 가벼운 음료와 칵테일</strong>을 즐기며 편안한 시간을 보낼 수 있습니다.</p>', '<p>位于著名的 <strong>万鸦老海滨大道</strong> 的 <strong>Aryaduta Manado</strong> 为旅客提供奢华舒适的住宿体验，并拥有壮丽的海景。酒店与 <strong>Siloam 医院 万鸦老</strong> 以及一座四层购物中心直接相连，为宾客带来极大的便利。</p><p>酒店最引人注目的亮点之一是 <strong>户外无边际泳池（Infinity Pool）</strong>。当您站在泳池边缘时，池水仿佛 <strong>与远处的苏拉威西海融为一体</strong>，形成水天相接的壮丽景观，让人仿佛置身于海天之间。</p><p>宾客可以在 <strong>健身中心</strong>锻炼身体，或在 <strong>水疗中心享受按摩与放松护理</strong>。</p><p>酒店面向壮丽的 <strong>苏拉威西海</strong>，同时还能欣赏到 <strong>克拉巴特山</strong> 的美丽景色，坐落于 <strong>万鸦老</strong> 市中心。酒店距离 <strong>Sam Ratulangi 国际机场</strong> 约 <strong>30分钟车程</strong>。</p><p>所有客房宽敞舒适，配备 <strong>空调、卫星电视、迷你吧和沙发</strong>。私人浴室设有 <strong>热水淋浴、浴缸和吹风机</strong>。</p><p>酒店还提供 <strong>会议室、汽车租赁服务以及24小时客房服务</strong>。</p><p>在 <strong>Cakrawala Coffee Shop</strong>，宾客可以享用丰富的 <strong>国际自助早餐</strong>。而 <strong>Lobby Lounge</strong> 则提供 <strong>轻食、鸡尾酒以及现场爵士乐表演</strong>，为夜晚增添优雅的氛围。</p>', '[\"1 kolam renang\",\"WiFi gratis\",\"Pusat kebugaran\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Spa & pusat kesehatan\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Pembuat teh\\/kopi di semua kamar\",\"Bar\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/fe0LbdfBbUuORvLYSgnilQyVFi3inyk60II30mCZ.jpg', '2026-04-21 08:03:42', '2026-04-21 08:03:43'),
(60, 'Victoria Inn', 'victoria-inn-4I2nTH', 'Manado', 'city_hotel', 3, '<p>Terletak di kawasan <strong>Paniki</strong>, <strong>Victoria Inn</strong> menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang nyaman dan tenang dengan suasana alami yang menyegarkan. Hotel bintang 4 ini menjadi pilihan ideal bagi wisatawan maupun pelancong bisnis yang mencari akomodasi dekat bandara namun tetap dekat dengan berbagai destinasi menarik di Manado.</p><p>Hotel ini menyediakan berbagai fasilitas untuk kenyamanan tamu, termasuk <strong>taman yang asri, lounge bersama yang nyaman, teras untuk bersantai, serta parkir pribadi gratis</strong>. Tamu juga dapat menikmati <strong>WiFi gratis di seluruh area hotel</strong>, <strong>layanan kamar</strong>, serta <strong>resepsionis 24 jam</strong> yang siap membantu kebutuhan Anda. Untuk menambah kenyamanan, hotel juga memiliki <strong>bar</strong> yang menyajikan berbagai minuman untuk dinikmati dalam suasana santai.</p><p>Setiap kamar di hotel dirancang luas dan modern, dilengkapi dengan <strong>AC, TV layar datar, lemari pakaian, serta area tempat duduk yang nyaman</strong>. Kamar juga memiliki <strong>kamar mandi pribadi lengkap dengan seprai dan handuk berkualitas</strong>, serta <strong>balkon pribadi dengan pemandangan pegunungan yang indah</strong>. Beberapa kamar bahkan menawarkan <strong>pemandangan kota</strong> yang memukau.</p><p>Lokasi hotel juga sangat strategis:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ee0ba5395b2e58b653a9c84555b614eb3\">sekitar <strong>11 km dari Pelabuhan Manado</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8f60ef991080c1a47ce2d4ded369a174\">sekitar <strong>11 km dari Kelenteng Ban Hin Kiong</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e88817ff024dfe2c412cfbcfe22d4a8b2\">sekitar <strong>32 km dari Gunung Lokon</strong></li></ul><p>Bagi tamu yang datang melalui udara, hotel ini sangat mudah dijangkau karena hanya berjarak sekitar <strong>3 km dari Bandara Sam Ratulangi</strong>.</p><p>Dengan suasana tenang, pemandangan alam yang indah, serta fasilitas lengkap, <strong>Victoria Inn</strong> menjadi pilihan sempurna bagi Anda yang ingin menikmati kenyamanan menginap di Manado.</p>', '<p>Located in the peaceful area of <strong>Paniki</strong>, <strong>Victoria Inn</strong> offers a comfortable and relaxing stay surrounded by natural scenery. This 4-star hotel is an ideal choice for both leisure and business travelers looking for accommodation close to the airport while still having easy access to the city of Manado.</p><p>The hotel features a variety of facilities designed for guest comfort, including a <strong>beautiful garden, a shared lounge, a relaxing terrace, and free private parking</strong>. Guests can also enjoy <strong>complimentary WiFi throughout the property</strong>, <strong>24-hour front desk service</strong>, and <strong>room service</strong>. A <strong>bar</strong> is also available, offering a selection of refreshing drinks in a cozy atmosphere.</p><p>Each room is spacious and thoughtfully designed with <strong>air conditioning, a flat-screen TV, wardrobe, and a comfortable seating area</strong>. Rooms also feature a <strong>private bathroom with fresh linens and towels</strong>, as well as a <strong>private balcony with scenic mountain views</strong>. Some rooms additionally offer <strong>beautiful views of the city</strong>.</p><p>The hotel’s convenient location allows easy access to several attractions:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e644f863239ae15511f743e3236d51c07\">approximately <strong>11 km from Manado Harbor</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"efaedbe842202b25e9a8459a0c3dcc0ff\">approximately <strong>11 km from Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0a32cf77468a7e0129f51ad17e3ef9a6\">approximately <strong>32 km from Mount Lokon</strong></li></ul><p>For travelers arriving by air, the hotel is only <strong>3 km from Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, making it extremely convenient.</p><p>With its tranquil atmosphere, beautiful mountain views, and modern facilities, <strong>Victoria Inn</strong> is a perfect place to relax and enjoy your stay in Manado.</p>', '<p>북술라웨시 <strong>파니키</strong> 지역에 위치한 <strong>빅토리아 인</strong>은 자연의 아름다움 속에서 편안한 휴식을 제공하는 4성급 호텔입니다. 공항과 가까우면서도 마나도 시내 주요 관광지로 이동하기 편리하여 비즈니스 여행객과 관광객 모두에게 이상적인 숙소입니다.</p><p>호텔에는 <strong>아름다운 정원, 공용 라운지, 휴식을 위한 테라스, 무료 전용 주차장</strong>이 마련되어 있습니다. 또한 <strong>전 구역 무료 Wi-Fi, 24시간 프런트 데스크, 룸서비스</strong>가 제공됩니다. 호텔의 <strong>바</strong>에서는 다양한 음료를 즐기며 여유로운 시간을 보낼 수 있습니다.</p><p>모든 객실은 넓고 편안하게 설계되어 있으며 <strong>에어컨, 평면 TV, 옷장, 휴식 공간</strong>이 갖춰져 있습니다. 객실에는 <strong>침구와 수건이 제공되는 전용 욕실</strong>이 있으며, <strong>아름다운 산 전망을 감상할 수 있는 전용 발코니</strong>도 마련되어 있습니다. 일부 객실에서는 <strong>도시 전망</strong>도 즐길 수 있습니다.</p><p>호텔은 다음 명소와도 가까운 위치에 있습니다:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e53025bc15e16155b423db919d245ccdb\"><strong>마나도 항구</strong> 약 11km</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2ace963713fd31158ab97b78901397eb\"><strong>반힌키옹 사원</strong> 약 11km</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed0406c41acc1071f028b95b2e0e1602f\"><strong>로콘 산</strong> 약 32km</li></ul><p>또한 **사무 라툴랑이 국제공항**까지 약 <strong>3km</strong> 거리로 이동이 매우 편리합니다.</p><p>아름다운 자연 경관과 편안한 시설을 갖춘 <strong>Victoria Inn</strong>은 마나도에서 편안한 휴식을 즐기기에 완벽한 호텔입니다.</p>', '<p>位于北苏拉威西 <strong>帕尼基</strong> 地区的 <strong>Victoria Inn</strong> 是一家四星级酒店，为旅客提供舒适宁静的住宿环境，并可欣赏到优美的自然景观。酒店靠近机场，同时前往万鸦老市区和各大景点也十分方便，非常适合商务和休闲旅客。</p><p>酒店设施完善，包括 <strong>花园、公共休息室、休闲露台以及免费私人停车场</strong>。酒店还提供 <strong>全区域免费 Wi-Fi、24小时前台服务以及客房服务</strong>。此外，酒店内设有 <strong>酒吧</strong>，宾客可以在轻松的氛围中享用各种饮品。</p><p>每间客房都宽敞舒适，配备 <strong>空调、平板电视、衣柜以及休息区</strong>。客房内设有 <strong>带床上用品和毛巾的私人浴室</strong>，并配有 <strong>可欣赏山景的私人阳台</strong>。部分客房还可以欣赏到 <strong>城市景观</strong>。</p><p>酒店距离多个著名景点也十分方便：</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e437281c24150891fdc52fa3a5ffa5bca\"><strong>万鸦老港口</strong> 约11公里</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e1ee63e89903dbbf9a6de7f3ed6feddf7\"><strong>Ban Hin Kiong 寺庙</strong> 约11公里</li><li data-list-item-id=\"efb7eab7a715c9d9672eaa4aba0f00a17\"><strong>洛孔火山</strong> 约32公里</li></ul><p>酒店距离 <strong>Sam Ratulangi 国际机场</strong> 仅 <strong>3公里</strong>，交通非常便利。</p><p>凭借宁静的环境、优美的山景以及完善的设施，<strong>Victoria Inn</strong> 是在万鸦老放松休息和探索城市的理想住宿选择。</p>', '[\"Kolam renang indoor\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"WiFi gratis\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Bar\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/6n5jFxZYkGX6vhk2a3mbpSoH9uwt4B3JYKEQskAK.jpg', '2026-04-21 08:15:17', '2026-04-21 08:15:17'),
(61, 'Mel\'s Inn Manado', 'mels-inn-manado-V6HYC8', 'Manado', 'city_hotel', 2, '<p>Terletak di kota <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>Mel\'s Inn Manado</strong> merupakan akomodasi bintang 2 yang nyaman dan praktis, sangat cocok bagi wisatawan maupun pelancong bisnis yang mencari tempat menginap dengan lokasi strategis. Hotel ini berada tidak jauh dari <strong>Bandara Sam Ratulangi</strong>, sehingga sangat ideal bagi tamu yang memiliki jadwal penerbangan pagi atau malam.</p><p>Selain dekat dengan bandara, hotel ini juga berada di area yang mudah dijangkau dari berbagai <strong>restoran lokal dan tempat makan populer</strong>, memungkinkan tamu untuk dengan mudah menikmati beragam kuliner khas Manado.</p><p>Hotel ini menawarkan berbagai fasilitas untuk kenyamanan tamu, termasuk <strong>resepsionis 24 jam, layanan concierge, layanan kamar, serta WiFi gratis di seluruh area hotel</strong>. Tersedia juga <strong>layanan transfer bandara</strong> bagi tamu yang membutuhkan transportasi yang praktis. Tamu dapat bersantai di <strong>teras hotel</strong> atau menikmati hidangan di <strong>restoran yang tersedia di dalam hotel</strong>.</p><p>Setiap kamar di hotel dirancang sederhana namun nyaman, dilengkapi dengan <strong>AC, TV layar datar, lemari pakaian, serta meja kerja</strong> yang cocok bagi tamu yang ingin tetap produktif selama menginap.</p><p>Hotel ini juga memiliki akses mudah menuju beberapa destinasi populer di Manado, di antaranya:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e6ac0f3b1818bb4409648aa5ba901472e\">sekitar <strong>12 km dari Kelenteng Ban Hin Kiong</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed9c1e69dcb188e4d90692eb9c8171b2f\">sekitar <strong>12 km dari Museum Negeri Provinsi Sulawesi Utara</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e4476c26271817f53a56cb9606ede9c6b\">sekitar <strong>12 km dari Pelabuhan Manado</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e32076d5c75e29c55f4efed0dc3ff4d81\">sekitar <strong>33 km dari Gunung Lokon</strong></li></ul><p>Dengan lokasi yang strategis, dekat bandara serta berbagai restoran, <strong>Mel\'s Inn Manado</strong> menjadi pilihan tepat bagi tamu yang mencari akomodasi nyaman dan praktis di Manado.</p>', '<p>Located in <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>Mel\'s Inn Manado</strong> is a comfortable 2-star accommodation that offers a convenient stay for both business and leisure travelers. The hotel is located close to <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, making it an ideal choice for guests with early morning or late-night flights.</p><p>In addition to its proximity to the airport, the hotel is also surrounded by <strong>various local restaurants and dining options</strong>, allowing guests to easily explore the rich culinary flavors of Manado.</p><p>The hotel provides several facilities designed for guest comfort, including a <strong>24-hour front desk, concierge service, room service, and free WiFi throughout the property</strong>. <strong>Airport transfer services</strong> are also available for added convenience. Guests can relax on the <strong>hotel terrace</strong> or enjoy meals at the <strong>on-site restaurant</strong>.</p><p>Each room is simply designed yet comfortable, featuring <strong>air conditioning, a flat-screen TV, a wardrobe, and a work desk</strong>, making it suitable for both relaxation and productivity.</p><p>The hotel also offers easy access to several popular attractions in Manado, including:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"efaaf0a52f69cbf0783a48d25ef0ec234\">about <strong>12 km from Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8aaf95d501a444e5bec84017cfa66eaf\">about <strong>12 km from North Sulawesi State Museum</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e60b49034805744f61d1e61810050bc42\">about <strong>12 km from Manado Harbor</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e470cb4fc1b6ac894e09c862dd56499b2\">about <strong>33 km from Mount Lokon</strong></li></ul><p>With its strategic location near the airport and a variety of restaurants, <strong>Mel\'s Inn Manado</strong> is a great choice for travelers looking for a practical and comfortable stay in Manado.</p>', '<p>북술라웨시의 도시 **마나도**에 위치한 <strong>멜스 인 마나도</strong>는 편리한 위치와 합리적인 가격을 제공하는 2성급 호텔입니다. 호텔은 **사무 라툴랑이 국제공항**과 가까워 이른 아침이나 늦은 밤 항공편을 이용하는 여행객에게 매우 편리합니다.</p><p>또한 호텔 주변에는 <strong>다양한 레스토랑과 현지 음식점</strong>이 있어 마나도의 다양한 요리를 쉽게 즐길 수 있습니다.</p><p>호텔에서는 <strong>24시간 프런트 데스크, 컨시어지 서비스, 룸서비스, 전 구역 무료 Wi-Fi</strong>를 제공합니다. 또한 <strong>공항 셔틀 서비스</strong>도 이용할 수 있습니다. 투숙객은 <strong>호텔 테라스</strong>에서 휴식을 취하거나 <strong>호텔 레스토랑</strong>에서 식사를 즐길 수 있습니다.</p><p>객실은 심플하면서도 편안하게 설계되어 있으며 <strong>에어컨, 평면 TV, 옷장, 업무용 책상</strong>이 갖춰져 있습니다.</p><p>호텔은 다음과 같은 명소와도 가까운 거리에 있습니다:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ed7ffef7e300a499aca05991efc08e843\"><strong>반힌키옹 사원</strong> 약 12km</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e99b72b465e0e9c39655e1f19edc4a40e\"><strong>북술라웨시 주립 박물관</strong> 약 12km</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e3f84da6c74a110928cd7e9b7f17b7a64\"><strong>마나도 항구</strong> 약 12km</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8ddda8c4723a23085282d5da3389ae1b\"><strong>로콘 산</strong> 약 33km</li></ul><p>공항과 레스토랑이 가까운 편리한 위치를 자랑하는 <strong>Mel\'s Inn Manado</strong>는 마나도 여행을 위한 실용적인 숙박 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>位于印度尼西亚北苏拉威西 <strong>万鸦老</strong> 的 <strong>Mel\'s Inn Manado</strong> 是一家舒适实用的二星级酒店，非常适合商务及休闲旅客入住。酒店靠近 <strong>Sam Ratulangi 国际机场</strong>，对于需要搭乘早班或晚班航班的旅客来说十分便利。</p><p>此外，酒店周边还有 <strong>许多当地餐厅和美食选择</strong>，宾客可以轻松品尝到万鸦老丰富多样的当地美食。</p><p>酒店提供多种便利设施，包括 <strong>24小时前台服务、礼宾服务、客房服务以及全区域免费 Wi-Fi</strong>。酒店还提供 <strong>机场接送服务</strong>。宾客可以在 <strong>酒店露台</strong>放松身心，或在 <strong>酒店餐厅</strong>享用美食。</p><p>每间客房设计简洁舒适，配备 <strong>空调、平板电视、衣柜以及办公桌</strong>，既适合休息也适合工作。</p><p>酒店距离多个热门景点也十分方便：</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e21c0d0252f96753704afeefb8415a3a2\"><strong>Ban Hin Kiong 寺庙</strong> 约12公里</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e4378d8f02839fceda752e00c2aea7c71\"><strong>北苏拉威西州博物馆</strong> 约12公里</li><li data-list-item-id=\"edbd3a5edb5ab2617aef58f963d4b3103\"><strong>万鸦老港口</strong> 约12公里</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e32ca28ab136251af151b0b09118d780d\"><strong>洛孔火山</strong> 约33公里</li></ul><p>凭借靠近机场、周边餐厅丰富以及舒适实用的设施，<strong>Mel\'s Inn Manado</strong> 是在万鸦老旅行时方便且经济的住宿选择。</p>', '[\"WiFi gratis\",\"Antar-jemput bandara\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Restoran\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/E3uxzFcw3pX8xvCkKLwlFx1FDQ4zXZYB5ovYF0aI.webp', '2026-04-21 08:33:54', '2026-04-21 08:33:54'),
(63, 'Highland Resort & Nature Tours', 'highland-resort-nature-tours-ry7yTc', 'Tomohon', 'resort', 2, '<p>erletak di dataran tinggi dengan ketinggian sekitar <strong>650 meter di atas permukaan laut</strong>, <strong>Highland Resort and Spa</strong> menawarkan suasana pegunungan yang sejuk, udara segar, serta pemandangan spektakuler menuju <strong>Gunung Lokon</strong> yang terkenal. Resort ini merupakan tempat yang sempurna bagi wisatawan yang ingin menikmati ketenangan alam sekaligus kenyamanan modern.</p><p>Dikelilingi oleh alam hijau yang asri, resort ini menghadirkan <strong>pondok-pondok kayu bergaya alami</strong> yang menghadap langsung ke perbukitan. Setiap kamar dirancang untuk memberikan kenyamanan maksimal dan dilengkapi dengan <strong>TV satelit, kelambu, serta kamar mandi pribadi dengan air panas dan dingin</strong>. Beberapa kamar juga dilengkapi dengan <strong>minibar dan kulkas</strong> untuk menambah kenyamanan selama menginap.</p><p>Para tamu dapat bersantai di <strong>Alam Spa</strong>, yang menawarkan berbagai perawatan relaksasi seperti <strong>pijat aromaterapi dan refleksi kaki</strong>, sempurna untuk menyegarkan tubuh setelah menikmati aktivitas di alam terbuka. Resort ini juga menyediakan <strong>Wi-Fi gratis</strong> serta restoran yang menyajikan hidangan <strong>khas Indonesia yang lezat</strong>.</p><p>Lokasinya sangat strategis untuk menjelajahi berbagai destinasi wisata di sekitarnya:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e1c92d8ea8924c2c030193d1b3ba1bef2\">sekitar <strong>10 menit berkendara dari Tomohon</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee744500316b566f58948f5430ff6383f\">sekitar <strong>15 menit dari Gunung Mahawu</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"efff4d26e969bcea4173251c22cb1137d\">sekitar <strong>1 jam dari Manado</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb930134b160579f38a3f60aa6400ac37\">sekitar <strong>1 jam dari Bandara Internasional Sam Ratulangi</strong></li></ul><p>Melalui meja layanan wisata, tamu juga dapat mengatur perjalanan menarik ke berbagai destinasi alam seperti <strong>Air Terjun Kali</strong>, <strong>Gua Jepang Tomohon</strong>, dan <strong>Pemandian Air Panas Ranopaso</strong>.</p><p>Dengan udara pegunungan yang sejuk, panorama alam yang indah, serta suasana yang tenang dan romantis, <strong>Highland Resort and Spa</strong> adalah tempat ideal untuk beristirahat, berbulan madu, atau menikmati liburan alam di Sulawesi Utara.</p>', '<p>Located at an altitude of <strong>650 meters above sea level</strong>, <strong>Highland Resort and Spa</strong> offers refreshing mountain air and breathtaking views of the famous <strong>Mount Lokon</strong>. Surrounded by lush greenery, this resort provides a peaceful retreat for travelers seeking relaxation and natural beauty.</p><p>The resort features charming <strong>wooden cottages overlooking scenic hills</strong>, creating a cozy and tranquil atmosphere. Each standard room is equipped with <strong>satellite TV, mosquito nets, and a private bathroom with hot and cold shower facilities</strong>. Selected rooms also include a <strong>minibar and refrigerator</strong> for additional convenience.</p><p>Guests can unwind at <strong>Alam Spa</strong>, where rejuvenating treatments such as <strong>aromatherapy baths and relaxing foot reflexology</strong> are available. The resort also offers <strong>free Wi-Fi</strong> and an on-site restaurant serving delicious <strong>Indonesian cuisine</strong>.</p><p>The resort is conveniently located near several attractions:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e40a22f499dbb79c8ff476f763d46cb99\">about <strong>10 minutes from Tomohon</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e888217158289458e8e14ec60d7bc0c1c\">about <strong>15 minutes from Mount Mahawu</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e6076c96c8d2e00cf5d9757ba07de035a\">about <strong>1 hour from Manado</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e984ca357fd8a57216df576d2411eb586\">about <strong>1 hour from Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong></li></ul><p>Guests can also arrange exciting day trips through the tour desk to nearby natural attractions such as <strong>Kali Waterfall</strong>, <strong>Japanese Cave Tomohon</strong>, and <strong>Ranopaso Hot Springs</strong>.</p><p>With its cool mountain climate, stunning natural scenery, and peaceful ambiance, <strong>Highland Resort and Spa</strong> is the perfect destination for a relaxing getaway, honeymoon, or nature escape in North Sulawesi.</p>', '<p>해발 약 <strong>650m</strong>의 고지대에 위치한 <strong>하이랜드 리조트 앤 스파</strong>는 시원한 산악 기후와 함께 유명한 **로콘 화산**의 아름다운 전망을 제공합니다. 울창한 자연 속에 자리 잡은 이 리조트는 평화롭고 편안한 휴식을 원하는 여행객들에게 완벽한 휴양지입니다.</p><p>리조트는 언덕을 향해 자리한 <strong>전통 목조 코티지</strong>로 이루어져 있으며 아늑하고 자연 친화적인 분위기를 제공합니다. 모든 객실에는 <strong>위성 TV, 모기장, 온수 및 냉수 샤워가 가능한 전용 욕실</strong>이 마련되어 있습니다. 일부 객실에는 <strong>미니바와 냉장고</strong>도 준비되어 있습니다.</p><p>투숙객은 <strong>Alam Spa</strong>에서 <strong>아로마 테라피, 발 마사지(리플렉솔로지)</strong> 등 다양한 힐링 트리트먼트를 즐기며 몸과 마음을 재충전할 수 있습니다. 또한 리조트 내 레스토랑에서는 <strong>인도네시아 요리</strong>를 맛볼 수 있으며 <strong>무료 Wi-Fi</strong>도 제공됩니다.</p><p>주요 위치:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"eea6a8f3df34d64d563076fc86bc3315f\">**토모혼**까지 차량 약 10분</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea864d699308a683f27e765c2e239daa0\">**마하우 화산**까지 약 15분</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e082f1e4e05fe51734a97b3ed235feb5a\">**마나도**까지 약 1시간</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebec8983c72fbc8d86c15ffcc39df88f0\">**사무 라툴랑이 국제공항**까지 약 1시간</li></ul><p>또한 투어 데스크를 통해 <strong>칼리 폭포</strong>, <strong>일본 동굴 토모혼</strong>, <strong>라노파소 온천</strong> 등 자연 관광지를 방문하는 여행도 예약할 수 있습니다.</p>', '<p>坐落于海拔约 <strong>650米</strong> 的高地，<strong>Highland Resort and Spa</strong> 拥有清新凉爽的山间气候，并可欣赏到著名 <strong>洛孔火山</strong> 的壮丽景色。度假村被郁郁葱葱的自然景观环绕，是远离城市喧嚣、放松身心的理想之地。</p><p>度假村设有 <strong>面向山丘景观的木屋别墅</strong>，营造出温馨而宁静的氛围。所有标准客房均配备 <strong>卫星电视、蚊帐以及带冷热水淋浴的私人浴室</strong>，部分客房还配有 <strong>迷你吧和冰箱</strong>，为宾客提供更多便利。</p><p>宾客可以在 <strong>Alam Spa</strong> 享受 <strong>芳香疗法浴和足底按摩</strong>，放松身心。度假村还提供 <strong>免费 Wi-Fi</strong>，并设有餐厅供应美味的 <strong>印尼特色美食</strong>。</p><p>度假村地理位置便利：</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e79081d111a71f24a48450fb09ac28c24\">距离 <strong>托莫洪</strong> 约10分钟车程</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eaa11aeabd2b184783ebb9b213abedaa1\">距离 <strong>马哈乌火山</strong> 约15分钟车程</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb921004eeac8f664c6a40f9775c3842a\">距离 <strong>万鸦老</strong> 约1小时车程</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eccf25b78015db8c8ebc90c04695474cf\">距离 <strong>Sam Ratulangi 国际机场</strong> 约1小时车程</li></ul><p>此外，宾客还可以通过旅游服务台安排前往 <strong>Kali 瀑布</strong>、<strong>托莫洪日本洞穴</strong> 以及 <strong>Ranopaso 温泉</strong> 等自然景点的一日游。</p>', '[\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Antar-jemput bandara\",\"WiFi gratis\",\"Restoran\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Kamar keluarga\",\"Pembuat teh\\/kopi di semua kamar\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/wIY7S02hXhlDdnGdnSx6sekb5qbUGwOxR31q57P1.jpg', '2026-04-21 09:10:25', '2026-04-21 09:10:25');
INSERT INTO `hotels` (`id`, `name`, `slug`, `location`, `category`, `stars`, `description`, `description_en`, `description_ko`, `description_zh`, `facilities`, `primary_image`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(64, 'Travello Hotel Manado', 'travello-hotel-manado-6ThOt7', 'Manado', 'city_hotel', 3, '<p>Terletak di kawasan strategis pusat kota, Travelo Hotel Manado menawarkan pengalaman menginap modern dengan konsep praktis dan nyaman. Hotel ini menjadi pilihan ideal bagi wisatawan maupun pelaku perjalanan bisnis yang mencari akomodasi terjangkau tanpa mengorbankan kualitas dan kenyamanan.</p><p>Dengan desain interior yang minimalis dan bersih, setiap kamar dirancang untuk memberikan suasana istirahat yang tenang. Fasilitas kamar meliputi AC, TV layar datar, WiFi gratis, meja kerja, serta kamar mandi pribadi dengan perlengkapan mandi lengkap. Tata ruang yang efisien membuat hotel ini cocok untuk tamu dengan mobilitas tinggi.</p><p>Hotel ini juga menyediakan berbagai fasilitas penunjang seperti restoran dengan pilihan menu lokal dan internasional, layanan resepsionis 24 jam, serta area parkir yang aman. Pelayanan yang ramah dan profesional menambah kenyamanan selama Anda menginap.</p><p>Berlokasi dekat dengan berbagai pusat aktivitas kota, hotel ini memberikan akses mudah ke kawasan Megamas Manado yang terkenal dengan kuliner dan hiburannya, serta Manado Town Square untuk kebutuhan belanja.</p><p>Bagi Anda yang ingin menikmati keindahan alam, Bunaken National Park dapat dijangkau sebagai destinasi wisata bahari unggulan. Sementara itu, Sam Ratulangi International Airport berjarak sekitar 30 menit perjalanan dari hotel.</p><p>Dengan lokasi strategis, fasilitas lengkap, dan harga yang terjangkau, Travelo Hotel Manado menjadi pilihan tepat untuk pengalaman menginap yang praktis, nyaman, dan efisien di kota Manado.</p>', '<p>Strategically located in the city center, Travelo Hotel Manado offers a modern stay experience with a practical and comfortable concept. It is an ideal choice for both leisure and business travelers seeking affordable accommodation without compromising quality.</p><p>Featuring a clean and minimalist interior design, each room is thoughtfully arranged to provide a relaxing atmosphere. Room amenities include air conditioning, a flat-screen TV, free WiFi, a work desk, and a private bathroom with complete toiletries. Its efficient layout makes it perfect for guests with high mobility.</p><p>The hotel also provides supporting facilities such as a restaurant serving local and international dishes, a 24-hour front desk, and secure parking. Friendly and professional service enhances the overall stay experience.</p><p>Conveniently located near key city attractions, the hotel offers easy access to Megamas Manado, known for its dining and entertainment scene, and Manado Town Square for shopping needs.</p><p>For nature lovers, Bunaken National Park is easily accessible as a top marine tourism destination. Meanwhile, Sam Ratulangi International Airport is approximately a 30-minute drive from the hotel.</p><p>With its strategic location, complete facilities, and affordable rates, Travelo Hotel Manado is the perfect choice for a practical, comfortable, and efficient stay in Manado.</p>', '<p>마나도 도심에 위치한 Travelo Hotel Manado는 실용적이고 편안한 현대적인 숙박 경험을 제공합니다. 합리적인 가격과 좋은 위치를 갖춘 이 호텔은 관광객과 비즈니스 여행객 모두에게 이상적인 선택입니다.</p><p>깔끔하고 미니멀한 인테리어의 객실은 에어컨, 평면 TV, 무료 Wi-Fi, 업무용 책상, 그리고 어메니티가 구비된 전용 욕실을 갖추고 있어 편안한 휴식을 제공합니다.</p><p>호텔은 레스토랑, 24시간 프런트 데스크, 주차 공간 등 다양한 편의시설을 제공하며, 친절하고 전문적인 서비스로 만족도를 높입니다.</p><p>또한 Megamas Manado 및 Manado Town Square과 가까워 쇼핑과 식사를 즐기기에 매우 편리합니다.</p><p>자연을 사랑하는 여행객은 Bunaken National Park을 쉽게 방문할 수 있으며, Sam Ratulangi International Airport까지는 약 30분이 소요됩니다.</p><p>전략적인 위치와 합리적인 가격, 그리고 편안한 시설을 갖춘 Travelo Hotel Manado는 실용적인 숙박을 원하는 분들에게 최적의 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>位于万鸦老市中心的 Travelo Hotel Manado，以现代简约的设计风格提供舒适且高性价比的住宿体验。无论是商务出行还是休闲旅游，这里都是理想之选。</p><p>酒店客房设计简洁舒适，配备空调、平板电视、免费WiFi、办公桌以及带齐全洗浴用品的独立浴室，营造出安静放松的休息环境，非常适合高效率出行的旅客。</p><p>酒店还提供多项便利设施，包括供应本地及国际美食的餐厅、24小时前台服务以及安全的停车区域。贴心且专业的服务让您的入住更加愉快。</p><p>酒店地理位置优越，靠近 Megamas Manado 娱乐美食区，以及 Manado Town Square 购物中心。</p><p>此外，酒店也是前往著名海洋旅游胜地 Bunaken National Park 的便捷出发点。距离 Sam Ratulangi International Airport 约30分钟车程。</p><p>凭借优越的位置、完善的设施以及实惠的价格，Travelo Hotel Manado 是追求便捷与舒适住宿体验旅客的理想选择。</p>', '[\"Restoran\",\"Bar\\/Lounge\",\"Sudah termasuk sarapan\",\"Layanan kamar\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/ioisam39gppvo5JgSO2kgA8i7NF1nOvqlPMQrcpa.webp', '2026-04-21 09:16:00', '2026-04-22 01:48:51'),
(65, 'Jle\'s Hotel Manado', 'jles-hotel-manado-DUiBnK', 'Jalan Walanda Maramis Lingk. III', 'city_hotel', 2, '<p>Berlokasi di Manado, 1,8 km dari Pantai Megamas, JLE\'S Hotel menawarkan pemandangan kota. Dengan lounge bersama, hotel bintang 2 ini memiliki kamar ber-AC dengan WiFi gratis, masing-masing dilengkapi dengan kamar mandi pribadi. Akomodasi ini menyediakan karaoke dan layanan kamar.\r\n\r\nSemua unit di hotel dilengkapi area tempat duduk dan TV. Di JLE\'S Hotel, setiap kamar dilengkapi seprai dan handuk.\r\n\r\nSarapan yang meliputi pilihan prasmanan, Asia, dan halal tersedia harian. Anda akan menemukan restoran yang menyajikan masakan Asia di JLE\'S Hotel. Pilihan hidangan vegetarian dan halal juga dapat dipesan.\r\n\r\nStaf resepsionis yang bisa menggunakan bahasa Inggris dan bahasa Indonesia siap membantu Anda sepanjang hari.\r\n\r\nTempat-tempat menarik yang populer di dekat hotel termasuk Pelabuhan Manado, Kelenteng Ban Hin Kiong, dan Museum Negeri Provinsi Sulawesi Utara. Bandara Bandara Sam Ratulangi berjarak sejauh 12 km.</p>', '<p>Located in Manado, 1.8 km from Megamas Beach, JLE\'S Hotel offers city views. Featuring a shared lounge, this 2-star hotel provides air-conditioned rooms with free WiFi, each equipped with a private bathroom. The accommodation also offers karaoke and room service.</p><p>All units at the hotel are equipped with a seating area and a TV. At JLE\'S Hotel, every room includes bed linen and towels.</p><p>A daily breakfast is available with buffet, Asian, and halal options. You will find a restaurant serving Asian cuisine at JLE\'S Hotel, with vegetarian and halal dishes also available upon request.</p><p>The reception staff, who speak English and Indonesian, are ready to assist you throughout the day.</p><p>Popular points of interest near the hotel include Manado Harbor, Ban Hin Kiong Temple, and the North Sulawesi State Museum. Sam Ratulangi Airport is 12 km away.</p>', '<p>마나도에 위치한 JLE\'S 호텔은 메가마스 해변에서 1.8km 거리에 있으며, 도시 전망을 제공합니다. 공용 라운지를 갖춘 이 2성급 호텔은 무료 Wi-Fi와 전용 욕실이 마련된 에어컨 객실을 제공합니다. 또한 노래방과 룸서비스도 이용하실 수 있습니다.</p><p>호텔의 모든 객실에는 휴식 공간과 TV가 구비되어 있습니다. JLE\'S 호텔의 모든 객실에는 침대 린넨과 수건이 제공됩니다.</p><p>매일 조식은 뷔페식, 아시아식, 할랄 옵션으로 제공됩니다. 호텔 내 레스토랑에서는 아시아 요리를 즐기실 수 있으며, 채식 및 할랄 메뉴도 요청 시 제공됩니다.</p><p>영어와 인도네시아어를 구사하는 프런트 직원이 하루 종일 고객을 도와드립니다.</p><p>호텔 인근의 인기 명소로는 마나도 항구, 반힌키옹 사원, 북술라웨시 주립 박물관이 있습니다. 사무 라툴랑이 공항은 12km 거리에 있습니다.</p>', '<p>JLE\'S 酒店位于马纳多，距离Megamas海滩1.8公里，提供城市景观。作为一家二星级酒店，酒店设有共用休息室，提供带空调的客房、免费WiFi以及配备私人浴室的住宿。酒店还提供卡拉OK和客房服务。</p><p>酒店的所有客房均配有休息区和电视。在JLE\'S 酒店，每间客房均配备床上用品和毛巾。</p><p>酒店每日提供自助式、亚洲风味及清真早餐。酒店内设有餐厅，供应亚洲美食，并可根据需求提供素食和清真菜品。</p><p>前台工作人员会讲英语和印尼语，可全天为客人提供帮助。</p><p>酒店附近的热门景点包括马纳多港、关帝庙（Ban Hin Kiong）以及北苏拉威西州立博物馆。萨姆·拉图兰吉机场距离酒店约12公里。</p>', '[\"WiFi gratis\",\"Antar-jemput bandara\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Restoran\",\"Pembuat teh\\/kopi di semua kamar\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/kqH30pJgo32cKPJO6TnwRkKb6SAo6xnavYoIJefF.jpg', '2026-04-22 01:51:27', '2026-04-22 07:39:06'),
(66, 'THREE R HOTEL', 'three-r-hotel-PTaITN', 'Jl Pangeran Hidayat No 19, Wawonasa', 'city_hotel', 3, '<p>Three R Hotel Manado menghadirkan pengalaman menginap yang nyaman dengan suasana modern dan pelayanan yang ramah. Berlokasi strategis di Kota Manado, hotel ini memudahkan akses ke pusat bisnis, tempat kuliner, dan berbagai destinasi wisata populer. Kamar-kamarnya dirancang dengan gaya minimalis yang bersih dan fungsional, dilengkapi fasilitas yang mendukung kenyamanan tamu. Cocok untuk perjalanan bisnis maupun liburan, Three R Hotel Manado menawarkan akomodasi praktis dengan harga yang terjangkau.</p>', '<p>Three R Hotel Manado offers a comfortable stay with a modern atmosphere and friendly service. Strategically located in the city, the hotel provides easy access to business centers, culinary spots, and popular attractions. The rooms are designed with a clean and functional minimalist style, equipped with essential amenities to ensure a pleasant stay. Whether for business or leisure, Three R Hotel Manado is a practical and affordable accommodation choice.</p>', '<p>Three R 호텔 마나도는 현대적인 분위기와 친절한 서비스로 편안한 숙박을 제공합니다. 마나도 시내의 전략적인 위치에 자리 잡고 있어 비즈니스 지역, 맛집, 주요 관광지로의 이동이 편리합니다. 객실은 깔끔하고 실용적인 미니멀리스트 스타일로 설계되었으며, 편안한 숙박을 위한 기본 시설이 잘 갖추어져 있습니다. 비즈니스 여행과 휴가 모두에 적합한 합리적인 숙소입니다.</p>', '<p>Three R 马纳多酒店为您提供舒适的住宿体验，融合现代设计与热情周到的服务。酒店位于马纳多市中心的优越位置，方便前往商业区、美食地点及热门旅游景点。客房采用简约实用的设计风格，配备齐全的基础设施，为您带来愉快的入住体验。无论是商务出行还是休闲度假，Three R 马纳多酒店都是经济实惠且便捷的理想选择。</p>', '[\"Kolam Renang\",\"WiFi\",\"AC\",\"Resepsionis 24 Jam\",\"Lift\",\"Restoran\",\"Penyimpanan Barang\",\"Parkir Gratis\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/jB7OGyuc4NoHzIGzMUPWIIddukTzsVUwRuKoWVmF.webp', '2026-04-22 07:19:33', '2026-04-24 03:11:16'),
(67, 'Sutan Raja Manado Hotel and Convention Centre', 'sutan-raja-manado-hotel-and-convention-centre-TQA6LV', 'Jl. Raya Manado Bitung, Watutumou II', 'city_hotel', 4, '<p>Terletak sekitar 10 km dari pusat kota Manado, Sutan Raja Hotel and Convention Centre menawarkan akomodasi berbintang 4 plus dengan fasilitas kolam renang yang dikelilingi taman, pusat kebugaran yang lengkap dan lapangan tenis. WiFi gratis berkecepatan tinggi dapat diakses di seluruh properti.</p><p>Didekorasi dengan lantai parket, kamar ber-AC yang cerah ini memiliki balkon pribadi dengan pemandangan gunung dan padang rumput yang hijau. Setiap kamar dilengkapi dengan TV satelit layar datar, meja kerja dan fasilitas pembuat kopi/teh. Kamar mandi dalam hadir dengan pengering rambut dan peralatan mandi. Suite memiliki Jacuzzi dan area ruang tamu dan ruang makan yang terpisah.</p><p>Tonsea Resto menyajikan berbagai hidangan klasik Asia dan Eropa untuk santapan sepanjang hari, sementara bar tepi kolam renang memiliki berbagai pilihan minuman, es krim dan makanan ringan. Dengan pemandangan gunung yang indah, Klabat Resto menawarkan pengalaman bersantap outdoor untuk para tamu sambil menikmati langit malam yang menawan. Layanan kamar 24 jam juga tersedia untuk pilihan bersantap dalam kamar.</p><p>Sutan Raja Hotel and Convention Centre memiliki klub dan 10 ruang karaoke sebagai pilihan untuk mengisi waktu luangmu. Tamu juga dapat bersantai dan memanjakan diri dengan layanan pijat tradisional yang tersedia. Layanan yang tersedia lainnya termasuk resepsionis 24 jam</p><p>Daerah Super prioritas Pariwisata Likupang hanya 1 jam dari hotel ini dan Pantai Malalayang di kota manado dan Air Terjun Tunan berlokasi sekitar 20 km dari Sutan Raja Hotel and Convention Centre, sementara Patung Yesus Memberkati dan Jembatan Soekarno terletak sekitar 12 km. Bandara Internasional Sam Ratulangi dapat ditempuh dalam 25 menit dengan berkendara dan layanan pengantaran bandara tersedia dengan biaya tambahan.</p>', '<p>Located approximately 10 km from the city center of Manado, <strong>Sutanraja Hotel and Convention Centre Manado</strong> offers 4-star plus accommodation featuring a swimming pool surrounded by lush gardens, a fully equipped fitness center, and a tennis court. High-speed free WiFi is available throughout the property.</p><p>Decorated with parquet flooring, the bright air-conditioned rooms feature a private balcony with views of the mountains and green fields. Each room is equipped with a flat-screen satellite TV, a work desk, and coffee/tea making facilities. The en suite bathroom includes a hairdryer and toiletries. Suites offer a Jacuzzi along with separate living and dining areas.</p><p>Tonsea Resto serves a variety of classic Asian and European dishes for all-day dining, while the poolside bar offers a selection of drinks, ice cream, and light snacks. With beautiful mountain views, Klabat Resto provides an outdoor dining experience where guests can enjoy the charming night sky. A 24-hour room service is also available for in-room dining.</p><p>Sutan Raja Hotel and Convention Centre features a club and 10 karaoke rooms for leisure activities. Guests can also relax and indulge in traditional massage services. Other facilities include a 24-hour front desk.</p><p>The super-priority tourism area of Likupang is only 1 hour from the hotel, while Malalayang Beach in Manado and Tunan Waterfall are located about 20 km away. The Blessing Christ Statue and Soekarno Bridge are around 12 km from the hotel. Sam Ratulangi International Airport can be reached within a 25-minute drive, and airport transfer service is available at an additional charge.</p>', '<p>마나도 시내에서 약 10km 거리에 위치한 <strong>Sutanraja Hotel and Convention Centre Manado</strong>는 정원으로 둘러싸인 수영장, 완비된 피트니스 센터, 테니스 코트를 갖춘 4성급 플러스 호텔입니다. 호텔 전 구역에서 고속 무료 Wi-Fi를 이용하실 수 있습니다.</p><p>객실은 파켓 바닥으로 꾸며져 있으며, 밝고 쾌적한 에어컨 객실에는 산과 푸른 들판 전망의 전용 발코니가 있습니다. 각 객실에는 평면 위성 TV, 업무용 책상, 커피/차 메이커가 구비되어 있습니다. 전용 욕실에는 헤어드라이어와 세면도구가 제공됩니다. 스위트룸에는 자쿠지와 별도의 거실 및 식사 공간이 마련되어 있습니다.</p><p>Tonsea 레스토랑에서는 아시아 및 유럽식 요리를 하루 종일 즐길 수 있으며, 수영장 바에서는 다양한 음료, 아이스크림 및 간단한 스낵을 제공합니다. 아름다운 산 전망을 자랑하는 Klabat 레스토랑에서는 야외에서 멋진 밤하늘을 감상하며 식사를 즐기실 수 있습니다. 또한 24시간 룸서비스도 제공됩니다.</p><p>호텔에는 클럽과 10개의 노래방 시설이 있어 여가 시간을 즐길 수 있으며, 전통 마사지 서비스도 이용하실 수 있습니다. 그 외에도 24시간 운영되는 프런트 데스크가 마련되어 있습니다.</p><p>리쿠팡 슈퍼 우선 관광 지역은 호텔에서 약 1시간 거리에 있으며, 말랄라양 해변과 투난 폭포는 약 20km 거리에 있습니다. 축복의 그리스도상과 수카르노 다리는 약 12km 거리에 위치해 있습니다. 사무 라툴랑이 국제공항은 차량으로 약 25분 거리에 있으며, 유료 공항 셔틀 서비스도 제공됩니다.</p>', '<p>位于距离马纳多市中心约10公里的 <strong>Sutanraja Hotel and Convention Centre Manado</strong> 提供四星级以上的住宿体验，配备被花园环绕的游泳池、完善的健身中心以及网球场。酒店全区域提供高速免费WiFi。</p><p>客房铺设木地板，明亮宽敞，配有空调，并设有可欣赏山景和绿色草地的私人阳台。每间客房均配备平板卫星电视、办公桌以及咖啡/茶冲泡设施。独立浴室提供吹风机和洗浴用品。套房还设有按摩浴缸以及独立的起居和用餐区域。</p><p>Tonsea餐厅全天供应亚洲及欧洲经典美食，而池畔酒吧则提供各种饮品、冰淇淋及小吃。Klabat餐厅拥有美丽的山景，提供户外用餐体验，让客人在迷人的夜空下享用美食。此外，酒店还提供24小时客房服务。</p><p>酒店设有俱乐部及10间卡拉OK房，供客人休闲娱乐。客人还可以享受传统按摩服务放松身心。其他设施包括24小时前台服务。</p><p>距离酒店约1小时车程的是利库庞超级优先旅游区，马纳多的马拉拉扬海滩及图南瀑布距离酒店约20公里。祝福基督雕像和苏加诺大桥距离酒店约12公里。萨姆·拉图兰吉国际机场车程约25分钟，酒店提供额外收费的机场接送服务。</p>', '[\"Kolam Renang\",\"WiFi\",\"Pusat Kebugaran\",\"tiket Green\",\"AC\",\"Resepsionis 24 Jam\",\"Lift\",\"Restoran\",\"Fasilitas Anak\",\"Ruang Tamu\",\"Penyimpanan Barang\",\"Fasilitas Ramah Difabel\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/QhmXjBMO0A1VUD8TD9ZWbEvEXUZd9nOdU78Gyi9N.jpg', '2026-04-22 08:15:18', '2026-04-22 08:15:18'),
(68, 'The Sentra Manado', 'the-sentra-manado-TbKwRf', 'Jalan Ir. Soekarno,', 'city_hotel', 4, '<p>The Sentra Hotel Manado memiliki segala fasilitas penunjang bisnis untuk Anda dan kolega. Jika Anda memiliki agenda kegiatan yang membutuhkan ruangan besar, maka The Sentra Hotel Manado adalah pilihan yang tepat.&nbsp;</p><p>Hotel ini memiliki ruang pertemuan yang luas dan dilengkapi dengan berbagai fasilitas penunjang. Pengalaman menginap Anda tak akan terlupakan berkat pelayanan istimewa yang disertai oleh berbagai fasilitas pendukung untuk kenyamanan Anda. Pusat kebugaran menjadi salah satu fasilitas yang wajib Anda coba saat menginap di tempat ini.&nbsp;</p><p>Tersedia kolam renang untuk Anda bersantai sendiri maupun bersama teman dan keluarga. Resepsionis siap 24 jam untuk melayani proses check-in, check-out dan kebutuhan Anda yang lain. Jangan ragu untuk menghubungi resepsionis, kami siap melayani Anda. Terdapat restoran yang menyajikan menu lezat ala The Sentra Hotel Manado khusus untuk Anda. WiFi tersedia di seluruh area publik properti untuk membantu Anda tetap terhubung dengan keluarga dan teman.&nbsp;</p><p>The Sentra Hotel Manado adalah akomodasi dengan fasilitas baik dan kualitas pelayanan memuaskan menurut sebagian besar tamu. Pengalaman berkesan dan tak terlupakan akan Anda dapatkan selama menginap di hotel The Sentra Hotel Manado</p>', '<p><strong>The Sentra Hotel Manado</strong> offers complete business facilities for you and your colleagues.</p><p>If you have events or activities that require a large venue, The Sentra Hotel Manado is the perfect choice. The hotel features spacious meeting rooms equipped with various supporting facilities.</p><p>Your stay will be unforgettable thanks to the exceptional service combined with a wide range of facilities designed for your comfort.</p><p>The fitness center is one of the must-try facilities during your stay.</p><p>A swimming pool is also available for you to relax, whether alone or with friends and family.</p><p>The reception is available 24 hours to assist with check-in, check-out, and any other needs. Do not hesitate to contact the front desk, as the staff is always ready to serve you.</p><p>There is also a restaurant serving delicious signature dishes of The Sentra Hotel Manado exclusively for you.</p><p>WiFi is available throughout the public areas of the property to help you stay connected with family and friends.</p><p>The Sentra Hotel Manado is an accommodation known for its excellent facilities and satisfying service quality according to most guests.</p><p>A memorable and unforgettable experience awaits you during your stay at The Sentra Hotel Manado.</p>', '<p><strong>The Sentra Hotel Manado</strong>는 고객과 동료를 위한 다양한 비즈니스 시설을 갖추고 있습니다.</p><p>대규모 행사를 위한 공간이 필요하다면 이 호텔은 최적의 선택입니다. 넓은 회의실과 다양한 지원 시설을 제공합니다.</p><p>특별한 서비스와 다양한 편의시설 덕분에 잊지 못할 숙박 경험을 선사합니다.</p><p>피트니스 센터는 투숙 중 꼭 이용해 보셔야 할 시설 중 하나입니다.</p><p>수영장도 마련되어 있어 혼자 또는 가족, 친구와 함께 편안하게 휴식을 취할 수 있습니다.</p><p>프런트 데스크는 24시간 운영되어 체크인, 체크아웃 및 기타 요청 사항을 도와드립니다. 언제든지 문의하시면 친절하게 안내해 드립니다.</p><p>호텔 내 레스토랑에서는 The Sentra Hotel Manado만의 특별한 요리를 즐기실 수 있습니다.</p><p>공용 공간 전역에서 WiFi를 이용할 수 있어 가족 및 친구들과 계속 연락을 유지할 수 있습니다.</p><p>The Sentra Hotel Manado는 훌륭한 시설과 만족스러운 서비스로 많은 고객에게 좋은 평가를 받고 있는 숙소입니다.</p><p>이곳에서의 숙박은 기억에 남는 특별한 경험이 될 것입니다.</p>', '<p><strong>The Sentra Hotel Manado</strong> 为您和您的同事提供完善的商务设施。</p><p>如果您有需要大型场地的活动安排，这里将是理想的选择。酒店拥有宽敞的会议室，并配备各种完善的配套设施。</p><p>凭借优质的服务和完善的设施，您的入住体验将令人难以忘怀。</p><p>健身中心是您入住期间不可错过的设施之一。</p><p>酒店还设有游泳池，您可以独自或与家人朋友一起放松身心。</p><p>前台提供24小时服务，协助办理入住、退房及其他需求。如有需要，请随时联系前台，我们将竭诚为您服务。</p><p>酒店内设有餐厅，提供The Sentra Hotel Manado特色美味菜肴。</p><p>公共区域提供WiFi，方便您与家人和朋友保持联系。</p><p>根据大多数住客评价，The Sentra Hotel Manado拥有良好的设施和令人满意的服务质量。</p><p>在这里的入住体验将为您留下深刻而难忘的回忆。</p>', '[\"Kolam renang indoor\",\"Antar-jemput bandara\",\"Pusat kebugaran\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Parkir di lokasi\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Restoran\",\"Fasilitas tamu difabel\",\"Bar\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/8ytvn6MfrWXXnw1GB2NWOEZXKbQfjgEPfehZYPcA.jpg', '2026-04-22 08:47:09', '2026-04-22 08:50:31'),
(69, 'Hotel Gran Central', 'hotel-gran-central-LGEXoz', 'Jl. Jendral Sudirman No.45,', 'city_hotel', 2, '<p>Gran Central Hotel Manado menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang nyaman di jantung kota Manado dengan konsep modern dan praktis. Lokasinya yang strategis memudahkan akses ke pusat bisnis, area perbelanjaan, serta berbagai destinasi kuliner dan wisata populer.</p><p>Hotel ini menghadirkan kamar-kamar dengan desain minimalis yang nyaman, dilengkapi fasilitas lengkap untuk menunjang kebutuhan tamu. Dengan pelayanan yang ramah dan profesional, Gran Central Hotel Manado menjadi pilihan ideal bagi wisatawan maupun pelaku perjalanan bisnis yang mencari akomodasi berkualitas dengan harga terjangkau.</p>', '<p>Gran Central Hotel Manado offers a comfortable stay in the heart of the city with a modern and practical concept. Its strategic location provides easy access to business centers, shopping areas, as well as popular culinary and tourist destinations.</p><p>The hotel features rooms designed in a comfortable minimalist style, equipped with essential amenities to ensure a pleasant stay. With friendly and professional service, Gran Central Hotel Manado is an ideal choice for both business and leisure travelers seeking quality accommodation at an affordable price.</p>', '<p>그란 센트럴 호텔 마나도는 도심 중심부에 위치한 현대적이고 실용적인 숙박 시설로 편안한 경험을 제공합니다. 전략적인 위치 덕분에 비즈니스 지역, 쇼핑몰, 맛집 및 주요 관광지로의 이동이 편리합니다.</p><p>객실은 미니멀하고 편안한 디자인으로 구성되어 있으며, 쾌적한 숙박을 위한 다양한 편의시설을 갖추고 있습니다. 친절하고 전문적인 서비스와 함께 합리적인 가격으로 비즈니스 및 여행객 모두에게 이상적인 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>Gran Central 马纳多酒店位于市中心，提供现代而实用的舒适住宿体验。优越的地理位置方便前往商业中心、购物区以及热门美食和旅游景点。</p><p>酒店客房采用简约舒适的设计风格，配备完善的基础设施，确保宾客拥有愉快的入住体验。凭借友好专业的服务，Gran Central 马纳多酒店是商务与休闲旅客的理想之选，同时也提供高性价比的住宿体验</p>', '[\"Parkir valet\",\"Internet Kecepatan Tinggi Gratis (Wi-Fi)\",\"Bar\\/lounge\",\"Transportasi bandara\",\"Layanan pijat\",\"Penyimpanan koper\",\"AC\",\"Lemari Besi\",\"Dapur kecil\",\"Minibar\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/5F2m07QSAKGtkv5sGcduBqwUot959YfuDyt5KegS.webp', '2026-04-22 09:10:36', '2026-04-23 06:57:59'),
(70, 'Paradise Hotel Golf & Resort', 'paradise-hotel-golf-resort-I4BPlJ', 'Likupang', 'resort', 4, '<p>Dengan menginap di <strong>Casabaio Likupang Paradise Resort</strong> di kawasan indah Likupang, Anda akan menikmati suasana resor tepi pantai yang tenang dengan pemandangan alam tropis yang memukau. Resor ini berjarak sekitar <strong>33 km (±1 jam perjalanan) dari Bandara Internasional Sam Ratulangi</strong> dan sekitar <strong>42 km dari pusat Kota Manado</strong>, menjadikannya pilihan ideal untuk liburan yang jauh dari keramaian namun tetap mudah dijangkau.</p><p>Resor pantai ini berlokasi sekitar <strong>34,8 km dari Klub Golf Wenang</strong>, serta sekitar <strong>41–42 km dari Ban Hin Kiong dan Museum Negeri Sulawesi Utara</strong>.</p><p>Sambil para pencinta golf menikmati permainan di lapangan, Anda dapat memanfaatkan berbagai fasilitas rekreasi seperti <strong>kolam renang outdoor</strong>, area pantai, serta fasilitas santai lainnya. Fasilitas tambahan meliputi <strong>Wi-Fi gratis, layanan concierge, area BBQ</strong>, serta berbagai layanan kenyamanan bagi para tamu.</p><p>Untuk pengalaman kuliner, nikmati hidangan lezat di <strong>Kadera Restaurant</strong> yang menyajikan pilihan <strong>hidangan lokal dan internasional</strong> untuk makan siang maupun makan malam. Anda juga dapat bersantai dengan minuman favorit di <strong>bar/lounge atau pool bar</strong>, atau menikmati <strong>layanan kamar 24 jam</strong>.</p><p>Resor ini juga dilengkapi dengan <strong>pusat bisnis, koran gratis di lobi, serta layanan laundry dan dry cleaning</strong>. Layanan <strong>antar-jemput bandara</strong> tersedia dengan biaya tambahan, dan <strong>parkir mandiri gratis</strong> tersedia bagi tamu yang membawa kendaraan.</p><p>Nikmati kenyamanan menginap di salah satu dari <strong>151 kamar ber-AC</strong> yang dilengkapi <strong>minibar dan televisi LCD</strong>. Akses <strong>Wi-Fi gratis</strong> dan saluran TV kabel tersedia untuk hiburan Anda. Setiap kamar memiliki <strong>kamar mandi pribadi dengan shower, perlengkapan mandi gratis, serta pengering rambut</strong>, serta dilengkapi <strong>brankas dan meja kerja</strong>. Layanan housekeeping tersedia setiap hari untuk memastikan kenyamanan Anda selama menginap.</p>', '<p>Located in the beautiful coastal area of Likupang, <strong>Casabaio Likupang Paradise Resort</strong> offers a relaxing beachfront retreat surrounded by tropical scenery. The resort is approximately <strong>33 km (about 1 hour drive) from Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong> and about <strong>42 km from Manado City Center</strong>, making it easily accessible while still offering a peaceful getaway from the city.</p><p>This beachside resort is about <strong>34.8 km from Wenang Golf Club</strong> and around <strong>41–42 km from Ban Hin Kiong Temple and the North Sulawesi State Museum</strong>.</p><p>While golf enthusiasts in your group enjoy the nearby course, other guests can take advantage of recreational facilities such as the <strong>outdoor swimming pool</strong> and relaxing beachfront areas. Additional amenities include <strong>complimentary Wi-Fi, concierge services, and barbecue facilities</strong>.</p><p>For dining, enjoy delicious meals at <strong>Kadera Restaurant</strong>, serving a variety of <strong>local and international cuisine</strong> for lunch and dinner. Guests can also unwind with their favorite drink at the <strong>bar/lounge or poolside bar</strong>, or enjoy the convenience of <strong>24-hour room service</strong>.</p><p>Business travelers will appreciate facilities such as a <strong>business center, complimentary newspapers in the lobby, and laundry/dry-cleaning services</strong>. An <strong>airport shuttle service</strong> is available for an additional charge, and <strong>free self-parking</strong> is provided on site.</p><p>Make yourself at home in one of the <strong>151 air-conditioned rooms</strong> featuring <strong>minibars and LCD televisions</strong>. Complimentary <strong>wireless internet access</strong> and cable programming are available for your entertainment. Private bathrooms include <strong>showers, complimentary toiletries, and hair dryers</strong>, along with <strong>in-room safes and desks</strong>. Daily housekeeping ensures a comfortable stay.</p>', '<p>아름다운 리쿠팡 해안 지역에 위치한 **카사바이오 리쿠팡 파라다이스 리조트(Casabaio Likupang Paradise Resort)**는 열대 자연 속에서 편안한 휴식을 즐길 수 있는 해변 리조트입니다. 리조트는 <strong>사무 라툴랑이 국제공항에서 약 33km(차로 약 1시간)</strong>, <strong>마나도 시내 중심에서 약 42km</strong> 거리에 있어 접근성이 좋으면서도 조용한 휴양을 즐기기에 이상적인 위치에 있습니다.</p><p>이 해변 리조트는 <strong>웨낭 골프 클럽에서 약 34.8km</strong>, <strong>반 힌 키옹 사원 및 북술라웨시 주립 박물관에서 약 41~42km</strong> 떨어져 있습니다.</p><p>골프를 즐기는 동안 다른 투숙객들은 <strong>야외 수영장</strong>, 해변 휴식 공간 등 다양한 레저 시설을 이용할 수 있습니다. 또한 <strong>무료 Wi-Fi, 컨시어지 서비스, 바비큐 시설</strong> 등 다양한 편의시설이 제공됩니다.</p><p>식사는 <strong>Kadera Restaurant</strong>에서 <strong>현지 요리와 세계 각국의 요리</strong>를 즐길 수 있으며, <strong>바 또는 풀사이드 바</strong>에서 음료를 마시며 휴식을 취할 수도 있습니다. <strong>24시간 룸서비스</strong>도 이용 가능합니다.</p><p>리조트에는 <strong>비즈니스 센터, 로비 무료 신문, 세탁 및 드라이클리닝 서비스</strong>가 마련되어 있습니다. 추가 요금으로 <strong>공항 셔틀 서비스</strong>를 이용할 수 있으며, <strong>무료 주차장</strong>도 제공됩니다.</p><p>총 <strong>151개의 에어컨 객실</strong>에는 <strong>미니바와 LCD TV</strong>가 갖춰져 있습니다. 객실에서는 <strong>무료 Wi-Fi와 케이블 TV</strong>를 이용할 수 있으며, 전용 욕실에는 <strong>샤워 시설, 무료 세면도구, 헤어드라이어</strong>가 준비되어 있습니다. 또한 <strong>금고와 업무용 책상</strong>이 마련되어 있으며 매일 객실 정비 서비스가 제공됩니다.</p>', '<p>位于风景优美的利库邦海岸地区，<strong>Casabaio Likupang Paradise Resort（卡萨拜奥利库邦天堂度假村）是一家充满热带风情的海滨度假酒店，为宾客提供宁静而舒适的度假体验。酒店距离萨姆·拉图兰吉国际机场约33公里（车程约1小时）</strong>，距离<strong>万鸦老市中心约42公里</strong>，交通便利，同时远离城市喧嚣。</p><p>度假村距离<strong>Wenang高尔夫俱乐部约34.8公里</strong>，距离<strong>Ban Hin Kiong寺庙和北苏拉威西州博物馆约41–42公里</strong>。</p><p>在高尔夫爱好者享受球场的同时，其他宾客也可以使用度假村的休闲设施，例如<strong>户外游泳池、海滨休闲区</strong>等。酒店还提供<strong>免费无线网络、礼宾服务以及烧烤设施</strong>。</p><p>宾客可以在 <strong>Kadera Restaurant</strong> 享用丰富的<strong>当地美食和国际料理</strong>，也可以在<strong>酒吧或泳池吧</strong>小酌放松，或者享受<strong>24小时客房服务</strong>带来的便利。</p><p>酒店还提供<strong>商务中心、大堂免费报纸以及洗衣和干洗服务</strong>。酒店可安排<strong>付费机场接送服务</strong>，并提供<strong>免费自助停车位</strong>。</p><p>度假村拥有 <strong>151间空调客房</strong>，配备<strong>迷你吧和液晶电视</strong>。客房提供<strong>免费Wi-Fi和有线电视</strong>供娱乐使用。私人浴室设有<strong>淋浴、免费洗浴用品和吹风机</strong>，同时还配备<strong>保险箱和书桌</strong>。酒店每日提供客房清洁服务，让您住得更加舒适。</p>', '[\"Restoran\",\"Kamar bebas alkohol (sesuai permintaan)\",\"Lapangan golf\",\"Snorkeling\",\"Ruang pijat\",\"Area ParkirGratis\",\"Penjemputan di bandaraBiaya tambahan\",\"Penyimpanan bagasi\",\"Pengantaran ke bandaraBiaya tambahan\",\"Pusat bisnis\",\"Wi-Fi di tempat umumGratis\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/oxNFUoGUxaMaTTdIyEOLhfCXEQi7Zi0KiuTNZxwl.webp', '2026-04-22 09:21:56', '2026-04-22 09:21:56'),
(71, 'Kuda Laut Boutique Dive Resort', 'kuda-laut-boutique-dive-resort-wiexjd', 'Siladen Island,', 'resort', 4, '<p>Kuda Laut Boutique Dive Resort menawarkan pengalaman menginap eksklusif di pulau tropis yang tenang, jauh dari hiruk-pikuk kota. Dikelilingi oleh keindahan laut jernih dan terumbu karang kelas dunia di kawasan Bunaken, resort ini menjadi surga bagi pecinta diving dan snorkeling.&nbsp;</p><p>Menawarkan kolam renang sepanjang tahun dan area pantai pribadi, Kuda Laut Boutique Dive Resort terletak di Pulau Siladen di Kepulauan Bunaken, Wilayah Sulawesi Utara. Anda dapat menikmati minuman di bar akomodasi. Semua unit memiliki area tempat duduk untuk menambah kenyamanan Anda.&nbsp;</p><p>Semua kamar mencakup pemandangan laut atau taman. Anda dapat menikmati kamar mandi pribadi yang dilengkapi dengan shower hujan.&nbsp;</p><p>Kuda Laut Boutique Dive Resort memiliki Wi-Fi gratis di seluruh akomodasinya. Setiap villa dirancang dengan sentuhan elegan dan alami, menghadirkan kenyamanan maksimal dengan pemandangan laut yang memukau. Nikmati pelayanan personal, hidangan lezat, serta suasana privat yang sempurna untuk relaksasi maupun petualangan bawah laut yang tak terlupakan.&nbsp;</p><p>Akomodasi ini menyediakan layanan kamar, meja layanan wisata, dan toko suvenir. Teras atapnya menawarkan pemandangan yang menakjubkan ke laut dan daratan Sulawesi. Properti ini memiliki pusat spa.&nbsp;</p><p>Anda bisa bermain biliar di resor ini, dan kawasan ini memiliki rumah karang untuk snorkeling. Bandara Sam Ratulangi berjarak 16 km dari akomodasi.</p>', '<p>Kuda Laut Boutique Dive Resort offers an exclusive stay experience on a tranquil tropical island, far from the hustle and bustle of the city. Surrounded by crystal-clear waters and world-class coral reefs in the Bunaken area, this resort is a paradise for diving and snorkeling enthusiasts.</p><p>Featuring a year-round outdoor swimming pool and a private beach area, Kuda Laut Boutique Dive Resort is located on Siladen Island in the Bunaken Archipelago, North Sulawesi. Guests can enjoy drinks at the on-site bar.</p><p>All units include a seating area for your comfort, and each room offers views of either the sea or the garden. Private bathrooms are equipped with a rain shower.</p><p>The resort provides free Wi-Fi throughout the property. Each villa is designed with an elegant and natural touch, offering maximum comfort along with stunning ocean views. Enjoy personalized service, delicious cuisine, and a private atmosphere—perfect for relaxation and unforgettable underwater adventures.</p><p>The property also offers room service, a tour desk, and a souvenir shop. Its rooftop terrace provides breathtaking views of the sea and the Sulawesi mainland. A spa center is also available.</p><p>Guests can play billiards at the resort, and the surrounding area features rich coral reefs ideal for snorkeling. Sam Ratulangi Airport is 16 km away from the property.</p>', '<p>Kuda Laut Boutique Dive Resort 는 번잡한 도시를 벗어나 한적한 열대 섬에서의 특별한 숙박 경험을 제공합니다. 맑고 투명한 바다와 세계적인 산호초로 둘러싸인 부나켄 지역에 위치하여 다이빙과 스노클링을 즐기는 분들에게 천국과 같은 곳입니다.</p><p>연중 운영되는 야외 수영장과 전용 해변을 갖춘 이 리조트는 북술라웨시 부나켄 군도 실라덴 섬에 위치해 있습니다. 숙소 내 바에서 음료를 즐기실 수 있습니다.</p><p>모든 객실에는 편안한 휴식을 위한 좌석 공간이 마련되어 있으며, 객실에서는 바다 또는 정원 전망을 감상하실 수 있습니다. 전용 욕실에는 레인 샤워가 구비되어 있습니다.</p><p>리조트 전 구역에서 무료 Wi-Fi를 이용하실 수 있습니다. 각 빌라는 자연과 우아함이 조화를 이루도록 설계되어 있으며, 아름다운 바다 전망과 함께 최상의 편안함을 제공합니다. 맞춤형 서비스, 맛있는 요리, 그리고 프라이빗한 분위기 속에서 휴식과 잊지 못할 해양 모험을 즐기실 수 있습니다.</p><p>또한 룸서비스, 투어 데스크, 기념품 상점을 이용하실 수 있으며, 옥상 테라스에서는 바다와 술라웨시 본섬의 멋진 전망을 감상할 수 있습니다. 스파 시설도 마련되어 있습니다.</p><p>리조트에서는 당구를 즐길 수 있으며, 주변 지역에는 스노클링에 적합한 산호초가 펼쳐져 있습니다. 사무 라툴랑이 공항까지의 거리는 16km입니다.</p>', '<p>Kuda Laut Boutique Dive Resort 为您提供远离城市喧嚣的宁静热带海岛度假体验。度假村坐落于布纳肯海域，周围环绕着清澈海水和世界级珊瑚礁，是潜水和浮潜爱好者的天堂。</p><p>度假村位于北苏拉威西布纳肯群岛的西拉登岛，设有全年开放的室外游泳池和私人海滩区。客人可以在酒店内的酒吧享用饮品。</p><p>所有客房均设有休息区以提升舒适度，并可欣赏海景或花园景观。私人浴室配备雨淋式淋浴。</p><p>度假村全区域提供免费Wi-Fi。每栋别墅融合优雅与自然设计，提供极致舒适体验及迷人的海景。宾客可享受个性化服务、美味佳肴以及私密宁静的氛围，是放松身心与探索海底世界的理想之地。</p><p>酒店还提供客房服务、旅游咨询台及纪念品商店。屋顶露台可欣赏壮丽的海景及苏拉威西本岛景观。度假村内还设有水疗中心。</p><p>客人可在度假村内打台球，周边海域拥有丰富的珊瑚礁资源，非常适合浮潜活动。萨姆·拉图兰吉机场距离度假村16公里。</p>', '[\"olam renang outdoor\",\"WiFi gratis\",\"Tepi pantai\",\"Antar-jemput bandara\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Spa & pusat kesehatan\",\"Restoran\",\"Bar\",\"Area pantai pribadi\",\"Sarapannya luar biasa\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/IXGmwKVnKLfbJacevvCpjAmhR9bi4KzAxysqVN0t.jpg', '2026-04-23 02:02:25', '2026-04-23 02:02:26'),
(72, 'Bunaken Oasis Dive Resort and Spa', 'bunaken-oasis-dive-resort-and-spa-TPNpNU', 'Liang Beach, Bunaken', 'resort', 5, '<p>Bunaken Oasis Dive Resort and Spa menghadirkan pengalaman liburan mewah yang menyatu dengan keindahan alam bawah laut kelas dunia di kawasan Bunaken. Terletak di pulau yang eksotis dan dikelilingi perairan jernih, resort ini menjadi pilihan ideal bagi pecinta diving, snorkeling, maupun wisatawan yang mencari ketenangan tropis yang eksklusif.</p><p>Setiap vila dibangun dengan desain elegan berbahan alami seperti kayu dan batu, menciptakan suasana hangat namun tetap berkelas. Vila-vila luas ini dilengkapi fasilitas modern, kolam renang pribadi di beberapa unit, serta balkon dengan pemandangan laut yang memukau—memberikan pengalaman menginap yang benar-benar privat dan nyaman.</p><p>Sebagai resort selam premium, Bunaken Oasis menawarkan pusat diving profesional dengan layanan lengkap, termasuk instruktur bersertifikat, peralatan berkualitas tinggi, dan akses langsung ke spot-spot penyelaman terbaik di Taman Nasional Bunaken yang terkenal dengan keanekaragaman hayatinya.</p><p>Untuk relaksasi, resort ini memiliki spa eksklusif yang menawarkan berbagai perawatan tubuh dengan sentuhan tradisional dan modern, sempurna untuk memulihkan energi setelah aktivitas laut. Kolam renang infinity yang menghadap laut, restoran dengan hidangan lokal dan internasional, serta pelayanan personal yang ramah semakin melengkapi pengalaman menginap yang tak terlupakan.</p><p>Dengan perpaduan kemewahan, ketenangan, dan petualangan bawah laut, Bunaken Oasis Dive Resort and Spa adalah destinasi sempurna bagi Anda yang ingin menikmati surga tropis Sulawesi Utara dengan cara yang istimewa.</p>', '<p>Bunaken Oasis Dive Resort and Spa offers a luxurious getaway seamlessly blended with the world-class underwater beauty of the Bunaken area. Located on an exotic island surrounded by crystal-clear waters, the resort is an ideal destination for diving and snorkeling enthusiasts, as well as travelers seeking an exclusive and tranquil tropical escape.</p><p>Each villa is thoughtfully designed using natural materials such as wood and stone, creating a warm yet sophisticated ambiance. The spacious villas feature modern amenities, with some offering private pools and balconies overlooking the ocean—ensuring a truly private and comfortable stay.</p><p>As a premium dive resort, Bunaken Oasis provides a fully equipped professional dive center, complete with certified instructors, high-quality equipment, and direct access to some of the best dive sites in Bunaken National Park, renowned for its incredible marine biodiversity.</p><p>For relaxation, guests can indulge in the resort’s exclusive spa treatments that combine traditional and modern techniques—perfect for rejuvenating after a day of ocean adventures. An infinity pool facing the sea, a restaurant serving local and international cuisine, and attentive personalized service further enhance the unforgettable experience.</p><p>With its perfect blend of luxury, serenity, and underwater adventure, Bunaken Oasis Dive Resort and Spa is a truly exceptional destination to experience the tropical paradise of North Sulawesi.</p>', '<p>Bunaken Oasis Dive Resort and Spa는 세계적으로 유명한 부나켄 해역의 아름다운 해양 환경과 조화를 이루는 럭셔리 휴양지를 제공합니다. 맑고 투명한 바다로 둘러싸인 이국적인 섬에 위치하여, 다이빙과 스노클링 애호가뿐만 아니라 조용하고 프라이빗한 휴식을 원하는 여행객들에게 이상적인 장소입니다.</p><p>각 빌라는 목재와 석재 등 자연 소재를 활용해 세련되면서도 따뜻한 분위기로 설계되었습니다. 넓은 공간과 현대적인 시설을 갖추고 있으며, 일부 빌라는 전용 수영장과 바다 전망의 발코니를 제공하여 더욱 편안하고 프라이빗한 숙박을 보장합니다.</p><p>프리미엄 다이빙 리조트로서, 전문 다이빙 센터를 운영하며 공인 강사, 고급 장비, 그리고 해양 생물 다양성으로 유명한 부나켄 국립공원의 최고의 다이빙 포인트로의 접근성을 제공합니다.</p><p>휴식을 원하는 분들을 위해 전통과 현대 기법이 결합된 다양한 스파 트리트먼트도 제공되어 바다 활동 후 몸과 마음을 재충전할 수 있습니다. 바다를 바라보는 인피니티 풀, 다양한 현지 및 세계 요리를 제공하는 레스토랑, 세심한 맞춤형 서비스가 잊지 못할 경험을 완성합니다.</p><p>럭셔리함, 평온함, 그리고 해양 모험이 완벽하게 어우러진 Bunaken Oasis Dive Resort and Spa는 북술라웨시의 열대 낙원을 특별하게 경험할 수 있는 최고의 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>Bunaken Oasis Dive Resort and Spa 将奢华度假体验与布纳肯海域世界级海底美景完美融合。度假村坐落于被清澈海水环绕的热带岛屿，是潜水和浮潜爱好者以及追求宁静私密度假的旅客的理想之选。</p><p>每栋别墅均采用木材与石材等天然元素精心设计，营造出温馨而高雅的氛围。宽敞的空间配备现代化设施，部分别墅设有私人泳池及可欣赏海景的阳台，为宾客提供极致舒适与私密的入住体验。</p><p>作为高端潜水度假村，Bunaken Oasis 拥有专业潜水中心，提供认证教练、高品质设备，并可直达布纳肯国家公园最著名的潜点，该地区以丰富的海洋生物多样性而闻名。</p><p>在放松方面，度假村提供融合传统与现代技艺的水疗护理，让宾客在海上活动后充分恢复身心活力。面朝大海的无边泳池、提供本地及国际美食的餐厅，以及贴心周到的个性化服务，为您打造难忘的度假体验。</p><p>融合奢华、宁静与海洋探险于一体，Bunaken Oasis Dive Resort and Spa 是体验北苏拉威西热带天堂的绝佳之地。</p>', '[\"Kolam renang luar ruangan\",\"WiFi gratis\",\"Antar-jemput bandara (gratis)\",\"Pusat spa dan kebugaran\",\"Room service\",\"Restoran\",\"Ruang keluarga\",\"Batang\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/ljsw4eW7V1uuStUOByT1MT2qNdrmYMIIGDDvIcjM.jpg', '2026-04-23 02:19:36', '2026-04-23 06:56:31'),
(73, 'PS Bunaken Resort and Dive', 'ps-bunaken-resort-and-dive-8yO0o4', 'Bunaken', 'resort', 4, '<p>PS Bunaken Resort and Dive menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang hangat dan autentik di tengah keindahan alami Pulau Bunaken. Dikelilingi oleh laut biru jernih dan taman laut yang kaya akan kehidupan bawah laut, resort ini menjadi pilihan sempurna bagi para pecinta diving dan snorkeling yang ingin menikmati suasana santai namun tetap berkualitas.</p><p>Dengan konsep yang lebih intimate dan ramah, setiap cottage di PS Bunaken Resort dirancang sederhana namun nyaman, menyatu dengan alam sekitar. Material alami dan sentuhan tradisional menciptakan suasana tropis yang tenang, dilengkapi dengan teras pribadi yang menghadap taman atau laut—tempat ideal untuk bersantai menikmati angin laut.</p><p>Sebagai resort selam, PS Bunaken menyediakan layanan diving profesional dengan akses mudah ke spot-spot terbaik di Taman Nasional Bunaken. Didukung oleh tim berpengalaman, tamu dapat menjelajahi keindahan terumbu karang, dinding laut yang spektakuler, serta beragam biota laut yang memukau.</p><p>Selain aktivitas laut, tamu dapat menikmati hidangan lezat di restoran resort yang menyajikan masakan lokal dan internasional dengan bahan segar. Suasana yang tenang, jauh dari keramaian, menjadikan resort ini cocok untuk relaksasi, liburan romantis, maupun pelarian dari rutinitas sehari-hari.</p><p>Pelayanan yang hangat dan personal menjadi nilai utama di PS Bunaken Resort and Dive, memberikan pengalaman menginap yang sederhana namun berkesan, di salah satu destinasi bawah laut terbaik di Indonesia.</p>', '<p>PS Bunaken Resort and Dive offers a warm and authentic stay experience amidst the natural beauty of Bunaken Island. Surrounded by crystal-clear blue waters and a vibrant marine park rich in underwater life, the resort is an ideal choice for diving and snorkeling enthusiasts seeking a relaxed yet quality tropical escape.</p><p>With an intimate and welcoming concept, each cottage is simply designed yet comfortable, blending harmoniously with the surrounding nature. Natural materials and traditional touches create a peaceful tropical atmosphere, complemented by private terraces overlooking the garden or the sea—perfect for unwinding while enjoying the ocean breeze.</p><p>As a dedicated dive resort, PS Bunaken provides professional diving services with easy access to the best dive sites in Bunaken National Park. Supported by an experienced team, guests can explore stunning coral reefs, dramatic wall dives, and diverse marine life.</p><p>Beyond water activities, guests can enjoy delicious meals at the resort’s restaurant, offering a selection of local and international cuisine prepared with fresh ingredients. The tranquil setting, away from the crowds, makes it ideal for relaxation, romantic getaways, or simply escaping daily routines.</p><p>Warm and personalized service is at the heart of PS Bunaken Resort and Dive, delivering a simple yet memorable stay in one of Indonesia’s most spectacular underwater destinations.</p>', '<p>PS Bunaken Resort and Dive는 부나켄 섬의 아름다운 자연 속에서 따뜻하고 진정성 있는 숙박 경험을 제공합니다. 맑고 푸른 바다와 다양한 해양 생물이 서식하는 해양 국립공원에 둘러싸여 있어, 여유롭고 품격 있는 휴식을 원하는 다이빙 및 스노클링 애호가들에게 이상적인 장소입니다.</p><p>아늑하고 친근한 콘셉트로 설계된 각 코티지는 단순하면서도 편안하며, 주변 자연과 조화를 이루고 있습니다. 자연 소재와 전통적인 요소가 어우러져 평온한 열대 분위기를 만들어내며, 정원이나 바다를 바라보는 전용 테라스에서 여유로운 시간을 보낼 수 있습니다.</p><p>다이빙 리조트로서 PS Bunaken은 전문적인 다이빙 서비스를 제공하며, 부나켄 국립공원의 최고의 다이빙 포인트로 쉽게 접근할 수 있습니다. 경험이 풍부한 팀과 함께 아름다운 산호초, 장관을 이루는 월 다이빙, 그리고 다양한 해양 생물을 탐험할 수 있습니다.</p><p>또한 리조트 내 레스토랑에서는 신선한 재료로 만든 현지 및 세계 각국의 요리를 즐길 수 있습니다. 조용하고 한적한 환경은 휴식, 로맨틱 여행, 혹은 일상에서 벗어난 힐링을 원하는 분들에게 최적입니다.</p><p>따뜻하고 세심한 맞춤형 서비스는 PS Bunaken Resort and Dive의 가장 큰 장점으로, 인도네시아 최고의 해양 여행지 중 한 곳에서 잊지 못할 추억을 선사합니다.</p>', '<p>PS Bunaken Resort and Dive 为您提供置身于布纳肯岛自然美景中的温馨而真实的度假体验。度假村被清澈蔚蓝的海水和丰富多彩的海洋生态所环绕，是潜水和浮潜爱好者放松身心、享受高品质热带度假的理想之选。</p><p>度假村以温馨私密为设计理念，每栋小屋简约舒适，与周围自然环境完美融合。采用天然材料与传统元素，营造出宁静的热带氛围，并配有可俯瞰花园或海景的私人露台，让宾客尽享惬意时光。</p><p>作为专业潜水度假村，PS Bunaken 提供完善的潜水服务，方便前往布纳肯国家公园最著名的潜点。在经验丰富的团队带领下，宾客可以探索绚丽的珊瑚礁、壮观的海底断层以及丰富的海洋生物。</p><p>除了水上活动，宾客还可以在度假村餐厅品尝以新鲜食材烹制的本地及国际美食。远离喧嚣的宁静环境，非常适合放松身心、浪漫度假或逃离日常生活。</p><p>温暖周到的个性化服务是 PS Bunaken Resort and Dive 的核心特色，为您在印尼最迷人的海底世界之一打造难忘的住宿体验。</p>', '[\"Kolam renang luar ruangan\",\"Tepi pantai\",\"Restoran\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"WiFi gratis\",\"Ruang keluarga\",\"Batang\",\"Area pantai pribadi\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/LYB0yMFeojKlPPISx655D6pLkSXkYUNRjcLtL4vY.jpg', '2026-04-23 03:34:19', '2026-04-23 03:34:20'),
(74, 'Bastianos Bunaken Dive Resort', 'bastianos-bunaken-dive-resort-S4hVdr', 'Bunaaken', 'resort', 4, '<p>Bastianos Bunaken Dive Resort menghadirkan pengalaman liburan tropis yang santai dan penuh petualangan di jantung Taman Nasional Bunaken. Dikelilingi oleh laut biru yang jernih dan keindahan terumbu karang yang memukau, resort ini menjadi destinasi ideal bagi para pecinta diving, snorkeling, maupun wisatawan yang ingin menikmati suasana pulau yang tenang.</p><p>Resort ini menawarkan berbagai pilihan akomodasi yang nyaman, mulai dari kamar dengan pemandangan taman hingga kamar dengan panorama laut yang menakjubkan. Desainnya sederhana namun fungsional, memberikan kenyamanan maksimal dengan nuansa tropis yang hangat dan bersahaja.</p><p>Sebagai salah satu resort selam yang populer di Bunaken, Bastianos dilengkapi dengan pusat diving profesional yang menyediakan layanan lengkap, termasuk peralatan berkualitas, boat diving harian, serta pemandu berpengalaman yang siap mengajak Anda menjelajahi spot-spot terbaik dengan dinding karang spektakuler dan keanekaragaman hayati laut yang luar biasa.</p><p>Selain aktivitas laut, tamu dapat menikmati kolam renang outdoor yang menghadap langsung ke laut, tempat sempurna untuk bersantai sambil menikmati matahari terbenam. Restoran resort menyajikan beragam hidangan lokal dan internasional dengan cita rasa autentik, melengkapi pengalaman menginap yang menyenangkan.</p><p>Dengan suasana yang ramah, pelayanan yang hangat, serta lokasi strategis untuk eksplorasi bawah laut, Bastianos Bunaken Dive Resort menjadi pilihan tepat bagi Anda yang mencari keseimbangan antara relaksasi dan petualangan di surga tropis Sulawesi Utara.</p>', '<p>Bastianos Bunaken Dive Resort offers a relaxing tropical getaway filled with adventure in the heart of Bunaken National Park. Surrounded by crystal-clear blue waters and stunning coral reefs, the resort is an ideal destination for diving and snorkeling enthusiasts, as well as travelers seeking a peaceful island escape.</p><p>The resort features a range of comfortable accommodations, from garden-view rooms to breathtaking ocean-view options. The design is simple yet functional, providing maximum comfort with a warm and laid-back tropical ambiance.</p><p>As one of the popular dive resorts in Bunaken, Bastianos is equipped with a professional dive center offering complete services, including high-quality equipment, daily boat dives, and experienced guides ready to take guests to the best dive sites with dramatic wall reefs and extraordinary marine biodiversity.</p><p>Beyond underwater activities, guests can unwind at the outdoor swimming pool overlooking the sea—an ideal spot to relax while enjoying beautiful sunsets. The on-site restaurant serves a variety of local and international dishes, enhancing the overall stay experience.</p><p>With its friendly atmosphere, warm hospitality, and strategic location for marine exploration, Bastianos Bunaken Dive Resort is the perfect choice for those seeking a balance between relaxation and adventure in North Sulawesi’s tropical paradise.</p>', '<p>Bastianos Bunaken Dive Resort는 부나켄 국립공원의 중심에서 휴식과 모험을 동시에 즐길 수 있는 열대 휴양지입니다. 맑고 푸른 바다와 아름다운 산호초로 둘러싸여 있어 다이빙과 스노클링을 즐기는 여행객은 물론, 조용한 섬 휴식을 원하는 분들에게 이상적인 장소입니다.</p><p>리조트는 정원 전망 객실부터 멋진 바다 전망 객실까지 다양한 숙박 옵션을 제공하며, 단순하면서도 실용적인 디자인으로 편안하고 아늑한 열대 분위기를 느낄 수 있습니다.</p><p>부나켄에서 인기 있는 다이빙 리조트 중 하나로, 전문 다이빙 센터를 갖추고 있으며 고품질 장비, 일일 보트 다이빙, 그리고 경험 많은 가이드가 최고의 다이빙 포인트로 안내합니다. 장관을 이루는 절벽형 산호초와 풍부한 해양 생태계를 직접 경험할 수 있습니다.</p><p>해양 활동 외에도 바다를 바라보는 야외 수영장에서 휴식을 취하며 아름다운 일몰을 감상할 수 있습니다. 리조트 레스토랑에서는 다양한 현지 및 세계 요리를 제공하여 더욱 풍성한 숙박 경험을 선사합니다.</p><p>친근한 분위기와 따뜻한 서비스, 그리고 뛰어난 위치를 갖춘 Bastianos Bunaken Dive Resort는 북술라웨시의 열대 낙원에서 휴식과 모험을 동시에 즐기기에 완벽한 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>Bastianos Bunaken Dive Resort 位于布纳肯国家公园核心区域，为宾客提供融合放松与探险的热带度假体验。度假村被清澈的蓝色海水和壮丽的珊瑚礁环绕，是潜水和浮潜爱好者以及寻求宁静海岛度假的旅客的理想选择。</p><p>度假村提供多种舒适的住宿选择，从花园景观客房到壮观的海景房应有尽有。设计简约而实用，营造出轻松温暖的热带氛围，让宾客尽享舒适体验。</p><p>作为布纳肯颇受欢迎的潜水度假村之一，Bastianos 配备专业潜水中心，提供完善服务，包括高品质潜水设备、每日船潜以及经验丰富的潜导，带领宾客探索壮观的海底断层和丰富多样的海洋生态。</p><p>除了海上活动，宾客还可在面朝大海的室外游泳池放松身心，欣赏迷人的日落景色。度假村餐厅提供多样化的本地及国际美食，为您的入住体验增添更多乐趣。</p><p>凭借友好的氛围、热情的服务以及优越的地理位置，Bastianos Bunaken Dive Resort 是在北苏拉威西热带天堂中体验休闲与探险完美结合的理想之选。</p>', '[\"Pantai\",\"Akses internet\",\"Kolam renang\",\"Spa\",\"Restoran\",\"Bar\",\"Pijat\",\"Shuttle bandara\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/Zk8Wlte5ZLkblLyRlzrcLzJxCczT5vcuq3j9Z0uI.webp', '2026-04-23 06:40:00', '2026-04-23 06:57:32');
INSERT INTO `hotels` (`id`, `name`, `slug`, `location`, `category`, `stars`, `description`, `description_en`, `description_ko`, `description_zh`, `facilities`, `primary_image`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(75, 'Tangkoko Sanctuary Villa', 'tangkoko-sanctuary-villa-YmzFDt', 'Jalan Rata, Desa Batu putih Bawah Kecamatan Ranowulu, Bitung Utara', 'eco_lodge', 3, '<p>Terletak di kota <strong>Bitung</strong>, <strong>Tangkoko Sanctuary Villa</strong> menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang nyaman di tengah suasana alam yang tenang. Akomodasi ini dilengkapi dengan taman hijau yang asri, teras santai, serta bar yang cocok untuk menikmati waktu bersantai setelah beraktivitas.</p><p>Setiap kamar dirancang untuk memberikan kenyamanan maksimal dengan fasilitas seperti AC, meja kerja, seprai berkualitas, serta balkon pribadi yang menghadap langsung ke pemandangan taman yang menenangkan. Kamar mandi pribadi dilengkapi bidet, perlengkapan mandi gratis, dan pengering rambut. Para tamu juga dapat menikmati fasilitas WiFi gratis serta parkir pribadi tanpa biaya tambahan.</p><p>Di pagi hari, tamu dapat menikmati berbagai pilihan sarapan mulai dari prasmanan, kontinental, hingga sarapan ala Amerika. Restoran di villa ini menyajikan beragam hidangan lezat seperti masakan Amerika, Indonesia, dan seafood segar, dengan pilihan menu vegetarian, vegan, serta bebas gluten yang juga tersedia.</p><p>Lokasinya yang sangat dekat dengan <strong>Tangkoko Nature Reserve</strong> menjadikan villa ini pilihan ideal bagi para pecinta alam dan petualangan. Kawasan konservasi ini terkenal sebagai habitat berbagai satwa langka Sulawesi seperti tarsius dan monyet hitam Sulawesi. Berbagai aktivitas menarik seperti trekking dan pengamatan satwa liar dapat dinikmati di sekitar area ini. Bagi tamu yang ingin menjelajah lebih jauh, tersedia juga layanan penyewaan mobil.</p><p>Bandara terdekat adalah <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong> yang berjarak sekitar 62 km dari akomodasi.</p>', '<p>Located in <strong>Bitung</strong>, <strong>Tangkoko Sanctuary Villa</strong> offers a relaxing stay surrounded by lush tropical nature. The property features a beautiful garden, a cozy terrace, and a bar where guests can unwind after a day of exploration.</p><p>Each room is designed for comfort and equipped with air conditioning, a work desk, quality linens, and a private balcony overlooking the peaceful garden view. The private bathroom includes a bidet, complimentary toiletries, and a hairdryer. Guests can also enjoy free WiFi and free private parking during their stay.</p><p>Every morning, guests can start their day with a buffet, continental, or American breakfast. The on-site restaurant serves a variety of delicious dishes including American, Indonesian, and fresh seafood cuisine. Vegetarian, vegan, and gluten-free options are also available upon request.</p><p>One of the highlights of staying here is its close proximity to <strong>Tangkoko Nature Reserve</strong>, a famous wildlife sanctuary known for its unique biodiversity, including the iconic tarsier and the Sulawesi black macaque. The surrounding area is perfect for hiking, wildlife watching, and nature exploration. Car rental services are also available for guests who wish to explore further.</p><p>The nearest airport is <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, located approximately 62 km from the property.</p>', '<p><strong>Tangkoko Sanctuary Villa</strong>는 **Bitung**에 위치한 자연 속 휴식 공간으로, 푸른 정원과 편안한 테라스, 그리고 여유롭게 시간을 보낼 수 있는 바를 제공합니다.</p><p>각 객실은 에어컨, 업무용 책상, 고급 침구, 그리고 정원 전망을 감상할 수 있는 전용 발코니를 갖추고 있어 편안한 휴식을 제공합니다. 전용 욕실에는 비데, 무료 세면도구, 헤어드라이어가 마련되어 있습니다. 또한 숙박객은 무료 Wi-Fi와 무료 전용 주차장을 이용할 수 있습니다.</p><p>아침에는 뷔페, 컨티넨탈, 또는 아메리칸 스타일의 조식을 즐길 수 있습니다. 숙소 내 레스토랑에서는 미국식, 인도네시아식, 신선한 해산물 요리를 제공하며, 채식, 비건, 글루텐 프리 메뉴도 요청 시 준비됩니다.</p><p>이 빌라는 <strong>Tangkoko Nature Reserve</strong>와 매우 가까워 자연과 야생동물을 사랑하는 여행객에게 이상적인 장소입니다. 이 보호구역은 타르시어와 술라웨시 검은원숭이 등 희귀 동물의 서식지로 유명합니다. 주변 지역에서는 트레킹과 야생동물 관찰 같은 다양한 야외 활동을 즐길 수 있으며, 차량 대여 서비스도 제공됩니다.</p><p>가장 가까운 공항은 약 62km 떨어진 <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>입니다.</p>', '<p>位于 <strong>Bitung</strong> 的 <strong>Tangkoko Sanctuary Villa</strong> 是一家被热带自然环境环绕的舒适住宿。酒店设有美丽的花园、休闲露台以及酒吧，让客人在探索自然之后可以放松身心。</p><p>每间客房都配备空调、书桌、高品质床品，并设有可欣赏花园景色的私人阳台。私人浴室配备坐浴盆、免费洗浴用品和吹风机。客人还可以享受免费 WiFi 和免费私人停车服务。</p><p>每天早晨，客人可以选择自助早餐、欧陆式早餐或美式早餐。酒店餐厅提供多种美食，包括美国菜、印尼菜以及新鲜海鲜，同时也提供素食、纯素食和无麸质餐食选择。</p><p>酒店的一大亮点是靠近著名的 <strong>Tangkoko Nature Reserve</strong>。这里是苏拉威西岛重要的自然保护区，以独特的野生动物闻名，例如眼镜猴（Tarsier）和苏拉威西黑猕猴。周边地区非常适合徒步旅行、野生动物观察和自然探险。酒店也提供汽车租赁服务，方便客人探索更多景点。</p><p>最近的机场是 <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>，距离酒店约 62 公里。</p>', '[\"WiFi gratis\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Spa & pusat kesehatan\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Restoran\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Bar\",\"Sarapannya\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/UhklgLDnk5fOKCZq98GooD2rzdqBAHoy4LIXEuE8.jpg', '2026-04-24 07:53:29', '2026-04-24 07:54:56'),
(76, 'Botanica Nature Resort', 'botanica-nature-resort-qSuS53', 'Jl. Johan Pinontoan- Kel.Danowudu Kec. Ranowulu-Bitung', 'resort', 2, '<p>Terletak di kawasan alam yang tenang di <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>Botanica Nature Resort</strong> menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang nyaman dan menyatu dengan alam. Resort ini dikelilingi pepohonan hijau dan suasana yang sejuk, menjadikannya tempat sempurna bagi wisatawan yang ingin beristirahat dari hiruk-pikuk kota.</p><p>Akomodasi ini berjarak sekitar <strong>46 km dari Port of Manado</strong> dan juga sekitar <strong>46 km dari pusat Kota Manado</strong>, sehingga tetap mudah dijangkau namun tetap memberikan suasana yang tenang dan privat. Untuk perjalanan udara, resort ini berada sekitar <strong>45 km dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, atau sekitar <strong>60–70 menit berkendara</strong>.</p><p>Botanica Nature Resort menyediakan berbagai fasilitas nyaman seperti restoran, taman tropis yang luas, lounge bersama yang hangat, serta teras santai untuk menikmati udara segar. Para tamu juga dapat menikmati <strong>WiFi gratis dan parkir pribadi gratis</strong> selama menginap.</p><p>Beberapa unit akomodasi dilengkapi dengan kamar mandi pribadi yang memiliki shower, perlengkapan mandi gratis, pengering rambut, serta sandal kamar untuk menambah kenyamanan. Di pagi hari, tamu dapat menikmati <strong>sarapan prasmanan atau sarapan kontinental</strong> yang lezat untuk memulai hari dengan energi penuh.</p><p>Dengan suasana alam yang menenangkan serta akses yang cukup dekat ke kota dan bandara, Botanica Nature Resort menjadi pilihan ideal bagi wisatawan yang mencari <strong>ketenangan, kenyamanan, dan pengalaman menginap yang berbeda di Sulawesi Utara</strong>.</p>', '<p>Nestled in a peaceful natural setting near <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>Botanica Nature Resort</strong> offers a relaxing retreat surrounded by lush greenery and fresh tropical air. This charming resort is perfect for travelers seeking tranquility while still staying connected to the city.</p><p>The resort is located approximately <strong>46 km from Port of Manado</strong> and about <strong>46 km from Manado city center</strong>, allowing guests to enjoy a peaceful environment away from the busy urban atmosphere. The nearest airport is <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, located around <strong>45 km away</strong>, which takes roughly <strong>60–70 minutes by car</strong>.</p><p>Botanica Nature Resort features a variety of comfortable facilities including an on-site restaurant, a lush tropical garden, a cozy shared lounge, and a relaxing terrace where guests can unwind and enjoy the surrounding nature. Complimentary <strong>WiFi and free private parking</strong> are also available.</p><p>Some accommodation units come with a private bathroom equipped with a shower, complimentary toiletries, a hairdryer, and slippers to ensure a comfortable stay. In the morning, guests can start their day with a delicious <strong>buffet or continental breakfast</strong> served at the resort.</p><p>With its serene natural surroundings and convenient access to the city and airport, Botanica Nature Resort is an ideal destination for travelers looking for <strong>comfort, relaxation, and a unique nature escape in North Sulawesi</strong>.</p>', '<p><strong>Botanica Nature Resort</strong>는 <strong>Manado</strong> 인근의 조용한 자연 환경 속에 위치한 리조트로, 푸른 자연과 신선한 공기에 둘러싸인 편안한 휴식을 제공합니다. 도시의 번잡함에서 벗어나 여유로운 시간을 보내고 싶은 여행객에게 이상적인 숙소입니다.</p><p>이 리조트는 **Port of Manado**에서 약 <strong>46km</strong>, 마나도 시내 중심에서도 약 <strong>46km</strong> 거리에 위치해 있습니다. 또한 가장 가까운 공항인 **Sam Ratulangi International Airport**까지는 약 <strong>45km</strong>로, 차량으로 약 <strong>60~70분 정도</strong> 소요됩니다.</p><p>리조트에는 레스토랑, 열대 정원, 아늑한 공용 라운지, 자연을 즐길 수 있는 테라스 등이 마련되어 있습니다. 숙박객은 <strong>무료 Wi-Fi와 무료 전용 주차장</strong>도 이용할 수 있습니다.</p><p>일부 객실에는 샤워 시설이 있는 전용 욕실과 무료 세면도구, 헤어드라이어, 슬리퍼가 제공되어 더욱 편안한 숙박을 제공합니다. 아침에는 <strong>뷔페 또는 컨티넨탈 스타일 조식</strong>을 즐길 수 있습니다.</p><p>자연 속의 평온함과 도시 및 공항과의 편리한 접근성을 동시에 갖춘 Botanica Nature Resort는 <strong>북술라웨시에서 특별한 휴식과 자연 체험을 원하는 여행객에게 완벽한 선택</strong>입니다.</p>', '<p><strong>Botanica Nature Resort</strong> 位于 <strong>Manado</strong> 附近宁静的自然环境中，被郁郁葱葱的热带植物环绕，是远离城市喧嚣、享受自然与放松时光的理想住宿选择。</p><p>度假村距离 <strong>Port of Manado</strong> 约 <strong>46 公里</strong>，距离马纳多市中心也约 <strong>46 公里</strong>，既能享受安静的自然氛围，又能方便前往城市。最近的机场是 <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>，距离度假村约 <strong>45 公里</strong>，车程约 <strong>60–70 分钟</strong>。</p><p>Botanica Nature Resort 提供多种舒适设施，包括餐厅、宽敞的热带花园、共享休息室以及可以放松身心的露台。客人还可以享受 <strong>免费 WiFi 和免费私人停车位</strong>。</p><p>部分住宿单元配有带淋浴的私人浴室，并提供免费洗浴用品、吹风机和室内拖鞋，为客人带来更加舒适的入住体验。每天早晨，客人可以享用 <strong>自助早餐或欧陆式早餐</strong>。</p><p>凭借宁静的自然环境以及方便前往城市和机场的地理位置，Botanica Nature Resort 是在北苏拉威西寻找 <strong>放松、自然与舒适体验</strong> 的旅行者的理想之选。</p>', '[\"WiFi gratis biasa (11 Mbps)\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\",\"Antar-jemput bandara\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Restoran\",\"Kamar keluarga\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/rEsUl4BJDegeqDWGJyS9p0Pl2dK4cHoNyZklntiK.jpg', '2026-04-24 08:26:48', '2026-04-24 08:26:48'),
(77, 'Fave Hotel Bitung', 'fave-hotel-bitung-vmCaGo', 'Bitung', 'city_hotel', 3, '<p>Terletak di kota pelabuhan <strong>Bitung</strong>, <strong>favehotel Bitung</strong> menawarkan akomodasi modern yang nyaman dengan lokasi strategis di kawasan taman negara bagian. Hotel ini hanya sekitar <strong>4 menit berjalan kaki dari Lembeh Strait</strong> dan sekitar <strong>3 menit berkendara dari Port of Bitung</strong>.</p><p>Bagi tamu yang ingin menjelajahi wilayah Sulawesi Utara, hotel ini berjarak sekitar <strong>45 km dari pusat kota Manado</strong> dan sekitar <strong>48 km dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, dengan waktu perjalanan sekitar <strong>60–70 menit</strong> menggunakan mobil.</p><p>Hotel ini menyediakan berbagai fasilitas untuk kenyamanan tamu, termasuk <strong>kolam renang indoor</strong>, taman yang asri, serta teras untuk bersantai. Tamu juga dapat menikmati <strong>WiFi gratis</strong>, layanan concierge, serta aula perjamuan yang cocok untuk acara bisnis maupun pertemuan.</p><p>Untuk pengalaman kuliner, tamu dapat menikmati hidangan lezat di restoran hotel atau mencicipi makanan ringan di kedai kopi/kafe. Bar dan lounge hotel juga menjadi tempat yang sempurna untuk bersantai sambil menikmati minuman favorit. Setiap pagi, tamu disuguhi <strong>sarapan prasmanan gratis</strong> yang tersedia mulai pukul <strong>06.00 hingga 10.00</strong>.</p><p>Fasilitas tambahan yang tersedia meliputi <strong>resepsionis 24 jam</strong>, koran gratis di lobi, penitipan koper, serta <strong>parkir mandiri gratis</strong> bagi tamu yang membawa kendaraan.</p><p>Hotel ini memiliki <strong>95 kamar ber-AC</strong> yang dirancang untuk memberikan kenyamanan seperti di rumah. Setiap kamar dilengkapi dengan kamar mandi pribadi dengan shower dan sandal, serta fasilitas tambahan seperti <strong>brankas dan meja kerja</strong>, dengan layanan kebersihan kamar yang tersedia setiap hari.</p><p>Dengan lokasi yang strategis dekat laut, fasilitas lengkap, serta akses mudah menuju kota Manado dan bandara, favehotel Bitung menjadi pilihan ideal bagi wisatawan bisnis maupun liburan yang ingin menjelajahi keindahan Sulawesi Utara.</p>', '<p>Located in the vibrant port city of <strong>Bitung</strong>, <strong>favehotel Bitung</strong> offers modern and comfortable accommodation in a strategic setting near a state park area. The hotel is just <strong>a 4-minute walk from the famous Lembeh Strait</strong> and only <strong>3 minutes by car from Port of Bitung</strong>.</p><p>For travelers exploring North Sulawesi, the hotel is conveniently located about <strong>45 km from downtown Manado</strong> and approximately <strong>48 km from Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, which takes around <strong>60–70 minutes by car</strong>.</p><p>Guests can enjoy a range of facilities including an <strong>indoor swimming pool</strong>, a peaceful garden, and a terrace where they can relax and unwind. The hotel also provides <strong>complimentary WiFi</strong>, concierge services, and a banquet hall suitable for meetings and events.</p><p>Dining options include a restaurant serving delicious meals as well as a coffee shop/café for light snacks. Guests can also relax with their favorite drinks at the hotel’s bar and lounge. A <strong>complimentary buffet breakfast</strong> is served daily from <strong>6:00 AM to 10:00 AM</strong>.</p><p>Additional services include <strong>24-hour front desk assistance</strong>, free newspapers in the lobby, luggage storage, and <strong>free self-parking</strong> on site.</p><p>The hotel features <strong>95 air-conditioned guest rooms</strong> designed for comfort. Each room includes a private bathroom with a shower and slippers, along with practical amenities such as a <strong>safe and work desk</strong>. Daily housekeeping ensures a pleasant and relaxing stay.</p><p>With its strategic location near the sea, modern facilities, and convenient access to Manado city and the airport, favehotel Bitung is an excellent choice for both business and leisure travelers visiting North Sulawesi.</p>', '<p><strong>favehotel Bitung</strong>는 <strong>Bitung</strong> 항구 도시에 위치한 현대적인 호텔로, 편안한 숙박과 편리한 위치를 제공합니다. 호텔은 유명한 **Lembeh Strait**에서 도보 약 4분, **Port of Bitung**에서 차로 약 3분 거리에 있습니다.</p><p>또한 호텔은 <strong>Manado</strong> 시내 중심에서 약 <strong>45km</strong>, **Sam Ratulangi International Airport**에서 약 <strong>48km</strong> 떨어져 있으며, 차량으로 약 <strong>60~70분</strong> 정도 소요됩니다.</p><p>호텔에는 <strong>실내 수영장</strong>, 아름다운 정원, 휴식을 위한 테라스가 마련되어 있습니다. 투숙객은 <strong>무료 Wi-Fi</strong>, 컨시어지 서비스, 연회장 등 다양한 편의시설을 이용할 수 있습니다.</p><p>레스토랑에서는 다양한 요리를 즐길 수 있으며, 카페에서는 간단한 스낵과 음료를 제공합니다. 바와 라운지에서는 좋아하는 음료를 마시며 여유로운 시간을 보낼 수 있습니다. 매일 아침 <strong>06:00~10:00</strong> 사이에는 <strong>무료 뷔페식 조식</strong>이 제공됩니다.</p><p>호텔에는 총 <strong>95개의 에어컨 객실</strong>이 있으며, 각 객실에는 샤워 시설이 있는 전용 욕실과 슬리퍼가 마련되어 있습니다. 또한 <strong>금고와 업무용 책상</strong>이 제공되며, 매일 객실 정리 서비스가 제공됩니다.</p>', '<p><strong>favehotel Bitung</strong> 位于 <strong>Bitung</strong> 这座充满活力的港口城市，是一家现代舒适的酒店，地理位置十分优越。酒店距离著名的 <strong>Lembeh Strait</strong> 仅 <strong>步行约4分钟</strong>，距离 <strong>Port of Bitung</strong> 约 <strong>3分钟车程</strong>。</p><p>酒店距离 <strong>Manado</strong> 市中心约 <strong>45公里</strong>，距离 <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong> 约 <strong>48公里</strong>，车程约 <strong>60–70分钟</strong>，交通便利。</p><p>酒店设施完善，包括 <strong>室内游泳池、花园、休闲露台</strong> 等，让客人可以在旅途中放松身心。酒店还提供 <strong>免费 WiFi、礼宾服务以及宴会厅</strong>，适合商务会议或活动。</p><p>客人可以在酒店餐厅享用美味餐点，也可以在咖啡厅品尝轻食和饮品。酒店的酒吧和休息室是放松和社交的理想场所。每天早上 <strong>06:00 至 10:00</strong> 提供 <strong>免费自助早餐</strong>。</p><p>酒店共有 <strong>95间空调客房</strong>，每间客房均配备带淋浴的私人浴室和拖鞋，并提供 <strong>保险箱和书桌</strong> 等设施。酒店每天提供客房清洁服务，为客人带来舒适愉快的入住体验。</p>', '[\"Restoran\",\"Kamar bebas alkohol (sesuai permintaan)\",\"Area Parkir\",\"Penyimpanan bagasi\",\"Ruang pertemuan\",\"Ruang multi-fungsi\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/AoRQAGZRKaqwOh3NDgMPFI72fsHaCUPIIlyUDrEI.webp', '2026-04-24 09:12:59', '2026-04-24 09:12:59'),
(78, 'Lun Hotel Manado', 'lun-hotel-manado-CgfhHo', 'Manado', 'city_hotel', 3, '<p>Terletak di jantung <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>Lun Hotel Manado</strong> menawarkan akomodasi modern yang nyaman dengan lokasi strategis di <strong>Pusat Kota Manado</strong>. Hotel ini menjadi pilihan ideal bagi wisatawan yang ingin menjelajahi budaya, sejarah, serta pusat aktivitas kota.</p><p>Dari hotel, Anda hanya beberapa langkah menuju <strong>Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong>, salah satu klenteng tertua dan paling bersejarah di Manado. Selain itu, hotel juga berada dekat dengan berbagai tempat menarik seperti <strong>North Sulawesi State Museum</strong> yang berjarak sekitar <strong>1,7 km</strong>, serta <strong>Kalimas Port</strong> sekitar <strong>1,9 km</strong> dari hotel.</p><p>Bagi tamu yang datang melalui jalur udara, hotel ini berjarak sekitar <strong>14 km dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, dengan waktu perjalanan sekitar <strong>25–30 menit berkendara</strong>.</p><p>Hotel menyediakan berbagai fasilitas untuk kenyamanan tamu, termasuk <strong>WiFi gratis di seluruh area</strong>, layanan concierge, serta resepsionis 24 jam yang siap membantu kebutuhan Anda. Tersedia juga staf multibahasa dan layanan penitipan koper untuk menambah kenyamanan selama menginap.</p><p>Di restoran hotel, para tamu dapat menikmati berbagai hidangan lezat dalam suasana yang nyaman. Bagi yang membutuhkan transportasi, tersedia juga <strong>layanan antar-jemput bandara 24 jam dengan biaya tambahan</strong>, serta <strong>parkir pribadi gratis</strong> bagi tamu yang membawa kendaraan.</p><p><strong>Lun Hotel Manado</strong> memiliki <strong>60 kamar</strong> yang dirancang untuk memberikan suasana hangat seperti di rumah. Setiap kamar dilengkapi dengan <strong>akses WiFi gratis</strong>, kamar mandi dengan bathtub atau shower, pengering rambut, meja kerja, serta <strong>air minum kemasan gratis</strong>. Layanan kebersihan kamar juga tersedia setiap hari untuk memastikan kenyamanan selama Anda menginap.</p><p>Dengan lokasi yang strategis di pusat kota serta akses mudah ke berbagai tempat wisata dan bandara, Lun Hotel Manado menjadi pilihan sempurna bagi wisatawan bisnis maupun liburan yang berkunjung ke Sulawesi Utara.</p>', '<p>Located in the heart of <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>Lun Hotel Manado</strong> offers comfortable and modern accommodation in the vibrant <strong>Manado City Center</strong>. Its prime location makes it an excellent choice for travelers who wish to explore the city’s cultural landmarks and local attractions.</p><p>The hotel is just steps away from <strong>Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong>, one of the oldest and most historic Chinese temples in Manado. Other nearby attractions include the <strong>North Sulawesi State Museum</strong>, located about <strong>1.7 km away</strong>, and <strong>Kalimas Port</strong>, approximately <strong>1.9 km from the hotel</strong>.</p><p>For travelers arriving by air, the hotel is located about <strong>14 km from Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, which takes around <strong>25–30 minutes by car</strong>.</p><p>Guests can enjoy a variety of convenient facilities including <strong>free WiFi throughout the property</strong>, concierge services, and a <strong>24-hour front desk</strong> ready to assist with any requests. Multilingual staff and luggage storage services are also available for added convenience.</p><p>At the hotel restaurant, guests can enjoy a selection of delicious dishes in a comfortable setting. For transportation needs, the hotel also offers a <strong>24-hour airport shuttle service (additional charge)</strong>, as well as <strong>free self-parking</strong> on site.</p><p><strong>Lun Hotel Manado</strong> features <strong>60 comfortable guest rooms</strong> designed to provide a home-like atmosphere. Each room is equipped with <strong>free WiFi</strong>, a private bathroom with a bathtub or shower, a hairdryer, a work desk, and <strong>complimentary bottled water</strong>. Daily housekeeping service ensures a pleasant and relaxing stay.</p><p>With its strategic downtown location and easy access to major attractions and the airport, Lun Hotel Manado is a perfect choice for both business and leisure travelers visiting North Sulawesi.</p>', '<p><strong>Lun Hotel Manado</strong>는 <strong>Manado</strong> 중심부에 위치한 편안하고 현대적인 호텔로, 마나도 시내를 여행하기에 매우 편리한 위치를 자랑합니다.</p><p>호텔은 마나도에서 가장 오래된 중국 사원 중 하나인 **Ban Hin Kiong Temple**에서 몇 걸음 거리에 있으며, **North Sulawesi State Museum**까지 약 <strong>1.7km</strong>, **Kalimas Port**까지 약 <strong>1.9km</strong> 거리에 있습니다.</p><p>또한 호텔은 **Sam Ratulangi International Airport**에서 약 <strong>14km</strong> 떨어져 있으며, 차량으로 약 <strong>25~30분</strong> 정도 소요됩니다.</p><p>호텔에서는 <strong>무료 Wi-Fi</strong>, 컨시어지 서비스, <strong>24시간 프런트 데스크</strong> 등 다양한 편의시설을 제공하며, 다국어를 구사하는 직원과 수하물 보관 서비스도 이용할 수 있습니다.</p><p>호텔 레스토랑에서는 다양한 맛있는 요리를 즐길 수 있으며, **24시간 공항 셔틀 서비스(유료)**와 <strong>무료 주차장</strong>도 제공됩니다.</p><p>총 <strong>60개의 객실</strong>은 아늑하고 편안한 분위기로 꾸며져 있으며, 각 객실에는 <strong>무료 Wi-Fi</strong>, 욕조 또는 샤워 시설이 있는 전용 욕실, 헤어드라이어, 업무용 책상, 무료 생수가 제공됩니다. 매일 객실 청소 서비스도 제공되어 편안한 숙박을 보장합니다.</p>', '<p><strong>Lun Hotel Manado</strong> 位于 <strong>Manado</strong> 市中心，地理位置优越，是探索马纳多城市文化和景点的理想住宿选择。</p><p>酒店距离历史悠久的 <strong>Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong> 仅几步之遥。附近还有 <strong>North Sulawesi State Museum</strong>（约 <strong>1.7 公里</strong>）以及 <strong>Kalimas Port</strong>（约 <strong>1.9 公里</strong>）。</p><p>酒店距离 <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong> 约 <strong>14 公里</strong>，车程约 <strong>25–30 分钟</strong>，交通十分便利。</p><p>酒店提供多种便利设施，包括 <strong>免费 WiFi、礼宾服务以及 24 小时前台服务</strong>。此外，还提供多语言工作人员服务和行李寄存服务，为客人提供更多便利。</p><p>酒店餐厅为客人提供美味餐点。酒店还提供 <strong>24 小时机场接送服务（需额外收费）</strong>，以及 <strong>免费停车场</strong>。</p><p>酒店共有 <strong>60 间舒适客房</strong>，每间客房均配备 <strong>免费 WiFi、带浴缸或淋浴的私人浴室、吹风机、书桌以及免费瓶装饮用水</strong>。每日客房清洁服务确保客人拥有舒适愉快的入住体验。</p>', '[\"Restoran\",\"Penjemputan di bandara\",\"Pengantaran ke bandara\",\"Rental mobil\",\"Ruang pertemuan\",\"Wi-Fi di tempat umum\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/weuUjADudtkPNZy1pZjzCyVcwKDygv26xibDqgqF.webp', '2026-04-25 02:31:28', '2026-04-25 02:31:28'),
(79, 'Uma Villa Manado', 'uma-villa-manado-E25KwR', 'Manado', 'boutique', 2, '<p>Terletak di kawasan tenang di <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>Uma Villa Manado</strong> menawarkan pengalaman menginap yang nyaman dengan suasana privat serta pemandangan pegunungan yang menenangkan. Villa ini sangat cocok bagi wisatawan yang mencari ketenangan sekaligus tetap dekat dengan pusat aktivitas kota.</p><p>Akomodasi ini berjarak sekitar <strong>9,2 km dari Port of Manado</strong> dan sekitar <strong>18 km dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, dengan waktu perjalanan sekitar <strong>30–35 menit berkendara</strong>.</p><p>Setiap unit villa dilengkapi dengan <strong>teras pribadi</strong>, pendingin ruangan (AC), dan <strong>TV layar datar</strong> untuk kenyamanan tamu. Kamar mandi pribadi menyediakan shower serta perlengkapan mandi gratis. Beberapa unit juga memiliki <strong>area tempat duduk dan balkon</strong>, memberikan ruang tambahan untuk bersantai sambil menikmati pemandangan alam sekitar.</p><p>Para tamu dapat menikmati fasilitas <strong>WiFi gratis dan parkir pribadi gratis</strong> selama menginap. Selain itu, tersedia <strong>taman hijau yang asri</strong>, tempat sempurna untuk bersantai, menikmati udara segar, atau menghabiskan waktu dengan tenang jauh dari keramaian kota.</p><p>Dengan suasana yang nyaman, pemandangan alam yang indah, serta akses yang cukup mudah menuju kota dan bandara, Uma Villa Manado menjadi pilihan ideal bagi wisatawan yang ingin merasakan <strong>pengalaman menginap yang santai dan privat di Sulawesi Utara</strong>.</p>', '<p>Located in a peaceful area of <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>Uma Villa Manado</strong> offers a relaxing private villa experience with beautiful mountain views. The property is perfect for travelers seeking tranquility while still staying close to the city.</p><p>The villa is located about <strong>9.2 km from Port of Manado</strong> and approximately <strong>18 km from Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, which takes around <strong>30–35 minutes by car</strong>.</p><p>Each villa unit features a <strong>private terrace</strong>, air conditioning, and a <strong>flat-screen TV</strong> for guests’ comfort. The private bathrooms are equipped with a shower and complimentary toiletries. Some units also offer a <strong>seating area and balcony</strong>, allowing guests to relax while enjoying the surrounding natural scenery.</p><p>Guests can enjoy <strong>free WiFi and free private parking</strong> during their stay. The property also features a <strong>lush garden area</strong>, providing a peaceful space where guests can unwind and enjoy the fresh air.</p><p>With its comfortable atmosphere, scenic mountain views, and convenient access to the city and airport, Uma Villa Manado is an excellent choice for travelers looking for a <strong>peaceful and private stay in North Sulawesi</strong>.</p>', '<p><strong>Uma Villa Manado</strong>는 **Manado**의 조용한 지역에 위치한 빌라 숙소로, 아름다운 산 전망과 함께 편안하고 프라이빗한 휴식을 제공합니다. 자연 속에서 여유로운 시간을 보내고 싶은 여행객에게 이상적인 숙소입니다.</p><p>이 숙소는 **Port of Manado**에서 약 <strong>9.2km</strong>, **Sam Ratulangi International Airport**에서 약 <strong>18km</strong> 떨어져 있으며, 차량으로 약 <strong>30~35분</strong> 정도 소요됩니다.</p><p>각 객실은 <strong>전용 테라스</strong>, 에어컨, <strong>평면 TV</strong>를 갖추고 있어 편안한 숙박을 제공합니다. 전용 욕실에는 샤워 시설과 무료 세면도구가 마련되어 있습니다. 일부 객실에는 <strong>휴식 공간과 발코니</strong>도 있어 주변 자연 경관을 감상하며 여유로운 시간을 보낼 수 있습니다.</p><p>숙소에서는 <strong>무료 Wi-Fi와 무료 전용 주차장</strong>을 이용할 수 있으며, 투숙객이 휴식을 취할 수 있는 <strong>아름다운 정원 공간</strong>도 마련되어 있습니다.</p><p>편안한 분위기와 아름다운 자연 전망, 그리고 공항과 도심으로의 편리한 접근성을 갖춘 Uma Villa Manado는 <strong>북술라웨시에서 조용하고 프라이빗한 휴식을 원하는 여행객에게 완벽한 선택</strong>입니다.</p>', '<p><strong>Uma Villa Manado</strong> 位于 <strong>Manado</strong> 安静的地区，提供带有美丽山景的私人别墅式住宿。这里环境宁静，非常适合希望远离城市喧嚣、享受放松假期的旅客。</p><p>酒店距离 <strong>Port of Manado</strong> 约 <strong>9.2 公里</strong>，距离 <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong> 约 <strong>18 公里</strong>，车程约 <strong>30–35 分钟</strong>，交通十分便利。</p><p>每个别墅单元都配备 <strong>私人露台、空调和平板电视</strong>，为客人提供舒适的住宿体验。私人浴室配有淋浴设施和免费洗浴用品。部分房型还设有 <strong>休息区或阳台</strong>，客人可以在这里放松身心并欣赏周围的自然景观。</p><p>住宿期间，客人可以享受 <strong>免费 WiFi 和免费私人停车位</strong>。此外，酒店还拥有 <strong>绿意盎然的花园</strong>，为客人提供一个安静舒适的休闲空间。</p><p>凭借宁静的环境、优美的自然景观以及方便前往市区和机场的地理位置，Uma Villa Manado 是在北苏拉威西寻找 <strong>安静、舒适与私密住宿体验</strong> 的理想选择。<br>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '[\"Kolam Renang Outdoor\",\"Area ParkirGratis\",\"Wi-Fi di tempat umum\",\"Kolam renang infinity\",\"Kolam dengan pemandangan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/uC0c3gPzg5Qz5PXnXCURCyL5HRA6tJdeisIFbB1O.webp', '2026-04-25 03:03:22', '2026-04-25 03:03:22'),
(80, 'De Ggii Hotel by Flip Inn Hotel', 'de-ggii-hotel-by-flip-inn-hotel-12Mvcp', 'Jl. Temboan No.5, Winangun Dua', 'city_hotel', 2, '<p>Terletak di kawasan <strong>Pusat Kota</strong> <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>De Ggii Hotel by Flip Inn</strong> menawarkan akomodasi yang nyaman dengan suasana modern dan lokasi strategis. Hotel ini cocok bagi wisatawan maupun pelancong bisnis yang ingin menikmati kemudahan akses ke berbagai pusat perbelanjaan, kuliner, dan tempat wisata di kota Manado.</p><p>Dari hotel, Anda hanya membutuhkan waktu sekitar <strong>10 menit berkendara menuju Manado Town Square</strong> dan <strong>Mega Mall Manado</strong>, dua pusat perbelanjaan populer di kota ini. Selain itu, hotel juga berjarak sekitar <strong>5,9 km dari Malalayang Beach</strong> yang terkenal dengan pemandangan laut dan tempat menikmati kuliner lokal, serta sekitar <strong>6,6 km dari Tomohon Market</strong>.</p><p>Bagi tamu yang datang melalui jalur udara, hotel ini berjarak sekitar <strong>19 km dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, dengan waktu perjalanan sekitar <strong>35–40 menit berkendara</strong>.</p><p>Hotel ini memiliki <strong>30 kamar</strong> yang dirancang sederhana namun nyaman untuk memberikan pengalaman menginap yang menyenangkan. Setiap kamar dilengkapi dengan <strong>akses WiFi gratis</strong>, kamar mandi pribadi dengan shower, serta <strong>meja kerja</strong> yang cocok bagi tamu yang bepergian untuk urusan bisnis. Layanan kebersihan kamar tersedia setiap hari untuk menjaga kenyamanan selama menginap.</p><p>Selain itu, hotel juga menyediakan <strong>parkir pribadi gratis</strong>, memberikan kemudahan bagi tamu yang membawa kendaraan pribadi.</p><p>Dengan lokasi strategis, akses mudah ke pusat kota dan tempat wisata, serta fasilitas yang nyaman, De Ggii Hotel by Flip Inn menjadi pilihan yang tepat bagi wisatawan yang mencari <strong>akomodasi praktis dan nyaman di Manado</strong>.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Located in the <strong>city center of</strong> <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>De Ggii Hotel by Flip Inn</strong> offers comfortable accommodation with a modern atmosphere and a strategic location. The hotel is ideal for both leisure and business travelers looking for easy access to shopping areas, dining spots, and local attractions in Manado.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The hotel is only about <strong>10 minutes by car from Manado Town Square</strong> and <strong>Mega Mall Manado</strong>, two of the most popular shopping destinations in the city. It is also located approximately <strong>5.9 km from Malalayang Beach</strong>, a well-known coastal area famous for its seaside views and local food stalls, and about <strong>6.6 km from Tomohon Market</strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">For guests arriving by air, the hotel is around <strong>19 km from Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, which takes approximately <strong>35–40 minutes by car</strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The property features <strong>30 comfortable guest rooms</strong> designed to provide a pleasant stay. Each room includes <strong>free WiFi</strong>, a private bathroom with a shower, and a <strong>work desk</strong>, making it suitable for both relaxation and business needs. Daily housekeeping service is available to ensure guest comfort.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The hotel also offers <strong>free private parking</strong> for guests traveling with their own vehicles.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">With its convenient location and comfortable facilities, De Ggii Hotel by Flip Inn is a great choice for travelers seeking <strong>a practical and pleasant stay in Manado</strong>.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>De Ggii Hotel by Flip Inn</strong>는 <strong>Manado</strong> 시내 중심부에 위치한 편안한 호텔로, 쇼핑몰과 관광지로 이동하기에 편리한 위치를 자랑합니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">호텔에서 **Manado Town Square**와 **Mega Mall Manado**까지는 차로 약 <strong>10분</strong> 정도 소요됩니다. 또한 **Malalayang Beach**까지 약 <strong>5.9km</strong>, **Tomohon Market**까지 약 <strong>6.6km</strong> 거리에 있습니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">호텔은 **Sam Ratulangi International Airport**에서 약 <strong>19km</strong> 떨어져 있으며, 차량으로 약 <strong>35~40분</strong> 정도 소요됩니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">호텔에는 총 <strong>30개의 객실</strong>이 있으며, 각 객실에는 <strong>무료 Wi-Fi</strong>, 샤워 시설이 있는 전용 욕실, 업무용 책상이 마련되어 있습니다. 또한 매일 객실 청소 서비스가 제공되어 쾌적한 숙박을 제공합니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">호텔에서는 <strong>무료 주차장</strong>도 이용할 수 있어 차량을 이용하는 여행객에게 편리합니다.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>De Ggii Hotel by Flip Inn</strong> 位于 <strong>Manado</strong> 市中心，是一家舒适便捷的酒店，方便客人前往城市的购物中心和主要景点。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">酒店距离 <strong>Manado Town Square</strong> 和 <strong>Mega Mall Manado</strong> 约 <strong>10 分钟车程</strong>。此外，酒店距离 <strong>Malalayang Beach</strong> 约 <strong>5.9 公里</strong>，距离 <strong>Tomohon Market</strong> 约 <strong>6.6 公里</strong>。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">酒店距离 <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong> 约 <strong>19 公里</strong>，车程约 <strong>35–40 分钟</strong>。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">酒店共有 <strong>30 间客房</strong>，每间客房均配备 <strong>免费 WiFi、带淋浴的私人浴室以及书桌</strong>。酒店每天提供客房清洁服务，为客人提供舒适愉快的住宿体验。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">此外，酒店还提供 <strong>免费私人停车位</strong>，为自驾旅客提供便利。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">凭借优越的地理位置和舒适的设施，De Ggii Hotel by Flip Inn 是在马纳多寻找 <strong>实用且舒适住宿</strong> 的理想选择。</p>', '[\"WiFi\",\"AC\",\"Resepsionis 24 Jam\",\"Lift\",\"Parkir Gratis\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/VU8gDXKwXsZJYdHn3O8Yl12X9jcWwSp71LPdFiGY.jpg', '2026-04-25 03:20:22', '2026-04-25 03:39:54'),
(81, 'Biz Boulevard Hotel', 'biz-boulevard-hotel-NUbDtB', 'Manado', 'city_hotel', 3, '<p>Terletak di pusat kota <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>Biz Boulevard Hotel</strong> menawarkan akomodasi modern dengan lokasi strategis yang memudahkan tamu menjelajahi berbagai pusat perbelanjaan, tempat wisata, dan kawasan bisnis di kota ini.</p><p>Hotel ini hanya sekitar <strong>3 menit berjalan kaki dari Mega Mall Manado</strong> dan sekitar <strong>2 menit berkendara dari North Sulawesi State Museum</strong>. Beberapa destinasi populer lainnya seperti <strong>Soekarno Bridge</strong> dan <strong>Manado Town Square</strong> juga dapat dicapai dalam waktu singkat, masing-masing sekitar <strong>1,8 km dari hotel</strong>.</p><p>Bagi tamu yang datang melalui jalur udara, hotel ini berjarak sekitar <strong>15 km dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, dengan waktu perjalanan sekitar <strong>30 menit berkendara</strong>.</p><p>Biz Boulevard Hotel menyediakan berbagai fasilitas untuk kenyamanan tamu, termasuk <strong>WiFi gratis di seluruh area</strong>, layanan concierge, pusat bisnis, serta layanan laundry dan dry cleaning. Resepsionis 24 jam siap membantu kebutuhan tamu kapan saja. Tersedia juga <strong>layanan antar-jemput bandara 24 jam dengan biaya tambahan</strong>, serta <strong>parkir valet gratis</strong> bagi tamu yang membawa kendaraan.</p><p>Hotel ini memiliki <strong>48 kamar ber-AC</strong> yang dirancang dengan nyaman dan modern. Setiap kamar dilengkapi dengan <strong>TV LCD dengan saluran kabel</strong>, akses <strong>WiFi gratis</strong>, serta kamar mandi pribadi dengan shower, perlengkapan mandi premium, dan sandal. Fasilitas tambahan seperti <strong>brankas dan meja kerja</strong> juga tersedia, sementara layanan kebersihan kamar dilakukan setiap hari untuk memastikan kenyamanan selama menginap.</p><p>Dengan lokasi strategis di pusat kota serta akses mudah ke berbagai tempat menarik di Manado, Biz Boulevard Hotel menjadi pilihan yang tepat bagi wisatawan bisnis maupun liburan.</p>', '<p>Located in the heart of <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>Biz Boulevard Hotel</strong> offers comfortable modern accommodation with a strategic location that allows guests to easily explore the city’s shopping areas, attractions, and business districts.</p><p>The hotel is just <strong>a 3-minute walk from Mega Mall Manado</strong> and about <strong>a 2-minute drive from North Sulawesi State Museum</strong>. Other popular landmarks such as <strong>Soekarno Bridge</strong> and <strong>Manado Town Square</strong> are also easily accessible, both located around <strong>1.8 km from the hotel</strong>.</p><p>For travelers arriving by air, the hotel is approximately <strong>15 km from Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, which takes around <strong>30 minutes by car</strong>.</p><p>Biz Boulevard Hotel provides a variety of convenient facilities including <strong>free WiFi throughout the property</strong>, concierge services, a business center, and laundry/dry cleaning services. A <strong>24-hour front desk</strong> is available to assist guests at any time. The hotel also offers a <strong>24-hour airport shuttle service (additional charge)</strong> and <strong>free valet parking</strong> on site.</p><p>The hotel features <strong>48 air-conditioned guest rooms</strong> designed with comfort and practicality in mind. Each room includes an <strong>LCD TV with cable channels</strong>, <strong>free WiFi</strong>, and a private bathroom with a shower, designer toiletries, and slippers. Additional amenities such as a <strong>safe and work desk</strong> are provided, and daily housekeeping ensures a pleasant stay.</p><p>With its central location and easy access to key attractions in Manado, Biz Boulevard Hotel is an ideal choice for both business and leisure travelers.</p>', '<p><strong>Biz Boulevard Hotel</strong>는 <strong>Manado</strong> 중심부에 위치한 현대적인 호텔로, 쇼핑몰과 주요 관광지에 쉽게 접근할 수 있는 편리한 위치를 자랑합니다.</p><p>호텔은 **Mega Mall Manado**에서 도보 약 <strong>3분</strong>, **North Sulawesi State Museum**에서 차로 약 <strong>2분</strong> 거리에 있습니다. 또한 **Soekarno Bridge**와 **Manado Town Square**도 약 <strong>1.8km</strong> 거리로 가까워 관광과 쇼핑을 즐기기에 좋습니다.</p><p>호텔은 **Sam Ratulangi International Airport**에서 약 <strong>15km</strong> 떨어져 있으며, 차량으로 약 <strong>30분</strong> 정도 소요됩니다.</p><p>호텔에서는 <strong>무료 Wi-Fi</strong>, 컨시어지 서비스, 비즈니스 센터, 세탁 및 드라이클리닝 서비스 등을 제공합니다. 또한 <strong>24시간 프런트 데스크</strong>와 **공항 셔틀 서비스(유료)**가 제공되며, <strong>무료 발레 주차 서비스</strong>도 이용할 수 있습니다.</p><p>총 <strong>48개의 에어컨 객실</strong>은 편안한 숙박을 위해 설계되었으며, 각 객실에는 <strong>LCD TV, 케이블 채널, 무료 Wi-Fi</strong>가 제공됩니다. 전용 욕실에는 샤워 시설, 고급 세면도구, 슬리퍼가 마련되어 있으며, <strong>금고와 업무용 책상</strong>도 갖추어져 있습니다. 매일 객실 청소 서비스가 제공되어 편안한 숙박을 보장합니다.</p>', '<p><strong>Biz Boulevard Hotel</strong> 位于 <strong>Manado</strong> 市中心，是一家现代舒适的酒店，地理位置优越，方便客人前往城市的购物中心、景点以及商业区。</p><p>酒店距离 <strong>Mega Mall Manado</strong> 仅 <strong>步行约3分钟</strong>，距离 <strong>North Sulawesi State Museum</strong> 约 <strong>2分钟车程</strong>。此外，<strong>Soekarno Bridge</strong> 和 <strong>Manado Town Square</strong> 也仅约 <strong>1.8 公里</strong>，交通十分便利。</p><p>酒店距离 <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong> 约 <strong>15 公里</strong>，车程约 <strong>30 分钟</strong>。</p><p>酒店提供多种便利设施，包括 <strong>免费 WiFi、礼宾服务、商务中心以及洗衣/干洗服务</strong>。酒店设有 <strong>24 小时前台</strong>，并提供 <strong>24 小时机场接送服务（需额外收费）</strong> 和 <strong>免费代客停车服务</strong>。</p><p>酒店共有 <strong>48 间空调客房</strong>，每间客房均配备 <strong>LCD 电视、卫星/有线频道以及免费 WiFi</strong>。私人浴室配有淋浴设施、设计师洗浴用品和拖鞋。此外，客房还配有 <strong>保险箱和书桌</strong>，并提供每日客房清洁服务，为客人带来舒适愉快的住宿体验。<br>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '[\"Restoran\",\"Spa\",\"Area ParkirGratis\",\"Penjemputan di bandara\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/MBck8vFy8r3kdj4aWI1w1MfLBv9vD4kMWqwP3Dqg.webp', '2026-04-25 03:24:18', '2026-04-26 13:26:08'),
(82, 'Maleosan Inn Hotel', 'maleosan-inn-hotel-OOX831', 'Tikala Kumaraka, Kec. Wenang,', 'city_hotel', 3, '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Maleosan Inn Manado</strong> merupakan hotel budget yang menawarkan kenyamanan menginap dengan harga terjangkau di lokasi yang sangat strategis di pusat Kota Manado. Terletak di kawasan Wenang, hotel ini memberikan kemudahan akses ke berbagai pusat bisnis, area kuliner, serta destinasi populer seperti kawasan Megamas dan pusat perbelanjaan, menjadikannya pilihan ideal baik untuk perjalanan bisnis maupun liburan.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setiap kamar di Maleosan Inn dirancang secara sederhana namun fungsional, dilengkapi dengan fasilitas seperti AC, TV layar datar, meja kerja, serta kamar mandi pribadi dengan perlengkapan lengkap. Suasana kamar yang bersih dan nyaman memberikan tempat istirahat yang ideal setelah beraktivitas seharian menjelajahi kota atau menghadiri agenda pekerjaan.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Untuk menunjang kenyamanan tamu, hotel ini juga menyediakan berbagai fasilitas seperti WiFi gratis, area parkir, restoran, serta layanan resepsionis 24 jam yang siap membantu kebutuhan Anda. Selain itu, tersedia pula layanan tambahan seperti laundry dan penyewaan kendaraan yang semakin memudahkan mobilitas selama berada di Manado.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Dengan kombinasi lokasi strategis, fasilitas yang memadai, serta harga yang bersahabat, Maleosan Inn Manado menghadirkan pengalaman menginap yang praktis, nyaman, dan efisien. Hotel ini sangat cocok bagi traveler modern yang mencari akomodasi sederhana namun tetap berkualitas di jantung Kota Manado.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Maleosan Inn Manado is a budget hotel that offers a comfortable stay at an affordable price, located in a highly strategic area in the heart of Manado. Situated in the Wenang district, the hotel provides easy access to business centers, culinary spots, and popular destinations such as the Megamas area and shopping centers, making it an ideal choice for both business and leisure travelers.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Each room at Maleosan Inn is designed simply yet functionally, equipped with facilities such as air conditioning, a flat-screen TV, a work desk, and a private bathroom with complete amenities. The clean and cozy atmosphere creates a perfect place to rest after a day of exploring the city or attending business activities.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">To enhance guests’ comfort, the hotel offers facilities such as free WiFi, parking area, a restaurant, and a 24-hour front desk ready to assist with your needs. Additional services such as laundry and car rental are also available, making your stay in Manado even more convenient.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">With its strategic location, adequate facilities, and affordable rates, Maleosan Inn Manado delivers a practical, comfortable, and efficient stay experience. It is a perfect choice for modern travelers seeking simple yet quality accommodation in the heart of the city.</p>', '<p>Maleosan Inn Manado는 합리적인 가격에 편안한 숙박을 제공하는 경제형 호텔로, 마나도 중심부의 전략적인 위치에 자리하고 있습니다. Wenang 지역에 위치하여 비즈니스 중심지, 다양한 맛집, 그리고 Megamas 지역 및 쇼핑센터와 같은 주요 명소로의 접근이 용이해 비즈니스 및 레저 여행객 모두에게 이상적인 선택입니다.</p><p>각 객실은 심플하면서도 기능적으로 설계되어 있으며, 에어컨, 평면 TV, 업무용 책상, 그리고 다양한 어메니티가 구비된 전용 욕실을 갖추고 있습니다. 깨끗하고 아늑한 객실 분위기는 하루 일정을 마친 후 편안한 휴식을 제공합니다.</p><p>호텔은 무료 Wi-Fi, 주차 공간, 레스토랑, 24시간 프런트 데스크 서비스를 제공하여 투숙객의 편의를 높입니다. 또한 세탁 서비스 및 차량 대여 서비스도 이용 가능하여 마나도에서의 이동과 숙박이 더욱 편리합니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">전략적인 위치와 합리적인 가격, 그리고 편리한 시설을 갖춘 Maleosan Inn Manado는 실용적이고 편안한 숙박 경험을 제공하며, 도심에서 합리적인 숙소를 찾는 현대 여행객에게 적합한 선택입니다.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Maleosan Inn Manado 是一家位于万鸦老市中心的经济型酒店，提供舒适且价格实惠的住宿体验。酒店坐落于 Wenang 区，地理位置优越，方便前往商业中心、美食区以及 Megamas 区和各大购物中心，是商务及休闲旅客的理想选择。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">酒店客房设计简约而实用，配备空调、平板电视、办公桌以及带齐全洗浴用品的独立浴室。整洁舒适的环境，为客人在一天的城市探索或商务活动后提供理想的休息空间。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">为提升入住体验，酒店提供免费 WiFi、停车场、餐厅以及24小时前台服务，随时满足客人的需求。此外，还提供洗衣服务和车辆租赁服务，让您在万鸦老的出行更加便捷。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">凭借其优越的地理位置、完善的设施以及亲民的价格，Maleosan Inn Manado 为旅客带来实用、舒适且高效的住宿体验，是寻求高性价比住宿的现代旅客的理想之选。</p>', '[\"Restoran\",\"Area Parkir Pribadi\",\"Penyimpanan bagasi\",\"Layanan bangun tidur\",\"Wi-Fi\",\"Kafe\",\"Rental mobil\",\"Area merokok\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/aKs3u0k0WpBc2XJ38XebHWH23AQXO01rARFQDMM7.webp', '2026-04-25 03:38:52', '2026-04-25 03:38:53'),
(83, 'Green Eden Hotel', 'green-eden-hotel-KJWyIZ', 'Manado', 'city_hotel', 3, '<p>Terletak di kota <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>Green Eden Hotel</strong> menawarkan akomodasi nyaman dengan lokasi strategis, hanya sekitar <strong>1 km dari Megamas Beach</strong>. Hotel ini menjadi pilihan tepat bagi wisatawan yang ingin menikmati suasana kota sekaligus mudah mengakses pusat perbelanjaan, kuliner, dan hiburan di Manado.</p><p>Hotel bintang 2 ini menyediakan berbagai fasilitas untuk menunjang kenyamanan tamu, termasuk <strong>lounge bersama yang nyaman</strong>, <strong>bar</strong>, serta <strong>parkir pribadi gratis</strong>. Resepsionis <strong>24 jam</strong> siap membantu kebutuhan tamu, termasuk <strong>layanan kamar, penyimpanan bagasi</strong>, serta <strong>layanan antar-jemput bandara</strong>. Akses <strong>WiFi gratis tersedia di seluruh area hotel</strong> sehingga tamu tetap dapat terhubung selama menginap.</p><p>Setiap kamar di hotel ini dirancang sederhana namun fungsional, dilengkapi dengan <strong>AC, TV layar datar dengan saluran kabel, ketel listrik, meja kerja</strong>, serta kamar mandi pribadi dengan <strong>shower dan sandal kamar</strong>. Seprai dan handuk juga disediakan untuk kenyamanan selama menginap.</p><p>Untuk pengalaman kuliner, tamu dapat menikmati berbagai <strong>hidangan khas Indonesia</strong> yang disajikan di restoran hotel.</p><p>Bagi tamu yang datang melalui jalur udara, <strong>Green Eden Hotel berjarak sekitar 17 km dari Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, dengan waktu perjalanan sekitar <strong>30–35 menit berkendara</strong>.</p><p>Dengan lokasi yang strategis dekat pantai dan pusat kota, serta fasilitas yang nyaman, Green Eden Hotel menjadi pilihan ideal bagi wisatawan yang mencari <strong>akomodasi praktis dan terjangkau di Manado</strong>.</p>', '<p>Located in <strong>Manado</strong>, <strong>Green Eden Hotel</strong> offers comfortable accommodation in a strategic location, less than <strong>1 km from Megamas Beach</strong>. The hotel is an ideal choice for travelers who want easy access to shopping areas, restaurants, and entertainment spots in Manado.</p><p>This <strong>2-star hotel</strong> features a variety of convenient facilities including a <strong>shared lounge, bar, and free private parking</strong>. Guests can also enjoy <strong>24-hour front desk service</strong>, <strong>room service</strong>, <strong>luggage storage</strong>, and <strong>airport transfer services</strong>. <strong>Free WiFi is available throughout the property</strong>, ensuring guests stay connected during their stay.</p><p>Each guest room is designed for comfort and practicality, featuring <strong>air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with cable channels, an electric kettle, and a work desk</strong>. The private bathrooms are equipped with <strong>a shower and slippers</strong>, while <strong>bed linen and towels</strong> are also provided.</p><p>Guests can enjoy a selection of <strong>Indonesian dishes</strong> served at the hotel’s restaurant, offering a convenient dining experience during their stay.</p><p>For travelers arriving by air, the hotel is located approximately <strong>17 km from Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong>, which takes around <strong>30–35 minutes by car</strong>.</p><p>With its convenient location near the beach and city center, Green Eden Hotel is a great choice for travelers seeking <strong>affordable and practical accommodation in Manado</strong>.</p>', '<p><strong>Green Eden Hotel</strong>은 **Manado**에 위치한 편안한 호텔로, **Megamas Beach**에서 약 <strong>1km 이내</strong> 거리에 있습니다. 쇼핑몰, 레스토랑, 관광지와 가까워 여행객들에게 편리한 위치를 제공합니다.</p><p>호텔은 <strong>공용 라운지, 바, 무료 전용 주차장</strong> 등 다양한 편의시설을 제공합니다. 또한 <strong>24시간 프런트 데스크</strong>, <strong>룸서비스</strong>, <strong>수하물 보관 서비스</strong>, <strong>공항 픽업 서비스</strong>를 이용할 수 있으며, 호텔 전역에서 <strong>무료 Wi-Fi</strong>가 제공됩니다.</p><p>객실에는 <strong>에어컨, 케이블 채널이 있는 평면 TV, 전기 주전자, 업무용 책상</strong>이 마련되어 있으며, 전용 욕실에는 <strong>샤워 시설과 슬리퍼</strong>가 제공됩니다. 또한 <strong>침대 린넨과 수건</strong>도 준비되어 있어 편안한 숙박을 즐길 수 있습니다.</p><p>호텔 레스토랑에서는 <strong>다양한 인도네시아 요리</strong>를 맛볼 수 있어 여행 중 편리하게 식사를 즐길 수 있습니다.</p><p>호텔은 **Sam Ratulangi International Airport**에서 약 <strong>17km</strong> 떨어져 있으며, 차량으로 약 <strong>30~35분</strong> 정도 소요됩니다.</p>', '<p><strong>Green Eden Hotel</strong> 位于 <strong>Manado</strong>，距离 <strong>Megamas Beach</strong> 不到 <strong>1 公里</strong>，地理位置优越，方便客人前往城市的购物中心、餐厅和娱乐区域。</p><p>这家 <strong>两星级酒店</strong> 提供多种便利设施，包括 <strong>公共休息区、酒吧以及免费私人停车场</strong>。酒店设有 <strong>24 小时前台服务</strong>，并提供 <strong>客房服务、行李寄存和机场接送服务</strong>。此外，酒店全区域均提供 <strong>免费 WiFi</strong>，方便客人在住宿期间保持网络连接。</p><p>酒店客房舒适实用，每间客房均配备 <strong>空调、带有线频道的平板电视、电热水壶以及书桌</strong>。私人浴室配有 <strong>淋浴设施和拖鞋</strong>，并提供 <strong>床单和毛巾</strong>。</p><p>客人还可以在酒店餐厅品尝到 <strong>多种印尼特色美食</strong>。</p><p>酒店距离 <strong>Sam Ratulangi International Airport</strong> 约 <strong>17 公里</strong>，车程约 <strong>30–35 分钟</strong>。</p><p>凭借便利的地理位置和舒适的设施，Green Eden Hotel 是在马纳多寻找 <strong>经济实惠住宿</strong> 的理想选择。</p>', '[\"Restoran\",\"Area Parkir PribadiGratis\",\"Penukaran mata uang\",\"Penyimpanan bagasi\",\"Wi-Fi di tempat umumGratis\",\"Bar\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/GmKixuEJQlbAWZhA0qoGWDooPerICvHH5I6xw3YM.webp', '2026-04-25 03:42:48', '2026-04-25 03:43:18');
INSERT INTO `hotels` (`id`, `name`, `slug`, `location`, `category`, `stars`, `description`, `description_en`, `description_ko`, `description_zh`, `facilities`, `primary_image`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(84, 'Arcadia Hotel', 'arcadia-hotel-manado-OpyNok', 'Jalan Pramuka No 74-76, sakobar', 'city_hotel', 2, '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Arcadia Hotel Manado adalah pilihan akomodasi yang menawarkan keseimbangan sempurna antara kenyamanan, lokasi strategis, dan harga terjangkau di jantung kota Manado. Hotel ini cocok untuk traveler modern—baik pebisnis maupun wisatawan—yang mencari tempat menginap praktis namun tetap nyaman.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Terletak di kawasan Sario yang cukup strategis, Arcadia Hotel menghadirkan suasana menginap yang tenang dengan sentuhan modern minimalis. Dari kamar, tamu dapat menikmati pemandangan kota Manado yang dinamis, sekaligus merasakan atmosfer yang nyaman dan privat. Dengan konsep sederhana namun fungsional, hotel ini menjadi pilihan ideal untuk perjalanan singkat maupun pejalanan panjang rubah kedalam bahasa inggris korea china</p>', '<p>Arcadia Hotel Manado is an accommodation choice that offers a perfect balance of comfort, strategic location, and affordable prices in the heart of Manado. This hotel is ideal for modern travelers—both business and leisure—who seek a practical yet comfortable stay.</p><p>Located in the strategic Sario area, Arcadia Hotel presents a calm and relaxing atmosphere with a modern minimalist touch. From the rooms, guests can enjoy views of the dynamic city of Manado while experiencing a cozy and private ambiance. With its simple yet functional concept, this hotel is an ideal choice for both short getaways and long stays.</p>', '<p>아르카디아 호텔 마나도는 마나도 중심부에 위치하여 편안함, 전략적인 위치, 합리적인 가격을 완벽하게 갖춘 숙소입니다. 이 호텔은 비즈니스 여행객과 관광객 모두에게 적합하며, 실용적이면서도 편안한 숙박을 원하는 현대적인 여행자들에게 이상적입니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">전략적인 사리오(Sario) 지역에 위치한 아르카디아 호텔은 모던 미니멀리즘 감각이 더해진 조용하고 편안한 분위기를 제공합니다. 객실에서는 활기찬 마나도 시내 전망을 감상할 수 있으며, 아늑하고 프라이빗한 환경을 경험할 수 있습니다. 심플하면서도 기능적인 콘셉트로, 단기 여행뿐만 아니라 장기 투숙에도 적합한 선택입니다.</p>', '<p>阿卡迪亚马纳多酒店是一家位于马纳多市中心的理想住宿选择，完美融合了舒适性、优越地理位置和实惠价格。无论是商务旅客还是休闲游客，这里都非常适合追求便捷与舒适住宿体验的现代旅行者。</p><p>酒店坐落于交通便利的Sario区域，营造出宁静且带有现代简约风格的住宿氛围。从客房内，客人可以欣赏到充满活力的马纳多城市景观，同时享受温馨而私密的环境。凭借简约而实用的设计理念，该酒店无论是短期旅行还是长期入住，都是理想之选。</p>', '[\"Wi-Fi gratis\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Resepsionis [24 jam]\",\"Restoran\",\"Sarapan\",\"Room service\",\"Cucian\",\"Kamar bebas rokok\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/DZdCTzWVByCZb1S62EFIjrFz8ugp63bCUX4AdWxG.webp', '2026-04-26 03:51:47', '2026-04-26 06:36:08'),
(85, 'Istanaku Hotel', 'istanaku-hotel-9Lqj3q', 'Jl. W.R. Supratman, Lawangirung', 'city_hotel', 2, '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Mengusung konsep guesthouse modern dengan desain kreatif, Istanaku dikenal dengan interiornya yang penuh ilustrasi unik dan dekorasi yang artistik. Setiap sudut hotel terasa hidup dan berbeda, memberikan pengalaman menginap yang tidak monoton. Suasananya tenang dan cozy, cocok bagi traveler yang mencari ketenangan di tengah hiruk-pikuk kota.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Hotel ini juga telah mengalami pembaruan sehingga tampil lebih rapi, bersih, dan modern tanpa kehilangan karakter khasnya. Banyak tamu menilai tempat ini sebagai salah satu penginapan yang nyaman dengan pelayanan yang ramah dan profesional</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Istanaku Hotel Manado</strong> adalah pilihan akomodasi yang menawarkan pengalaman menginap unik dengan nuansa hangat, artistik, dan penuh karakter di tengah kota Manado. Berbeda dari hotel pada umumnya, hotel ini menghadirkan suasana “homey” yang membuat tamu merasa seperti tinggal di rumah sendiri—nyaman, santai, dan penuh sentuhan personal.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Adopting a modern guesthouse concept with a creative design, Istanaku is known for its interiors filled with unique illustrations and artistic décor. Every corner of the hotel feels lively and distinctive, offering a stay experience that is far from ordinary. The atmosphere is calm and cozy, making it perfect for travelers seeking tranquility amidst the hustle and bustle of the city.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The hotel has also undergone renovations, resulting in a cleaner, neater, and more modern appearance without losing its distinctive character. Many guests consider this place to be one of the most comfortable accommodations, with friendly and professional service.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Istanaku Hotel Manado is an accommodation choice that offers a unique stay experience with a warm, artistic, and character-filled ambiance in the heart of Manado. Unlike typical hotels, it provides a “homey” atmosphere that makes guests feel as if they are staying in their own home—comfortable, relaxed, and full of personal touches.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">이 스타나쿠 호텔은 창의적인 디자인이 돋보이는 현대적인 게스트하우스 콘셉트를 바탕으로, 독특한 일러스트와 예술적인 장식으로 꾸며진 인테리어가 특징입니다. 호텔의 모든 공간은 생동감 있고 개성이 넘쳐, 단조롭지 않은 특별한 숙박 경험을 제공합니다. 또한 조용하고 아늑한 분위기를 갖추고 있어 도시의 번잡함 속에서도 평온함을 찾고자 하는 여행객에게 적합합니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">호텔은 최근 리노베이션을 거쳐 더욱 깔끔하고 세련된 현대적 공간으로 탈바꿈했으며, 기존의 개성 있는 매력을 그대로 유지하고 있습니다. 많은 투숙객들이 이곳을 편안한 숙소로 평가하며, 친절하고 전문적인 서비스 역시 높은 만족도를 얻고 있습니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">이 스타나쿠 호텔 마나도는 따뜻하고 예술적이며 개성 넘치는 분위기를 제공하는 독특한 숙박 시설로, 마나도 중심부에 위치해 있습니다. 일반적인 호텔과 달리, 집처럼 편안하고 여유로운 “홈리(homey)”한 환경을 제공하여 마치 자신의 집에 머무는 듯한 느낌을 선사합니다.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Istanaku酒店采用现代民宿概念与创意设计，以充满独特插画和艺术装饰的室内风格而闻名。酒店的每一个角落都充满活力与个性，为宾客带来与众不同且不单调的入住体验。整体氛围安静而舒适，非常适合在城市喧嚣中寻求宁静的旅客。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">酒店也经过翻新升级，使环境更加整洁、干净且现代化，同时依然保留其独特的个性魅力。许多住客认为这里是一个非常舒适的住宿选择，并对其友好且专业的服务给予高度评价。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Istanaku马纳多酒店是一家提供独特住宿体验的理想选择，位于马纳多市中心，拥有温馨、艺术感十足且富有个性的氛围。不同于一般酒店，这里营造出如家般的舒适环境，让宾客感受到放松、自在以及充满人情味的入住体验。</p>', '[\"Wi-Fi gratis\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Resepsionis [24 jam]\",\"Restoran\",\"Transfer bandara\",\"Ruang keluarga\",\"Penyimpanan bagasi\",\"Sarapan\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/nSql4ovVEpqnOzobjUuNX0gx6Utq7qWvDHhVftSZ.jpg', '2026-04-26 06:35:07', '2026-04-26 06:35:09'),
(86, 'Avon\'s Residence', 'avons-residence-jx7XF0', 'Jl. 17 Agustus Jl. Titiwungen 5', 'city_hotel', 2, '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Mengusung konsep hotel budget modern, Avons Residence menghadirkan suasana sederhana namun tetap hangat dan fungsional. Desain interiornya menggabungkan nuansa modern dengan sentuhan lokal, menciptakan atmosfer yang nyaman dan tidak berlebihan—pas untuk beristirahat setelah aktivitas seharian di kota.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Salah satu daya tarik utamanya adalah <strong>area rooftop</strong> yang menawarkan pemandangan kota Manado hingga laut yang memukau, terutama saat matahari terbenam. Suasana ini memberikan pengalaman menginap yang lebih dari sekadar tempat tidur—melainkan tempat untuk bersantai dan menikmati suasana kota dari ketinggia</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Avons Residence Manado</strong> adalah pilihan akomodasi yang menawarkan pengalaman menginap praktis dengan sentuhan modern, nyaman, dan harga yang ramah di tengah kota Manado. Hotel ini cocok bagi traveler yang mengutamakan efisiensi tanpa mengorbankan kenyamanan.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Jika kamu mencari hotel di Manado yang <strong>simple, nyaman, dan value for money</strong>, Avons Residence adalah pilihan yang tepat. Dengan kombinasi lokasi strategis, fasilitas memadai, dan bonus pemandangan roofto</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Adopting a modern budget hotel concept, Avons Residence offers a simple yet warm and functional atmosphere. Its interior design combines modern elements with local touches, creating a comfortable and unpretentious ambiance—perfect for relaxing after a full day of activities in the city.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">One of its main highlights is the rooftop area, which offers stunning views of Manado city stretching out to the sea, especially during sunset. This setting provides more than just a place to stay—it becomes a space to unwind and enjoy the city from above.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Avons Residence Manado is an accommodation choice that delivers a practical stay experience with a modern touch, comfort, and affordable pricing in the heart of Manado. It is ideal for travelers who prioritize efficiency without compromising comfort.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">If you are looking for a hotel in Manado that is simple, comfortable, and offers great value for money, Avons Residence is the perfect choice. With its strategic location, adequate facilities, and the added bonus of a scenic rooftop view, it ensures a pleasant and memorable stay.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">아본스 레지던스는 현대적인 버짓 호텔 콘셉트를 바탕으로, 심플하면서도 따뜻하고 실용적인 분위기를 제공합니다. 인테리어는 모던한 요소와 로컬 감성을 조화롭게 결합하여, 과하지 않으면서도 편안한 공간을 만들어주며, 하루 일과를 마친 후 휴식을 취하기에 적합합니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">이곳의 가장 큰 매력 중 하나는 루프탑 공간으로, 특히 해질녘에는 마나도 시내와 바다가 어우러진 아름다운 전망을 감상할 수 있습니다. 단순한 숙박 공간을 넘어, 여유롭게 휴식을 즐기며 도시의 분위기를 느낄 수 있는 특별한 장소를 제공합니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">아본스 레지던스 마나도는 도심 한가운데에서 합리적인 가격과 편안함, 그리고 모던한 감각을 동시에 제공하는 실용적인 숙소입니다. 효율성을 중시하면서도 편안함을 포기하지 않는 여행객에게 이상적인 선택입니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">마나도에서 심플하면서도 편안하고 가성비 좋은 호텔을 찾고 있다면, 아본스 레지던스가 좋은 선택이 될 것입니다. 전략적인 위치와 충분한 시설, 그리고 아름다운 루프탑 전망까지 더해져 만족스러운 숙박 경험을 제공합니다.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Avons Residence 采用现代经济型酒店概念，营造出简约而温馨、实用的住宿氛围。其室内设计融合了现代风格与本地元素，打造出舒适且不过于张扬的空间，非常适合在忙碌一天后放松休息。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">酒店的一大亮点是屋顶区域，在日落时分尤为迷人，可欣赏到马纳多城市与海景相连的壮丽景色。这不仅仅是一个住宿的地方，更是一个可以放松身心、从高处欣赏城市风光的空间。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Avons Residence 马纳多是一家位于市中心的理想住宿选择，提供现代感、舒适性与实惠价格兼具的入住体验，非常适合注重效率同时又不愿牺牲舒适度的旅客。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">如果您正在寻找一家简单、舒适且性价比高的马纳多酒店，Avons Residence 将是理想之选。凭借其优越的地理位置、完善的设施以及迷人的屋顶景观，为您带来愉快而难忘的住宿体验。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p>', '[\"Pusat kebugaran\",\"Layanan kamar\",\"Parkir gratis\",\"Restoran\",\"WiFi gratis\",\"Sarapan\",\"AC\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/zladGZWh3Jpek5fuWTPfczrYJi9KzdR2NRV1EMPg.jpg', '2026-04-26 07:01:17', '2026-04-26 13:14:39'),
(87, 'Coral Eye Boutique Resort and Marine Outpost', 'coral-eye-boutique-resort-and-marine-outpost-1wZQVh', 'Pulau Bangka, Desa Lihunu', 'resort', 4, '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Terletak di Pulau Bangka, Sulawesi Utara, <strong>Coral Eye Resort</strong> bukan sekadar tempat menginap—ini adalah sebuah pengalaman menyatu dengan alam yang jarang ditemukan di tempat lain.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Bayangkan sebuah resort butik yang berdiri di antara hutan tropis yang rimbun dan hamparan pantai pasir putih yang masih alami. Suasananya tenang, eksklusif, dan terasa “jauh dari dunia”, namun tetap menghadirkan kenyamanan modern yang elegan tanpa berlebihan. Filosofi desainnya sederhana: menghadirkan harmoni antara arsitektur, manusia, dan alam sekitar.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Keunikan Coral Eye terletak pada asal-usulnya—berawal sebagai <strong>marine outpost</strong>, tempat para ilmuwan laut melakukan penelitian. Kini, tempat ini berkembang menjadi titik temu antara peneliti, penyelam, fotografer bawah laut, dan traveler yang memiliki satu kesamaan: kecintaan terhadap laut.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Dari sisi pengalaman, resort ini berada di jantung <strong>Coral Triangle</strong>, kawasan dengan keanekaragaman hayati laut tertinggi di dunia. Di sekitar resort terdapat lebih dari 50 spot diving kelas dunia, dengan pemandangan bawah laut yang luar biasa—mulai dari karang warna-warni, biota mikro yang langka, hingga kemungkinan bertemu penyu, hiu karang, bahkan dugong.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Namun Coral Eye bukan hanya untuk penyelam. Dari dermaga resort saja, kamu sudah bisa snorkeling di house reef yang hidup dan penuh warna. Aktivitas lain seperti kayaking, paddleboarding, hingga trekking ringan ke desa nelayan sekitar membuat pengalaman di sini terasa lengkap—baik untuk petualang maupun pencari ketenangan.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Akomodasinya dirancang dengan sentuhan lokal—villa-villa luas dengan kamar mandi terbuka, teras pribadi, dan pemandangan laut atau taman tropis. Material alami dan pengerjaan tangan oleh pengrajin lokal menciptakan suasana hangat, autentik, dan intimate.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Di pusat resort, terdapat area komunal yang menjadi “jiwa” Coral Eye—tempat tamu berkumpul, berbagi cerita, bahkan berdiskusi tentang laut dan konservasi. Di sinilah pengalaman menginap terasa lebih personal, bukan sekadar liburan biasa.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Singkatnya, Coral Eye Resort adalah perpaduan langka antara:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ed89ac0f8f2120e91e244cbb271761149\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Keindahan alam tropis yang masih murni</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e53fc3c6548c37f7b381194d676fab83a\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Petualangan bawah laut kelas dunia</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"efecbda1ef88f550615a5622c1211f1f8\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Sentuhan edukasi dan konservasi</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e4d212446a7a9073010f6d570b91349c5\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Suasana eksklusif namun tetap hangat dan bersahaja</p></li></ul><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Tempat ini bukan hanya untuk dikunjungi—tetapi untuk dirasakan, dipelajari, dan dikenang lama setelah perjalanan berakhir.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Located on Bangka Island, North Sulawesi, Coral Eye Resort is more than just a place to stay—it is an immersive experience in nature that is rarely found elsewhere.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Imagine a boutique resort nestled between lush tropical forests and pristine white sandy beaches. The atmosphere is शांत, exclusive, and feels “far from the world,” yet still offers elegant modern comforts without excess. Its design philosophy is simple: to create harmony between architecture, people, and the surrounding environment.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">What makes Coral Eye unique is its origin—initially established as a marine outpost where ocean scientists conducted research. Today, it has evolved into a meeting point for researchers, divers, underwater photographers, and travelers who share one passion: the ocean.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The resort sits in the heart of the Coral Triangle, home to the highest marine biodiversity in the world. With over 50 world-class dive sites nearby, guests can explore vibrant coral reefs, rare macro species, and encounter sea turtles, reef sharks, and even dugongs.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">But Coral Eye is not only for divers. Right from the jetty, guests can snorkel in a thriving house reef. Activities such as kayaking, paddleboarding, and light trekking to nearby fishing villages offer a well-rounded experience for both adventurers and those seeking tranquility.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The accommodations feature spacious villas with local touches—open-air bathrooms, private terraces, and views of the ocean or tropical gardens. Natural materials and handcrafted details create a warm, authentic, and intimate ambiance.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">At the heart of the resort lies a communal space where guests gather, share stories, and even discuss marine conservation. This is where the stay becomes more personal—beyond just a vacation.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In essence, Coral Eye Resort offers a rare blend of untouched natural beauty, world-class marine adventures, educational value, and a warm yet exclusive atmosphere.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">북술라웨시 방카섬에 위치한 Coral Eye Resort는 단순한 숙박 시설이 아니라, 자연과 하나 되는 특별한 경험을 제공합니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">울창한 열대 숲과 깨끗한 백사장 사이에 자리한 부티크 리조트를 상상해보세요. 이곳은 조용하고 프라이빗하며 세상과 떨어진 듯한 느낌을 주면서도, 과하지 않은 세련된 현대적 편안함을 제공합니다. 디자인 철학은 건축, 인간, 그리고 자연의 조화를 이루는 것입니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Coral Eye의 가장 큰 특징은 해양 연구 기지로 시작되었다는 점입니다. 현재는 연구자, 다이버, 수중 사진가, 그리고 바다를 사랑하는 여행자들이 모이는 특별한 장소로 발전했습니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">리조트는 세계에서 가장 높은 해양 생물 다양성을 자랑하는 ‘코랄 트라이앵글’ 중심에 위치해 있습니다. 50개 이상의 세계적인 다이빙 포인트에서 형형색색의 산호, 희귀 해양 생물, 바다거북, 리프 상어, 심지어 듀공까지 만날 수 있습니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">다이버가 아니어도 충분히 즐길 수 있습니다. 리조트의 제티에서 바로 스노클링이 가능하며, 카약, 패들보드, 인근 어촌 마을 트레킹 등 다양한 활동을 즐길 수 있습니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">객실은 넓은 빌라 형태로, 야외 욕실, 개인 테라스, 바다 또는 열대 정원 전망을 갖추고 있습니다. 자연 소재와 수공예 디테일이 따뜻하고 아늑한 분위기를 만들어냅니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">리조트 중심에는 공용 공간이 있어, 투숙객들이 모여 이야기를 나누고 해양 보전에 대해 교류할 수 있습니다. 이곳에서의 경험은 단순한 휴가를 넘어 더욱 특별해집니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Coral Eye Resort는 자연의 아름다움, 세계적인 해양 경험, 교육적 가치, 그리고 따뜻하면서도 프라이빗한 분위기를 모두 갖춘 특별한 곳입니다.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">位于印度尼西亚北苏拉威西邦加岛的 Coral Eye Resort，不仅仅是一处住宿，更是一种难得的沉浸式自然体验。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">想象一座坐落在茂密热带森林与洁白沙滩之间的精品度假村。这里环境宁静、私密，仿佛远离尘世，同时又提供恰到好处的现代舒适体验。其设计理念在于实现建筑、人类与自然之间的和谐共存。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Coral Eye 的独特之处在于它最初是一个海洋研究站。如今，这里已成为科学家、潜水员、水下摄影师以及热爱海洋的旅行者的聚集地。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">度假村位于“珊瑚三角区”的核心地带，这是全球海洋生物多样性最丰富的区域之一。周边拥有超过50个世界级潜水点，游客可以欣赏到色彩斑斓的珊瑚礁、稀有海洋生物，并有机会看到海龟、礁鲨甚至儒艮。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">即使不潜水，也能尽情享受这里的魅力。从码头即可浮潜，探索生机勃勃的珊瑚礁。此外，还可以体验皮划艇、立式划桨以及前往附近渔村的轻徒步活动。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">住宿方面，度假村提供宽敞的别墅，配有露天浴室、私人露台以及海景或热带花园景观。天然材料与手工工艺营造出温馨、真实且私密的氛围。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">度假村中心设有公共区域，宾客可以在此交流故事，甚至探讨海洋保护。这让整个入住体验更加深刻，不仅仅是一次普通的旅行。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">总体而言，Coral Eye Resort融合了原始自然之美、世界级海洋探险、教育意义以及温暖而私密的氛围，是一个值得深入体验与回味的独特目的地。</p>', '[\"Outdoor swimming pool\",\"Airport shuttle\",\"Non-smoking rooms\",\"Spa and wellness centre\",\"Beachfront\",\"Restaurant\",\"Free WiFi\",\"Bar\",\"Private beach area\",\"Breakfast\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/uVj1SKZg6Vk68bI6tRT2aJ0RZlbX9AJGv6QAfWTF.jpg', '2026-04-26 14:29:09', '2026-04-26 14:29:09'),
(88, 'Tangkoko Lodge', 'tangkoko-lodge-d9GFCR', 'Jalan Batu Putih Kelurahan Batuputih', 'eco_lodge', 3, '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Jika kamu mencari pengalaman menginap yang benar-benar berbeda—bukan sekadar hotel, tetapi petualangan yang hidup—maka <strong>Tangkoko Lodge</strong> adalah jawabannya.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Tersembunyi di Desa Batu Putih, tepat di tepi hutan dari Tangkoko Nature Reserve, lodge ini menghadirkan suasana yang begitu dekat dengan alam liar. Pagi hari dimulai dengan suara burung tropis, dan malam hari diiringi simfoni hutan—sunyi yang justru terasa hidup.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Tidak ada kemewahan berlebihan di sini, dan justru di situlah pesonanya. Tangkoko Lodge menawarkan kenyamanan yang sederhana namun hangat, dengan kamar-kamar yang bersih, taman hijau yang asri, dan atmosfer yang membuatmu merasa seperti tinggal di tengah alam, bukan sekadar mengunjunginya.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Daya tarik utamanya? Pengalaman wildlife yang luar biasa. Hanya beberapa langkah dari lodge, kamu bisa memasuki hutan dan bertemu langsung dengan penghuni khas Sulawesi—dari tarsius mungil yang aktif di senja hari, hingga monyet hitam Sulawesi yang langka. Setiap perjalanan trekking terasa seperti dokumenter alam yang nyata, dipandu oleh guide lokal yang berpengalaman.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah seharian menjelajah, kamu bisa kembali ke lodge, menikmati hidangan rumahan yang hangat, dan berbagi cerita dengan sesama traveler dari berbagai penjuru dunia. Suasananya akrab, santai, dan penuh cerita—membuat pengalaman menginap terasa lebih personal.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Singkatnya, Tangkoko Lodge bukan untuk mereka yang mencari kemewahan—melainkan untuk mereka yang ingin:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"edac5eafcded88411da6214d6fee19f48\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">merasakan alam secara langsung</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec52a18c0e09af23f455ac76b80118095\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">melihat satwa liar di habitat aslinya</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee95562b08267c25fe4b600b5c5f4b550\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">dan menikmati ketenangan yang autentik</p></li></ul><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Ini adalah tempat di mana kamu tidak hanya menginap, tetapi <strong>benar-benar mengalami kehidupan liar Sulawesi </strong>dengan cara yang sederhana, jujur, dan tak terlupakan.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">If you are looking for a truly different stay—not just a hotel, but a living adventure—then Tangkoko Lodge is the perfect choice.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Hidden in Batu Putih Village, right on the edge of Tangkoko Nature Reserve, this lodge offers an atmosphere that is deeply connected to the wild. Mornings begin with the sounds of tropical birds, while nights are filled with the natural symphony of the forest—quiet, yet vividly alive.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">There is no excessive luxury here, and that is exactly its charm. Tangkoko Lodge provides simple yet warm comfort, with clean rooms, lush green gardens, and an ambiance that makes you feel like you are living in nature, not just visiting it.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Its main highlight? An extraordinary wildlife experience. Just steps from the lodge, you can enter the forest and encounter Sulawesi’s unique inhabitants—from the tiny tarsier active at dusk to the rare black crested macaque. Every trekking journey feels like a real-life nature documentary, guided by experienced local experts.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After a day of exploration, return to the lodge to enjoy home-style meals and share stories with fellow travelers from around the world. The atmosphere is friendly, relaxed, and full of stories—making your stay feel more personal.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In short, Tangkoko Lodge is not for those seeking luxury, but for those who want to experience nature in its purest form—authentic, immersive, and unforgettable.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">진정으로 특별한 숙박 경험—단순한 호텔이 아닌 살아있는 모험을 찾고 있다면 Tangkoko Lodge가 완벽한 선택입니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">바투 푸티 마을에 위치하며, Tangkoko Nature Reserve 바로 옆에 자리한 이 로지는 자연과 깊이 연결된 분위기를 제공합니다. 아침에는 열대 새들의 소리로 시작하고, 밤에는 숲의 자연스러운 소리로 가득 차 조용하면서도 생동감 넘칩니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">이곳에는 화려한 럭셔리가 없습니다. 하지만 그것이 바로 매력입니다. 깨끗한 객실과 푸른 정원, 그리고 자연 속에 머무는 듯한 편안한 분위기를 제공합니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">가장 큰 매력은 바로 놀라운 야생 동물 체험입니다. 로지에서 몇 걸음만 나가면 숲으로 들어가 설무렵에 활동하는 작은 타르시우스와 희귀한 검은 원숭이 등 술라웨시 고유의 동물을 만날 수 있습니다. 전문 가이드와 함께하는 트레킹은 마치 실제 자연 다큐멘터리 같은 경험을 선사합니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">하루의 탐험을 마친 후에는 따뜻한 가정식 식사를 즐기며 전 세계 여행자들과 이야기를 나눌 수 있습니다. 분위기는 친근하고 편안하며, 더욱 특별한 추억을 만들어 줍니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Tangkoko Lodge는 럭셔리를 찾는 여행자가 아닌, 자연을 있는 그대로 경험하고 싶은 이들에게 완벽한 장소입니다.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">如果你正在寻找一种与众不同的住宿体验——不仅仅是酒店，而是一场真实的自然探险，那么 Tangkoko Lodge 将是理想之选。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">它隐藏在 Batu Putih 村庄，紧邻 Tangkoko Nature Reserve，为你带来与野外自然紧密相连的氛围。清晨从热带鸟鸣中醒来，夜晚则伴随着森林的自然交响，宁静却充满生命力。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">这里没有奢华的装饰，而这正是它的魅力所在。简单而温馨的客房、绿意盎然的花园，以及仿佛置身自然中的氛围，让人真正融入环境，而不仅仅是短暂停留。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">最大的亮点是令人难忘的野生动物体验。从旅馆出发，几步之遥即可进入森林，邂逅苏拉威西独特的动物——如黄昏时活动的小眼镜猴，以及稀有的黑冠猕猴。在经验丰富的向导带领下，每一次徒步都像一场真实的自然纪录片。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">一天的探险结束后，你可以回到旅馆，享用温暖的家常美食，并与来自世界各地的旅行者分享故事。这里的氛围轻松、友好，让整个旅程更加难忘。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">总的来说，Tangkoko Lodge并不是为追求奢华的人准备的，而是为那些渴望真实、沉浸式自然体验的旅行者而存在。</p>', '[\"Non-smoking rooms\",\"Airport shuttle\",\"Room service\",\"Restaurant\",\"Free WiFi\",\"Free parking\",\"Breakfast\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/wgWNwubdmAPy53qNZHVFt22F82TXWp6rHEhnwQ3A.jpg', '2026-04-26 15:18:19', '2026-04-27 01:35:35'),
(89, 'Tangkoko Hill', 'tangkoko-hill-ODiEGs', 'Batuh Putih', 'eco_lodge', 1, '<p><strong>Tangkoko Hill</strong> adalah permata tersembunyi di kawasan Tangkoko Nature Reserve yang menawarkan pengalaman alam yang masih murni dan menenangkan. Terletak di perbukitan hijau yang menghadap langsung ke hutan tropis dan laut, tempat ini menghadirkan perpaduan sempurna antara petualangan dan ketenangan.</p><p>Dari puncaknya, pengunjung akan disuguhi panorama spektakuler—hamparan hutan lebat yang menjadi rumah bagi satwa endemik seperti Tarsius yang mungil dan unik, serta Celebes crested macaque yang eksotis. Saat pagi hari, kabut tipis yang menyelimuti pepohonan menciptakan suasana magis, sementara sore hari menghadirkan pemandangan matahari terbenam yang dramatis dengan siluet pepohonan tropis.</p><p>Tangkoko Hill juga menjadi tempat ideal bagi pecinta fotografi dan trekking ringan. Jalur-jalur alami yang mengarah ke puncak memberikan sensasi eksplorasi yang autentik, ditemani suara alam yang menenangkan. Udara segar khas perbukitan membuat setiap langkah terasa menyegarkan, jauh dari hiruk-pikuk kota.</p><p>Bagi traveler yang mencari pengalaman berbeda di Sulawesi Utara, Tangkoko Hill bukan sekadar destinasi, tetapi sebuah perjalanan untuk menyatu dengan alam—tempat di mana keindahan, ketenangan, dan keajaiban alam berpadu dalam satu lanskap yang memikat.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Tangkoko Hill</strong> is a hidden gem located within the Tangkoko Nature Reserve, offering a serene and unspoiled natural experience. Nestled among lush green hills overlooking tropical forests and the sea, this destination presents a perfect blend of adventure and tranquility.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">From its summit, visitors are rewarded with breathtaking panoramic views—dense forests that serve as the natural habitat of unique endemic wildlife such as the tiny Tarsius and the striking Celebes crested macaque. In the early morning, a thin mist drapes the treetops, creating a magical atmosphere, while in the late afternoon, the setting sun paints the sky with dramatic hues against silhouettes of tropical trees.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Tangkoko Hill is also an ideal spot for photography enthusiasts and light trekking. Natural trails leading to the top offer an authentic exploration experience, accompanied by the soothing sounds of nature. The crisp, fresh air of the hills adds a refreshing touch to every step, far from the bustle of the city.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">For travelers seeking a unique experience in North Sulawesi, Tangkoko Hill is more than just a destination—it is a journey into nature, where beauty, serenity, and wonder come together in one captivating landscape.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Tangkoko Hill</strong>은 Tangkoko Nature Reserve에 위치한 숨겨진 보석 같은 장소로, 때묻지 않은 자연과 평온함을 동시에 경험할 수 있는 곳입니다. 울창한 열대우림과 바다가 내려다보이는 푸른 언덕에 자리 잡고 있어 모험과 휴식이 완벽하게 어우러집니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">정상에 오르면 숨막히는 파노라마 풍경이 펼쳐집니다. 이곳은 작은 영장류인 Tarsius와 독특한 매력을 지닌 Celebes crested macaque의 서식지이기도 합니다. 아침에는 옅은 안개가 숲을 감싸 신비로운 분위기를 자아내고, 저녁에는 노을이 하늘을 물들이며 열대 나무의 실루엣과 어우러져 장관을 이룹니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">또한 Tangkoko Hill은 사진 애호가와 가벼운 트레킹을 즐기는 이들에게 이상적인 장소입니다. 정상으로 이어지는 자연 산책로는 자연의 소리와 함께 진정한 탐험의 즐거움을 선사합니다. 상쾌한 언덕의 공기는 도시의 번잡함에서 벗어나 여유로운 시간을 제공합니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">북술라웨시에서 특별한 경험을 찾는 여행자들에게 Tangkoko Hill은 단순한 관광지를 넘어 자연과 하나가 되는 여정을 선사하는 곳입니다.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Tangkoko Hill</strong> 是位于 Tangkoko Nature Reserve 的一处隐秘瑰宝，这里为游客提供原始、宁静的自然体验。坐落在郁郁葱葱的山丘之上，可俯瞰热带森林与大海，将探险与放松完美结合。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">登上山顶，壮丽的全景尽收眼底——茂密的森林是许多独特物种的家园，例如小巧可爱的 Tarsius 和极具特色的 Celebes crested macaque。清晨，薄雾缭绕在树梢间，营造出梦幻般的氛围；傍晚时分，夕阳将天空染成绚丽色彩，与热带树林的剪影交相辉映。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Tangkoko Hill 也是摄影爱好者和轻徒步旅行者的理想之地。通往山顶的自然小径带来真实的探索体验，伴随着大自然的声音，让人倍感宁静。清新的山间空气令人神清气爽，远离城市的喧嚣。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">对于在北苏拉威西寻求独特体验的旅行者来说，Tangkoko Hill 不仅是一个目的地，更是一段融入自然、感受美丽与宁静的难忘旅程。</p>', '[\"Free Wi-Fi\",\"Free parking\",\"Restaurants\",\"Bar\",\"Kitchen\",\"Luggage storage\",\"Garden\",\"Breakfast\"]', 'https://api.welcomemanado.my.id/storage/hotels/CsgZG9wlJI55c7yi22D7hPEwboQs4Jw2cg8U4cSo.jpg', '2026-04-27 01:34:26', '2026-04-27 01:34:27');
