(2210, 'App\\Models\\InternationalTour', 57, 2, 'BANGKOK - KANCHANABURI - BANGKOK | BREAKFAST/LUNCH', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">ABF at Hotel, transfer to Kanchanaburi, <strong>Kanchanaburi Skywalk, Dead Railway</strong>, Take a train to <strong>Tham Krasae Bridge</strong>, lunch at local restaurant, Transfer to <strong>Kanchanaburi Safari Park </strong>(include Elephant Show and interact with Giraffe), Back Bangkok, Dinner by own expense at <strong>Jodd Fairs Nighl Market</strong>, back to hotel</p>', NULL, NULL, '2026-04-29 06:38:49', '2026-04-29 06:38:49'),
