(2230, 'App\\Models\\InternationalTour', 19, 2, 'BANGKOK - KHAOYAI - BANGKOK | BREAKFAST/LUNCH', '<p>Breakfast at Hotel, 07.00 Pick up from hotel, The Market Mall, transfer to Khaoyai, Hokkaido Flower Park, Lunch at local restaurant, Photo stop at Toscana Valley, free time playing with Alpaca at Khmong Alpaca Khaoyai, Take Me Home Park,<br>Floryday Khaoyai Cafe &amp; Flower (own expense), back to Bangkok, back to Hotel</p>', NULL, NULL, '2026-04-29 07:06:25', '2026-04-29 07:06:25'),
