(2271, 'App\\Models\\InternationalTour', 61, 2, 'BANGKOK - PATTAYA | BREAKFAST/LUNCH/DINNER', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Breakfast at Hotel, Check out from hotel, Visit Honey Bee farm, <strong>Great and Grand Sweet Destination</strong>, Bus tour to <strong>The Valley of Dinosaurs (Dinosaurs Park)</strong>, <strong>Nongnooch Village (Include Thai Culture and Elephant Show) </strong>Lunch buffet at Nongnooch Village, <strong>Laser Buddha Hill, </strong>Erawadee Herb Shop, Pattaya Beach at <strong>Hard Rock Cafe</strong>, optional cabaret show, Dinner at Local restaurant, Check in hotel at Pattaya.</p>', NULL, NULL, '2026-04-29 08:45:41', '2026-04-29 08:45:41'),
