(2499, 'App\\Models\\InternationalTour', 65, 4, 'BANGKOK - KHAOYAI - BANGKOK | BREAKFAST/LUNCH', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Breakfast at Hotel, 07.00 Pick up from hotel, The Market Mall, transfer to Khaoyai, <strong>Hokkaido Flower Park</strong>, Lunch at local restaurant, Photo stop at <strong>Toscana Valley</strong>, free time playing with Alpaca at <strong>Khmong Alpaca Khaoyai</strong>, <strong>Take Me Home Park, </strong>Floryday Khaoyai Cafe &amp; Flower (own expense)<strong>, </strong>back to Bangkok, back to Hotel</p>', NULL, NULL, '2026-05-02 13:19:04', '2026-05-02 13:19:04'),
