iful scenery, where coffee or tea will be served. Return to Manado City. Optional dinner at a local restaurant, followed by transfer back to the hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-03 01:43:57', '2026-05-03 01:43:57'),
(2765, 'App\\Models\\ManadoTour', 11, 3, 'LIHAGA ISLAND – BUDO TOURISM VILLAGE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at the hotel, the participants will be picked up by the tour guide and travel to the Likupang area, approximately 1 hour and 20 minutes from Manado city center. The first stop is <strong>Serei Port</strong>, and upon arrival, continue by boat for about 15 minutes to <strong>Lihaga Island</strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">On <strong>Lihaga Island</strong>, participants can enjoy its stunning white and powder-soft sandy beaches, explore the island, and take photos at various beautiful and Instagrammable spots. Guests may also join optional activities such as snorkeling, canoeing, or diving. Lunch will be served on the island. After lunch, participants will have additional free time to relax by the beach.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">On the return journey to Manado, make a stop at <strong>Budo Tourism Village</strong>, where guests can enjoy a beautiful sunset accompanied by local treats of fried bananas and fresh coconut. Optional dinner at a local restaurant, followed by transfer back to the hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-03 01:43:57', '2026-05-03 01:43:57'),
(2766, 'App\\Models\\ManadoTour', 11, 4, 'TRANSFER OUT – DEPARTURE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast and completing the hotel check-out process, the tour participants will be picked up by the guide and transferred directly to the airport for their return flight. Tour ends.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-03 01:43:57', '2026-05-03 01:43:57'),
