(4654, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 45, 4, 'SUMBA TIMUR', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah sarapan, Anda akan diajak full day tour dimulai dari <i><strong>Bukit Tanarara</strong></i>. Tanarara adalah perbukitan berselimut rumput dan disatu titik di puncak Bukit Tanarara ada kubur batu yang diberi ukiran khas Sumba.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah itu, mengunjungi <i><strong>Air Terjun Waimarang.</strong></i> Air Terjun Waimarang ini memiliki ketinggian sekitar 2 Meter dan dibagian bawahnya ada sebuah kolam yang dikelilingi tebing, seperti kolam renang.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Dan setelah itu, Anda akan diajak untuk mengunjungi <i><strong>pusat toko oleh-oleh khas Sumba</strong></i> dan dilanjutkan menuju <i><strong>Pantai Walakiri.</strong></i> Di pantai ini anda akan disuguhi deretan pohon kelapa dipinggirnya, dengan hamparan pasir putih yang luas dan lautnya yang biru dan di sebelah baratnya terdapat pohon bakau yang tersusun rapi yang dapat dijadikan spot foto terbaik.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah itu, Anda akan makan malam di resto lokal. Setelah makan malam, kembali ke hotel untuk istirahat.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast/Lunch/Dinner', '2026-05-29 14:50:06', '2026-05-29 14:50:06'),
(4655, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 45, 5, 'TRANSFER OUT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah sarapan, Anda akan check out<i><strong>.</strong></i> Dan setelah itu, anda akan diantar menuju Bandara dan trip selesai.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-29 14:50:06', '2026-05-29 14:50:06'),
(4656, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 44, 1, 'ARRIVAL - SUMBA BARAT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Tibanya di <i><strong>Bandara Tambolaka, </strong></i>Anda akan disambut oleh guide kami. Setelah itu, Anda akan menuju resto lokal untuk makan siang.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah makan siang, Anda akan menuju <i><strong>Rumah Budaya. </strong></i>Di rumah budaya ini, Anda akan diperkenalkan sejarah Sumba.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah itu, Anda akan menuju <i><strong>Bukit Lendongara. </strong></i>Dibukit ini anda akan disuguhi pemandangan perbukitan yang ditumbuhi rerumputan bak layaknya seperti dalam film teletubis.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Dan dilanjutkan, ke <i><strong>Pantai Mananga Aba atau Pantai Kita.</strong></i> Di pantai ini, Anda akan disuguhi bentangan pasir putih meluas dan suasana pantai yang sunyi dan tenang.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah itu, Anda akan makan malam di resto lokal. Setelah makan malam, check in hotel untuk istirahat.</p>', NULL, 'Lunch/Dinner', '2026-05-29 14:50:51', '2026-05-29 14:50:51'),
(4657, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 44, 2, 'SUMBA BARAT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Pagi ini kita akan menuju menuju rumah adat ratenggaro lanjut pantai pero <i><strong>Pantai Pero.&nbsp;</strong></i></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Dan dilanjutkan menuju <i><strong>Danau Waekuri.</strong></i> Danau Waekuri merupakan salah satu landmark dari Sumba, danau yang sangat luas dan airnya adalah air payau.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah itu, Anda akan makan malam di resto lokal. Setelah makan malam, kembali ke hotel untuk istirahat.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast/Lunch/Dinner', '2026-05-29 14:50:51', '2026-05-29 14:50:51'),
(4658, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 44, 3, 'SUMBA BARAT-SUMBA TIMUR', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah sarapan, Anda akan check out dari Sumba Barat dan Anda akan menuju <i><strong>Kampung Praijing.</strong></i> Kampung Praijing ini merupakan kampung adat yang paling terkenal di Sumba Barat. Di Kampung ini terdapat 38 rumah tradisional khas Sumba.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah itu, Anda akan menuju <i><strong>wee kacura. </strong></i>Dan dilanjutkan menuju <i><strong>Bukit Wairinding.</strong></i> Bukit Wairinding ini merupakan salah satu tempat terbaik untuk menikmati <strong>Sumba Timur</strong> dari ketinggian. Hamparan padang savana yang terhampar luas berwarna kuning saat musim kemarau dan berwarna hijau pada saat musin hujan.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah itu, Anda akan diajak untuk mengunjungi <i><strong>pusat toko oleh-oleh khas Sumba</strong></i> dan dilanjutkan menuju <i><strong>Pantai Walakiri.</strong></i> Di pantai ini anda akan disuguhi deretan pohon kelapa dipinggirnya, dengan hamparan pasir putih yang luas dan lautnya yang biru dan di sebelah baratnya terdapat pohon bakau yang tersusun rapi yang dapat dijadikan spot foto terbaik.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Dan setelah itu, Anda akan makan malam di resto lokal. Setelah makan malam, check in hotel untuk istirahat.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast/Lunch/Dinner', '2026-05-29 14:50:51', '2026-05-29 14:50:51'),
(4659, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 44, 4, 'TRANSFER OUT', '<p>Setelah sarapan, Anda akan check out<i><strong>.</strong></i> Dan setelah itu, anda akan diantar menuju bandara dan trip selesai.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-29 14:50:51', '2026-05-29 14:50:51'),
(4660, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 43, 1, 'SUMBA BARAT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Tibanya di <strong>Bandara Tambolaka, </strong>Anda akan disambut oleh guide kami. Setelah itu, makan siang di resto local.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah makan siang Anda akan menuju <strong>Rumah Budaya. </strong>Di rumah budaya ini, Anda akan diperkenalkan sejarah Sumba.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah itu, Anda akan menuju <strong>Bukit Lendongara. </strong>Dibukit ini anda akan disuguhi pemandangan perbukitan yang ditumbuhi rerumputan bak layaknya seperti dalam film teletubis.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Dan dilanjutkan, ke <strong>Pantai Mananga Aba atau Pantai Kita.</strong> Di pantai ini, Anda akan disuguhi bentangan pasir putih meluas dan suasana pantai yang sunyi dan tenang.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah itu, Anda akan makan malam di resto lokal. Setelah makan malam, check in hotel untuk istirahat.</p>', NULL, 'Lunch/Dinner', '2026-05-29 14:52:04', '2026-05-29 14:52:04'),
(4661, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 43, 2, 'SUMBA BARAT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Sarapan di hotel, setelah ittu kita akan menuju <strong>Pantai Mandorak.</strong>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah itu menuju<strong> Danau Waekuri.</strong> Danau Waekuri merupakan salah satu landmark dari Sumba, danau yang sangat luas dan airnya adalah air payau.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah itu, makan siang di resto local, setalah makan siang, Anda akan menuju <strong>Kampung Praijing.</strong> Kampung Praijing ini merupakan kampung adat yang paling terkenal di Sumba Barat. Di Kampung ini terdapat 38 rumah tradisional khas Sumba.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Di lanjutkan menuju <strong>Pantai Pero</strong> untuk hunting sunset. makan malam di resto lokal . Setelah makan malam, kembali ke hotel untuk istirahat.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast/Lunch/Dinner', '2026-05-29 14:52:04', '2026-05-29 14:52:04'),
(4662, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 43, 3, 'TRANSFER OUT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah sarapan, Anda akan check out<strong>.</strong> Dan setelah itu, Anda akan mengunjungi <strong>pusat toko oleh-oleh khas Sumba</strong>. Dan setelah itu, anda akan diantar menuju bandara dan trip selesai.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-29 14:52:04', '2026-05-29 14:52:04'),
(4663, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 42, 1, 'KEDATANGAN – BATU CERMIN – BUKIT SYLVIA', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setibanya di Bandara Komodo, Anda akan dijemput oleh perwakilan kami. Perjalanan langsung &nbsp;dilanjutkan menuju restoran lokal untuk makan siang.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah itu, mengunjungi <strong>Goa Batu Cermin</strong> untuk melihat dinding batu kapur yang memantulkan cahaya didampingi oleh pemandu goa setempat.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Kemudian menuju <strong>Bukit Sylvia</strong> untuk menikmati pemandangan perbukitan yang ikonik sambil menunggu matahari terbenam.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Makan malam disajikan di restoran lokal, lalu menuju hotel untuk proses <i>check-in</i> dan istirahat.</p>', NULL, 'Lunch/Dinner', '2026-05-29 14:52:46', '2026-05-29 14:52:46'),
(4664, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 42, 2, 'FULL DAY KOMODO ADVENTURE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Persiapan dimulai pukul 05.00 pagi. Setelah sarapan di hotel atau membawa <i>breakfast box</i>, Anda akan diantar menuju pelabuhan untuk menaiki &nbsp;<strong>Speedboat</strong> pada pukul 06.30.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Destinasi pertama adalah &nbsp;<strong>Pulau Padar</strong> untuk trekking ke puncak guna melihat panorama tiga teluk yang spektakuler.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Perjalanan berlanjut ke <strong>Long Pink Beach</strong> untuk snorkeling dan bersantai, lalu mengunjungi <strong>Pulau Komodo</strong> untuk melihat langsung habitat asli komodo. Makan siang disediakan dalam bentuk <i>box</i>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Sore harinya, mengunjungi <strong>Taka Makassar</strong>, snorkeling di <strong>Manta Point</strong>, dan menikmati keindahan <strong>Pulau Kanawa</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Kembali ke Labuan Bajo untuk makan malam di restoran lokal sebelum beristirahat di hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast/Lunch Box/Dinner', '2026-05-29 14:52:46', '2026-05-29 14:52:46'),
(4665, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 42, 3, 'GOA RANGKO – RUMAH TENUN – SUNSET', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah sarapan di hotel, kami akan mengantar Anda menuju <strong>Goa Rangko</strong> untuk merasakan sensasi berenang di kolam air asin alami di dalam gua. Makan siang di restoran lokal.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Perjalanan dilanjutkan dengan mengunjungi <strong>Rumah Tenun Baku Peduli</strong> untuk melihat proses pembuatan kain tenun tradisional oleh masyarakat setempat.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah itu, Anda berkesempatan berbelanja oleh-oleh di <strong>Exotic Komodo</strong> atau <strong>Kado Bajo</strong>. Menjelang sore, menikmati pemandangan matahari terbenam di <strong>Puncak Waringin</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Makan malam disajikan di restoran lokal sebelum kembali ke hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast/Lunch/Dinner', '2026-05-29 14:52:46', '2026-05-29 14:52:46'),
(4666, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 42, 4, 'TRANSFER OUT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah sarapan di hotel dan menikmati fasilitas hotel, dilakukan proses <i>check-out</i>. pengantaran menuju Bandara Komodo untuk penerbangan pulang ke kota asal.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-29 14:52:46', '2026-05-29 14:52:46'),
(4667, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 41, 1, 'KEDATANGAN – BATU CERMIN – SUNSET HUNTING', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setibanya di Bandara Komodo, Anda akan dijemput oleh perwakilan kami. Sebelum memulai tour, Anda akan menuju resto lokal untuk makan siang.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Tour dimulai dengan mengunjungi <strong>Goa Batu Cermin</strong> yang dipandu oleh pemandu goa profesional untuk melihat stalaktit dan stalagmit yang unik.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Perjalanan dilanjutkan menuju <strong>Bukit Silviya</strong> dan <strong>Puncak Waringin</strong> untuk menikmati panorama matahari terbenam (sunset) terbaik di Labuan Bajo.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Makan malam disajikan di resto lokal. Check-in hotel dan istirahat.</p>', NULL, 'Lunch/Dinner', '2026-05-29 14:53:51', '2026-05-29 14:53:51'),
(4668, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 41, 2, 'FULL DAY KOMODO ADVENTURE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah sarapan, Anda akan diantar ke pelabuhan pada pukul 06.00-06.30 untuk memulai petualangan dengan <i>speedboat</i>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Agenda hari ini mencakup <i>trekking</i> di <strong>Pulau Padar</strong> untuk melihat panorama tiga teluk, bersantai&nbsp; di <strong>Long Pink Beach</strong>, serta melihat habitat komodo di <strong>Pulau Komodo</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Makan siang disiapkan dalam bentuk <i>box</i>. Keseruan berlanjut dengan <i>snorkeling</i> di <strong>Taka Makassar</strong>, berenang bersama pari manta di <strong>Manta Point</strong>, dan menikmati bawah laut <strong>Pulau Kanawa</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Sore harinya, kita kembali ke Labuan Bajo untuk makan malam sebelum beristirahat di hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast/Lunch Box/Dinner', '2026-05-29 14:53:51', '2026-05-29 14:53:51'),
(4669, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 41, 3, 'BELANJA OLEH-OLEH – KEBERANGKATAN', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah sarapan dan menikmati fasilitas hotel, Anda akan diberikan waktu untuk berbelanja oleh-oleh khas Labuan Bajo di <strong>exotic Komodo/kado bajo</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Lalu setelah itu anda akan diantar pulang ke bandara Komodo.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-29 14:53:51', '2026-05-29 14:53:51'),
(4670, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 15, 1, 'Arrival Makassar – City Tour', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at Sultan Hasanuddin International Airport Makassar, meeting services. Afterwards, we continue for a short city tour in Makassar by visiting <strong>Paotere Harbour</strong> to see the traditional harbour of Bugis-Makassarese sailors. Then, proceed to <strong>Fort Rotterdam</strong>, the Old Dutch Fortress.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the late afternoon we will visit <strong>“Anjungan Pantai Losari Makassar”</strong> the Boulevard and the icon of Makassar where you enjoy the Sunset (if the weather allows). Overnight at hotel.</p>', NULL, 'No Meal', '2026-05-30 03:21:05', '2026-05-30 03:21:05'),
(4671, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 15, 2, 'Rammang-Rammang Tour', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Today, full day tour will be started by visiting <strong>Rammang-rammang the limestone valley</strong>, located in Maros Regency, taking for approximately 90 minute\'s drive from downtown. The karst mountains are surrounded by beautiful rice fields (the rice fields look nicer from May till August).&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Afterwards, we will take you to explore the <strong>karst mountain</strong> formation using small wooden boat at the <strong>Pute River</strong>. If you are lucky, you could also see the real endemic from the forest such as birds and monkeys.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">We will also take you for a walk to visit the pre-historic cave, where you can see the pre-historic paintings, then short explore inside the cave to see the stalactite and stalagmite.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Break and lunch will be taken at the Kampung Berua, afternoon we will have a little walk at the <strong>Stone Garden of Rammang-Rammang</strong>. Then, drive back to Makassar. Overnight at hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:21:05', '2026-05-30 03:21:05'),
(4672, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 15, 3, 'Makassar – Pare-Pare – Toraja', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, set out on a picturesque drive to <strong>Toraja</strong> for approximately 8 hours\' drive, passing thru the Buginese area. Stopover in <strong>Pare-Pare</strong>, the harbour city between Makassar and Toraja.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue driving to Toraja precedes a scenic drive with many photo-stops enroute. Afternoon stop at <strong>Puncak Lakawan</strong> which is also known as erotic mountain. In the late afternoon arrive at <strong>Rantepao</strong>, Toraja. overnight at the hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:21:05', '2026-05-30 03:21:05'),
(4673, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 15, 4, 'Toraja tour Lemo - Kambira - Londa - Kete Kesu', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, a full day tour exploring <strong>Toraja</strong>. First, we will visit <strong>Lemo</strong> to see rows of <strong>tau-tau statues</strong> and the <strong>hanging graves</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Onwards to <strong>Kambira</strong> to discover the secret of the <strong>baby tree</strong>. visiting <strong>Londa</strong>, to see an ancient grave where the deceased are entombed.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">At <strong>Kete Kesu</strong> one of the oldest torajan villages, we can see tongkonan and old rice barns, also famous for its traditional colourful woodcarving. overnight at hotel.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:21:05', '2026-05-30 03:21:05'),
(4674, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 15, 5, 'Toraja tour Batutumonga – short walking - Bori', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, we set out on a trip to <strong>Batutumonga</strong>, enjoying superb views over <strong>Rantepao</strong> and surrounding valleys from the top of <strong>Toraja</strong>. Then we will do a short walking for approximately 2 hours passing thru the rice field, local village where you can also see the daily life of the people in Toraja.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then, we will continue to visit <strong>Bori the Megalith area</strong>. This area symbolizes the great funeral ceremonies, which is held in the past. overnight at hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:21:05', '2026-05-30 03:21:05'),
(4675, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 15, 6, 'Toraja – Pendolo', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, depart to <strong>Pendolo</strong> via Palopo. The drive to <strong>Palopo</strong> takes approximately 2 hours. You could enjoy beautiful panorama along the way. Palopo is a small Muslim port known as the oldest harbour city in Indonesia. You could also find the oldest mosque in Indonesia here.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then, continue driving to Pendolo for another 6 hours passing thru the Palmolive Plantation. In the late afternoon arrive in Pendolo, a small village on the south shore of <strong>Lake Poso</strong>. overnight at hotel</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:21:05', '2026-05-30 03:21:05'),
(4676, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 15, 7, 'Pendolo – Tentena', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, drive for around 4 hours, to <strong>Tentena</strong>. On arrival we will take you to visit the <strong>Balinese</strong> <strong>Transmigration Village.</strong> Afterwards, we will visit the twelve steps waterfall which is called <strong>Sulewana Waterfall</strong>. Free program in the afternoon for your leisure at the <strong>Lake Poso</strong>. overnight at hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:21:05', '2026-05-30 03:21:05'),
(4677, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 15, 8, 'Tentena – Palu', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, we will drive to <strong>Palu</strong>, the capital city of Central Sulawesi for around 8 hours. On the way, we will pass <strong>Kebun Kopi</strong>, the rain forest area.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">We will also pass Poso regency, which was famous as the centre of <strong>the black ebony wood</strong>. In the afternoon arrive in Palu. overnight at hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:21:05', '2026-05-30 03:21:05'),
(4678, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 15, 9, 'Palu Donggala day tour', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast we will take you for tour to <strong>Donggala</strong>. We will first stop at <strong>Kampong Lere</strong> to see the traditional house of Joyo Kodi, the former King of Kaili people.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then, we will stop at the <strong>fishing village</strong>, where you could take a look at the daily activities of the locals. Free at your own leisure on sandy beach around <strong>Donggala</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the afternoon drive back to <strong>Palu</strong>. overnight at hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:21:05', '2026-05-30 03:21:05'),
(4679, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 15, 10, 'Hotel – Palu airport', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, transfer to <strong>Mutiara Airport</strong> at Palu to catch your flight to the next destination.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:21:05', '2026-05-30 03:21:05'),
(4680, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 12, 1, 'Makassar  (City Tour)', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at <strong>Sultan Hasanuddin International Airport Makassar</strong>, meeting services. Afterwards, we continue for a short city tour in Makassar by visiting&nbsp;<strong>Paotere Harbour</strong>&nbsp;to see the traditional harbour of Bugis-Makassarese sailors. Lunch will be served in a local restaurant.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then, proceed to&nbsp;<strong>Fort Rotterdam</strong>, the Old Dutch Fortress. In the late afternoon we will visit&nbsp;<strong>“Anjungan Pantai Losari Makassar”</strong>&nbsp;the Boulevard and the icon of Makassar where you enjoy the Sunset (if the weather allows).</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Dinner will be served in a local seafood restaurant (Optional).</p>', NULL, 'No Meal', '2026-05-30 03:44:43', '2026-05-30 03:44:43');
INSERT INTO `itineraries` (`id`, `itinerable_type`, `itinerable_id`, `day_number`, `title`, `description`, `hotel_info`, `meals_info`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(4681, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 12, 2, 'Makassar  (Rammang-Rammang Tour)', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Today, full day tour will be started by visiting&nbsp;<strong>Rammang-Rammang</strong>&nbsp;<strong>the limestone valley</strong>, located in <strong>Maros Regency</strong>, taking for approximately 90 minutes’ drive from downtown.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The K<strong>arst Mountains </strong>are surrounded by beautiful <strong>rice fields</strong> (the rice fields look nicer from May till August).&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Afterwards, we will take you to explore the karst mountain formation using small wooden boat at the <strong>Pute River</strong>. If you are lucky, you could also see the real endemic from the forest such as birds and monkeys. We will also take you for a walk to visit the <strong>pre-historic cave</strong>, where you can see the pre-historic paintings, then short explore inside the cave to see the stalactite and stalagmite.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the afternoon we will have a little walk at the <strong>Stone Garden of Rammang-Rammang</strong>. Then, drive back to Makassar.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:44:43', '2026-05-30 03:44:43'),
(4682, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 12, 3, 'Makassar - Toraja', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the morning we will start for a wondrous journey to <strong>Toraja</strong> that moves through <strong>lofty mountains landscape</strong>. This trip offers plenty of picturesque stop for you to have coffee or photo shoots.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the afternoon, we pass the notorious “erotic” <strong>mountain Buttu Kabobong in Bambapuang</strong> before entering the <strong>Toraja land.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">“The mountainous district of Toraja is the homeland of several ethnic groups who are called Toraja (Toraja means ‘the people of the mountains’ or ‘the people of the west’. The Toraja call their traditional religion Aluk Todolo (rites of the ancestors) and they live according to the patron that was defined by the ancestor’s and gods.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">These include the impressive rituals of burying the deceased. &nbsp;The beautiful carved houses with the remarkable roofs, the so-called <strong>Tongkonan</strong>, are also built according to principles of Aluk Todolo. Although most Toraja are Christian nowadays, still many traditions live on. If during your stay in Toraja, there is an opportunity to visit an impressive funeral - or house ceremony or the big animal market, program could be adjusted to fit in these visits”</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:44:43', '2026-05-30 03:44:43'),
(4683, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 12, 4, 'Toraja', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Spend the morning exploring the highlights of the region. First, we will visit <strong>Lemo</strong> where graves are carved into the stone cliff and the wooden effigies of the dead gaze upon from its balcony. Continue explore the different ways the Toraja burry their death; from the <strong>baby graves</strong> <strong>in the trunk of big trees</strong> <strong>Kambira</strong>, then visit the <strong>King’s grave of&nbsp; Suaya</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the afternoon, continue to the curious <strong>cave of Londa</strong>. Use as grave, we can see bones and deceased in these natural caves. Then Ke’te Kesu, a small village well known for its original <strong>Tongkonan houses</strong>, beautiful wood carvings and typical Toraja paintings; this village is a Unesco World Heritage site.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:44:43', '2026-05-30 03:44:43'),
(4684, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 12, 5, 'Toraja', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, catch the dawn chorus of buﬀalo grunts and excited haggling at <strong>Bolu buffalo market</strong>. This open-air market – which takes place on Tuesdays and Saturdays – is surely one of Indonesia’s most fascinating animal shows, yet it remains very much a local event with few visitors.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Today excursion will give us a further insight into the local traditions and captivated us with its beautiful scenery. The megalith collections of Bori and beautiful <strong>Tongkonan</strong> adorned with ornaments, carvings and majestic <strong>buffalo horns in Pallawa</strong> are our cultural starter.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">We continue to the mountain towards <strong>Batutumonga</strong>, located on a dramatic ridge, high on the slope of <strong>Mount Sesean</strong>. The area offers relaxing ambiance, cool temperature and beautiful scenery – a mixture of terraced paddy fields, forest and open grassland. It is really a perf &nbsp;ect place to sit, relax and enjoy a warm cup of Toraja coffee.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After lunch, we walk to <strong>Lo’komata</strong>. The sheer size and colourful motives on the doors of this big stone grave creates a sense of amazements to everyone standing upon it. Walking our way down to <strong>Tikala</strong>, we will get the first-hand experience of the local people daily life - women pounding rice, men scrubbing their buffalo, children laughing and playing… a seemingly happy and unworried existence contrasting the seriousness of funerals and graves.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Pick up by car then return to hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:44:43', '2026-05-30 03:44:43'),
(4685, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 12, 6, 'Toraja – Makassar - Departure', '<p>After breakfast, you’ll return to <strong>Makassar</strong>. You’ll arrive in the afternoon and directly transferred to the airport to catch your onward</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:44:43', '2026-05-30 03:44:43'),
(4686, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 11, 1, 'Makassar - Toraja', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Recommended arrival / pick up time between 08:00 – 10:00 AM</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Welcome to the gritty metropolis of <strong>Makassar</strong>, one of Indonesia’s greatest port and air hubs; full of history and culture diversity. You’ll be met upon arrival by the guide then set on a wondrous journey to <strong>Toraja</strong> that moves through lofty mountains landscape.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">This trip offers plenty of picturesque stop for you to have coffee or photo shoots. In the afternoon, we pass the notorious “erotic” in<strong> Bambapuang</strong> before entering the Toraja land.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">“The mountainous district of Toraja is the homeland of several ethnic groups who are called Toraja &nbsp;(Toraja means ‘the people of the mountains’ or ‘the people of the west’. The Toraja call their traditional religion <strong>Aluk Todolo</strong> (rites of the ancestors) and they live according to the patron that was defined by the ancestor’s and gods. These include the impressive rituals of burying the deceased.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The beautiful carved houses with the remarkable roofs, the so-called <strong>Tongkonan</strong>, are also built according to principles of Aluk Todolo. Although most Toraja are Christian nowadays, still many traditions live on. If during your stay in Toraja, there is an opportunity to visit an impressive funeral - or house ceremony or the big animal market, program could be adjusted to fit in these visits”</p>', NULL, 'No Meal', '2026-05-30 03:51:17', '2026-05-30 03:51:17'),
(4687, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 11, 2, 'Toraja', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Spend the morning exploring the highlights of the region. First, we will visit <strong>Lemo</strong> where graves are carved into the stone cliff and the wooden effigies of the dead gaze upon from its balcony. Continue explore the different ways the Toraja burry their death; from the <strong>baby graves</strong> in the trunk of big trees Kambira, then visit the <strong>King’s grave of&nbsp; Suaya</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the afternoon, continue to the curious cave of Londa. Use as grave, we can see bones and deceased in these natural caves. Then <strong>Ke’te Kesu,</strong> a small village well known for its original <strong>Tongkonan houses</strong>, beautiful wood carvings and typical Toraja paintings; this village is a Unesco World Heritage site.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:51:17', '2026-05-30 03:51:17'),
(4688, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 11, 3, 'Toraja', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, catch the dawn chorus of buﬀalo grunts and excited haggling at <strong>Bolu buffalo market</strong>. This open-air market – which takes place on Tuesdays and Saturdays – is surely one of Indonesia’s most fascinating animal shows, yet it remains very much a local event with few visitors.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Today excursion will give us a further insight into the local traditions and captivated us with its beautiful scenery. The beautiful <strong>Tongkonan</strong> adorned with ornaments, carvings and majestic <strong>buffalo horns in Pallawa</strong> are our cultural starter.</p><p><i>Overnight in Toraja</i></p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:51:17', '2026-05-30 03:51:17'),
(4689, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 11, 4, 'Toraja', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Today excursion will give us a further insight into the local traditions and captivated us with its beautiful scenery. The megalith collections of <strong>Bori</strong>. We continue to the mountain towards <strong>Batutumonga</strong>, located on a dramatic ridge, high on the slope of <strong>Mount Sesean</strong>. The area offers relaxing ambiance, cool temperature and beautiful scenery – a mixture of terraced paddy fields, forest and open grassland. It is really a perfect place to sit, relax and enjoy a warm cup of <strong>Toraja coffee</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the afternoon, we walk to <strong>Lo’komata</strong>. The sheer size and colourful motives on the doors of this big stone grave creates a sense of amazements to everyone standing upon it.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Walking our way down to <strong>Tikala</strong>, we will get the first-hand experience of the local people daily life - women pounding rice, men scrubbing their buffalo, children laughing and playing… a seemingly happy and unworried existence contrasting the seriousness of funerals and graves. Pick up by car then return to hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:51:17', '2026-05-30 03:51:17'),
(4690, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 11, 5, 'Toraja – Makassar - Departure', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, you’ll return to <strong>Makassar</strong>. You’ll arrive in the afternoon and directly transferred to the airport to catch your onwards flight.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 03:51:17', '2026-05-30 03:51:17'),
(4691, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 10, 1, 'Makassar - Toraja', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Welcome to the gritty metropolis of <strong>Makassar</strong>, one of Indonesia’s greatest port and air hubs; full of history and culture diversity. You’ll be met upon arrival by the guide then set on a wondrous journey to <strong>Toraja</strong> that moves through lofty mountains landscape. This trip offers plenty of picturesque stop for you to have coffee or photo shoots.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the afternoon, we pass the notorious “erotic” mountain <strong>Buttu Kabobong in Bambapuang</strong> before entering the <strong>Toraja land</strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">“The mountainous district of Toraja is the homeland of several ethnic groups who are called Toraja (Toraja means ‘the people of the mountains’ or ‘the people of the west’. The Toraja call their traditional religion Aluk Todolo (rites of the ancestors) and they live according to the patron that was defined by the ancestor’s and gods. These include the impressive rituals of burying the deceased.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The beautiful carved houses with the remarkable roofs, the so-called <strong>Tongkonan</strong>, are also built according to principles of Aluk Todolo. Although most Toraja are Christian nowadays, still many traditions live on. If during your stay in Toraja, there is an opportunity to visit an impressive funeral - or house ceremony or the big animal market, program could be adjusted to fit in these visits”</p>', NULL, 'No Meal', '2026-05-30 04:02:34', '2026-05-30 04:02:34'),
(4692, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 10, 2, 'Toraja', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Spend the morning exploring the highlights of the region. First, we will visit <strong>Lemo</strong> where graves are carved into the stone cliff and the wooden effigies of the dead gaze upon from its balcony. Continue explore the different ways the <strong>Toraja</strong> burry their death; from the <strong>baby graves</strong> in the trunk of big trees Kambira, then visit the <strong>King’s grave of&nbsp; Suaya</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the afternoon, continue to the curious <strong>cave of Londa</strong>. Use as grave, we can see bones and deceased in these natural caves. Then <strong>Ke’te Kesu</strong>, a small village well known for its original <strong>Tongkonan houses</strong>, beautiful wood carvings and typical Toraja paintings; this village is a Unesco World Heritage site.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 04:02:34', '2026-05-30 04:02:34'),
(4693, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 10, 3, 'Toraja', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, catch the dawn chorus of buﬀalo grunts and excited haggling at <strong>Bolu buffalo market</strong>. This open-air market – which takes place on Tuesdays and Saturdays – is surely one of Indonesia’s most fascinating animal shows, yet it remains very much a local event with few visitors.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Today excursion will give us a further insight into the local traditions and captivated us with its beautiful scenery. The megalith collections of Bori and beautiful <strong>Tongkonan</strong> adorned with ornaments, carvings and majestic buffalo horns in <strong>Pallawa</strong> are our cultural starter.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">We continue to the mountain towards <strong>Batutumonga</strong>, located on a dramatic ridge, high on the slope <strong>of Mount Sesean</strong>. The area offers relaxing ambiance, cool temperature and beautiful scenery – a mixture of terraced paddy fields, forest and open grassland. It is really a perfect place to sit, relax and enjoy a warm cup of <strong>Toraja</strong> coffee.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After lunch, we walk to <strong>Lo’komata</strong>. The sheer size and colourful motives on the doors of this big stone grave creates a sense of amazements to everyone standing upon it.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Walking our way down to <strong>Tikala</strong>, we will get the first-hand experience of the local people daily life - women pounding rice, men scrubbing their buffalo, children laughing and playing… a seemingly happy and unworried existence contrasting the seriousness of funerals and graves. Pick up by car then return to hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 04:02:34', '2026-05-30 04:02:34'),
(4694, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 10, 4, 'Toraja – Makassar - Departure', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, you’ll return to <strong>Makassar</strong>. You’ll arrive in the afternoon anddirectly transferred to the airport to catch your onwards flight.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-05-30 04:02:34', '2026-05-30 04:02:34'),
(4698, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 18, 1, 'Arrival - Luwuk – Banggai Kepulauan', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setibanya di Bandara Syukuran Aminuddin Amir Luwuk, peserta tour akan disambut dan langsung diantar menuju restoran lokal untuk makan siang.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Perjalanan dilanjutkan mengunjungi <strong>Air Terjun Piala</strong> – air terjun unik dengan formasi bertingkat menyerupai tangga alami &amp; dikelilingi dengan pepohonan hijau yang asri serta aliran air jernih yang menyegarkan.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah itu, menuju ke dermaga untuk penyeberangan ke <strong>Banggai Kepulauan</strong> menggunakan kapal ferry. Tiba di Banggai Kepulauan, makan malam di restoran lokal lalu menuju penginapan untuk beristirahat.</p><p><strong>Bermalam di Banggai Kepulauan</strong></p>', NULL, 'Lunch/Dinner', '2026-06-01 15:22:58', '2026-06-01 15:22:58'),
(4699, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 18, 2, 'Banggai Kepulauan (Paisupok – Paisu Batango – Kawalu Bay – Ndulubas)', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah sarapan pagi, peserta tour dijemput untuk memulai tour di Banggai Kepulauan dengan mengunjungi <strong>Danau Paisupok</strong> – danau alami berair biru kehijauan dengan dasar yang terlihat jelas.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Selanjutnya menuju Paisu Batango untuk makan siang (lunch box) sambil menikmati suasana alam di tepian laut dengan kolam alami jernih berwarna biru kehijauan yang tenang serta suasana yang sejuk.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Perjalanan dilanjutkan ke <strong>Kawalu Bay</strong> dan <strong>Ndulubas</strong> untuk menikmati keindahan bawah laut dengan aktivitas snorkeling <i>(sudah termasuk alat snorkeling)</i>. Makan malam disediakan di restoran lokal. Setelah makan malam, kembali ke penginapan untuk beristirahat.</p><p><strong>Bermalam di Banggai Kepulauan</strong></p>', NULL, 'Breakfast/Lunch/Dinner', '2026-06-01 15:22:58', '2026-06-01 15:22:58'),
(4700, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 18, 3, 'Banggai Laut (Tanjung Gundul – Pantai Pasir Panjang – Pantai Oyama – Pantai Bontolan)', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah sarapan pagi, peserta tour memulai perjalanan ke <strong>Banggai Laut </strong>menggunakan speedboat; perjalanan diawali ke <strong>Tanjung Gundul</strong> yang menawarkan panorama laut indah dengan tebing unik berlubang alami, cocok sebagai spot foto dan tempat bersantai menikmati suasana pantai yang tenang.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Perjalanan selanjutnya menuju <strong>Pantai</strong> <strong>Pasir Panjang </strong>yang dikenal dengan hamparan pasir putihnya yang luas dan indah. Selanjutnya, peserta tour diajak mengunjungi <strong>Pantai</strong> <strong>Oyama </strong>yang menawarkan kejernihan air laut serta suasana yang tenang cocok untuk bersantai dan menikmati keindahan alam.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Kemudian menuju ke <strong>Pantai Bontolan </strong><i>(makan siang – lunch box)</i>, dimana peserta tour dapat mengeksplorasi pesona bawah laut yang memukau dengan melihat ikan endemik yaitu <strong>Cardinal Fish </strong><i>(sudah termasuk alat snorkeling)</i>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Menjelang sore hari, kembali ke Banggai Kepulauan, makan malam di restoran lokal, lalu menuju penginapan untuk beristirahat.</p><p><strong>Bermalam di Banggai Kepulauan</strong></p>', NULL, 'Breakfast/Lunch/Dinner', '2026-06-01 15:22:58', '2026-06-01 15:22:58'),
(4701, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 18, 4, 'Banggai Kepulauan (Pantai Mandel – Pantai Pompon – Pulau Bobilon)', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah sarapan pagi &amp; check out dari penginapan, peserta tour dijemput dan diantar perjalanan menuju <strong>Pantai</strong> <strong>Mandel </strong>untuk menikmati keindahan alam serta suasana pantai yang tenang dan menyegarkan.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Perjalanan kemudian dilanjutkan ke <strong>Pantai</strong> <strong>Pompon </strong>yang menawarkan pesona pantai yang masih alami dan cocok untuk bersantai sambil menikmati panorama laut. Dari Pantai Pompon, peserta tour dapat menyeberang ke <strong>Pulau</strong> <strong>Bobilon </strong>menggunakan boat kecil dan melakukan aktivitas snorkeling <i>(sudah termasuk alat snorkeling)</i>. Pelayanan makan siang disediakan di lokal restoran.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Menjelang sore hari, kembali ke Luwuk menggunakan kapal ferry. Setibanya di Luwuk, menuju restoran lokal untuk makan malam, dan setelah makan malam diantar ke hotel untuk proses check-in dan beristirahat.</p><p><strong>Bermalam di Luwuk&nbsp;</strong></p>', NULL, 'Breakfast/Lunch/Dinner', '2026-06-01 15:22:58', '2026-06-01 15:22:58'),
(4702, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 18, 5, 'Luwuk - Transfer Out', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah <strong>sarapan pagi &amp; proses check-out</strong> hotel, peserta tour diantar ke Bandara untuk penerbangan kembali. Tour selesai.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-01 15:22:58', '2026-06-01 15:22:58'),
(4703, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 40, 1, 'ARRIVAL – SEKONYER RIVER – TANJUNG HARAPAN', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival, we begin our journey cruising the <strong>Sekonyer River</strong> by Klotok boat.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">We will visit <strong>Tanjung Harapan</strong> to witness the afternoon <strong>Orangutan feeding</strong> and enjoy a jungle trek.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the evening, we will embark on a <strong>Night Trekking</strong> adventure to discover the rainforest\'s nocturnal wildlife. Lunch and dinner are served on the boat.</p>', NULL, 'Lunch/Dinner', '2026-06-01 15:24:04', '2026-06-01 15:24:04'),
(4704, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 40, 2, 'DEEP JUNGLE – JERUMBUN – CAMP LEAKEY', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, we head deeper into the forest for a <strong>Long Trekking</strong> experience in the <strong>Jerumbun</strong> area. &nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">We then cruise through the mirror-like waters of the <strong>Black River</strong> towards the legendary <strong>Camp Leakey</strong>. Here, you will visit the conservation center and explore the trails of this world-renowned orangutan research site.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast/Lunch/Dinner', '2026-06-01 15:24:04', '2026-06-01 15:24:04'),
(4705, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 40, 3, 'PONDOK TANGGUI – SEKONYER VILLAGE – FIREFLY DINNER', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The morning starts with a visit to <strong>Pondok Tanggui</strong> for the orangutan feeding session.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Afterward, we visit <strong>Sekonyer Village</strong> to experience the local Dayak community\'s lifestyle followed by a peaceful <strong>Canoeing</strong> activity along the river.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The day ends with a magical <strong>Firefly Dinner</strong> as thousands of fireflies light up the riverbanks.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast/Lunch/Dinner', '2026-06-01 15:24:04', '2026-06-01 15:24:04'),
(4706, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 40, 4, 'NIPAH FOREST – RUMAH BETANG – DEPARTURE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Enjoy your final breakfast while cruising through the <strong>Nipah Palm forest</strong> towards Kumai Port.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Before heading to the airport, we will visit the <strong>traditional Dayak Longhouse (Rumah Betang)</strong> in Pasir Panjang to learn about the local culture.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Finally, you will be transferred to the airport or your hotel for your departure.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-01 15:24:04', '2026-06-01 15:24:04'),
(4707, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 57, 1, 'BEACH TOUR', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setibanya di Bandara Tanjung Pandan, Anda akan disambut oleh tim kami dan langsung memulai&nbsp; perjalanan menyusuri deretan pantai indah di Belitung.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Destinasi pertama adalah <strong>Pantai Tanjung Kelayang</strong> dan <strong>Pantai Tanjung Tinggi (Laskar Pelangi)</strong> yang terkenal dengan formasi batu granit raksasanya. Setelah menikmati makan siang di restoran lokal, perjalanan dilanjutkan menuju <strong>Pantai Bukit Berahu</strong> dan <strong>Pantai Tanjung Pendam</strong> untuk menikmati suasana pesisir yang menenangkan.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Di sini, Anda juga memiliki kesempatan untuk mencicipi kopi legendaris di \"<strong>Kong Djie Coffee</strong>\" &nbsp;secara opsional. Sebelum hari berakhir, Anda akan diajak mengunjungi pusat oleh-oleh khas Belitung untuk berbelanja buah tangan, disusul dengan makan malam di restoran lokal sebelum menuju hotel untuk proses <i>check-in</i> dan istirahat.</p>', NULL, 'Lunch/Dinner', '2026-06-02 02:50:53', '2026-06-02 02:50:53'),
(4708, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 57, 2, 'CITY TOUR – KULINER (BELITUNG NOODLES)', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Setelah sarapan dan <i>check-out</i>, Anda akan diajak mengunjungi <strong>Rumah Adat Belitung</strong>, menikmati sajian tradisional Mie Belitung dan Es Jeruk Konci, serta melihat keindahan Danau Kaolin sebelum langsung diantar ke Bandara untuk penerbangan pulang. Tour selesai.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast/Lunch', '2026-06-02 02:50:53', '2026-06-02 02:50:53'),
(4709, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 8, 1, 'Makassar - Toraja', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Recommended arrival / pick up time between 08:00 – 10:00 AM</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Welcome to the gritty metropolis of Makassar, one of Indonesia’s greatest port and air hubs; full of history and culture diversity. You’ll be met upon arrival by the guide then set on a wondrous journey to <strong>Toraja</strong> that moves through lofty mountains landscape.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">This trip offers plenty of picturesque stop for you to have coffee or photo shoots. In the afternoon, we pass the notorious “erotic” <strong>mountain Buttu Kabobong</strong> in <strong>Bambapuang</strong> &nbsp;before entering the Toraja land.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">“The mountainous district of Toraja is the homeland of several ethnic groups who are called Toraja (Toraja means ‘the people of the mountains’ or ‘the people of the west’. The Toraja call their traditional religion <strong>Aluk&nbsp; Todolo</strong> (rites of the ancestors) and they live according to the patron that was defined by the ancestor’s and gods. These include the impressive rituals of burying the deceased.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The beautiful carved houses with the remarkable roofs, the so-called <strong>Tongkonan</strong>, are also built according to principles of Aluk Todolo. Although most Toraja are Christian nowadays, still many traditions live on. If during your stay in Toraja, there is an opportunity to visit an impressive funeral - or house ceremony or the big animal market, program could be adjusted to fit in these visits”</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><i>Overnight in Toraja</i></p>', NULL, 'No Meal', '2026-06-02 03:34:38', '2026-06-02 03:34:38'),
(4710, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 8, 2, 'Toraja - (Lemo, Kambira, Suaya, Londa, Kete Kesu)', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Spend the morning exploring the highlights of the region. First, we will visit <strong>Lemo</strong> where graves are carved into the stone cliff and the wooden effigies of the dead gaze upon from its balcony. Continue explore the different ways the Toraja burry their death; from the baby graves in the trunk of big trees <strong>Kambira</strong>, then visit the <strong>King’s grave of&nbsp; Suaya</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the afternoon, continue to the curious <strong>cave of Londa</strong>. Use as grave, we can see bones and deceased in these natural caves. Then <strong>Ke’te Kesu</strong>, a small village well known for its original <strong>Tongkonan houses</strong>, beautiful wood carvings and typical Toraja paintings; this village is a Unesco World Heritage site.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><i>Overnight in Toraja</i></p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 03:34:38', '2026-06-02 03:34:38'),
(4711, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 8, 3, 'Toraja – Makassar - Departure', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, you’ll return to <strong>Makassar</strong>. You’ll arrive in the afternoon and directly transferred to the airport to catch your onwards flight.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 03:34:38', '2026-06-02 03:34:38'),
(4712, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 9, 1, 'Makassar  (City Tour)', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at <strong>Sultan Hasanuddin International Airport Makassar</strong>, meeting services. Afterwards, we continue for a short city tour in Makassar by visiting&nbsp;<strong>Paotere Harbour</strong>&nbsp;to see the traditional harbour of Bugis-Makassarese sailors.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After lunch Then, proceed to&nbsp;<strong>Fort Rotterdam</strong>, the Old Dutch Fortress. In the late afternoon we will visit&nbsp;<strong>“Anjungan Pantai Losari Makassar”</strong>&nbsp;the Boulevard and the icon of Makassar where you enjoy the Sunset (if the weather allows).&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'No Meal', '2026-06-02 03:42:42', '2026-06-02 03:42:42'),
(4713, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 9, 2, 'Makassar  (Rammang-Rammang Tour)', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Today, full day tour will be started by visiting&nbsp;<strong>Rammang-Rammang&nbsp;the limestone valley</strong>, located in Maros Regency, taking for approximately 90 minutes’ drive from downtown. The Karst Mountains are surrounded by beautiful <strong>rice fields</strong> (the rice fields look nicer from May till August).</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Afterwards, we will take you to explore the <strong>karst mountain</strong> formation using small wooden boat at the <strong>Pute River</strong>. If you are lucky, you could also see the real endemic from the forest such as birds and monkeys. We will also take you for a walk to visit the pre-historic cave, where you can see the pre-historic paintings, then short explore inside the cave to see the stalactite and stalagmite.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the afternoon we will have a little walk at the <strong>Stone Garden of Rammang-Rammang</strong>. Then, drive back to Makassar.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 03:42:42', '2026-06-02 03:42:42'),
(4714, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 9, 3, 'Makassar  (Balla Lompoa Museum, Fort Somba Opu, Shopping)', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, we will take you to the <strong>Gowa Regency</strong> to visit&nbsp;<strong>Balla Lompoa Museum</strong>, which is the traditional house Gowa Kingdom during colonial time, where you can see some collections from one of the most famous Gowa Kings, Sultan Hasanuddin.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Afterwards, proceed to&nbsp;<strong>Fort Somba Opu</strong>&nbsp;where you can see the collections of the traditional houses from the four ethnics in South and West Sulawesi.In the afternoon free shopping time at <strong>Jalan Somba Opu</strong>, which is the centre of the souvenir and gold store in Makassar.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 03:42:42', '2026-06-02 03:42:42'),
(4715, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 9, 4, 'Depart Makassar', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">You will be picked up at a good time and transferred to the airport to catch your flight to the next destination.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 03:42:42', '2026-06-02 03:42:42'),
(4716, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 35, 1, 'KNO - Parapat - Samosir Island --> arr flight must be in the morning before 11 am', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">KNO - Parapat ±170 km ±&nbsp;4 hrs / Parapat - Samosir by&nbsp;ferry 1 hour</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Arrive at airport, meet and greet at the airport then depart for <strong>Parapat</strong> – famous mountain and lake resort on the east shore of the immense <strong>volcanic Lake Toba</strong>,&nbsp;about 175 km from airport.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">En route, first hour pass by several small towns and then followed by vast view of rubber, oil palm plantations, paddy terraces, etc. Stopover at Paten, local&nbsp;snack&nbsp;shop for toilet break.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Arrive in <strong>Parapat</strong>, cross over to <strong>Samosir Island</strong>, an island in the middle of Lake Toba in 45 mins by public&nbsp;ferry. Check in hotel.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 03:58:32', '2026-06-02 03:58:32'),
(4717, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 35, 2, 'Samosir Island tour halfday by boat', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast start on <strong>Samosir</strong> Tour halfday by motorboat. Visit the <strong>Tomb of King Sidabutar and Batak Toba Village at Tomok</strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then to <strong>Ambarita</strong>, a traditional village with ancient megalithic furniture in front of the traditional house. Back to hotel.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Rest of the day free on own activities to explore the beauty of <strong>Samosir Island</strong>. You can walk around the island, rent bicycles (own expenses) or just swimming and sunbathing.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 03:58:32', '2026-06-02 03:58:32'),
(4718, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 35, 3, 'Samosir Island - Parapat - Brastagi - Medan', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast depart for <strong>Brastagi</strong> via the Ring Road of Lake Toba. En route pass by pine tree plantation, the magnificent scenery of <strong>Lake Toba</strong>, fertile vegetable and fruit farms.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Visit the slender <strong>Sipiso-piso Waterfall</strong> which drops into Lake Toba from hundreds of meter height.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Arrive in <strong>Brastagi</strong>, a refreshing mountain resort dominated by two active volcanoes, visit the fruit market.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Depart for Medan via some part of the lush <strong>tropical rain forest of Sumatra</strong> in two-and-half-hour time.&nbsp;Arrive in Medan, check in hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 03:58:32', '2026-06-02 03:58:32'),
(4719, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 35, 4, 'City Tour - Transfer Out / Dept', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Breakfast at hotel. Start on <strong>Medan City</strong> Tour if time is permissible.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>City tour of Medan visits Maimun Palace of Old Deli Sultanate and Tjong A Fie Mansion.</strong> Four hours before departure flight start transfer to the airport for the flight to your next destination.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Objects of city tour can be reduced if dept flight is early.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 03:58:32', '2026-06-02 03:58:32'),
(4726, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 37, 1, 'KUALA NAMU - MEDAN – BOHOROK / BUKIT LAWANG', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Arrive at <strong>Medan Kuala Namu airport </strong>before&nbsp;12 pm, meet and greet then drive to north-westward for about&nbsp;3.5 hours to <strong>Bohorok, orang utan center.</strong>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">En route passing through several small towns followed by vast view of rubber and oil palm plantations with some countryside landscape.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Stop to see palm oil plantation from outside. If it’s in season you can stop to see local <strong>“rambutan”</strong> and <strong>cacao garden</strong>, also stop to see <strong>local market in Kuala</strong>. Arrive in <strong>Bohorok</strong>, check-in at hotel.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 05:18:20', '2026-06-02 05:18:20'),
(4727, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 37, 2, 'BOHOROK TREKKING TO SEE THE ORANG UTANS - MEDAN', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast,&nbsp;start on a&nbsp;3 hrs jungle trekking where you can see the semi or <strong>wild Orangutans</strong>. Steep, slopes and dense vegetation will bring you to the excitement of the <strong>Sumatra rainforest</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Here you have the opportunity to see several species of indigenous flora and fauna. If you are lucky, you may encounter Orang Utan, leaf monkey, macaque, gibbons, siamang and abundant bird life. Walkers must be fit and have suitable, large profile shoes. Trekking pace will be adjusted with client\'s stamina.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Back to hotel. After the trek transfer to Medan via rubber and oil-palm plantation road in 3 hrs time. Check in hotel.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 05:18:20', '2026-06-02 05:18:20'),
(4728, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 37, 3, 'MEDAN - BRASTAGI - PARAPAT - SAMOSIR ISLAND', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast leave for&nbsp;<strong>Brastagi</strong> - a highland resort with its refreshing weather and magnificent <strong>mountain scenery</strong>, through some part of the lush <strong>tropical rain forest of Sumatra</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Reaching <strong>Brastagi</strong> visit <strong>Taman Lumbini</strong>, Golden Burmese Pagoda and the &nbsp;fruit market of Brastagi. Continue to Parapat famous lake resort lies on the east shore of Lake Toba. On the way, visit <strong>traditional Batak Karo village</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Stop at <strong>Sipisopiso</strong> with its 120m high waterfall and very scenic view over <strong>lake Toba</strong>. Proceed to <strong>Parapat</strong> through vegetable and fruits plantations, pine tree forests and some spectacular views of Lake Toba.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Arrive in Parapat, leave for Samosir, an Island in the <strong>center of Lake Toba</strong> by&nbsp;public boat&nbsp; in one hour time. Check in hotel.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 05:18:20', '2026-06-02 05:18:20'),
(4729, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 37, 4, 'SAMOSIR ISLAND TOUR HALFDAY BY BOAT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast start on <strong>Samosir</strong> Tour halfday by motorboat. Visit the <strong>Tomb of King Sidabutar</strong> and <strong>Batak Toba Village at Tomok</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then to <strong>Ambarita</strong>, a tradition&nbsp;&nbsp; al village with ancient megalithic furniture in front of the traditional house. Back to hotel.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Rest of the day free on own activities to explore the beauty of <strong>Samosir Island</strong>. You can walk around the island, rent bicycles (own expenses) or just swimming and sunbathing.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 05:18:20', '2026-06-02 05:18:20'),
(4730, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 37, 5, 'SAMOSIR – PARAPAT – MEDAN CITY TOUR', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Morning free time at <strong>Samosir Island</strong>. In the afternoon return to Parapat by public ferry then depart for Medan.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">En route, first three hours passing by vast view of rubber, oil palm plantations, paddy terraces, &nbsp;etc and small towns such as <strong>Pematang Siantar and Tebing Tinggi</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Arrive in Medan,&nbsp;Start city tour of Medan visit&nbsp;<strong>Maimoon Palace</strong>, the palace of Old Deli Kingdom. Also visit <strong>The Temple of East Mountain,</strong> a Chinese temple with its unique characteristics.&nbsp;Check in hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 05:18:20', '2026-06-02 05:18:20'),
(4731, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 37, 6, 'TRANSFER OUT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Medan - apt ± 40 km ± 60-90 mins</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Free on own activities until transfer time to airport.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Based on current traffic,&nbsp;we will transfer&nbsp;clients to airport from hotel 4 hours before dept flight.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 05:18:20', '2026-06-02 05:18:20'),
(4732, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 38, 1, 'ARRIVAL – BOHOROK', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">KNO - Bohorok / Bukit Lawang&nbsp;± 130 km ± 3,5 hrs drive</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Arrive at <strong>Medan Kuala Namu airport</strong> before&nbsp;12 pm, meet and greet then drive to north-westward for about&nbsp;3,5 hours to <strong>Bohorok, orang utan center</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">En route passing through several small towns followed by vast view of rubber and oil palm plantations with some countryside landscape. Stop to see palm oil plantation from outside. If it’s in season you can stop to see local <strong>“rambutan” </strong>and <strong>cacao garden, </strong>also stop to see <strong>local market in Kuala.</strong>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Arrive in Bohorok, check-in at hotel.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 05:55:51', '2026-06-02 05:55:51'),
(4733, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 38, 2, 'BOHOROK TREKKING TO SEE THE ORANG UTANS - MEDAN', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast,&nbsp;start on a&nbsp;3 hrs jungle trekking where you can see the semi or <strong>wild Orangutans</strong>. Steep, slopes and dense vegetation will bring you to the excitement of the <strong>Sumatra rainforest</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Here you have the opportunity to see several species of indigenous flora and fauna. If you are lucky you may encounter Orang Utan, leaf monkey, macaque, gibbons, siamang and abundant bird life. Walkers must be fit and have suitable, large profile shoes. Trekking pace will be adjusted with clients\'s stamina. Back to hotel.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After the trek transfer to Medan via rubber and oil-palm plantation road in 3 hrs time. Check in hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 05:55:51', '2026-06-02 05:55:51'),
(4734, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 38, 3, 'MEDAN - BRASTAGI - PARAPAT - SAMOSIR ISLAND', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast leave for&nbsp;<strong>Brastagi</strong> - a highland resort with its refreshing weather and magnificent <strong>mountain scenery</strong>, through some part of the lush <strong>tropical rain forest of Sumatra</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Reaching Brastagi visit <strong>Taman Lumbini</strong>, <strong>Golden Burmese Pagoda </strong>and<strong> the fruit market of Brastagi</strong>. Continue to Parapat famous lake resort lies on the east shore of Lake Toba. On the way, visit traditional <strong>Batak Karo village.</strong>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Stop at <strong>Sipisopiso</strong> with its 120m high waterfall and very scenic view over <strong>lake Toba</strong>. Proceed to Parapat through vegetable and fruits plantations, pine tree forests and some spectacular views of <strong>Lake Toba</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Arrive in Parapat, leave for <strong>Samosir</strong>, an Island in <strong>the center of Lake Toba by&nbsp;public boat</strong>&nbsp; in one hour time. Check in hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 05:55:51', '2026-06-02 05:55:51'),
(4735, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 38, 4, 'SAMOSIR ISLAND TOUR HALFDAY BY BOAT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast start on Samosir Tour halfday by motorboat. Visit the <strong>Tomb of King Sidabutar</strong> and <strong>Batak Toba Village at Tomok</strong>. Then to <strong>Ambarita</strong>, a traditional village with ancient megalithic furniture in front of the traditional house. Back to hotel.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Rest of the day free on own activities to explore the beauty of Samosir Island. You can walk around the island, rent bicycles (own expenses) or just swimming and sunbathing.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 05:55:51', '2026-06-02 05:55:51'),
(4736, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 38, 5, 'SAMOSIR INSEL - PARAPAT - PADANG SIDEMPUAN', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, check out from your hotel in <strong>Samosir</strong> and return by public (private for more than 5 paxs ) boat to the mainland at <strong>Parapat</strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue your journey for transit town <strong>Padang Sidempuan</strong>. Visit <strong>Lumban Binanga village</strong> and the small town <strong>Balige</strong> with its rich ornamented market hall.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">On the way we stop at local pineapple, clove and coffee farms. Take a walk along the banks of <strong>the Sarulla river</strong> and <strong>the beautiful, terraced rice fields</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Arrive at transit town <strong>Padang Sidempuan</strong>, check in your hotel for rest and overnight.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 05:55:51', '2026-06-02 05:55:51'),
(4737, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 38, 6, 'PADANG SIDEMPUAN - BUKITTINGGI', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Padang Sidempuan – Bukittinggi ± 350 km ± 10 hrs with stops.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The journey today is rather long but worthwhile. It exhibits the inner part of Sumatra. The scenery of mountains, rivers, valleys and traditional villages will relieve you from your weariness.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Passing through &nbsp;<strong>Aek Sijornih Waterfall</strong> and local villages. The <strong>Equator Monument at Bonjol</strong> should nonetheless be remarkable in your personal record. Remember to take a photo when you cross the white line marking the north and south side of the equator.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then proceed to the most charming town, the heart of <strong>Minangkabau Highland</strong>, and the center of matrilineal society of Sumatra, <strong>Bukittinggi</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Arrive in Bukittinggi in the&nbsp;evening. Transferred to hotel for rest and overnight.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 05:55:51', '2026-06-02 05:55:51'),
(4738, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 38, 7, 'BUKITTINGGI TOUR', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast check out and start on a fullday tour to explore the beauty and the cultural aspects of <strong>Minangkabau Highland.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">See the landmark of <strong>Bukittinggi – Jam Gadang (Clock Tower),</strong> the uniqueness of the local market and museum.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Enjoy the sight of the majestic <strong>Ngarai Sianok</strong> – a grand valley famous for its underground bunkers and tunnels built by the Japanese during World War II.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then to <strong>Koto Gadang village</strong> which is renowned for its silver works and hand embroidery. Also visit &nbsp;<strong>Pandai Sikek Village</strong> for wood carving and weaving handicraft.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Travel further to <strong>Pagaruyung</strong> – the site of the ancient Minangkabau Kingdom where women ruled in matrilineal society. The palace is a replica of the original Pagaruyung royal palace which was set on fire by the nation’s Dutch colonists in 1804. With 3 storeys and 5 stacked sweeping roofs ending with eleven sharp horns and covered with over 26 tons of palm fibers, Pagarayung is the most beautiful example of traditional Minangkabau architecture.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Drive to Padang the capital city of West Sumatra. Check in for rest and overnight.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 05:55:51', '2026-06-02 05:55:51'),
(4739, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 38, 8, 'TRANSFER OUT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast city tour of Padang (only if time permits) or direct transfer to the airport for departure to your next destination.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 05:55:51', '2026-06-02 05:55:51'),
(4740, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 7, 1, 'Makassar  (City Tour)', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at <strong>Sultan Hasanuddin International Airport Makassar</strong>, meeting services. Afterwards, we continue for a short city tour in Makassar by visiting&nbsp; <strong>Paotere Harbour to</strong> see the traditional harbour of Bugis-Makassarese sailors. Lunch will be served in a local restaurant.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then, proceed <strong>to Fort Rotterdam</strong>, the Old Dutch Fortress. In the late afternoon we will visit&nbsp;<strong>“Anjungan Pantai Losari Makassar”</strong>&nbsp;the Boulevard and the icon of Makassar where you enjoy the Sunset (if the weather allows). Dinner will be served in a local seafood restaurant.</p><p><i>Overnight in Makassar</i></p>', NULL, 'No Meal', '2026-06-02 07:30:45', '2026-06-02 07:30:45');
INSERT INTO `itineraries` (`id`, `itinerable_type`, `itinerable_id`, `day_number`, `title`, `description`, `hotel_info`, `meals_info`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(4741, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 7, 2, 'Makassar  (Rammang-Rammang Tour)', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Today, full day tour will be started by visiting&nbsp;<strong>Rammang-Rammang</strong>&nbsp;<strong>the limestone valley</strong>, located in <strong>Maros Regency</strong>, taking for approximately 90 minutes’ drive from downtown. <strong>The Karst Mountains</strong> are surrounded by beautiful rice fields (the rice fields look nicer from May till August).</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Afterwards, we will take you to explore the karst mountain formation using small wooden boat at the <strong>Pute River</strong>. If you are lucky, you could also see the real endemic from the forest such as birds and monkeys.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">We will also take you for a walk to visit the pre-historic cave, where you can see the pre-historic paintings, then short explore inside the cave to see the stalactite and stalagmite.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the afternoon we will have a little walk at the Stone Garden of <strong>Rammang-Rammang</strong>. Then, drive back to Makassar.</p><p><i>Overnight in Makassar</i></p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 07:30:45', '2026-06-02 07:30:45'),
(4742, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 7, 3, 'Makassar - Airport', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast continue with the check-out process, afterwards we will visit Jalan <strong>Somba Opu</strong>, which is the centre of the souvenir and gold store in Makassar. Afterwards transfer to Sultan Hasanuddin International Airport to catch your flight to the next destination.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 07:30:45', '2026-06-02 07:30:45'),
(4743, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 22, 1, 'ARRIVAL - PARANGTRITIS – OBELIX SEAVIEW', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Arrival at Yogyakarta Airport, you will be picked up by our representative. Straight, we will take you to <strong>Parangtritis Beach</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then, visit <strong>Gumuk Pasir sand dune</strong> is rare phenomenon, only few in the world. They are a very high sedimentation of sand coming from <strong>Merapi and Merbabu mountains</strong> forming like a desert.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Next, enjoy sunset from <strong>Obelix Seaview</strong> with Hindian Ocean panorama.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Check in hotel, free program. Lunch and dinner will be served at local restaurant (Optional).</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 07:46:37', '2026-06-02 07:46:37'),
(4744, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 22, 2, 'LAVA TOUR – BOROBUDUR – MALIOBORO', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, we take you to enjoy <strong>Lava Tour in Merapi Mountain</strong> by riding jeep 4x4 WD visiting ruin houses museum caused by Merapi eruption in 2010, <strong>“alien stone”</strong>,<strong> </strong>and bunker.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Lunch at local restaurant (Optional), continue stepping up to <strong>Borobudur Temple structure floor, </strong>buil &nbsp;t in 9th Century during the Sailendra Dynasty and has been listed as a UNESCO World Heritage Site.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Free shopping at <strong>Malioboro Street</strong>. Back to hotel, free program.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 07:46:37', '2026-06-02 07:46:37'),
(4745, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 22, 3, 'TRANSFER OUT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, check out procedure. Transfer to airport to leave Jogja.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 07:46:37', '2026-06-02 07:46:37'),
(4746, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 23, 1, 'ARRIVAL - PARANGTRITIS – OBELIX SEAVIEW', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Arrival at Yogyakarta Airport, you will be picked up by our representative. Straight, we will take you to <strong>Parangtritis Beach</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then, visit <strong>Gumuk Pasir sand dune</strong> is rare phenomenon, only few in the world. They are a very high sedimentation of sand coming from <strong>Merapi and Merbabu mountains</strong> forming like a desert.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Next, enjoy sunset from <strong>Obelix Seaview</strong> with Hindian Ocean panorama. Check in hotel, free program. Lunch and dinner will be served at local restaurant (Optional).&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 08:37:51', '2026-06-02 08:37:51'),
(4747, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 23, 2, 'LAVA TOUR – BOROBUDUR', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, we will take you to <strong>Merapi Mountain</strong> to enjoy <strong>Lava Tour </strong>by riding jeep 4x4 WD visiting <strong>ruin houses museum</strong> caused by Merapi eruption in 2010, “alien stone”,<strong> </strong>and bunker.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Lunch at local restaurant (Optional). Continue s<strong>tepping up to Borobudur Temple structure floor, </strong>built in 9th Century during the Sailendra Dynasty and has been listed as a UNESCO World Heritage Site.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to <strong>Candi Mendut</strong> (Mendut Temple) is older than Candi Borobudur there are story of children in it walls and <strong>Candi Pawon</strong> (Pawon temple) it\'s not a grave but a place to keep King Indra’s weapon namely Vajranala.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Dinner at local restaurant (Optional). Back to hotel, free program.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 08:37:51', '2026-06-02 08:37:51'),
(4748, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 23, 3, 'CITY TOUR – TEBING BREKSI – OBELIX HILLS', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Breakfast at hotel, we will take you to <strong>Sultan Palace</strong> which still today considered the highest-ranking court of Indonesia where old custom of courtesy is still practiced.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Not far from the Palace, proceed to <strong>Taman Sari Water castle </strong>is a recreation garden for Sri Sultan’s family. There is a pool that was once used as a bath for the king\'s concubines.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Lunch at local restaurant (Optional). Continue to <strong>Tebing Breksi,</strong> ruins of traditional mining then managed to become tourist destination equipped with several instagramable spot selfie.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then continue to visit <strong>Obelix Hills, </strong>is one of the newest one tourist destinations with sunset point that equipped with&nbsp; instagramable spot selfie. &nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Dinner at local restaurant (Optional), back to hotel, free program.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 08:37:52', '2026-06-02 08:37:52'),
(4749, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 23, 4, 'TRANSFER OUT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, check out procedure. Transfer to airport to leave Jogja.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 08:37:52', '2026-06-02 08:37:52'),
(4761, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 91, 1, 'DETAIL ITINERARY', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Duration: Estimate 12 Hours&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Tour Starting / Ending: Surabaya City</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or pick-up from your hotel in Surabaya, meet your guide and begin a scenic journey to the beautiful coastline of South Malang. Explore <strong>Teluk Asmara Beach</strong>, famous for its breathtaking panorama of small islands scattered across the turquoise sea, followed by <strong>Goa Cina Beach</strong>, known for its dramatic cliffs, unique cave, and stunning ocean scenery.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to <strong>Tanjung Penyu Beach</strong>, a peaceful hidden beach offering spectacular coastal views and a relaxing atmosphere. The tour concludes at <strong>Balekambang Beach</strong>, one of East Java’s most iconic beaches, featuring a beautiful temple standing on a rocky island connected to the mainland by a bridge.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After enjoying the natural beauty of South Malang, return comfortably to Surabaya and be transferred to <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel. This tour is perfect for travelers looking to discover East Java’s hidden coastal treasures in a single unforgettable day.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 11:32:20', '2026-06-02 11:32:20'),
(4762, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 92, 1, 'DETAIL ITINERARY', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Duration: Estimate 12 Hours&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Tour Starting / Ending: Surabaya</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Meet and greet with your guide at <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel in Surabaya before starting the tour at approximately <strong>11.30 PM</strong>. Begin the overnight journey to the legendary <strong>Mount Bromo</strong>, one of Indonesia’s most iconic natural attractions. Upon arrival at the jeep station in Sukapura, continue the adventure aboard a 4WD jeep across the spectacular volcanic landscape of Bromo Tengger Semeru National Park.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Witness a breathtaking sunrise from one of Bromo’s famous viewpoints, where the first rays of sunlight illuminate the magnificent panorama of Mount Bromo, Mount Batok, and the towering Mount Semeru in the distance. Continue to <strong>Widodaren Hill</strong>, offering another impressive perspective of the surrounding mountains and valleys.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The adventure continues to the foot of <strong>Mount Bromo</strong>, where you can cross the vast Sea of Sand and climb to the crater rim to experience the beauty of this active volcano up close. Explore the picturesque <strong>Savannah Field</strong>, known for its rolling green grasslands, and visit the unique <strong>Whispering Sand</strong>, a volcanic desert famous for the sound created by wind passing over its fine black sand.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After enjoying the beauty of Bromo and breakfast, return comfortably to Surabaya and transfer to <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel. End of tour with unforgettable memories from East Java’s most spectacular volcanic landscape.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 11:32:46', '2026-06-02 11:32:46'),
(4763, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 93, 1, 'DETAILED ITINERARY', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Duration: Estimate 12 Hours&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Tour Starting / Ending: Surabaya</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Meet and greet with your guide at <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel in Surabaya before starting the journey at approximately <strong>07.30 AM</strong> towards the spectacular <strong>Tumpak Sewu Waterfall</strong>, widely known as one of the most beautiful waterfalls in Indonesia. Enjoy a scenic drive through East Java\'s countryside before arriving at the waterfall area.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Begin the adventure by visiting the famous <strong>Panorama Viewpoint</strong>, where you can admire the breathtaking sight of hundreds of cascading streams forming a magnificent curtain of water surrounded by lush green cliffs. Continue the trek down to the <strong>base of Tumpak Sewu Waterfall</strong> for a closer encounter with its impressive natural beauty and refreshing atmosphere.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The exploration continues to <strong>Goa Tetes</strong>, a unique cave adorned with natural rock formations and flowing spring water, followed by a visit to the stunning <strong>Telaga Biru</strong>, a picturesque blue pool hidden among the cliffs. Enjoy the beautiful scenery from <strong>Kapas Biru Viewpoint</strong> and <strong>Bukit Nirwana</strong>, both offering spectacular panoramic views of the surrounding mountains, valleys, and waterfalls.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the adventure and enjoying the incredible landscapes of East Java, return comfortably to Surabaya and transfer to <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel. End of tour with unforgettable memories from one of Indonesia’s most breathtaking waterfall destinations.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 11:32:59', '2026-06-02 11:32:59'),
(4764, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 94, 1, 'DETAILED ITINERARY', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Duration: Estimate 22 Hours&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong>Tour Starting / Ending: Surabaya</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Meet and greet with your guide at <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel in Surabaya before starting the adventure at approximately <strong>11.30 PM</strong>. Travel to the Bromo area and continue by 4WD jeep through the spectacular landscape of <strong>Bromo Tengger Semeru National Park</strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Experience the world-famous <strong>Mount Bromo Sunrise</strong>, where the first light of day reveals a breathtaking panorama of Mount Bromo, Mount Batok, and the majestic Mount Semeru. Continue exploring the volcanic wonders of Bromo, including <strong>Widodaren Hill</strong>, the vast <strong>Sea of Sand</strong>, the picturesque <strong>Savannah Field</strong>, and the unique <strong>Whispering Sand</strong>, offering unforgettable views and incredible photo opportunities.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the Bromo exploration, continue the journey to <strong>Lumajang</strong> for an exciting adventure at <strong>Tumpak Sewu Waterfall</strong>, often referred to as the \"Niagara of Indonesia.\" Enjoy the spectacular panorama from the viewpoint before descending to the base of the waterfall, where hundreds of cascading streams create one of the most impressive natural landscapes in the country.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the adventure, return comfortably to Surabaya and transfer to <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel. End of tour with unforgettable memories from two of East Java\'s most iconic natural wonders in a single extraordinary journey.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 11:33:11', '2026-06-02 11:33:11'),
(4765, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 95, 1, 'DETAILED ITINERARY', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Duration: Estimate 10 Hours&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Tour Starting / Ending: Surabaya</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Meet and greet with your guide at <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel in Surabaya before starting the journey at approximately <strong>07.30 AM</strong>. Travel towards the beautiful highlands of <strong>Bromo Tengger Semeru National Park</strong>, where fresh mountain air and stunning natural scenery await.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Begin the exploration at <strong>Bromo Hillside</strong>, a scenic destination offering panoramic views of the surrounding mountains, valleys, and lush landscapes. Continue to the charming <strong>Ranu Pani Lake</strong>, a peaceful mountain lake nestled at the foot of Mount Semeru and known as the gateway to Indonesia’s highest volcano on Java Island.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Experience the daily life of local villagers through a visit to a <strong>potato plantation farm</strong>, where you can learn about traditional farming activities while enjoying the cool climate of the highlands. The journey continues to the picturesque <strong>Ranu Regulo Lake</strong>, surrounded by pine forests and beautiful mountain scenery, creating a perfect setting for relaxation and photography.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Before returning, stop at <strong>Bantengan View Point</strong>, one of the best locations to admire the breathtaking landscapes of the Tengger highlands and capture memorable photos of East Java’s natural beauty.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the tour, return comfortably to Surabaya and transfer to <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel. End of tour with unforgettable memories from the serene lakes, mountain scenery, and hidden beauty of the Bromo highlands.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 11:33:21', '2026-06-02 11:33:21'),
(4766, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 96, 1, 'DETAILED ITINERARY', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Meet and greet with your guide at <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel in Surabaya before starting the journey at approximately <strong>07.30 AM</strong> to <strong>Trowulan</strong>, the former capital of the legendary <strong>Majapahit Kingdom</strong>, one of the greatest empires in Indonesian history.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Begin your exploration at <strong>Wringin Lawang Gate</strong>, an impressive red-brick gateway believed to be one of the entrances to the ancient Majapahit city. Continue to the <strong>Trowulan Museum</strong>, where a fascinating collection of artifacts, statues, ceramics, and historical relics provides insight into the glory of the Majapahit civilization.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The tour continues to <strong>Segaran Lake</strong>, a historic reservoir believed to have played an important role during the Majapahit era, followed by visits to several important archaeological sites including <strong>Bajang Ratu Temple</strong>, <strong>Tikus Temple</strong>, and <strong>Brahu Temple</strong>, each showcasing unique architecture and rich historical significance. Complete the journey with a visit to the majestic <strong>Sleeping Buddha Statue</strong>, one of the largest reclining Buddha statues in Indonesia.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After discovering the remarkable heritage of the Majapahit Kingdom, return comfortably to Surabaya and transfer to <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel. End of tour with unforgettable memories of East Java\'s rich history, culture, and ancient civilization.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 11:41:31', '2026-06-02 11:41:31'),
(4767, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 97, 1, 'DETAILED ITINERARY', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Duration: Estimate 8 Hours&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Tour Starting / Ending: Surabaya</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Meet and greet with your guide at <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel in Surabaya before starting the tour at approximately <strong>08.30 AM</strong>. Discover the vibrant capital of East Java through a journey that combines history, culture, local life, and modern city attractions.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Begin by exploring <strong>Surabaya Old City</strong> aboard a classic jeep or mini train, passing through beautifully preserved colonial-era buildings and historic streets that reflect the city\'s rich heritage. Continue to the <strong>City Cultural Square</strong> and the iconic <strong>Heroes Monument</strong>, a symbol of Surabaya\'s important role in Indonesia\'s struggle for independence.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The tour continues to <strong>Sanggar Agung Temple</strong>, a unique waterfront temple known for its impressive architecture and the magnificent <strong>Four Faces Buddha</strong> statue overlooking the sea. Enjoy the blend of spirituality, culture, and scenic coastal views before heading into the city\'s modern district.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Explore the famous <strong>Tunjungan area</strong>, including <strong>Tunjungan Plaza</strong> and the historic <strong>Tunjungan Street</strong>, where old-world charm meets contemporary urban life. Complete the experience with a visit to <strong>Pasar Genteng</strong>, known for its traditional snacks and local delicacies, as well as local handicraft and art shops, perfect for finding authentic souvenirs from Surabaya.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the city exploration, return comfortably to <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel. End of tour with unforgettable memories of Surabaya\'s fascinating blend of history, culture, and modern lifestyle.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 12:14:14', '2026-06-02 12:14:14'),
(4768, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 98, 1, 'DETAILED ITINERARY', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Duration: Estimate 10 Hours&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong>Tour Starting / Ending: Banyuwangi</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Meet and greet with your guide at <strong>Blimbingsari Airport</strong>, Ketapang Harbour, Banyuwangi Train Station, or your hotel in Banyuwangi before starting the tour at approximately <strong>08.30 AM</strong>. Begin your island adventure with a scenic boat ride across the crystal-clear waters separating Java and Bali, heading towards the famous <strong>Menjangan Island</strong>, one of Indonesia’s premier snorkeling destinations.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Explore the island’s vibrant underwater world, renowned for its colorful coral reefs, tropical marine life, and exceptional water clarity. Enjoy snorkeling in the calm turquoise waters while discovering the rich biodiversity that makes Menjangan a paradise for nature lovers and underwater enthusiasts.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue the journey to the beautiful <strong>Tabuhan Island</strong>, a small tropical island surrounded by white sandy beaches and stunning ocean views. Relax by the shore, swim in the clear waters, or simply enjoy the peaceful atmosphere of this hidden gem. The adventure also includes a visit to <strong>Takat Pasir</strong>, a unique sandbar that emerges in the middle of the sea during low tide, creating a spectacular setting for photos and unforgettable moments.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After enjoying the natural beauty of the islands and surrounding marine park, return to Banyuwangi and transfer comfortably to <strong>Blimbingsari Airport</strong>, Ketapang Harbour, Banyuwangi Train Station, or your hotel. End of tour with unforgettable memories from one of East Java’s most beautiful tropical island experiences.</p>', NULL, 'Lunch Box', '2026-06-02 12:26:20', '2026-06-02 12:26:20'),
(4770, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 99, 1, 'DETAILED ITINERARY', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Duration: Estimate 10 Hours&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong>Tour Starting / Ending: Banyuwangi</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Meet and greet with your guide at <strong>Blimbingsari Airport</strong>, Ketapang Harbour, Banyuwangi Train Station, or your hotel in Banyuwangi before starting the adventure at approximately <strong>11.30 PM</strong>. Travel to <strong>Paltuding</strong>, the gateway to the famous <strong>Mount Ijen</strong>, and begin a memorable night trek through the cool mountain landscape.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Reach the summit area to witness the world-renowned <strong>Blue Fire phenomenon</strong> (subject to volcanic and weather conditions), one of the rare natural attractions that can only be found in a few places on Earth. As dawn approaches, enjoy a spectacular sunrise overlooking the stunning turquoise crater lake, recognized as the largest acidic crater lake in the world.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Along the journey, observe the remarkable dedication of local sulfur miners who carry heavy sulfur loads along the mountain trails, offering a unique insight into the daily life and traditions of the Ijen community. The combination of volcanic landscapes, dramatic scenery, and cultural encounters makes this experience truly unforgettable.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the trek and enjoying the breathtaking beauty of Mount Ijen, return comfortably to Banyuwangi and transfer to <strong>Blimbingsari Airport</strong>, Ketapang Harbour, Banyuwangi Train Station, or your hotel. End of tour with unforgettable memories from one of Indonesia\'s most extraordinary volcanic adventures.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 12:35:49', '2026-06-02 12:35:49'),
(4772, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 101, 1, 'DETAILED ITINERARY', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Duration: Estimate 10 Hours&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong>Tour Starting / Ending: Banyuwangi</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Meet and greet with your guide at <strong>Blimbingsari Airport</strong>, Ketapang Harbour, Banyuwangi Train Station, or your hotel in Banyuwangi before starting the tour. Embark on a journey that combines lush tropical forests, pristine beaches, and breathtaking coastal scenery, showcasing some of Banyuwangi’s most beautiful natural attractions.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Begin with a visit to <strong>De Djawatan Forest</strong>, a magical woodland famous for its towering ancient trees and enchanting atmosphere, often compared to scenes from a fantasy movie. Continue to the stunning <strong>Meru Betiri National Park</strong>, a protected conservation area known for its rich biodiversity and untouched natural beauty.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The adventure continues to the spectacular <strong>Green Bay (Teluk Hijau)</strong>, where emerald-green waters, soft sandy beaches, and surrounding tropical forests create a true hidden paradise. Enjoy the peaceful atmosphere and stunning coastal views before heading to <strong>Rajegwesi Beach</strong>, a charming fishing village beach offering authentic local scenery and a glimpse into the daily life of coastal communities.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Complete the journey at the iconic <strong>Red Island Beach</strong>, one of Banyuwangi’s most famous coastal destinations, renowned for its beautiful sunsets, golden sands, and unique offshore hill that creates a spectacular backdrop for photography.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After exploring the natural wonders of Banyuwangi’s southern coastline, return comfortably to <strong>Blimbingsari Airport</strong>, Ketapang Harbour, Banyuwangi Train Station, or your hotel. End of tour with unforgettable memories of Banyuwangi’s forests, beaches, and stunning coastal landscapes.</p>', NULL, 'Lunch', '2026-06-02 12:53:19', '2026-06-02 12:53:19'),
(4773, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 100, 1, 'DETAILED ITINERARY', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Duration: Estimate 10 Hours&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong>Tour Starting / Ending: Banyuwangi</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Meet and greet with your guide at <strong>Blimbingsari Airport</strong>, Ketapang Harbour, Banyuwangi Train Station, or your hotel in Banyuwangi before starting the tour. Discover the charm of Banyuwangi through a journey that combines local culture, natural beauty, and the unique character of East Java’s easternmost region.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Begin with a visit to the iconic <strong>Gandrung Statue</strong>, a symbol of Banyuwangi’s rich cultural heritage and the famous Gandrung dance tradition. Continue to the scenic <strong>Terasering Siring Rice Plantation</strong>, where lush green rice fields create a beautiful landscape and offer a glimpse into the agricultural life of the local community.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The journey continues to <strong>Jagir Waterfall</strong>, a refreshing natural attraction surrounded by tropical greenery and known for its crystal-clear mountain water. Afterwards, visit the elegant <strong>Pendopo Banyuwangi</strong>, showcasing the region’s cultural identity and architectural beauty.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Complete the tour at <strong>Marina Boom Beach</strong>, a popular waterfront destination offering stunning coastal views, relaxing seaside atmosphere, and picturesque photo opportunities overlooking the Bali Strait.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After exploring the highlights of Banyuwangi, return comfortably to <strong>Blimbingsari Airport</strong>, Ketapang Harbour, Banyuwangi Train Station, or your hotel. End of tour with wonderful memories of Banyuwangi’s culture, nature, and coastal beauty.</p>', NULL, 'Lunch', '2026-06-02 12:53:43', '2026-06-02 12:53:43'),
(4774, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 102, 1, 'DETAILED ITINERARY', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Duration: Estimate 10 Hours&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong>Tour Starting / Ending: Banyuwangi</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Meet and greet with your guide at <strong>Blimbingsari Airport</strong>, Ketapang Harbour, Banyuwangi Train Station, or your hotel in Banyuwangi before starting the tour. Begin your adventure with a visit to <strong>De Djawatan Forest</strong>, a mystical woodland famous for its giant ancient trees and enchanting atmosphere, creating a unique setting that feels like stepping into a fantasy world.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to the spectacular <strong>Baluran National Park</strong>, often referred to as the <strong>\"Little Africa of Java\"</strong> due to its vast savannah landscapes and diverse wildlife. Explore the famous <strong>Bekol Savannah</strong>, where open grasslands, Mount Baluran, and roaming wildlife create one of the most iconic natural panoramas in Indonesia.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The journey continues to <strong>Bama Beach</strong>, a peaceful coastal area located within the national park, offering beautiful sea views and opportunities to observe wildlife in their natural habitat. Enjoy a relaxing walk along the <strong>Mangrove Trail</strong>, where you can discover the unique ecosystem of mangrove forests while enjoying the tranquil surroundings and fresh coastal air.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After exploring the remarkable natural beauty of Banyuwangi, return comfortably to <strong>Blimbingsari Airport</strong>, Ketapang Harbour, Banyuwangi Train Station, or your hotel. End of tour with unforgettable memories of East Java’s wildlife, savannah landscapes, tropical forests, and coastal scenery.</p>', NULL, 'Lunch', '2026-06-02 13:02:14', '2026-06-02 13:02:14'),
(4777, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 103, 1, 'TROWULAN HERITAGE EXPLORATION', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or pick-up from your hotel in Surabaya, meet your guide and begin the journey to <strong>Trowulan</strong>, the former capital of the legendary <strong>Majapahit Kingdom</strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Start the exploration at <strong>Wringin Lawang Gate</strong>, a magnificent red-brick gateway believed to have been one of the entrances to the ancient Majapahit city. Continue to the <strong>Trowulan Museum</strong>, home to an impressive collection of archaeological artifacts, statues, ceramics, and relics that tell the story of Majapahit’s golden era.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Visit <strong>Segaran Lake</strong>, an ancient reservoir associated with royal ceremonies and daily life during the Majapahit period, followed by <strong>Pendopo Agung</strong>, a cultural site connected to the history of King Hayam Wuruk and the Majapahit Kingdom. The journey continues to <strong>Bajang Ratu Temple</strong>, an elegant gateway believed to commemorate a former Majapahit king, and <strong>Tikus Temple</strong>, a unique water sanctuary showcasing the kingdom’s advanced engineering and architecture.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Explore <strong>Brahu Temple</strong>, one of the oldest temples in Trowulan, before completing the day at the impressive <strong>Sleeping Buddha Statue</strong>, one of the largest reclining Buddha statues in Indonesia. After the tour, return to Surabaya for check-in and overnight stay at the hotel.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 13:17:24', '2026-06-02 13:17:24'),
(4778, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 103, 2, 'SURABAYA CITY TOUR & DEPARTURE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, begin exploring <strong>Surabaya</strong>, Indonesia’s famous <strong>\"City of Heroes.\"</strong> Discover the charm of <strong>Surabaya Old City</strong>, where colonial-era buildings and historic streets reflect the city’s rich heritage. Continue to the iconic <strong>Heroes Monument</strong>, a symbol of Surabaya’s important role in Indonesia’s struggle for independence.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Visit the beautiful <strong>Sanggar Agung Temple</strong>, located on the waterfront and known for its unique architecture and impressive <strong>Four Faces Buddha</strong> statue overlooking the sea. Enjoy the peaceful atmosphere while learning about the city\'s cultural diversity.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to the historic <strong>Tunjungan Street</strong>, one of Surabaya’s most famous heritage districts, where old colonial buildings blend with modern city life. Take time to explore the surrounding area, enjoy local souvenirs, and experience the vibrant atmosphere of East Java’s largest city.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the tour, transfer comfortably to <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel in Surabaya.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>End of tour with unforgettable memories of the Majapahit Kingdom\'s glorious heritage and the cultural charm of Surabaya.</strong></p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 13:17:24', '2026-06-02 13:17:24'),
(4779, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 104, 1, 'ARRIVAL SURABAYA CITY TOUR - BROMO', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or pick-up from your hotel in Surabaya, meet your guide and begin exploring the highlights of Indonesia\'s <strong>\"City of Heroes.\"</strong> Visit <strong>Surabaya Old City</strong>, known for its colonial architecture and historic atmosphere, followed by the iconic <strong>Heroes Monument</strong>, a symbol of Indonesia\'s struggle for independence.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to <strong>Sanggar Agung Temple</strong> and the impressive <strong>Four Faces Buddha</strong> statue overlooking the sea, before exploring the famous <strong>Tunjungan Historical Street</strong>, where heritage buildings blend with modern city life. After the city tour, continue to the Bromo area for check-in and overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 13:48:50', '2026-06-02 13:48:50'),
(4780, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 104, 2, 'BROMO SUNRISE TOUR - TUMPAK SEWU', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Begin an unforgettable adventure by 4WD jeep through <strong>Bromo Tengger Semeru National Park</strong>. Witness the spectacular sunrise from the viewpoint overlooking <strong>Mount Bromo</strong>, <strong>Mount Batok</strong>, and <strong>Mount Semeru</strong>. Continue to the <strong>Mount Bromo Crater</strong>, cross the vast <strong>Sea of Sand</strong>, and explore the beautiful <strong>Savannah Field</strong> and mystical <strong>Whispering Sand</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the Bromo experience, continue to the Tumpak Sewu area with a stop at <strong>Kapas Biru View Point</strong>, offering breathtaking views of waterfalls and surrounding valleys. Check in and overnight at Tumpak Sewu area.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 13:48:50', '2026-06-02 13:48:50'),
(4781, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 104, 3, 'TUMPAK SEWU WATERFALL ADVENTURE - MALANG', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Discover the beauty of <strong>Tumpak Sewu Waterfall</strong>, often called the \"Niagara of Indonesia.\" Enjoy the spectacular panorama from the viewpoint before descending to the base of the waterfall, where hundreds of cascading streams create a truly unforgettable sight.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue exploring <strong>Telaga Biru</strong>, <strong>Goa Tetes</strong>, and <strong>Bukit Nirwana</strong>, each offering unique natural scenery, hidden caves, and stunning photography opportunities. After the adventure, continue to Malang for hotel check-in and overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 13:48:50', '2026-06-02 13:48:50'),
(4782, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 104, 4, 'BATU HIGHLAND TOUR - SURABAYA', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, explore the cool highlands of <strong>Batu</strong>, one of East Java\'s most popular mountain destinations. Visit a local <strong>Apple Plantation</strong>, where you can experience the region\'s famous fruit-growing culture and enjoy the refreshing mountain atmosphere.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to <strong>Flora Santerra de Laponte</strong>, a colorful garden destination featuring beautiful flower landscapes, European-inspired architecture, and numerous photo spots.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the tour, return to Surabaya for check-in and overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 13:48:50', '2026-06-02 13:48:50'),
(4783, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 104, 5, 'MALANG HERITAGE TOUR - DEPARTURE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast and check-out, enjoy a relaxing heritage tour through the historic areas of Malang. Visit <strong>Kampoeng Heritage Kajoetangan</strong>, a charming neighborhood showcasing colonial architecture and local culture.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue along the elegant <strong>Ijen Boulevard</strong>, one of the city\'s most iconic streets, before stopping at the legendary <strong>Toko Oen</strong>, a historic restaurant dating back to the colonial era. Explore the surrounding <strong>Cathedral Church</strong>, <strong>Alun-Alun Tugu</strong>, and local souvenir shops for last-minute shopping.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the tour, transfer comfortably to <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel in Surabaya.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>End of tour with unforgettable memories of East Java\'s volcanoes, waterfalls, highland landscapes, cultural heritage, and vibrant city life.</strong></p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 13:48:50', '2026-06-02 13:48:50'),
(4784, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 105, 1, 'ARRIVAL SURABAYA - TUMPAK SEWU WATERFALL - MALANG', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or pick-up from your hotel in Surabaya, meet your guide and begin the journey to the spectacular <strong>Tumpak Sewu Waterfall</strong>, often called the \"Niagara of Indonesia.\" Enjoy the breathtaking <strong>Panorama Viewpoint</strong> overlooking the magnificent curtain-shaped waterfall before descending to the base of the falls for an unforgettable close-up experience.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue exploring the natural attractions surrounding the area, including <strong>Bukit Nirwana</strong>, the crystal-clear <strong>Telaga Biru</strong>, and the unique <strong>Goa Tetes</strong>, famous for its limestone formations and natural springs. After the tour, continue to Malang for check-in and overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 14:04:41', '2026-06-02 14:04:41'),
(4785, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 105, 2, 'MALANG HERITAGE TOUR - BROMO AREA', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, explore the historical and cultural highlights of <strong>Malang</strong>, one of East Java\'s most charming colonial cities. Visit <strong>Kampoeng Heritage Kajoetangan</strong>, known for its preserved colonial architecture and local atmosphere.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue along the elegant <strong>Ijen Boulevard</strong>, one of the city\'s most iconic heritage streets, and visit the legendary <strong>Toko Oen</strong>, a historic restaurant dating back to the Dutch colonial era.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Explore <strong>Malang Cathedral</strong>, <strong>Alun-Alun Tugu</strong>, and local souvenir centers before continuing to the Bromo area for hotel check-in and overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 14:04:41', '2026-06-02 14:04:41'),
(4786, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 105, 3, 'BROMO SUNRISE TOUR - BANYUWANGI', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Begin an early morning adventure by jeep through <strong>Bromo Tengger Semeru National Park</strong>. Witness the world-famous sunrise from the viewpoint overlooking <strong>Mount Bromo</strong>, <strong>Mount Batok</strong>, and <strong>Mount Semeru</strong>. Continue across the vast <strong>Sea of Sand</strong> to reach the crater rim of <strong>Mount Bromo</strong>, followed by visits to the beautiful <strong>Savannah Field</strong> and the mystical <strong>Whispering Sand Sea</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the Bromo experience, continue the overland journey across East Java to Banyuwangi for overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 14:04:41', '2026-06-02 14:04:41'),
(4787, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 105, 4, 'IJEN CRATER TOUR - SURABAYA', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Early in the morning, travel to <strong>Paltuding</strong> and begin the trek to the famous <strong>Mount Ijen</strong>. Experience the unique volcanic landscape while hiking toward the crater area. Depending on volcanic conditions, witness the world-renowned <strong>Blue Fire phenomenon</strong>, one of the rarest natural attractions on Earth.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Enjoy the spectacular sunrise and admire the stunning turquoise crater lake from the <strong>Ijen Summit Viewpoint</strong>. Observe the traditional sulfur miners carrying heavy sulfur loads, offering a unique cultural insight into local life.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After the tour, return to Surabaya for hotel check-in and overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 14:04:41', '2026-06-02 14:04:41'),
(4788, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 105, 5, 'SURABAYA CITY TOUR - DEPARTURE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast and check-out, explore the highlights of <strong>Surabaya</strong>, Indonesia\'s famous <strong>\"City of Heroes.\"</strong> Visit <strong>Surabaya Old City</strong>, where beautifully preserved colonial buildings showcase the city\'s rich history. Continue to the iconic <strong>Heroes Monument</strong>, followed by a visit to <strong>Sanggar Agung Temple</strong> and the impressive <strong>Four Faces Buddha</strong> statue overlooking the sea.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Complete the city tour at the famous <strong>Tunjungan Historical Street</strong>, a vibrant district where heritage architecture meets modern urban life.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the tour, transfer comfortably to <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel in Surabaya.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>End of tour with unforgettable memories of East Java\'s most iconic volcanoes, waterfalls, cultural heritage, and natural wonders.</strong></p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 14:04:41', '2026-06-02 14:04:41'),
(4789, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 106, 1, 'ARRIVAL BANYUWANGI - SOUTH COAST ADVENTURE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at <strong>Banyuwangi Airport, Train Station, Ketapang Harbour, or your hotel</strong>, meet your guide and begin exploring the natural beauty of Banyuwangi. Start with a visit to the enchanting <strong>De Djawatan Forest</strong>, famous for its giant ancient trees and magical atmosphere.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to the stunning <strong>Green Bay (Teluk Hijau)</strong>, known for its crystal-clear emerald waters and secluded tropical beach. The journey continues to <strong>Batu Beach</strong>, offering spectacular coastal scenery, before ending the day at the iconic <strong>Red Island Beach</strong>, renowned for its beautiful shoreline and breathtaking sunset views.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Transfer to the hotel for check-in and overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 14:22:34', '2026-06-02 14:22:34'),
(4790, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 106, 2, 'MENJANGAN ISLAND & TABUHAN ISLAND SNORKELING TOUR', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, embark on a boat excursion to some of the most beautiful marine destinations between Java and Bali. Enjoy snorkeling around <strong>Menjangan Island</strong>, famous for its vibrant coral reefs, colorful tropical fish, and exceptional underwater visibility.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to the picturesque <strong>Tabuhan Island</strong>, a small tropical island surrounded by crystal-clear turquoise waters. The adventure also includes a visit to <strong>Takat Pasir</strong>, a unique sandbar emerging in the middle of the sea, creating a perfect setting for photography and relaxation.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Return to Banyuwangi and overnight at the hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 14:22:34', '2026-06-02 14:22:34'),
(4791, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 106, 3, 'BALURAN NATIONAL PARK SAFARI ADVENTURE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, discover the unique landscapes of <strong>Baluran National Park</strong>, often called the <strong>\"Little Africa of Java.\"</strong> Explore the vast <strong>Bekol Savannah</strong>, where open grasslands, wildlife, and the majestic backdrop of Mount Baluran create a spectacular natural panorama.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue through the protected forest area before visiting <strong>Bama Beach</strong>, a peaceful coastal destination located within the national park. Enjoy the beautiful scenery and opportunities to observe wildlife in their natural habitat before returning to the hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 14:22:34', '2026-06-02 14:22:34'),
(4792, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 106, 4, 'IJEN SUNRISE TOUR - DEPARTURE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In the early morning, travel to <strong>Paltuding</strong> and begin the trek to the world-famous <strong>Mount Ijen</strong>. Witness the incredible <strong>Blue Fire phenomenon</strong> (subject to volcanic conditions) and enjoy a breathtaking sunrise overlooking the stunning turquoise crater lake, one of the most remarkable volcanic landscapes in Indonesia. Along the journey, observe the traditional sulfur miners carrying sulfur from the crater, offering a unique cultural insight into local life.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the trek, return to the hotel for breakfast, refreshment, and check-out. Transfer comfortably to <strong>Banyuwangi Airport, Train Station, Ketapang Harbour, or your hotel</strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>End of tour with unforgettable memories of Banyuwangi\'s tropical islands, pristine beaches, wildlife safari, and extraordinary volcanic wonders.</strong></p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 14:22:34', '2026-06-02 14:22:34'),
(4793, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 107, 1, 'ARRIVAL SURABAYA - SOUTH MALANG HIDDEN BEACH TOUR - TUMPAK SEWU', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or pick-up from your hotel in Surabaya, meet your guide and begin the journey to the beautiful southern coastline of Malang. Visit <strong>Teluk Asmara</strong>, often referred to as the \"Raja Ampat of East Java\" due to its stunning panorama of small islands scattered across turquoise waters.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to <strong>Goa China Beach</strong>, famous for its dramatic coastal scenery and powerful ocean waves, followed by <strong>Tanjung Penyu</strong>, a scenic cape offering spectacular views of the Indian Ocean. Complete the day at the iconic <strong>Balekambang Beach</strong>, known for its offshore temple and picturesque coastline often compared to Bali\'s Tanah Lot.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Afterwards, continue to the Tumpak Sewu area for check-in and overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 14:37:44', '2026-06-02 14:37:44'),
(4794, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 107, 2, 'TUMPAK SEWU WATERFALL ADVENTURE - BROMO AREA', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, explore the magnificent <strong>Tumpak Sewu Waterfall</strong>, widely recognized as one of the most beautiful waterfalls in Indonesia. Enjoy breathtaking views from the <strong>Panorama Viewpoint</strong> before descending to the base of the waterfall to witness its impressive curtain-like formation up close.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to <strong>Bukit Nirwana</strong>, the crystal-clear <strong>Telaga Biru</strong>, and the unique <strong>Goa Tetes</strong>, where natural caves, springs, and lush vegetation create a magical atmosphere.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the adventure, transfer to the Bromo area for hotel check-in and overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 14:37:44', '2026-06-02 14:37:44');
INSERT INTO `itineraries` (`id`, `itinerable_type`, `itinerable_id`, `day_number`, `title`, `description`, `hotel_info`, `meals_info`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(4795, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 107, 3, 'BROMO SUNRISE – BATU HIGHLAND TOUR - MALANG', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Begin the day with an exciting jeep adventure through <strong>Bromo Tengger Semeru National Park</strong>. Witness the famous sunrise over <strong>Mount Bromo</strong>, <strong>Mount Batok</strong>, and <strong>Mount Semeru</strong>, then continue to the <strong>Bromo Crater</strong>, <strong>Whispering Sand Sea</strong>, and the beautiful <strong>Savannah Field</strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After the Bromo tour, continue to <strong>Batu</strong>, a charming mountain resort town known for its cool climate and natural beauty. Visit a local <strong>Apple Plantation</strong>, explore the refreshing <strong>Coban Rondo Waterfall</strong>, and enjoy the colorful gardens and European-style scenery at <strong>Flora Santerra de Laponte</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Afterwards, transfer to Malang for overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 14:37:44', '2026-06-02 14:37:44'),
(4796, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 107, 4, 'MALANG HERITAGE TOUR - SURABAYA DEPARTURE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast and check-out, discover the historical charm of <strong>Malang City</strong>. Visit <strong>Kampoeng Heritage Kajoetangan</strong>, a preserved heritage village showcasing colonial architecture and local culture. Continue along the elegant <strong>Ijen Boulevard</strong>, one of Malang\'s most iconic streets, and stop at the legendary <strong>Toko Oen</strong>, a historic landmark dating back to the Dutch colonial era. Explore the surrounding <strong>Cathedral Church</strong>, <strong>Alun-Alun Tugu</strong>, and local souvenir shops for last-minute shopping.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the tour, transfer comfortably to <strong>Juanda International Airport</strong> or your hotel in Surabaya.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>End of tour with unforgettable memories of East Java\'s hidden beaches, spectacular waterfalls, volcanic landscapes, mountain highlands, and cultural heritage.</strong></p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 14:37:44', '2026-06-02 14:37:44'),
(4797, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 108, 1, 'ARRIVAL SURABAYA - TUMPAK SEWU WATERFALL - MALANG', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at <strong>Juanda International Airport Surabaya</strong> or pick-up from your hotel, meet your guide and begin the journey to the spectacular <strong>Tumpak Sewu Waterfall</strong>, often referred to as the \"Niagara of Indonesia.\" Enjoy the breathtaking panorama from the viewpoint before descending to the waterfall area to witness hundreds of water streams cascading down a massive cliff.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue exploring <strong>Bukit Nirwana</strong>, the crystal-clear <strong>Telaga Biru</strong>, and the unique <strong>Goa Tetes</strong>, known for its natural caves and dripping limestone formations.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After the tour, transfer to Malang for hotel check-in and overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 14:53:47', '2026-06-02 14:53:47'),
(4798, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 108, 2, 'MALANG HERITAGE TOUR - BROMO AREA', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, explore the cultural and historical highlights of <strong>Malang City</strong>. Visit <strong>Kampoeng Heritage Kajoetangan</strong>, a charming heritage village showcasing colonial architecture and local traditions.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue along the iconic <strong>Ijen Boulevard</strong>, one of the most beautiful colonial streets in East Java, followed by a stop at the legendary <strong>Toko Oen</strong>, famous for its nostalgic atmosphere dating back to the Dutch colonial era.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Visit <strong>Malang Cathedral</strong>, <strong>Alun-Alun Tugu</strong>, and a local souvenir center before continuing to the Bromo area for check-in and overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 14:53:47', '2026-06-02 14:53:47'),
(4799, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 108, 3, 'BROMO SUNRISE TOUR - TRANSFER TO BANYUWANGI', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">At approximately <strong>01.30 AM</strong>, depart from the hotel by 4WD jeep and begin the adventure into <strong>Bromo Tengger Semeru National Park</strong>. Arrive at the famous <strong>Sunrise View Point</strong>, where you will witness one of Indonesia\'s most spectacular sunrises overlooking the majestic panorama of <strong>Mount Bromo</strong>, <strong>Mount Batok</strong>, and <strong>Mount Semeru</strong>, the highest volcano in Java.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After sunrise, continue descending into the vast <strong>Sea of Sand</strong> before reaching the foot of <strong>Mount Bromo</strong>. Climb the staircase leading to the crater rim and enjoy breathtaking views of the active volcano and surrounding caldera.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The journey continues to the beautiful <strong>Savannah Field (Teletubbies Hill)</strong>, known for its rolling green hills and picturesque landscapes, followed by a visit to the mystical <strong>Whispering Sand</strong>, a unique volcanic desert where the wind creates a distinctive whispering sound across the sand.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the Bromo exploration, return to the hotel for breakfast and check-out. Continue the overland journey across East Java to <strong>Banyuwangi</strong>, passing scenic countryside, mountains, and local villages. Upon arrival, check-in at the hotel and enjoy a well-deserved rest before the next adventure.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 14:53:47', '2026-06-02 14:53:47'),
(4800, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 108, 4, 'IJEN BLUE FIRE & SUNRISE TOUR - DEPARTURE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Late in the evening (around <strong>11.30 PM</strong>), depart from the hotel and travel to <strong>Paltuding Base Camp</strong>, the starting point of the Mount Ijen trek. Accompanied by your guide, begin hiking through the cool mountain forest toward the crater area.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon reaching the crater, witness the world-famous <strong>Blue Fire phenomenon</strong> (subject to volcanic conditions), one of the rarest natural phenomena on Earth and found in only a few locations worldwide. Continue to the crater rim to enjoy the stunning, turquoise-colored acidic crater lake, the largest of its kind in Indonesia.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">As dawn approaches, enjoy the spectacular <strong>sunrise from the Ijen Viewpoint</strong>, offering panoramic views of the crater, surrounding mountains, and volcanic landscape. Along the trail, observe the remarkable daily activities of local sulfur miners who carry sulfur loads weighing up to 60–70 kilograms from the crater, providing a unique cultural and human-interest experience.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After the trek, return to the hotel for breakfast, freshen up, and complete the check-out process. Afterwards, transfer to <strong>Juanda International Airport Surabaya</strong>, your hotel in Surabaya, <strong>Banyuwangi Airport</strong>, or <strong>Ketapang Harbour</strong> according to your departure arrangement.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>End of tour with unforgettable memories of East Java\'s most iconic natural wonders, from the majestic sunrise of Mount Bromo to the extraordinary Blue Fire of Mount Ijen.</strong></p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 14:53:47', '2026-06-02 14:53:47'),
(4801, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 109, 1, 'ARRIVAL SURABAYA - TUMPAK SEWU AREA', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at <strong>Juanda International Airport Surabaya</strong> or pick-up from your hotel, meet your guide and begin the journey to the beautiful Tumpak Sewu area in Lumajang. En route, enjoy the scenic landscapes of East Java before visiting <strong>Kapas Biru Viewpoint</strong>, offering breathtaking panoramic views of lush valleys, waterfalls, and surrounding mountains.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to <strong>Kabut Pelangi Waterfall Viewpoint</strong>, where you can admire the stunning waterfall cascading through a tropical canyon, often accompanied by a beautiful rainbow mist effect.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After the tour, check in at the hotel near Tumpak Sewu and enjoy the peaceful mountain atmosphere.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 15:06:36', '2026-06-02 15:06:36'),
(4802, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 109, 2, 'TUMPAK SEWU WATERFALL ADVENTURE - BROMO AREA', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, begin exploring the magnificent <strong>Tumpak Sewu Waterfall</strong>, widely known as one of the most spectacular waterfalls in Indonesia. Enjoy the incredible panorama from the viewpoint before descending to the bottom of the waterfall to witness the impressive curtain-like formation created by hundreds of water streams.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue the adventure to <strong>Bukit Nirwana</strong>, offering stunning views of the surrounding landscape, followed by a visit to the crystal-clear <strong>Telaga Biru</strong> and the unique <strong>Goa Tetes</strong>, famous for its natural cave formations, limestone walls, and fresh mountain springs.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the waterfall exploration, transfer to the Bromo area for hotel check-in and overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 15:06:37', '2026-06-02 15:06:37'),
(4803, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 109, 3, 'BROMO SUNRISE TOUR - SURABAYA DEPARTURE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">At approximately <strong>01.30 AM</strong>, depart by 4WD jeep and head into <strong>Bromo Tengger Semeru National Park</strong>. Arrive at the famous <strong>Sunrise Viewpoint</strong> to witness the spectacular sunrise over <strong>Mount Bromo</strong>, <strong>Mount Batok</strong>, and <strong>Mount Semeru</strong>, creating one of the most iconic landscapes in Indonesia.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After sunrise, continue across the vast <strong>Sea of Sand</strong> and climb to the rim of <strong>Mount Bromo Crater</strong> to enjoy breathtaking views of the active volcano. The adventure continues to the beautiful <strong>Savannah Field (Teletubbies Hill)</strong>, known for its rolling green hills, followed by the mystical <strong>Whispering Sand</strong>, a unique volcanic desert where the wind creates a distinctive whispering sound across the sand.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the Bromo tour, return to the hotel for breakfast and check-out. Transfer comfortably back to <strong>Juanda International Airport Surabaya</strong> or your hotel in Surabaya.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>End of tour with unforgettable memories of East Java\'s most spectacular waterfalls, volcanic landscapes, and world-famous sunrise experiences.</strong></p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 15:06:37', '2026-06-02 15:06:37'),
(4804, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 110, 1, 'ARRIVAL SURABAYA - MALANG HERITAGE TOUR', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at <strong>Juanda International Airport Surabaya</strong> or pick-up from your hotel, meet your guide and begin the journey to <strong>Malang</strong>, one of East Java\'s most charming heritage cities. Explore <strong>Kampoeng Heritage Kajoetangan</strong>, a historic neighborhood featuring preserved colonial architecture and local cultural heritage. Continue along the elegant <strong>Ijen Boulevard</strong>, famous for its tree-lined streets and beautiful colonial-era residences.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Visit the legendary <strong>Toko Oen</strong>, a historic café and restaurant that has become an icon of Malang since the Dutch colonial period. Continue to <strong>Malang Cathedral</strong> and the scenic <strong>Alun-Alun Tugu</strong>, a city landmark surrounded by beautiful gardens and historic buildings. Before ending the day, visit a local souvenir center to discover Malang\'s famous snacks and specialty products.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Check in at the hotel and overnight stay in Malang.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-02 15:17:36', '2026-06-02 15:17:36'),
(4805, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 110, 2, 'BATU HIGHLAND TOUR', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, enjoy a full-day exploration of <strong>Batu</strong>, a popular mountain resort town known for its cool climate and scenic landscapes. Visit a local <strong>Apple Plantation</strong>, where you can learn about Malang\'s famous apple industry and experience the refreshing countryside atmosphere.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to the beautiful <strong>Coban Rondo Waterfall</strong>, surrounded by lush tropical forest and mountain scenery, offering a relaxing escape into nature. The journey continues to <strong>Flora Santerra de Laponte</strong>, a colorful garden destination featuring vibrant flower landscapes, European-inspired architecture, and numerous picturesque photo spots.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After the tour, return to Malang and overnight at the hotel.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 15:17:36', '2026-06-02 15:17:36'),
(4806, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 110, 3, 'SURABAYA CITY TOUR - DEPARTURE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast and check-out, transfer to <strong>Surabaya</strong>, Indonesia\'s famous <strong>\"City of Heroes.\"</strong> Discover the historical charm of <strong>Surabaya Old City</strong>, where colonial-era buildings and heritage districts reflect the city\'s rich history. Continue to the iconic <strong>Heroes Monument</strong>, a symbol of Indonesia\'s struggle for independence.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Visit the waterfront <strong>Sanggar Agung Temple</strong>, home to the impressive <strong>Four Faces Buddha</strong> statue overlooking the sea. Complete the city tour at the famous <strong>Tunjungan Historical Street</strong>, one of Surabaya\'s most vibrant heritage areas, were historic architecture blends with modern city life.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the tour, transfer comfortably to <strong>Juanda International Airport Surabaya</strong> or your hotel in Surabaya.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>End of tour with unforgettable memories of Malang\'s colonial heritage, Batu\'s refreshing highland scenery, and Surabaya\'s rich cultural history.</strong></p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-02 15:17:36', '2026-06-02 15:17:36'),
(4807, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 24, 1, 'ARRIVAL - PARANGTRITIS – OBELIX SEAVIEW', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Arrival at Yogyakarta Airport, you will be picked up by our representative. Straight, we will take you to Parangtritis Beach.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then, visit <strong>Gumuk Pasir sand dune</strong> is rare phenomenon, only few in the world. They are a very high sedimentation of sand coming from Merapi and Merbabu mountains forming like a desert.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Next, enjoy sunset from <strong>Obelix Seaview</strong> with Hindia Ocean panorama. Check in hotel, free program.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Lunch and dinner will be served at local restaurant (Optional).</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-03 02:21:11', '2026-06-03 02:21:11'),
(4808, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 24, 2, 'LAVA TOUR – BOROBUDUR - MALIOBORO', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, we will take you to Merapi Mountain to enjoy <strong>Lava Tour </strong>by riding jeep 4x4 WD visiting ruin houses museum caused by Merapi eruption in 2010, “alien stone”,<strong> </strong>and bunker.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Lunch at local restaurant (Optional). Continue stepping up to<strong> Borobudur Temple structure floor, </strong>built in 9th Century during the Sailendra Dynasty and has been listed as a UNESCO World Heritage Site.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Free shopping at <strong>Malioboro Street</strong>. Dinner at local restaurant, back to hotel (Optional), free program.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 02:21:11', '2026-06-03 02:21:11'),
(4809, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 24, 3, 'JOMBLANG CAVE - TIMANG', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Early breakfast at hotel, we have to get Jomblang Cave at 09.00 in the morning. Activities to explore Cave<strong> Jomblang</strong>&nbsp; using Single Rope Technique which is helped by professional tenant. Enjoy the cave by exploring stalactites and stalagmite in it.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Lunch traditionally. Continue to go to&nbsp; <strong>Timang Beach</strong> that is famous for its traditional gondola, formerly used for local fishermen to get lobsters. Now, it is open for tourist as an optional gondola or bridge (personal account).&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Back to Yogyakarta, dinner at local restaurant (Optional), back to hotel, free program.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast/Lunch', '2026-06-03 02:21:11', '2026-06-03 02:21:11'),
(4810, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 24, 4, 'TRANSFER OUT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, check out procedure. Transfer to airport to leave Jogja.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 02:21:11', '2026-06-03 02:21:11'),
(4815, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 25, 1, 'ARRIVAL - KOTAGEDE -   MALIOBORO', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at Yogyakarta Airport, you will be picked up by our representative. Straight, we will take you to <strong>Kotagede</strong> , silver made centre and the old centre of Mataram Yogyakarta.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then continue to <strong>Malioboro</strong> as a shopping street where you can buy special foods, clothes, or souvenirs from Jogja.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Check in hotel, free program. Lunch and dinner will be served at local restaurant (Optional).</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-03 02:54:28', '2026-06-03 02:54:28'),
(4816, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 25, 2, 'BOROBUDUR - PRAMBANAN', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, we will take you to <strong>Borobudur Temple until its structure floor, </strong>built in 9th Century during the Sailendra Dynasty and has been listed as a UNESCO World Heritage Site.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to <strong>Candi Mendut</strong> (Mendut Temple) is older than Candi Borobudur there are story of children in it walls and <strong>Candi Pawon</strong> (Pawon temple) it’s not a grave but a place to keep King Indra’s weapon namely Vajranala.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Lunch at local restaurant (Optional). Continue to <strong>Prambanan Temple</strong> built in the 10th century, this is the largest temple compound dedicated to Shiva in Indonesia.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Dinner at local restaurant (Optional), back to hotel, free program.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 02:54:28', '2026-06-03 02:54:28'),
(4817, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 25, 3, 'CITY TOUR – PARANGTRITIS', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, we will take you to <strong>Sultan Palace</strong> which still today considered the highest-ranking court of Indonesia where old custom of courtesy is still practiced.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Not far from the Palace, proceed to <strong>Taman Sari Watercastle </strong>is a recreation garden for Sri Sultan’s family. There is a pool that was once used as a bath for the king\'s concubines. Lunch at local restaurant (Optional).&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to visit <strong>Gumuk Pasir sand dune</strong> is rare phenomenon, only few in the world. They are a very high sedimentation of sand coming from Merapi and Merbabu mountains forming like a desert.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to <strong>Parangtritis Beach</strong>. &nbsp;Dinner at local restaurant (Optional), back to hotel, free program.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 02:54:29', '2026-06-03 02:54:29'),
(4818, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 25, 4, 'TRANSFER OUT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, check out procedure. Transfer to airport to leave Jogja.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 02:54:29', '2026-06-03 02:54:29'),
(4819, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 26, 1, 'ARRIVAL - KOTAGEDE -   MALIOBORO', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at Yogyakarta Airport, you will be picked up by our representative. Straight, we will take you to Kotagede , silver made centre and the old centre of <strong>Mataram Yogyakarta</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then continue to <strong>Malioboro</strong> as a shopping street where you can buy special foods, clothes, or souvenirs from Jogja.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Check in hotel, free program. Lunch and dinner will be served at local restaurant (Optional).</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-03 03:08:50', '2026-06-03 03:08:50'),
(4820, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 26, 2, 'DIENG TOUR', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Breakfast at hotel, continue to Dieng Plateu around 3 – 4 hours driving.&nbsp; Continue <strong>to Arjuna Temple Complex</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then, visit <strong>Sikidang Crater </strong>is literally a pond full of boiling acid mud spewing out thick sulphuric smoke.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Afterwards, enjoy the beauty of <strong>Color Lake</strong>. Back to hotel Jogja, free program. Lunch and dinner will be served at local restaurant (Optional).&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 03:08:50', '2026-06-03 03:08:50'),
(4821, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 26, 3, 'LAVA TOUR – PRAMBANAN', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Breakfast at hotel, we will go to Merapi Mountain to enjoy <strong>Lava tour</strong> by riding 4x4 Wheel drive Jeep visiting three main points: ruin houses museum, alien rock, and bunker exclude river crossing.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Lunch at local restaurant (Optional), continue to visit <strong>Prambanan Temple</strong> built in the 10th century, this is the largest temple compound dedicated to Shiva in Indonesia.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then continue to <strong>Breksi Cliffs, </strong>the ruins of traditional mining that to beco &nbsp;me tourist destination equipped with several ornament and several spot selfies Back to hotel, free program.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 03:08:50', '2026-06-03 03:08:50'),
(4822, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 26, 4, 'TRANSFER OUT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Breakfast at hotel, visit. There is a pool that was once used as a bath for the king\'s concubines. Transfer to airport to leave Jogja.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 03:08:51', '2026-06-03 03:08:51'),
(4823, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 27, 1, 'ARRIVAL - BOROBUDUR - SEMARANG', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at Yogyakarta Airport, you will be picked up by our representative.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Straight, we will take you <strong>to Borobudur Temple</strong> as the world’s largest Buddhist Temple, built in 9th Century during the Sailendra Dynasty and has been listed as a UNESCO World Heritage Site.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then continue to Semarang, check in hotel. Dinner will be served at local restaurant.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-03 03:13:50', '2026-06-03 03:13:50'),
(4824, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 27, 2, 'SEMARANG TOUR', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, we will take you to enjoy sightseeing in <strong>Sam Po Khong Temple</strong> was built to commemorate Admiral Zheng He (Cheng Ho) expedition from China to Southeast Asia with acculturation of Moslem and Chinese culture.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to <strong>Lawang Sewu</strong> was built in 1904, originally was the administrative office of the Dutch Railway Company. Lawang in Javanese language means doors and Sewu means thousand. Therefore, since the building has many doors, it is called Lawang Sewu.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Next, we will go to <strong>Kota Lama</strong> as the Old town of Semarang where you can see old building with European architecture built in the Butch colonial era (Kota Lama). Here you can see the round-shaped dome, so called <strong>Gereja Blenduk</strong>&nbsp; (Belnduk Church) which was built in 1753.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Dinner (Optional) will be served at local restaurant.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 03:13:50', '2026-06-03 03:13:50'),
(4825, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 27, 3, 'AMBARAWA – GEDONGSONGO', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, check out procedure. Then continue to enjoy <i><strong>Train Museum</strong></i> at Ambarawa, there are several old locomotives neatly arranged in <strong>Ambarawa Train museum</strong> as tourist destination. Lunch at local restaurant (Optional).</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then continue visit to <strong>Gedongsongo Temple at Bandungan</strong>, the cool air and temple which is located under the slopes of <strong>Mount Ungaran</strong> make Gedong Songo Temple look beautiful and natural.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then, drive to Yogyakarta check in and free program. Dinner at local restaurant (Optional), back to hotel, free program.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 03:13:50', '2026-06-03 03:13:50'),
(4826, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 27, 4, 'TRANSFER OUT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, check out procedure.&nbsp; Free program till transfer to airport to leave Jogja.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 03:13:50', '2026-06-03 03:13:50'),
(4835, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 28, 1, 'ARRIVAL - TRANSFER TO HOTEL', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at Yogyakarta Airport, you will be picked up by our representative. Straight, we will take you to hotel for check in. Dinner will be served at local restaurant (Optional).</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-03 06:44:26', '2026-06-03 06:44:26'),
(4836, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 28, 2, 'JOGJA – SEMARANG', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, we will take you to Semarang around 4 hours driving.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Arrive Semarang, enjoy sight-seeing in <strong>Sam Po Khong Temple</strong> was built to commemorate Admiral Zheng He (Cheng Ho) expedition from China to Southeast Asia with acculturation of Moslem and Chinese culture.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to <strong>Lawang Sewu</strong> was built in 1904, originally was the administrative office of the Dutch Railway Company. Lawang in Javanese language means doors and Sewu means thousand. Therefore, since the building has many doors, it is called Lawang Sewu.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Next, we will go to <strong>Kota Lama</strong> as the Old town of Semarang where you can see old building with European&nbsp;architecture built in the Butch colonial era (Kota Lama). Here you can see the round-shaped dome, so called <strong>Gereja Blenduk</strong> (Blenduk Church) which was built in 1753.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Back to hotel in Jogja, free program. Dinner will be served at local restaurant (Optional).&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 06:44:26', '2026-06-03 06:44:26'),
(4837, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 28, 3, 'LAVA TOUR - BOROBUDUR', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, to enjoy <strong>Lava tour</strong> by riding 4x4 Wheel drive Jeep visiting three main points: ruin houses museum, alien rock, and bunker.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Lunch at local restaurant (Optional), visit <strong>Borobudur Temple</strong> as the world’s largest Buddhist Temple, built in 9th Century during the Sailendra Dynasty and has been listed as a UNESCO World Heritage Site.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to <strong>Candi Mendut</strong> (Mendut Temple) is older than Candi Borobudur there are story of children in it walls, then direct to <strong>Candi Pawon</strong> (Pawon temple) it\'s not a grave but a place to keep King Indra’s weapon namely Vajranala.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Dinner at local restaurant (Optional), back to hotel, free program.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 06:44:26', '2026-06-03 06:44:26'),
(4838, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 28, 4, 'CITY TOUR – AIRPORT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, check out procedure. Visit <strong>Sultan Palace</strong> which still today considered the highest-ranking court of Indonesia where old custom of courtesy is still practiced.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Not far from the Palace, proceed to <strong>Taman Sari Watercastle </strong>is a recreation garden for Sri Sultan’s family. There is a pool that was once used as a bath for the king\'s concubines.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Lunch at local restaurant (Optional), transfer to airport to leave Jogja</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 06:44:26', '2026-06-03 06:44:26'),
(4839, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 111, 1, 'ARRIVAL SURABAYA - SURABAYA CITY TOUR - BROMO AREA', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at <strong>Juanda International Airport Surabaya</strong> or pick-up from your hotel, meet your guide and begin exploring the highlights of Indonesia\'s famous <strong>\"City of Heroes.\"</strong> Start with a unique exploration of <strong>Surabaya Old City</strong>, where colonial-era buildings, historical landmarks, and cultural heritage tell the story of the city\'s rich past. Continue to the iconic <strong>Heroes Monument</strong>, a symbol of Indonesia\'s independence struggle.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Visit the beautiful <strong>Sanggar Agung Temple</strong>, located by the waterfront and home to the impressive <strong>Four Faces Buddha</strong> statue overlooking the sea. Complete the city tour at the vibrant <strong>Tunjungan Historical Street</strong>, were historic architecture blends with modern city life.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After the tour, continue to the Bromo area for hotel check-in and overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-03 06:46:51', '2026-06-03 06:46:51'),
(4840, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 111, 2, 'BROMO SUNRISE TOUR - BATU HIGHLAND TOUR - MALANG', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">At approximately <strong>01.30 AM</strong>, depart by 4WD jeep and head into <strong>Bromo Tengger Semeru National Park</strong>. Arrive at the famous <strong>Sunrise View Point</strong> to witness one of Indonesia\'s most spectacular sunrises overlooking <strong>Mount Bromo</strong>, <strong>Mount Batok</strong>, and <strong>Mount Semeru</strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After sunrise, continue across the vast <strong>Sea of Sand</strong> and climb to the rim of <strong>Mount Bromo Crater</strong> for breathtaking views of the active volcano. The adventure continues to the beautiful <strong>Savannah Field (Teletubbies Hill)</strong> and the mystical <strong>Whispering Sand</strong>, a unique volcanic desert landscape.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the Bromo tour, continue to the cool highland town of <strong>Batu</strong>. Visit a local <strong>Apple Plantation</strong>, explore the refreshing <strong>Coban Rondo Waterfall</strong>, and enjoy the colorful gardens and European-style atmosphere at <strong>Flora Santerra de Laponte</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Afterwards, transfer to Malang for hotel check-in and overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 06:46:51', '2026-06-03 06:46:51'),
(4841, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 111, 3, 'MALANG HERITAGE TOUR URABAYA DEPARTURE- S', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast and check-out, discover the historical charm of <strong>Malang City</strong>. Visit <strong>Kampoeng Heritage Kajoetangan</strong>, a preserved heritage village featuring colonial architecture and local culture. Continue along the elegant <strong>Ijen Boulevard</strong>, one of the most iconic streets in East Java, and stop at the legendary <strong>Toko Oen</strong>, a historic landmark dating back to the Dutch colonial era.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The tour continues to <strong>Malang Cathedral</strong>, followed by a visit to the scenic <strong>Alun-Alun Tugu</strong>, one of the city\'s most recognizable landmarks. Before departure, enjoy shopping for local specialties and souvenirs at a local souvenir center.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the tour, transfer comfortably to <strong>Juanda International Airport Surabaya</strong> or your hotel in Surabaya.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>End of tour with unforgettable memories of Surabaya\'s historical heritage, the spectacular sunrise of Mount Bromo, the refreshing highlands of Batu, and the cultural charm of Malang.</strong></p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 06:46:51', '2026-06-03 06:46:51'),
(4842, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 29, 1, 'ARRIVAL - TRANSFER TO HOTEL', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at Yogyakarta Airport, you will be picked up by our representative. Straight, we will take you to hotel for check in. Dinner will be served at local restaurant.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-03 07:10:50', '2026-06-03 07:10:50'),
(4843, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 29, 2, 'PRAMBANAN - BOROBUDUR', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, continue to <strong>Prambanan Temple</strong> built in the 10th century, this is the largest temple compound dedicated to Shiva in Indonesia. Lunch at local restaurant (Optional).&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Visit <strong>Borobudur Temple</strong> as the world’s largest Buddhist Temple, built in 9th Century during the Sailendra Dynasty and has been listed as a UNESCO World Heritage Site.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to <strong>Candi Mendut</strong> (Mendut Temple) is older than Candi Borobudur there are story of children in it walls, then direct to <strong>Candi Pawon</strong> (Pawon temple) its not a grave but a p &nbsp;lace to keep King Indra’s weapon namely Vajranala.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Dinner at local restaurant (Optional). Back to hotel, free program.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 07:10:50', '2026-06-03 07:10:50'),
(4844, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 29, 3, 'SOLO CITY TOUR - JOGJA', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, drive to Solo around 2 hours. Enjoy city tour in <i><strong>Mangkunegaran Solo Palace</strong></i>, <i><strong>Triwindu Antique Market</strong></i> (which is sell all the antiques and unique goods from all places), Lunch at local restaurant (Optional).&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Then, shopping in <strong>Laweyan Batik complex</strong> and <strong>Pasar Grosir Solo</strong> (PGS). Back to Jogja,&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">dinner at local restaurant (Optional). Back to hotel, free program.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 07:10:50', '2026-06-03 07:10:50'),
(4845, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 29, 4, 'CITY TOUR – AIRPORT', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast at hotel, check out procedure. Visit <strong>Sultan Palace</strong> which still today considered the highest-ranking court of Indonesia where old custom of courtesy is still practiced.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Not far from the Palace, proceed to <strong>Taman Sari Watercastle </strong>is a recreation garden for Sri Sultan’s family. There is a pool that was once used as a bath for the king\'s concubines.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Lunch at local restaurant (Optional), transfer to airport to leave Jogja.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 07:10:50', '2026-06-03 07:10:50'),
(4846, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 112, 1, 'ARRIVAL SURABAYA - TUMPAK SEWU WATERFALL ADVENTURE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Upon arrival at <strong>Juanda International Airport Surabaya</strong> or pick-up from your hotel, meet your guide and begin the journey to the spectacular <strong>Tumpak Sewu Waterfall</strong>, often recognized as one of the most beautiful waterfalls in Indonesia. Enjoy the breathtaking <strong>Panorama Viewpoint</strong> overlooking the magnificent curtain-shaped waterfall before descending to the base of the falls for a closer experience.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue exploring the surrounding natural attractions including <strong>Bukit Nirwana</strong>, the crystal-clear <strong>Telaga Biru</strong>, and the unique <strong>Goa Tetes</strong>, famous for its natural cave formations and mountain springs.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After the tour, check in at the hotel near Tumpak Sewu and enjoy the peaceful atmosphere of the surrounding highlands.</p>', NULL, 'No Meals', '2026-06-03 07:15:34', '2026-06-03 07:15:34'),
(4847, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 112, 2, 'KAPAS BIRU VIEWPOINT - BATU HIGHLAND TOUR - MALANG', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast, visit <strong>Kapas Biru Waterfall Viewpoint</strong>, offering spectacular views of one of East Java\'s hidden natural gems surrounded by lush green valleys and mountain scenery.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue to the cool highland town of <strong>Batu</strong>, known for its refreshing climate and beautiful landscapes. Visit a local <strong>Apple Plantation</strong> and experience the region\'s famous agricultural heritage before continuing to the scenic <strong>Coban Rondo Waterfall</strong>, nestled within a tropical forest setting.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The journey continues to <strong>Flora Santerra de Laponte</strong>, a colorful flower garden featuring European-style architecture and picturesque photo spots.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After the tour, transfer to Malang for hotel check-in and overnight stay.</p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 07:15:34', '2026-06-03 07:15:34'),
(4848, 'App\\Models\\IndonesiaDestination', 112, 3, 'MALANG HERITAGE TOUR - SURABAYA DEPARTURE', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After breakfast and check-out, discover the cultural and historical charm of <strong>Malang City</strong>. Explore <strong>Kampoeng Heritage Kajoetangan</strong>, a preserved heritage village showcasing colonial architecture and local traditions. Continue along the elegant <strong>Ijen Boulevard</strong>, one of the most iconic streets in East Java, and visit the legendary <strong>Toko Oen</strong>, a historic landmark dating back to the Dutch colonial era.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The tour continues to <strong>Malang Cathedral</strong> and the beautiful <strong>Alun-Alun Tugu</strong>, surrounded by historical buildings and landscaped gardens. Before departure, enjoy shopping for local specialties and souvenirs at a local souvenir center.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">After completing the tour, transfer comfortably to <strong>Juanda International Airport Surabaya</strong> or your hotel in Surabaya.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>End of tour with unforgettable memories of East Java\'s magnificent waterfalls, refreshing mountain landscapes, colorful gardens, and rich cultural heritage.</strong></p>', NULL, 'Breakfast', '2026-06-03 07:15:34', '2026-06-03 07:15:34');
INSERT INTO `manado_tours` (`id`, `category_id`, `title`, `location`, `slug`, `description`, `description_en`, `description_ko`, `description_zh`, `base_price`, `price_usd`, `tour_type`, `duration_days`, `duration_nights`, `duration_hours`, `duration_hours_min`, `duration_hours_max`, `highlights`, `inclusions`, `exclusions`, `itinerary_pdf_path`, `is_featured`, `featured_badge`, `terms_conditions`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(8, 1, '4D3N Manado Highlights Tour', 'NORTH SULAWESI', '4d3n-manado-highlights-tour', '<h2><strong>4D3N Manado Highlights Tour: Jelajahi Keajaiban Alam dan Budaya Sulawesi Utara!</strong>&nbsp;</h2><p>Nikmati petualangan tak terlupakan selama 4 hari 3 malam di Manado dan sekitarnya. Paket ini menyatukan keindahan bawah laut dunia, pesona pegunungan yang sejuk, hingga keunikan budaya lokal dalam satu perjalanan eksklusif yang dirancang untuk kenyamanan maksimal Anda.</p><h3><strong>Mengapa Memilih Paket Ini?</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ea1b589669dcdfd69cd61ab7b58ed273b\"><strong>Destinasi Ikonik Kota:</strong> Mengunjungi <strong>Ban Hin Kiong</strong>, pura tertua di Manado yang kaya sejarah , serta kemegahan <strong>Monumen Yesus Memberkati</strong> dengan posisi unik yang menghadap kota.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed293c0088ed18bd1971384f602d46be7\"><strong>Surga Bahari Bunaken:</strong> Menjelajahi <strong>Taman Nasional Bunaken</strong> yang legendaris, tempat Anda bisa melihat terumbu karang warna-warni dan beragam kehidupan laut tropis.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e99a0f6475832d74b6bfcd76fa5662f6f\"><strong>Pesona Dataran Tinggi Minahasa:</strong> Merasakan udara sejuk Tomohon, melihat pasar ekstrem yang unik , hingga bersantai di <strong>Danau Linow</strong> yang airnya bisa berubah warna.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e190b1918fd1ee4f060f271d07c1dbdee\"><strong>Spot Foto Instagrammable:</strong> Mulai dari panorama 360 derajat di <strong>Makatete Hill</strong> hingga hutan pohon aren yang estetik di <strong>Tuur Maasering</strong>.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>4D3N Manado Highlights Tour: Discover the Wonders of Nature and Culture in North Sulawesi!</strong></h2><p>Embark on an unforgettable 4-day, 3-night adventure in and around Manado. This tour combines world-class underwater beauty, refreshing mountain charms, and unique local culture into one exclusive journey designed for your ultimate comfort.</p><h3><strong>Highlights:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ec6f4fd9fc1de8b8949086bf5e81aafc2\"><strong>Iconic Landmarks:</strong> Visit the historic <strong>Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong> and the majestic <strong>Blessing Jesus Monument</strong> overlooking the city.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9402e0f57d737dacda9eb406a4ea0eab\"><strong>Bunaken Marine Paradise:</strong> Explore the legendary <strong>Bunaken National Marine Park</strong>, home to colorful coral reefs and diverse marine life.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9dc905784f88a71c2b4093be6ec216d5\"><strong>Minahasa Highland Charms:</strong> Experience the cool air of Tomohon, witness the unique <strong>Extreme Market</strong>, and relax at the color-changing <strong>Lake Linow</strong>.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e690202f492f7665d8049e686658d4454\"><strong>Instagrammable Spots:</strong> Capture 360-degree views at <strong>Makatete Hill</strong> and the aesthetic palm forest at <strong>Tuur Maasering</strong>.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>4박 3일 마나도 하이라이트 투어: 북설라웨시의 자연과 문화의 기적을 탐험하세요!</strong></h2><p>마나도와 그 주변에서 잊지 못할 3박 4일간의 모험을 즐겨보세요. 이 패키지는 세계적인 수준의 수중 아름다움, 시원한 산의 매력, 그리고 독특한 현지 문화를 여러분의 최적의 편안함을 위해 설계된 하나의 독점적인 여행으로 결합했습니다.</p><h3><strong>여행 하이라이트:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e85287bc5e1a81c9ef84e399f9d84a235\"><strong>상징적인 명소:</strong> 역사가 깊은 <strong>반힌콩 사원</strong>과 도시를 내려다보는 웅장한 <strong>축복하는 예수상</strong> 방문.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebe10d44fd0d3f173c17d88bd2b0f821a\"><strong>부나켄 해양 파라다이스:</strong> 화려한 산호초와 다양한 해양 생물의 고향인 전설적인 <strong>부나켄 국립해양공원</strong> 탐험.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9f06bf36983086a3b0c73e7a694fe918\"><strong>미나하사 고원의 매력:</strong> 토모혼의 시원한 공기를 느끼고, 독특한 <strong>익스트림 마켓</strong>을 견학하며, 색이 변하는 <strong>리노우 호수</strong>에서 휴식.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e3cc8e1bd06a3219b80749573bcf8de2f\"><strong>인스타 감성 스팟:</strong> <strong>마카테테 힐</strong>의 360도 파노라마 뷰와 <strong>투루 마세링</strong>의 미학적인 종려나무 숲.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>4天3夜 美娜多精彩之旅：探索北苏拉威西的自然与文化奇观！</strong></h2><p>在美娜多及其周边开启一场难忘的4天3夜冒险之旅 。本行程完美融合了世界级的水下美景、清爽的山地风光以及独特的当地文化，为您提供专属且舒适的旅行体验。</p><h3><strong>行程亮点：</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ec23a3f804d598f641a4a5dc4d2a142ec\"><strong>标志性景点：</strong> 参观历史悠久的<strong>万兴宫 (Ban Hin Kiong)</strong> 以及俯瞰全城的宏伟<strong>基督祝福雕像</strong> 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee1e3d4f299770a0a16bca30301a95da4\"><strong>布纳肯海洋天堂：</strong> 探索传奇的<strong>布纳肯国家海洋公园</strong>，欣赏绚丽的珊瑚礁和丰富的海洋生物 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e1a2d36180611c1afb572cb7f9aec19ba\"><strong>米纳哈사高原魅力：</strong> 感受托莫洪 (Tomohon) 清新的空气，参观独特的<strong>极端市场</strong>，并在颜色多变的<strong>林诺湖 (Lake Linow)</strong> 尽情放松 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e13ab61083b2e94e70a52db727e4cfbdc\"><strong>网红打卡地：</strong> 在 <strong>Makatete Hill</strong> 捕捉360度全景，游览 <strong>Tuur Maasering</strong> 极具美感的棕榈林 。</li></ul>', 0.00, NULL, 'package', 4, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e471204a79d04f381b4df48abd3568538\">Full AC transportation according to the group size</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5b23337d0965051bf73eab7da059f4d6\">Private boat to <strong>Bunaken Island&nbsp;</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee8b3c0ce962717687e5c7022da4a5338\">3 nights hotel accommodation as selected – twin/double sharing</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb352e4cf3b88e05f28979629bdbb9af3\">Experienced guide &amp; driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e15fdff726b9e0d6b7522d89e853d30c7\">Entrance fees to tourist attractions &amp; parking fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eea1816d36947b4e805dd272a628cdf0e\">Meals as per the program</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb97366b44df314dee7b6f99ac3ca6044\">Tour services as per the itinerary</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e15fff39ee2756b1703ce5cb3c6a898cf\">Mineral water 1 bottle/pax/day</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e96b7b72b91c673e978df24be855f3346\">Handling service</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e1dc181d36af8406f97796d1769568909\">Return airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e71726909053b640df3cf3fad15a8fa02\">Tips for guide &amp; driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e11be5b6ad773248b059620b238aee9b8\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2d93bfcb857f4cecda93f3d73f2629ee\">Personal expenses outside the package (additional meals/drinks, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef7dd221a222f7b6c5b9e01cefa4cc2e4\">Porter service, airport tax &amp; excess baggage fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebadfd3cab7dc05d402522ac0ce442654\">Personal expenses (laundry, mini bar, room service, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e81328aad0a1b986831eed337f4f20e9b\">Travel insurance</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e59c4a681478a9f8e689ec94ec3db1a1d\">Other expenses not mentioned in the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-20 06:52:46', '2026-05-03 01:44:45'),
(9, 1, '4D3N Manado Island Gateway', 'NORTH SULAWESI', '4d3n-manado-island-gateway', '<h2><strong>4D3N Manado Island Getaway: Jelajahi Pesona Tropis Sulawesi Utara!</strong>&nbsp;</h2><p>Nikmati pelarian sempurna selama 4 hari 3 malam menyusuri keindahan bahari dan kekayaan budaya Manado. Dari kemegahan bawah laut <strong>Taman Nasional Bunaken</strong> hingga hamparan pasir putih yang lembut di <strong>Pulau Lihaga</strong>, paket ini dirancang untuk memberikan pengalaman liburan yang tak terlupakan.</p><h3><strong>Mengapa Memilih Paket Ini?</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e02fa1df3286948fbfbfbd54a485547b6\"><strong>Destinasi Ikonik:</strong> Mengunjungi <strong>Ban Hin Kiong</strong>, pura tertua di Manado, serta kemegahan <strong>Monumen Yesus Memberkati</strong>.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e4eec390dc4f7c9a8916c9cec9d500164\"><strong>Surga Bahari Dunia:</strong> Menjelajahi terumbu karang berwarna-warni di <strong>Bunaken</strong> dan bersantai di pulau eksotis <strong>Lihaga</strong> yang sangat <i>Instagrammable</i>.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e7093c6c9ccb8774b8ba9e022d8dde50a\"><strong>Panorama Menakjubkan:</strong> Menikmati pemandangan kota dan pulau-pulau dari ketinggian <strong>Makatete Hill</strong> serta momen matahari terbenam yang syahdu di <strong>Desa Wisata Budo</strong>.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e4b2d98014516e2b30c396f9aa66b8478\"><strong>Wisata Kuliner &amp; Lokal:</strong> Mencicipi kopi khas Sulawesi Utara langsung di rumah produksinya dan berburu oleh-oleh khas Manado.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>4D3N Manado Island Getaway: Explore the Tropical Charm of North Sulawesi!</strong></h2><p>Experience the perfect 4-day, 3-night escape through the marine beauty and rich culture of Manado. From the world-class underwater majesty of <strong>Bunaken National Marine Park</strong> to the soft white sands of <strong>Lihaga Island</strong>, this package is designed for an unforgettable holiday.</p><h3><strong>Highlights:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"eb06c16c7562f566930ad1e7cd69bbac3\"><strong>Iconic Landmarks:</strong> Visit <strong>Ban Hin Kiong</strong>, the oldest temple in Manado, and the majestic <strong>Blessing Jesus Monument</strong>.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eed0d6cce402e1677e55f49b3610f0165\"><strong>Marine Paradise:</strong> Explore colorful coral reefs in <strong>Bunaken</strong> and relax at the Instagrammable <strong>Lihaga Island</strong>.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8286182a4f36d11bd66d17a73df2e9df\"><strong>Breathtaking Panoramas:</strong> Enjoy views of the city and islands from <strong>Makatete Hill</strong> and a serene sunset at <strong>Budo Tourism Village</strong>.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e65bf9c5111391210ed6174fca229a3f3\"><strong>Local Flavors:</strong> Taste authentic North Sulawesi coffee and shop for unique Manado specialties.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>4박 3일 마나도 아일랜드 겟어웨이: 북설라웨시의 열대 매력을 탐험하세요!</strong></h2><p>마나도의 아름다운 바다와 풍부한 문화를 가로지르는 완벽한 3박 4일간의 휴식을 경험해 보세요. 세계적인 수준의 <strong>부나켄 국립해양공원</strong>의 수중 장관부터 <strong>리하가 섬</strong>의 부드러운 화이트 샌드까지, 잊지 못할 추억을 선사합니다.</p><h3><strong>여행 하이라이트:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e960af66542d5527ca3e6f55c90558a2c\"><strong>상징적인 명소:</strong> 마나도에서 가장 오래된 사원인 <strong>반힌콩</strong>과 웅장한 <strong>축복하는 예수상</strong> 방문.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e815efbfd84f410d655db60364af05f00\"><strong>해양 파라다이스:</strong> <strong>부나켄</strong>의 화려한 산호초 탐험과 인스타 감성 가득한 <strong>리하가 섬</strong>에서의 휴식.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e81474ef463ba7b644f28737c7b7588d9\"><strong>숨막히는 파노라마:</strong> <strong>마카테테 힐</strong>에서 내려다보는 도시 전경과 <strong>부도 관광 마을</strong>의 평화로운 일몰.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed969083e1049fe4e574b2204d073dda5\"><strong>현지의 맛:</strong> 북설라웨시 정통 커피 시음 및 마나도 특산품 쇼핑.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>4天3夜 美娜多海岛之旅：探索北苏拉威西的熱帶魅力！</strong></h2><p>开启一场完美的美娜多海岛之旅，尽情领略那里的海洋美景与浓厚文化 。从世界级的<strong>布纳肯国家海洋公园</strong>水下壮观景象，到<strong>利哈加岛 (Lihaga Island)</strong> 柔软洁白的沙滩，本行程为您打造难忘的度假体验 。</p><h3><strong>行程亮点：</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ef6f072dff2f4705f08c8913a73d4cd72\"><strong>标志性景点：</strong> 参观美娜多最古老的寺庙——<strong>万兴宫 (Ban Hin Kiong)</strong>，以及宏伟的<strong>基督祝福雕像</strong> 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e357de79db7780919bc0bd5d2c8234ffc\"><strong>海洋天堂：</strong> 在<strong>布纳肯</strong>探索绚丽的珊瑚礁，在网红打卡地<strong>利哈加岛</strong>尽情放松 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2651ef51f662fed1c3bfa218e9e4e914\"><strong>壮丽全景：</strong> 从 <strong>Makatete Hill</strong> 俯瞰城市美景，在<strong>布多旅游村 (Budo Village)</strong> 感悟宁静的日落时刻 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e62e0ac74679777a283d802c25706bc95\"><strong>地道风味：</strong> 品尝正宗的北苏拉威西咖啡，选购美娜多特色伴手礼 。</li></ul>', 0.00, NULL, 'package', 4, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e471204a79d04f381b4df48abd3568538\">Full AC transportation according to the group size</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5b23337d0965051bf73eab7da059f4d6\">Private boat to <strong>Bunaken Island &amp; Lihaga Island</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee8b3c0ce962717687e5c7022da4a5338\">3 nights hotel accommodation as selected – twin/double sharing</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb352e4cf3b88e05f28979629bdbb9af3\">Experienced guide &amp; driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e15fdff726b9e0d6b7522d89e853d30c7\">Entrance fees to tourist attractions &amp; parking fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eea1816d36947b4e805dd272a628cdf0e\">Meals as per the program</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb97366b44df314dee7b6f99ac3ca6044\">Tour services as per the itinerary</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e15fff39ee2756b1703ce5cb3c6a898cf\">Mineral water 1 bottle/pax/day</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e96b7b72b91c673e978df24be855f3346\">Handling service</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e1dc181d36af8406f97796d1769568909\">Return airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e71726909053b640df3cf3fad15a8fa02\">Tips for guide &amp; driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e11be5b6ad773248b059620b238aee9b8\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2d93bfcb857f4cecda93f3d73f2629ee\">Personal expenses outside the package (additional meals/drinks, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef7dd221a222f7b6c5b9e01cefa4cc2e4\">Porter service, airport tax &amp; excess baggage fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebadfd3cab7dc05d402522ac0ce442654\">Personal expenses (laundry, mini bar, room service, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e81328aad0a1b986831eed337f4f20e9b\">Travel insurance</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e59c4a681478a9f8e689ec94ec3db1a1d\">Other expenses not mentioned in the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-20 07:54:02', '2026-05-03 01:44:27'),
(10, 1, '5D4N Tropical Wonders of Manado', 'NORTH SULAWESI', '5d4n-tropical-wonders-of-manado', '<h2><strong>Tropical Wonders of Manado: Penjelajahan 5 Hari di Surga Eksotis Sulawesi Utara</strong></h2><p>Temukan harmoni sempurna antara petualangan bawah laut yang mendunia dan ketenangan dataran tinggi yang asri. Paket <strong>5D4N Tropical Wonders of Manado</strong> adalah undangan eksklusif bagi Anda untuk mengeksplorasi setiap sudut keajaiban Sulawesi Utara—dari sejarah kota tua, kristal biru di Pulau Lihaga, hingga simbol perdamaian di Bukit Kasih.</p><h3><strong>Highlight Perjalanan Anda:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e65f17fc5a62b64a446bec044306ad9ce\"><strong>Eksplorasi Ikon Kota Manado:</strong> Menapak tilas sejarah di Ban Hin Kiong (Kuil tertua), mengunjungi Monumen Perang Dunia II, dan menyaksikan kemegahan Patung Yesus Memberkati yang berdiri megah menghadap ke laut.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec94469d6be03206316f3a0a414166575\"><strong>Keajaiban Bawah Laut Bunaken:</strong> Rasakan pengalaman <i>sightseeing</i> di Taman Laut Bunaken yang legendaris, rumah bagi terumbu karang raksasa dan ribuan spesies ikan tropis berwarna-warni.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e93cc3654c5f23bb3ae272693115fbdbb\"><strong>Kemilau Pulau Lihaga:</strong> Manjakan diri Anda di pulau tak berpenghuni dengan hamparan pasir putih sehalus tepung dan air laut yang sangat jernih—spot sempurna untuk relaksasi dan foto <i>Instagrammable</i>.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e88408445655eca765ae636f129fa6b09\"><strong>Harmoni di Bukit Kasih (Hill of Love):</strong> Rasakan kesejukan Highland Minahasa dan kunjungi pusat toleransi Sulawesi Utara. Di sini, Anda bisa mendaki tangga menuju puncak untuk melihat lima rumah ibadah yang berdiri berdampingan sebagai simbol persatuan.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee1b419dd08a2631a7de1ad6dff59eb2e\"><strong>Pesona Danau Linow:</strong> Tutup hari Anda dengan bersantai di tepi danau sulfur unik yang airnya dapat berubah warna secara ajaib, menciptakan suasana yang sangat menenangkan.</li></ul><h3><strong>Mengapa Memilih Paket Ini?</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e9995e75b5b98854a799719be7311d317\"><strong>Destinasi Terlengkap:</strong> Menggabungkan wisata kota (City Tour), petualangan pulau (Island Hopping), dan keindahan pegunungan (Highland Tour) dalam satu perjalanan.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eddaab418efffa784c3f87714c729af95\"><strong>Kearifan Lokal:</strong> Kunjungi rumah produksi kopi lokal dan saksikan langsung proses pembuatan camilan tradisional khas Manado.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ece61e5b012e51e52ddd2662b0f91a501\"><strong>Keseimbangan Perjalanan:</strong> Jadwal yang disusun dengan baik memberikan Anda waktu yang cukup untuk menikmati setiap destinasi tanpa harus terburu-buru.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>Tropical Wonders of Manado: A 5-Day Exploration of North Sulawesi’s Exotic Paradises</strong></h2><p>Discover the perfect harmony between world-class underwater adventures and the serene beauty of the highlands. The <strong>5D4N Tropical Wonders of Manado</strong> package is an exclusive invitation to explore every magical corner of North Sulawesi—from the history of the old city and the crystal-clear waters of Lihaga Island to the symbol of peace at Bukit Kasih.</p><h3><strong>Tour Highlights:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e3691e5b14c1972bf666dfaa0e4049c18\"><strong>Manado Iconic City Exploration:</strong> Trace history at Ban Hin Kiong (Manado’s oldest temple), visit the World War II Monument, and witness the majesty of the Blessing Jesus Statue overlooking the sea.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e58464dea836c52ef26c6b7234c0ddb7a\"><strong>Bunaken Marine Wonders:</strong> Experience sightseeing at the legendary Bunaken Marine Park, home to massive coral walls and thousands of vibrant tropical fish species.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e397b072e2fcc518bdbe32752ec41b87c\"><strong>The Radiance of Lihaga Island:</strong> Indulge in an uninhabited island paradise with powdery white sand and crystal-clear waters—a perfect spot for relaxation and Instagrammable moments.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e332ce3c43e7acb7d0e9ef53bfed24c78\"><strong>Harmony at Bukit Kasih (Hill of Love):</strong> Breathe in the cool air of the Minahasa Highlands and visit North Sulawesi’s center of tolerance. Hike the stairs to the peak to see five houses of worship standing side-by-side as a symbol of unity.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef01aaf1e583ab97e0c0374fc1c4bcbc6\"><strong>The Charm of Lake Linow:</strong> End your day relaxing by a unique sulfur lake where the water magically changes colors, creating a deeply tranquil atmosphere.</li></ul><h3><strong>Why Choose This Package?</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e8816f46080e83959333a73f02db3a7f0\"><strong>Comprehensive Destinations:</strong> Combines city heritage, island hopping adventures, and highland beauty in one seamless journey..</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e13796a566b7ad5253452b07e3c623bf2\"><strong>Local Wisdom:</strong> Visit local coffee production houses and witness the authentic process of making traditional Manado snacks.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e3814acc5d563337c1c27b050b25394a7\"><strong>Balanced Itinerary:</strong> A well-paced schedule ensures you enjoy every destination without feeling rushed.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>트로피컬 원더스 오브 마나도: 북설라웨시의 이국적인 낙원으로 떠나는 5일간의 탐험</strong></h2><p>세계적인 수중 어드벤처와 평화로운 고원의 아름다움이 완벽한 조화를 이루는 곳을 발견해 보세요. <strong>4박 5일 트로피컬 원더스 오브 마나도</strong> 패키지는 고도시의 역사부터 리하가 섬의 투명한 바다, 그리고 부킷 카시(Bukit Kasih)의 평화의 상징까지 북설라웨시의 모든 매력을 탐험할 수 있는 특별한 초대장입니다.</p><h3><strong>투어 하이라이트:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e77001c00b321eac33270746faf233a30\"><strong>마나도 상징적 도시 탐방:</strong> 마나도에서 가장 오래된 사원인 반힌콩(Ban Hin Kiong)에서 역사를 되짚어보고, 제2차 세계대전 기념비와 바다를 굽어보는 웅장한 예수 축복 동상을 방문합니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea1c526cd2b08a2a229db33902f597c34\"><strong>부나켄 수중의 경이로움:</strong> 거대한 산호벽과 수천 마리의 화려한 열대어가 서식하는 전설적인 부나켄 해양 공원에서 관광을 즐겨보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebe617186e810867012db27c276bb9d33\"><strong>눈부신 리하가 섬:</strong> 밀가루처럼 부드러운 백사장과 투명한 바다가 있는 무인도 낙원에서 휴식을 취하고 인생샷을 남겨보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eeb38ceade6c0ff68f09eb357ce28a35a\"><strong>부킷 카시(사랑의 언덕)의 조화:</strong> 미나하사 고원의 시원한 공기를 마시며 북설라웨시 관용의 중심지를 방문하세요. 정상까지 계단을 올라 연합의 상징으로 나란히 서 있는 5개의 종교 시설을 관람할 수 있습니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eceb94137f5acf79cd2c0c3a096f009b9\"><strong>리노우 호수의 매력:</strong> 물빛이 마법처럼 변하는 독특한 유황 호숫가에서 휴식을 취하며 하루를 마무리하세요.</li></ul><h3><strong>왜 이 패키지를 선택해야 하나요?</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ed95ab131203ae6b53c382bea09e46c4b\"><strong>최고의 목적지 구성:</strong> 도시 유산, 섬 투어, 그리고 고원의 아름다움을 하나의 여정에 모두 담았습니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecd63796dba1e88e6c97c7b26caccce89\"><strong>현지 문화 체험:</strong> 현지 커피 생산지를 방문하고 마나도 전통 간식이 만들어지는 과정을 직접 확인하세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecc35ff43d0aa7fa831de29256c73a44f\"><strong>여유로운 일정:</strong> 서두르지 않고 각 목적지를 충분히 즐길 수 있도록 세심하게 설계된 일정입니다.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>美娜多热带奇观：北苏拉威西异域天堂五日探索之旅</strong></h2><p>探索世界级水下冒险与宁静高原美景的完美融合。<strong>“5天4晚美娜多热带奇观之旅”</strong> 诚邀您探索北苏拉威西的每一个神奇角落——从古城的历史到里哈加岛的晶莹海水，再到布吉卡席 (Bukit Kasih) 的和平象征。</p><h3><strong>行程亮点：</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ec634d28e406a8a94ac20313c6935e34b\"><strong>美娜多地标城市探访：</strong> 在美娜多最古老的寺庙——万兴宫寻访历史足迹，参观二战纪念碑，并瞻仰雄伟的救世主耶稣雕像。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e052d158add18f0796d165f065cc6f753\"><strong>布纳肯水下奇观：</strong> 在传奇的布纳肯国家海洋公园观光，这里拥有巨大的珊瑚墙和数千种斑斓的热带鱼。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e94ff76c21b4b23c163bc4c45a1894bae\"><strong>里哈加岛的璀璨：</strong> 在这座拥有如粉末般洁白沙滩和清澈海水的无人岛上尽情放松——这里是享受宁静和拍摄网红大片的绝佳地点。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea3cebf7456d3f57e476c4eaf39dd99b8\"><strong>布吉卡席（爱之丘）的和谐：</strong> 呼吸米纳哈萨高原的凉爽空气，参观北苏拉威西的宽容中心。您可以拾级而上前往山顶，参观并排而立的五座宗教建筑，这是团结的象征。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef95556a2ea61228245cad98bce94a936\"><strong>林诺湖的魅力：</strong> 在独特的水色多变硫磺湖畔放松身心，结束您的一天，感受那份沁人心脾的宁静。</li></ul><h3><strong>为什么选择这个行程？</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e37f973459c7862a4c2ced20a34a6fb42\"><strong>全方位目的地：</strong> 集合了城市历史、跳岛冒险和高原美景，打造一站式完美旅行。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5161466854de0667f6ceca2711222859\"><strong>地道文化体验：</strong> 参观当地咖啡生产厂，亲眼目睹美娜多传统特色点心的制作过程。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e71b3c48e9adea49760e3cb5aa824e6c0\"><strong>合理的行程安排：</strong> 精心设计的节奏确保您有充足的时间享受每个景点，无需匆忙赶路。</li></ul>', 0.00, NULL, 'package', 5, 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"eea05a0fde3c9ad132dbf48ce720f5561\">Full AC transportation according to the group size</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e35785e5ddfb6a5dbd4ed40faf695693a\">Private boat to <strong>Bunaken Island &amp; Lihaga Island</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e11a26ee9d49a5ac1820047c130a6dfd5\">4 nights hotel accommodation as selected – twin/double sharing</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed5854fe627dc7e654934ab1e976947b9\">Experienced guide &amp; driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e81a3939bb0ae47c432179a015b5820f9\">Entrance fees to tourist attractions &amp; parking fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eabab84f65a739c80174326ae687d6b04\">Meals as per the program</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecc87f33179f708ea4e88eab3be33ec4b\">Tour services as per the itinerary</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e103e760176de41ca65afc60d31e98ff4\">Mineral water 1 bottle/pax/day</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef790cc1f991b5e82333a286a94bd3e06\">Handling service</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ef5d685346305b0f7f7808e0b74584d12\">Return airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e94d1cf8dad2496875a013333c9a2fb20\">Tips for guide &amp; driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e78256fbdd7f99f311466b507bd7703f6\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e3cd0374398d870ebbfd590981eab8338\">Personal expenses outside the package (additional meals/drinks, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e863d09a2873702f66d5a57da029388d2\">Porter service, airport tax &amp; excess baggage fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec55c74e4c2067333dd4c54aa28d879f1\">Personal expenses (laundry, mini bar, room service, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee355dc061e586232a936ec63b0305405\">Travel insurance</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e321a09c3a477e2305453ecd7e331735d\">Other expenses not mentioned in the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-20 08:06:06', '2026-05-03 01:44:12'),
(11, 1, '4D3N Exotic Manado Explorer', 'NORTH SULAWESI', '4d3n-exotic-manado-explorer', '<h2><strong>Manado Beyond Boundaries: 4 Hari Menjelajah Surga Tersembunyi dari Highland hingga Lihaga</strong></h2><p>Siap untuk melarikan diri ke surga tropis yang memadukan keajaiban bawah laut, perbukitan hijau yang asri, hingga kekayaan budaya yang unik? Paket <strong>4D3N Exotic Manado Explorer</strong> dari <strong>Welcome Manado Tours</strong> dirancang khusus untuk Anda yang mendambakan pengalaman liburan yang lengkap dan berkesan.</p><p>Dari pesona kota tua hingga pulau-pulau eksotis dengan pasir putih yang lembut, kami akan membawa Anda menjelajahi setiap sudut terbaik Sulawesi Utara.</p><h3><strong>Highlight Perjalanan Anda:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ed0f1c29deb96f4787634331b7b3d11bd\"><strong>Jelajah Kota &amp; Ikon Ikonik:</strong> Mengunjungi Patung Yesus Memberkati yang megah di CitraLand dan menapak tilas sejarah di Ban Hin Kiong, kuil tertua di Manado.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e43150cb6bf88bd1904207acfe95e928c\"><strong>Keajaiban Dataran Tinggi Minahasa:</strong> Rasakan udara sejuk di Tomohon, kunjungi pasar ekstrem yang mendunia, hingga bersantai sambil menikmati kopi di tepi Danau Linow yang airnya bisa berubah warna.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0693e6514329746ae5a1af13d5821c01\"><strong>Surga Tropis Pulau Lihaga:</strong> Manjakan mata Anda dengan hamparan pasir putih halus dan air laut yang jernih di Pulau Lihaga—spot sempurna untuk snorkeling, diving, atau sekadar berfoto <i>Instagrammable</i>.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e26a70d51cf835159d8a1ba8362248b73\"><strong>Sunset di Desa Wisata Budo:</strong> Tutup petualangan pulau Anda dengan pemandangan matahari terbenam yang memukau sambil menikmati pisang goreng khas lokal dan kelapa muda.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecab1cb11bdafe60853eb230b8eccf832\"><strong>Kearifan Lokal yang Autentik:</strong> Lihat langsung proses pembuatan minuman tradisional \"Cap Tikus\" dan saksikan <i>live cooking</i> camilan khas Manado yang menggugah selera.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>Manado Beyond Boundaries: A 4-Day Journey to Hidden Paradises from Highlands to Lihaga</strong></h2><p>Are you ready to escape to a tropical paradise that blends underwater wonders, lush green hills, and unique cultural heritage? The <strong>4D3N Exotic Manado Explorer</strong> package is meticulously designed for those seeking a complete and memorable vacation experience. From the charm of the old city to exotic islands with powder-soft white sand, we will take you to explore the very best of North Sulawesi.</p><h3><strong>Tour Highlights:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e5a0b1737e5682b9def93ca54f82d799b\"><strong>Iconic City Exploration:</strong> Visit the majestic Blessing Jesus Statue in CitraLand and trace history at Ban Hin Kiong, the oldest temple in Manado.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecee709c9ef871f4c6c6e18f0498bac94\"><strong>Minahasa Highland Wonders:</strong> Feel the cool breeze of Tomohon, visit the world-famous extreme market, and relax with coffee or tea by the color-changing waters of Lake Linow.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8172f04545690eb0e20f942380a00768\"><strong>Tropical Paradise of Lihaga Island:</strong> Indulge your senses with the stunning white sand and crystal-clear waters of Lihaga Island—a perfect spot for snorkeling, diving, or capturing Instagrammable moments.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e42a705d309d1e999bf275cfa5eed1d69\"><strong>Sunset at Budo Tourism Village:</strong> Conclude your island adventure with a breathtaking sunset while enjoying local treats like fried bananas and fresh coconut.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5f7e61ece6b6cff736304e4a135d08dc\"><strong>Authentic Local Wisdom:</strong> Witness the traditional production of \"Cap Tikus\" liquor and watch live cooking demonstrations of delicious local Manado snacks</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>마나도 비욘드 바운더리: 고원에서 리하가 섬까지, 숨겨진 낙원으로의 4일간의 여정</strong></h2><p>수중 세계의 경이로움, 푸른 언덕, 그리고 독특한 문화 유산이 어우러진 열대 낙원으로 떠날 준비가 되셨나요? <strong>4박 3일 엑조틱 마나도 익스플로러(4D3N Exotic Manado Explorer)</strong> 패키지는 완벽하고 기억에 남는 휴가를 원하는 분들을 위해 세심하게 설계되었습니다. 고풍스러운 도시의 매력부터 부드러운 백사장이 있는 이국적인 섬까지, 북설라웨시의 정수를 경험할 수 있도록 안내해 드립니다.</p><h3><strong>투어 하이라이트:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ee351062c5cf0ad56b3314692cd51ebc5\"><strong>상징적인 도시 탐방:</strong> 시트라랜드(CitraLand)의 웅장한 예수 축복 동상과 마나도에서 가장 오래된 사원인 반힌콩(Ban Hin Kiong)에서 역사의 발자취를 따라가보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e6f71bc35d32dc808e9731012a6bb4abd\"><strong>미나하사 고원의 기적:</strong> 토모혼(Tomohon)의 시원한 공기를 느끼며 세계적으로 유명한 익스트림 마켓을 방문하고 , 물빛이 변하는 리노우 호수(Lake Linow)가에서 커피나 차를 마시며 여유를 즐겨보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee659d5efbba01ef8e605c2fc02d45bfa\"><strong>리하가 섬의 열대 낙원:</strong> 눈부시게 하얀 모래와 투명한 바닷물이 있는 리하가 섬에서 스노클링, 다이빙을 즐기거나 인생샷을 남겨보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed68c2f71c4d583800d018d5f57804efe\"><strong>부도(Budo) 관광 마을의 일몰:</strong> 섬 모험의 마무리는 환상적인 일몰과 함께 현지 별미인 튀긴 바나나와 신선한 코코넛을 즐기는 것입니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2b6ab62514701b22cc31e7f2e8bb357a\"><strong>생생한 현지 문화 체험:</strong> 전통주 \'찹 티쿠스(Cap Tikus)\'의 제조 과정을 직접 확인하고 마나도 전통 간식의 라이브 쿠킹 쇼를 관람하세요.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>美娜多无界之旅：从高原到里哈加岛，探访隐藏天堂的四日游</strong></h2><p>您准备好逃离城市，前往一个融合了水下奇观、郁郁葱葱的绿丘和独特文化遗产的热带天堂了嗎？<strong>“4天3晚美娜多异域探索之旅” (4D3N Exotic Manado Explorer)</strong> 专为追求完美且难忘度假体验的您而设计 。从古城的魅力到拥有洁白细软沙滩的异国岛屿，我们将带您领略北苏拉威西的每一处精彩 。</p><h3><strong>行程亮点：</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ef8a374ba11e09e7e6158e9055317853a\"><strong>城市地标探索：</strong> 参观位于 CitraLand 雄伟的救世主耶稣雕像 ，并在美娜多最古老的寺庙——万兴宫，寻访历史足迹 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea826b17ea1fb694601cefffd27aedd7e\"><strong>米纳哈萨高原奇观：</strong> 感受托莫洪 (Tomohon) 的凉爽空气 ，参观闻名世界的“极边市场” ，并在色彩斑斓的林诺湖 (Lake Linow) 畔品茗或喝咖啡，享受惬意时光 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef253d5fce3a4c39b8e83143ccdfa68df\"><strong>里哈加岛热带天堂：</strong> 在里哈加岛 (Lihaga Island) 令人惊叹的白沙滩和清澈的海水中尽情放松——这里是浮潜、潜水或拍摄网红大片的绝佳地点 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec4b9b0893f299a3c2d4ae1fb4e9f8d65\"><strong>布多 (Budo) 旅游村落日：</strong> 以迷人的日落美景结束您的海岛冒险，同时品尝当地特色的炸香蕉和新鲜椰子 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e6415700136555d99d14bc60e7189df9d\"><strong>地道民俗体验：</strong> 亲眼目睹传统烈酒 “Cap Tikus” 的酿造过程 ，并观看美娜多传统糕点的现场制作 。</li></ul>', 0.00, NULL, 'package', 4, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e11c918e1af328b6b0e6bd2c3d6c46e5d\">Full AC transportation according to the group size</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebc2761735faa295be9869faeba5ef9c3\">Private Boat to Lihaga Island</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e1f7e9ade1181eb30404b6c4f7263c2b1\">3 nights hotel accommodation as selected – twin/double sharing</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebbdb40dd9308cc6ba65794e075cced2f\">Experienced guide &amp; driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2279728b3feae8fdd9a4669a3cecffd3\">Entrance fees to tourist attractions &amp; parking fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e827fd57d3a5e570b5b508c9fc5e721fa\">Meals as per the program</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8468f13ea9c16c3b266d42594e607992\">Tour services as per the itinerary</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e10fb1ed65e37365dbfff95f53601fbdb\">Mineral water 1 bottle/pax/day</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed4846e433289ae5057f860554a9f6f0d\">Handling service</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ef8f2361176c16ceca608dff85850a599\">Return airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea8a90f748b0acc8d8c682bc6aba46c8f\">Tips for guide &amp; driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e018e34ac8cbe045803a46d616e48d4aa\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed2e1a8df37b435a7b0217ea2351babdd\">Personal expenses outside the package (additional meals/drinks, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0b26c90da4e226af6c485c66f215a053\">Porter service, airport tax &amp; excess baggage fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e892a7a71628c913e7c40d29cad4c8939\">Personal expenses (laundry, mini bar, room service, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb026a0cc55dc3225736ba4099fbe22c9\">Travel insurance</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0d7036afa0726248cfb0462f1cd28859\">Other expenses not mentioned in the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-20 08:13:41', '2026-05-03 01:43:57'),
(12, 1, '3D2N Manado Highland Escape', 'NORTH SULAWESI', '3d2n-manado-bliss-gateway', '<h2><strong>Manado Highland Escape: Jelajah Budaya &amp; Pesona Alam Pegunungan (3 Hari 2 Malam)</strong></h2><p>Lepaskan penat dan rasakan kesegaran udara pegunungan Sulawesi Utara dalam perjalanan yang menenangkan jiwa. Paket ini membawa Anda mengeksplorasi warisan sejarah Kota Manado hingga keindahan dataran tinggi Minahasa yang ikonik. Dari puncak bukit yang megah hingga danau vulkanik yang berwarna unik, setiap momen dirancang untuk memberikan pengalaman liburan yang berkesan.</p><h3><strong>Sorotan Perjalanan Anda:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ea1e464fa25b0cd132b89377ca339797b\"><strong>Jelajah Sejarah Manado:</strong> Temukan pesona masa lalu di <strong>Klenteng Ban Hin Kiong</strong> yang berusia 300 tahun, Gereja Sentrum era kolonial, serta kemegahan <strong>Monumen Yesus Memberkati</strong> yang menghadap ke arah kota.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb10b2eaadd81e45064727e7d609d18ab\"><strong>Panorama Makatete Hill:</strong> Rasakan sensasi berdiri di atas awan dengan pemandangan \"360 derajat\" yang mencakup Kota Manado, Pulau Bunaken, hingga kegagahan Gunung Klabat.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0e8aa5a986712c445f7ce23725bf2235\"><strong>Kesejukan Dataran Tinggi Minahasa:</strong> Kunjungi <strong>Tomohon</strong>, kota bunga yang asri. Anda akan diajak melihat dari dekat <strong>Gunung Mahawu</strong>, keindahan <strong>Danau Linow</strong> yang airnya bisa berubah warna.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e3648d6159a81570db6e579034462122c\"><strong>Pesona Danau Tondano:</strong> Nikmati makan siang dengan suasana tenang di tepi Danau Tondano, danau terbesar di Sulawesi Utara yang dikelilingi perbukitan hijau.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e7f7c2ef1c14769fc2b61e236765fb76e\"><strong>Gaya Hidup &amp; Belanja:</strong> Bersantai di <strong>SunBae</strong>, tempat <i>hangout</i> tepi pantai yang trendi di Manado, serta kunjungan khusus ke rumah produksi kopi lokal dan pusat oleh-oleh khas Sulawesi.</li></ul><p><strong>“Escape to the heights – Discover the soul of Minahasa and the serenity of the highlands.”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>Manado Highland Escape: Nature &amp; Minahasa Cultural Journey (3D2N)</strong></h2><p>Unwind and breathe in the fresh mountain air of North Sulawesi on a soul-soothing journey. This package invites you to explore the iconic heritage of Manado City and the breathtaking beauty of the Minahasa Highlands. From majestic hilltop views to serene volcanic lakes, every moment is crafted for a relaxing and memorable holiday experience.</p><h3><strong>Tour Highlights:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e8dc1ab1ce673ce692f9379616bad2720\"><strong>Manado City Icons:</strong> Trace history at <strong>Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong> (the oldest in Manado), the colonial-era Sentrum Church, and the magnificent <strong>Blessing Jesus Monument</strong>, a symbol of the city’s protection.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e51fd6f848cba2d6592d228adc2e42175\"><strong>Makatete Hill Panorama:</strong> Enjoy a \"360-degree\" view from the heights, overlooking Manado City, the islands of Bunaken Marine Park, and the mighty Mount Klabat.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e46c228f74dd7f2ab845c593206a12120\"><strong>Cool Tomohon Flower City:</strong> Experience the fresh air at the foot of <strong>Mount Mahawu</strong>. Visit the unique <strong>Lake Linow</strong>, a volcanic lake whose waters change color depending on the sunlight.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9dc429f9dec067b2f8fe68a0dc53bf70\"><strong>Lunch by Lake Tondano:</strong> Savor authentic local dishes while gazing at the tranquil waters of Lake Tondano, North Sulawesi\'s largest lake, surrounded by lush green hills.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0b9195db89ec9080ca9ef7b40830d81f\"><strong>Lifestyle &amp; Shopping:</strong> Relax at <strong>SunBae</strong>, a trendy seaside hangout, and visit a local coffee production house to bring home the authentic aroma of Sulawesi.</li></ul><p><strong>“Escape to the heights – Discover the soul of Minahasa and the serenity of the highlands.”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>마나도 하이랜드 이스케이프: 자연과 미나하사 문화 탐방 (3박 2일)</strong></h2><p>지친 일상을 벗어나 북술라웨시의 상쾌한 고원 공기를 마시며 몸과 마음을 치유하는 여정을 떠나보세요. 마나도 시내의 상징적인 유산부터 미나하사 고원의 매혹적인 아름다움까지 모두 경험할 수 있습니다. 웅장한 언덕의 절경과 평화로운 화산 호수가 어우러진 이번 투어는 당신에게 최고의 휴식을 선사할 것입니다.</p><h3><strong>투어 하이라이트:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e85f005567008609fe8f7450b6b06b189\"><strong>마나도 시내 아이콘:</strong> 마나도에서 가장 오래된 <strong>반힌콩 사원(Ban Hin Kiong)</strong>, 식민지 시대의 센트룸 교회, 그리고 도시의 상징인 웅장한 <strong>축복하는 예수상</strong>에서 역사의 발자취를 따라가 보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eef41128c171fbe62bfad8a0d6e0a5ef1\"><strong>마카테테 힐 파노라마:</strong> 마나도 시내, 부나켄 해양 공원의 섬들, 클라바트 산이 한눈에 들어오는 \'360도\' 고원 절경을 감상하세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eedfdb15369039a886470d138ea890570\"><strong>꽃의 도시 토모혼의 청량함:</strong> <strong>마하우산</strong> 기슭의 상쾌한 공기를 느껴보세요. 햇빛에 따라 물빛이 변하는 신비로운 화산 호수, <strong>리노우 호수</strong>를 방문합니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec6449dea24b6c62bbb48308a0a7921e7\"><strong>톤다노 호숫가 중식:</strong> 푸른 언덕으로 둘러싸인 북술라웨시 최대 규모의 톤다노 호수의 평온한 풍경을 바라보며 정통 현지 요리를 즐기세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec4e1c2b9595b655ca5d8b552df4e3cec\"><strong>라이프스타일 및 쇼핑:</strong> 바닷가 핫플레이스 **선배(SunBae)**에서 여유를 즐기고, 현지 커피 생산지를 방문하여 술라웨시의 향기를 담아 가세요.</li></ul><p><strong>“Escape to the heights – Discover the soul of Minahasa and the serenity of the highlands.”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>美娜多高地避世之旅：自然风光与米那哈萨文化之旅（3天2夜）</strong></h2><p>从繁忙的生活中抽身，在北苏拉威西清新的山间空气中放松身心。本行程将带您领略美娜多市的标志性遗产以及米那哈萨高地令人叹为观止的美景。从雄伟的山顶全景到宁静的火山湖，每一个瞬间都旨在为您打造一段轻松且难忘的假期。</p><h3><strong>行程亮点：</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ef7a29712ad9095f23c014e4dcfe61862\"><strong>美娜多城市地标：</strong> 在<strong>万兴宫</strong>（美娜多最古老的寺庙）、殖民时期的中心教堂以及作为城市守护象征的宏伟<strong>耶稣降福雕像</strong>中追寻历史痕迹。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb3e9352a901de4e83b20fd8c982d7f8f\"><strong>马卡特特山全景：</strong> 在高处尽情俯瞰美娜多市区、布纳肯海洋公园的群岛以及雄伟的克拉巴火山，享受“360度”无死角美景。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5f001c5ba8c7fcc69025a074ef1afefe\"><strong>清爽的花之城托莫洪：</strong> 在<strong>马哈武火山</strong>脚下呼吸新鲜空气。游览独特的<strong>林诺湖</strong>，这是一座湖水颜色会随阳光照射而变化的火山湖。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea9e966e36a15b0fe6992c0c389256352\"><strong>通达诺湖畔午餐：</strong> 在北苏拉威西最大的湖泊——通达诺湖畔，一边欣赏绿意盎然的山色与静谧湖水，一边品尝正宗的当地美食。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5c3485a20c13439fa7f237ca08fe541f\"><strong>生活方式与购物：</strong> 在海滨潮流打卡地 <strong>SunBae</strong> 悠闲放松，并参观当地咖啡工厂，将苏拉威西的独特香气带回家。</li></ul><p><strong>“Escape to the heights – Discover the soul of Minahasa and the serenity of the highlands.”</strong></p>', 0.00, NULL, 'package', 3, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e8e6883a6e56a2407f008c457746ff1b6\">Full AC transportation according to the group size</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8de14905ae06a64f87cc60b7707f22d0\">2 nights hotel accommodation as selected – twin/double sharing</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e4bb6b6d5246389f96275d7a9a8a82136\">Meals as per the program</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eea1dca8498d90beff0733fbed2b12b77\">Experienced guide &amp; driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec02237fe232f55cc706fb1297ad87fad\">Entrance fees to tourist attractions &amp; parking fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed6a3feef8a8add362060ccd621024e6d\">Tour services as per the itinerary</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec668e506dcb5e72b186b8387ab536b9a\">Mineral water 1 bottle/pax/day</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e532893443396609a2ad9f6b124a36b95\">Handling service</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e3b523e8375ebb8c9d79946b95b626000\">Return airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebb59df0fa48ba937a21926c9d7e1f3dd\">Tips for guide &amp; driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e3ce39bff4df98057a82869976df231d7\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e3f219b92323c9770103f518bec22b1ba\">Personal expenses outside the package (additional meals/drinks, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e11ba73fd8e73eef138f3ca4ad9edebf4\">Porter service, airport tax &amp; excess baggage fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec1219e9200318981e942067b191d0e19\">Personal expenses (laundry, mini bar, room service, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eeb6d510ef8ff5842d69e6e91a30b5aa4\">Travel insurance</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0bf84136b233377c9c534be5adbe9757\">Other expenses not mentioned in the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-20 08:16:46', '2026-05-03 01:43:45'),
(13, 1, '3D2N Manado Bliss Getaway', 'NORTH SULAWESI', '3d2n-manado-highland-escape', '<h2><strong>Manado Bliss Getaway: Pesona Kota, Ketinggian, dan Bawah Laut (3 Hari 2 Malam)</strong></h2><p>Jelajahi keajaiban Sulawesi Utara dalam paket liburan singkat namun berkesan! Dari situs bersejarah di jantung kota Manado, panorama spektakuler dari puncak bukit, hingga taman laut Bunaken yang tersohor di dunia. Paket ini adalah pilihan sempurna bagi Anda yang ingin menikmati harmoni antara budaya, relaksasi, dan petualangan alam.</p><h3><strong>Sorotan Perjalanan Anda:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e73f836b6f1054871d5db0c169792372a\"><strong>Eksplorasi Sejarah &amp; Budaya:</strong> Telusuri jejak masa lalu Manado dengan mengunjungi <strong>Klenteng Ban Hin Kiong</strong> yang ikonik (klenteng tertua dari abad ke-18), Gereja Sentrum era kolonial, hingga kemegahan <strong>Monumen Yesus Memberkati</strong> di CitraLand.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed7a8f7dfd53c9ef5bd0ce4472fd7d748\"><strong>Panorama dari Makatete Hill:</strong> Nikmati pemandangan \"360 derajat\" Kota Manado, Pulau Bunaken, dan Gunung Klabat dari ketinggian. Tempat yang sempurna untuk berfoto dan menghirup udara segar.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eba63dcde6d834353155c6f8e70345feb\"><strong>Keajaiban Bawah Laut Bunaken:</strong> Rasakan pengalaman <i>sightseeing</i> menggunakan perahu katamaran untuk melihat terumbu karang dan biota laut yang memukau tanpa harus basah, atau pilih opsi snorkeling untuk interaksi lebih dekat dengan penyu dan ikan warna-warni.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e6e8d741de23e4a47d90a68202e44271e\"><strong>Gaya Hidup Lokal:</strong> Nikmati suasana santai di <strong>SunBae</strong>, tempat <i>hangout</i> tepi pantai yang kekinian, serta kunjungan ke rumah produksi kopi lokal untuk mencicipi aroma autentik Sulawesi.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed91ae6cf6aa600abebffaa97567c5433\"><strong>Wisata Belanja Oleh-Oleh:</strong> Lengkapi perjalanan Anda dengan berburu buah tangan khas Manado yang lezat dan unik sebelum kembali pulang.<br><br><strong>“Experience the bliss of Manado – where history, heights, and crystal waters meet.”</strong></li></ul>', '<h2><strong>Manado Bliss Getaway: City Charm, Highland Views &amp; Underwater Wonders (3D2N)</strong></h2><p>Explore the magic of North Sulawesi in a short yet memorable holiday package! From historical sites in the heart of Manado and spectacular panoramas from hilltop peaks to the world-renowned Bunaken Marine Park. This package is the perfect choice for those seeking a harmony of culture, relaxation, and nature adventure.</p><h3><strong>Tour Highlights:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ec87e7f54eab505024176814ebf781da1\"><strong>Historical &amp; Cultural Exploration:</strong> Trace Manado’s past at the iconic <strong>Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong> (the oldest temple from the 18th century), the colonial-era Sentrum Church, and the magnificent <strong>Blessing Jesus Monument</strong> at CitraLand.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e04f8948718c05ace6fb51a8a4fccafa4\"><strong>Panoramas from Makatete Hill:</strong> Enjoy a \"360-degree\" view of Manado City, Bunaken Island, and Mount Klabat from the highlands. A perfect spot for photography and fresh mountain air.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eda7662b8c7bd6af6c4fc8c35d086f80a\"><strong>Bunaken Underwater Magic:</strong> Experience a sightseeing tour via catamaran to see stunning coral reefs and marine life without getting wet, or choose to snorkel for a closer look at sea turtles and colorful fish.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e91f0ad67aee62944a3c39f0581cff264\"><strong>Local Lifestyle:</strong> Relax at <strong>SunBae</strong>, a trendy seaside hangout spot, and visit a local coffee production house to taste the authentic aroma of Sulawesi coffee.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec1d3073c70edb6ed2377cea36c2e7ef8\"><strong>Souvenir Shopping:</strong> Complete your journey by hunting for delicious and unique Manado traditional snacks and gifts before heading home.</li></ul><p><strong>“Experience the bliss of Manado – where history, heights, and crystal waters meet.”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>마나도 블리스 겟어웨이: 도시의 매력, 고원의 풍경 &amp; 수중 세계 (3박 2일)</strong></h2><p>짧지만 강렬한 추억을 선사할 북술라웨시의 마법 같은 여행을 떠나보세요! 마나도 중심부의 역사적 명소부터 고원에서 내려다보는 환상적인 파노라마, 그리고 세계적으로 유명한 부나켄 해양 공원까지. 문화와 휴식, 그리고 자연 어드벤처의 완벽한 조화를 원하는 분들께 최고의 선택이 될 것입니다.</p><h3><strong>투어 하이라이트:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e1b4d9ad4dd3658bfe2752cdb6e72950b\"><strong>역사 및 문화 탐방:</strong> 18세기에 세워진 마나도에서 가장 오래된 <strong>반힌콩 사원(Ban Hin Kiong)</strong>, 식민지 시대의 센트룸 교회, 그리고 시트라랜드의 웅장한 <strong>축복하는 예수상</strong>을 방문하며 마나도의 과거와 현재를 만나보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5f1532b5cccabb174a313ed743b6541d\"><strong>마카테테 힐의 파노라마:</strong> 해발 200m 높이에서 마나도 시내, 부나켄 섬, 클라바트 산이 어우러진 360도 절경을 감상하세요. 상쾌한 공기와 함께 인생샷을 남기기에 완벽한 장소입니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e33fd63b123a3e2b9da4c6d2c07f96918\"><strong>부나켄의 수중 신비:</strong> 카타마란 보트를 타고 젖지 않고도 아름다운 산호초와 해양 생물을 관찰하거나, 스노클링을 통해 거북이와 열대어들을 더 가까이서 만나보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2358a9f393595f5a9bcf44e9277c6d07\"><strong>현지 라이프스타일 체험:</strong> 바닷가 핫플레이스인 **선배(SunBae)**에서 여유로운 저녁을 즐기고, 현지 커피 생산지를 방문하여 술라웨시 커피 특유의 진한 향을 음미해 보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eac667e49ed3ccae7e2119494e4a62a07\"><strong>기념품 쇼핑:</strong> 마나도만의 특별하고 맛있는 전통 간식과 기념품 쇼핑으로 여행의 즐거움을 마무리하세요.</li></ul><p><strong>“Experience the bliss of Manado – where history, heights, and crystal waters meet.”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>美娜多极乐之旅：城市魅力、高地胜景与水下奇观（3天2夜）</strong></h2><p>在短暂而令人难忘的假期中探索北苏拉威西的魔力！从美娜多市中心的的历史古迹，到山顶的壮丽全景，再到闻名世界的布纳肯海洋公园。本套餐是寻求文化、放松与自然探险完美结合的理想选择。</p><h3><strong>行程亮点：</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"eb3dcf36f637c5909d132969d31b3a1ce\"><strong>历史与文化探索：</strong> 参观标志性的<strong>万兴宫</strong>（始建于18世纪的美娜多最古老寺庙）、殖民时期的中心教堂，以及位于 CitraLand 宏伟的<strong>耶稣降福雕像</strong>，追寻美娜多的历史足迹。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e1be719e2a2430ba801b8f3a7633241fe\"><strong>马卡特特山全景：</strong> 在海拔 200 米的高处，尽情俯瞰美娜多市区、布纳肯岛和克拉巴火山的 360 度美景。这里是拍照留念和呼吸清新空气的最佳地点。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecee73521ee1c2a87d8e2f3df55baea18\"><strong>布纳肯水下奇迹：</strong> 乘坐双体船观光，无需湿身即可欣赏迷人的珊瑚礁和海洋生物；您也可以选择浮潜，与海龟和五彩斑斓的热带鱼近距离接触。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebc1060b0a3c7990a59e2c3e2455f0722\"><strong>当地生活方式：</strong> 在海滨潮流打卡点 <strong>SunBae</strong> 享受悠闲时光，并参观当地咖啡生产厂，品尝苏拉威西咖啡的纯正香气。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef1b45b0a38a54b91e3f98a19a09f2c5a\"><strong>伴手礼购物：</strong> 在回程前，尽情选购美味且独特的美娜多特色小吃和纪念品，为旅程画上圆满句号。</li></ul><p><strong>“Experience the bliss of Manado – where history, heights, and crystal waters meet.”</strong></p>', 0.00, NULL, 'package', 3, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e06181f8916c033d055bf431ea9bb507d\">Full AC transportation according to the group size</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec74f2f93cf89580ce2eba2c1def0a181\">Private boat to <strong>Bunaken Island</strong></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8e4a93b41c7a6ed50ed3813194bd6e59\">2 nights hotel accommodation as selected – twin/double sharing</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e91c056088dcfc8c669ef740833e245c5\">Meals as per the program</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e065c54e6af38a7ad1bd490f01b5b5818\">Experienced guide &amp; driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee0e35b2c23993c0791e055d49f1f6f9d\">Entrance fees to tourist attractions &amp; parking fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e76df34d52a6a29e995f5d9be291dd79b\">Tour services as per the itinerary</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e620b8eda8fdcede4f1fbaf8c0908a778\">Mineral water 1 bottle/pax/day</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2640041a620be5c0b2575af63aa0074e\">Handling service</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e6fe90ccd0d08c5ebfa1c0966f14e1e37\">Return airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee405bf5b6e9984c12726b290bcf96832\">Tips for guide &amp; driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e54a6f1381c6ba9c3e26eb7685fcccedb\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e202c477f749dc16522c760ea26ce63fe\">Personal expenses outside the package (additional meals/drinks, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e3eee6b6c5ec03bcbabcb277307efbc5f\">Porter service, airport tax &amp; excess baggage fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"edd02c634ddc4057311fbdaabd045c0cb\">Personal expenses (laundry, mini bar, room service, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e054a8fc0bec74542de93820aa5038d72\">Travel insurance</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed8953b086fc7833fe1607e7f3df48f49\">Other expenses not mentioned in the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-20 08:20:15', '2026-05-03 01:43:31');
INSERT INTO `manado_tours` (`id`, `category_id`, `title`, `location`, `slug`, `description`, `description_en`, `description_ko`, `description_zh`, `base_price`, `price_usd`, `tour_type`, `duration_days`, `duration_nights`, `duration_hours`, `duration_hours_min`, `duration_hours_max`, `highlights`, `inclusions`, `exclusions`, `itinerary_pdf_path`, `is_featured`, `featured_badge`, `terms_conditions`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(14, 1, 'Paragliding Adventure At Mount Tumpa', 'NORTH SULAWESI', 'paragliding-adventure-at-mount-tumpa', '<h2><strong>Terbang Bebas di Langit Manado: Paragliding Adventure at Mount Tumpa</strong></h2><p>Pernahkah Anda membayangkan rasanya terbang bebas seperti burung di atas panorama alam yang luar biasa? Jadikan impian Anda nyata dengan <strong>Paragliding Adventure di Gunung Tumpa</strong>, destinasi terbaik untuk memacu adrenalin sekaligus memanjakan mata dengan pemandangan cakrawala Sulawesi Utara.</p><h3><strong>Mengapa Anda Harus Mencoba Petualangan Ini?</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e98140ed5799a0f9432dbb83ce6de9c34\"><strong>Sensasi Ketinggian 1.000 Meter:</strong> Rasakan detak jantung Anda berpacu saat terbang di ketinggian sekitar 1.000 meter. Nikmati kebebasan mutlak sambil melayang di atas lanskap pegunungan yang megah.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e3fe1185fb9cd34b9c0062354db38c9de\"><strong>Panorama Tiga Alam:</strong> Dari udara, Anda akan disuguhi pemandangan spektakuler yang menggabungkan hijaunya hutan rimbun, gugusan pegunungan, dan jernihnya air laut biru di kejauhan.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2c75343fd13498d3c308baf77da442d0\"><strong>Aman untuk Pemula &amp; Profesional:</strong> Gunung Tumpa dikenal memiliki kondisi cuaca yang stabil dan angin yang lembut, menjadikannya lokasi yang sangat aman bagi pemula yang ingin mencoba terbang pertama kali maupun bagi mereka yang ingin mengasah keterampilan.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee42cb8f11343f8e76b2aa5ff8d212f1d\"><strong>Pendampingan Profesional:</strong> Keamanan Anda adalah prioritas kami. Anda akan didampingi oleh instruktur paragliding profesional yang berpengalaman serta dilengkapi dengan peralatan keselamatan standar internasional.</li></ul><p><strong>“Feel the thrill, see the beauty, and make your Manado trip truly unforgettable!”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>Soar Above the Horizon: Paragliding Adventure at Mount Tumpa</strong></h2><p>Have you ever dreamed of flying freely like a bird over an extraordinary landscape? Make that dream a reality with <strong>Paragliding at Mount Tumpa</strong>, the ultimate destination to pump your adrenaline while indulging your eyes with the breathtaking skyline of North Sulawesi.</p><h3><strong>Why Should You Try This Adventure?</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e3d995532e5da06a872b9f02a6107d4dc\"><strong>A 1,000-Meter Thrill:</strong> Feel your heart race as you take flight at an altitude of approximately 1,000 meters. Enjoy absolute freedom as you glide over majestic mountain landscapes.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea3c0df71e04aeed41336ad6aba1efdee\"><strong>Triple-View Panorama:</strong> From the air, you will be treated to a spectacular view that combines lush green forests, mountain ranges, and the crystal-clear blue sea in the distance.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e89c859b093439fb473051420f28f301e\"><strong>Safe for Beginners &amp; Professionals:</strong> Mount Tumpa is renowned for its stable weather and gentle winds, making it a very safe location for first-timers and those looking to hone their skills.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e08a433a0bd80251bd18a24fe9db97261\"><strong>Professional Guidance:</strong> Your safety is our priority. You will be accompanied by a certified paragliding instructor and equipped with international standard safety gear.</li></ul><p><strong>“Feel the thrill, see the beauty, and make your Manado trip truly unforgettable!”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>마나도의 하늘을 날다: 툼파산 패러글라이딩 어드벤처</strong></h2><p>새처럼 자유롭게 하늘을 날며 환상적인 자연을 내려다보는 상상을 해보셨나요? 북술라웨시의 스카이라인을 한눈에 담으며 아드레날린을 깨울 수 있는 최고의 명소, <strong>툼파산(Mount Tumpa) 패러글라이딩</strong>에서 그 꿈을 실현해 보세요.</p><h3><strong>이 어드벤처를 놓치지 말아야 할 이유:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e2d8b5bc9fd6da25a114429aea15c7f61\"><strong>1,000미터 상공의 전율:</strong> 약 1,000미터 고도에서 날아오를 때의 짜릿함을 느껴보세요. 웅장한 산맥 위를 미끄러지듯 날며 완벽한 자유를 경험할 수 있습니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef899af4bfe07b67fba2c41ff765c06ba\"><strong>세 가지 매력의 파노라마:</strong> 하늘 위에서 울창한 초록빛 숲, 굽이치는 산맥, 그리고 저 멀리 펼쳐진 맑고 푸른 바다가 어우러진 장관을 감상하세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e4c8c25228feb9fca0331b101410ee5d7\"><strong>초보자 및 전문가 모두에게 안전:</strong> 툼파산은 안정적인 기상 조건과 부드러운 바람으로 유명하여, 처음 비행을 시도하는 초보자부터 실력을 연마하려는 전문가까지 모두에게 안전한 최적의 장소입니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed9a5cd08d05a2192edfae559358dac58\"><strong>전문가 동행:</strong> 여러분의 안전이 최우선입니다. 숙련된 전문 패러글라이딩 강사가 동행하며, 국제 표준 안전 장비가 제공됩니다.</li></ul><p><strong>“Feel the thrill, see the beauty, and make your Manado trip truly unforgettable!”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>翱翔于美娜多之巅：图姆帕山滑翔伞探险之旅</strong></h2><p>是否曾梦想过像鸟儿一样，在绝美的自然风光上空自由翱翔？在<strong>图姆帕山（Mount Tumpa）滑翔伞</strong>体验中，让梦想成真！这里是挑战极限、俯瞰北苏拉威西迷人天际线的绝佳目的地。</p><h3><strong>为什么选择这次探险？</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e3da76f84175871804fec428e1aa83366\"><strong>千米高空的震撼：</strong> 在约 1,000 米的高空起飞，感受心跳加速的快感。在雄伟的山峦景观上空滑行，享受绝对的自由。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0bd7b3866301c01ba4fb09f840e730f6\"><strong>海陆空全景：</strong> 从空中俯瞰，葱郁的森林、起伏的山脉与远方湛蓝的海洋完美交织，呈现出壮丽的视觉盛宴。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e186323bb3c0759fee0564928abef1567\"><strong>新手与专业人士的理想选择：</strong> 图姆帕山以稳定的天气条件和柔和的气流而闻名。无论是初次体验者还是希望提升技能的专业人士，这里都是一个非常安全的飞行场地。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e151bda41263db451d975b228a545c9da\"><strong>专业指导：</strong> 您的安全是我们的首要任务。您将由经验丰富的专业滑翔伞教练全程陪同，并配备国际标准的专业安全装备。</li></ul><p><strong>“Feel the thrill, see the beauty, and make your Manado trip truly unforgettable!”</strong></p>', 0.00, NULL, 'daily', 1, 0, NULL, 4, 5, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ea1013fe641dbc74405bab4a89c5269d4\">Professional paragliding guide</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e270763c5cc1b5c10062db7e71349a127\">Entrance fees to attractions</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0c8e90b12db6655ee96a9b9c53a48929\">Tour services as per the program</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e09808b568f0f7cf8b77bb2460fbf04c1\">Airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e7861cd3a295b5e9e7e7e32ec1bb61a65\">Car (Drop &amp; Pick up) Optional</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb8cd71ddf1d59066b0fe144c54b66278\">Airport tax</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e571d4f230715ed2fbe507807bb77544d\">Porter&nbsp;</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e11238ef8ad6bdc98761802c20dafcd49\">Hotel</li><li data-list-item-id=\"edcff8a0aeff894bd3a8e1024cb208edb\">Guide</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e68946d32764504f4bc586c60286973e8\">Driver tips</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed0f9917e71858b2d5a6c5bc0a3788568\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea0fb1478644b3360fcfc07c2524c963e\">Other expenses outside the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-20 08:55:30', '2026-05-03 01:43:15'),
(15, 1, 'Tarsius Canoe Adventure & Highland Sunset', 'NORTH SULAWESI', 'tarsius-canoe-adventure-highland-sunset', '<h2><strong>Petualangan Sampan &amp; Senja: Tarsius Canoe Adventure &amp; Highland Sunset</strong></h2><p>Temukan sisi lain dari keajaiban alam Sulawesi Utara dalam satu perjalanan yang memadukan petualangan air yang tenang dengan keindahan langit senja yang memukau. Dari mencari primata terkecil di dunia di antara hutan mangrove hingga menikmati sunset di ketinggian, paket ini menawarkan momen yang benar-benar tak terlupakan.</p><h3><strong>Keunikan yang Menanti Anda:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ea2cbb918749975fdcfb8293ad1afb837\"><strong>Eksplorasi Mangrove dengan Sampan:</strong> Rasakan ketenangan menyusuri perairan jernih di sekitar <strong>Pantai Rap-Rap</strong> menggunakan <i>canoe</i> (sampan). Biarkan suara alam menemani Anda saat menembus rimbunnya hutan mangrove yang asri.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0e9321c31ecc144e2603124d8c5c62e6\"><strong>Bertemu Tarsius di Habitat Alami:</strong> Dapatkan kesempatan langka untuk melihat <strong>Tarsius</strong>, primata kecil bermata besar yang mempesona, langsung di antara pepohonan bakau. Anda bebas mengabadikan momen ajaib ini sepuasnya!</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e7b254fd816ba0bc204d66a113a057413\"><strong>Sunset Ikonik di Gunung Tumpa:</strong> Tutup hari Anda dengan menyaksikan kemegahan matahari terbenam dari dataran tinggi <strong>Gunung Tumpa</strong>. Pemandangan garis pantai dan cakrawala dari ketinggian ini adalah salah satu yang terbaik di Manado.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb0e7cf754c6d9c5e126f4696c3a0a366\"><strong>Cita Rasa Lokal:</strong> Sambil menanti senja, Anda bisa mencicipi berbagai camilan khas Manado seperti Pisang Goreng Sambal Roa atau Es Kacang Brenebon yang legendaris (opsional).</li></ul><p><strong>“From the quiet mangroves to the golden heights – discover the hidden soul of North Sulawesi.”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>Canoe &amp; Twilight Adventure: Tarsius Canoe &amp; Highland Sunset</strong></h2><p>Discover a hidden side of North Sulawesi’s natural wonders in a journey that blends serene water exploration with a breathtaking sunset. From spotting the world’s smallest primate in the heart of a mangrove forest to witnessing the golden hour from the highlands, this package offers moments that are truly unforgettable.</p><h3><strong>Tour Highlights:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e4c38a56bb2531b9df36152451e56e547\"><strong>Mangrove Exploration by Canoe:</strong> Experience the tranquility of gliding through the crystal-clear waters of <strong>Rap-Rap Beach</strong> in a traditional canoe. Let the sounds of nature accompany you through the lush, pristine mangrove forest.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0c17af555cd6de31f7ceae7bd91eb5bb\"><strong>Meet the Tarsier in Its Natural Habitat:</strong> Enjoy a rare opportunity to see the <strong>Tarsier</strong>, a fascinating tiny primate with enchanting large eyes, nestled among the mangrove trees. You are free to capture these magical moments as much as you like!</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecf51fdfc1c1a9bd95af4023a3a3dc72a\"><strong>Iconic Sunset at Mount Tumpa:</strong> End your day by witnessing the majestic sun dip below the horizon from the highlands of <strong>Mount Tumpa</strong>. This panoramic view of the coastline and skyline is one of the best in Manado.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e68e80433226922d573e9e9cdd72494b3\"><strong>Local Flavors:</strong> While waiting for the sunset, you may treat yourself to various traditional Manado snacks, such as the legendary Fried Banana with Roa Chili Sauce or Red Bean Ice (optional).</li></ul><p><strong>“From the quiet mangroves to the golden heights – discover the hidden soul of North Sulawesi.”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>카누와 노을 어드벤처: 타르시어 카누 &amp; 하이랜드 선셋</strong></h2><p>고요한 물길 탐험과 환상적인 노을이 어우러진 여정을 통해 북술라웨시 자연의 숨겨진 매력을 발견해 보세요. 맹그로브 숲 사이에서 세계에서 가장 작은 영장류를 찾아보고, 고원에서 황금빛 석양을 감상하는 이 패키지는 진정으로 잊지 못할 순간을 선사합니다.</p><h3><strong>투어 하이라이트:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"eb1f9b4ea900864fee5cc1acac91643aa\"><strong>맹그로브 카누 탐험:</strong> <strong>랍랍(Rap-Rap) 해변</strong>의 맑은 물줄기를 따라 카누를 타고 평화로운 시간을 즐겨보세요. 울창하고 푸른 맹그로브 숲 사이로 들려오는 자연의 소리에 귀를 기울여 보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e4868dfe8413bc9c98d6fe76d02feb697\"><strong>야생 타르시어와의 만남:</strong> 맹그로브 나무 사이에서 서식하는 매혹적인 커다란 눈의 주인공, **타르시어(안경원숭이)**를 직접 만나는 특별한 기회를 가져보세요. 마음껏 사진을 찍으며 이 마법 같은 순간을 기록하실 수 있습니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecb54faf5847fadb2c34aa0beaf839f46\"><strong>툼파산의 상징적인 노을:</strong> <strong>툼파산(Mount Tumpa)</strong> 고원에서 장엄한 일몰을 감상하며 하루를 마무리하세요. 높은 곳에서 내려다보는 해안선과 스카이라인의 조화는 마나도 최고의 절경 중 하나입니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e6c350a0b01c107c14f4e8a4ff4906d4a\"><strong>현지 미식 체험:</strong> 노을을 기다리는 동안 매콤한 로아 소스를 곁들인 바나나 튀김이나 전설적인 팥빙수와 같은 마나도 전통 간식을 즐겨보세요(선택 사항).</li></ul><p><strong>“From the quiet mangroves to the golden heights – discover the hidden soul of North Sulawesi.”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>独木舟与落日探险：眼镜猴划舟与高地日落之旅</strong></h2><p>开启一场结合了宁静水上探险与绝美黄昏景致的旅程，探索北苏拉威西自然奇观的另一面。从红树林中寻找世界上最小的灵长类动物，到在高地迎接金色余晖，本行程将为您留下真正难忘的回忆。</p><h3><strong>行程亮点：</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e809a69eee2a9190cc4f2b06ed77b5969\"><strong>红树林独木舟探险：</strong> 乘坐独木舟穿行于 <strong>Rap-Rap 海滩</strong> 清澈的水域。在静谧的氛围中，听着大自然的声音，深入郁郁葱葱的红树林。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eef83cdc37b21cb937b9b41301179a694\"><strong>邂逅原生眼镜猴：</strong> 获得难得的机会，在红树林间寻找迷人的<strong>眼镜猴</strong>（有着迷人大眼睛的小型灵长类动物）。您可以尽情捕捉这些神奇的瞬间！</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e03324e9e1392c7497013560cb905a15a\"><strong>图姆帕山标志性日落：</strong> 在<strong>图姆帕山</strong>（Mount Tumpa）高地见证壮丽的夕阳沉入地平线。从高处俯瞰海岸线与天际线的交汇，是美娜多最美的景观之一。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed6f2df17729b50655c63a4368ff763f6\"><strong>地道风味：</strong> 在等待日落时，您可以自费品尝当地特色小吃，如著名的 Roa 辣椒酱炸香蕉或经典的红豆冰（可选）。</li></ul><p><strong>“From the quiet mangroves to the golden heights – discover the hidden soul of North Sulawesi.”</strong></p>', 0.00, NULL, 'daily', 1, 0, NULL, 4, 5, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e7bc9e1165c9336d08f046154ec23b677\">Full air-conditioned transportation according to the number of tour participants</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea7af70bb2a82bcea77255af2e5bee5f8\">Experienced mangrove guide and driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eae204140fa5bb1dcce46af8f50941376\">Canoe</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e80f346479d08bc79ba631e2cd3b91eb6\">Entrance fees to tourist attractions&nbsp;</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e464bfce6ecdcffccb9875ff5346cfc6b\">Parking fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e276d3b05d37581d3fd4159c5dd2f2075\">1 bottle of mineral water per person</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e285b78b0ee79f6f91b8f1fc2b17ac847\">Tour services as per the program</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e08be48cb4f21a5377ce9748c0ca49109\">Airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed90b677285985025078bdb06a9cf6c45\">Airport tax</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea142622087caa49b2ff7e4c53a07b979\">Porter</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb25e5a10849163e000f250df28b0b66d\">Meals</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e6afc882721d3368dc426447ed90c3af0\">Hotel</li><li data-list-item-id=\"edb5d4d26a2cfe5fde84d5a34dde54592\">Guide &amp; driver tips</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eab39da60f0dd66cad430d5382fc5acdc\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e4ce6a2be042d0929991d5051e57283ca\">Other expenses outside the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-20 09:04:27', '2026-05-03 01:43:01'),
(16, 1, 'Tangkoko Nature Reserve Tour & Tunan Waterfall', 'NORTH SULAWESI', 'tangkoko-nature-reserve-tour-tunan-waterfall', '<h2><strong>Jelajahi Alam Liar &amp; Air Terjun: Tangkoko &amp; Tunan Adventure</strong></h2><p>Siapkan kamera dan jiwa petualang Anda! Paket ini membawa Anda keluar dari jalur biasa menuju jantung konservasi terbaik di Indonesia serta keajaiban air terjun yang tersembunyi. Dari primata terkecil di dunia hingga gemuruh air terjun setinggi 86 meter, pengalaman ini akan menjadi sorotan utama perjalanan Anda di Sulawesi Utara.</p><h3><strong>Keunikan yang Menanti Anda:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"eef627910a1bbc6285ce62661ded664c7\"><strong>Kemegahan Air Terjun Tunan:</strong> Awali petualangan Anda di Desa Talawaan. Rasakan embun sejuk dari air terjun setinggi 86 meter yang jatuh deras di tengah hutan yang masih sangat asli dan alami.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0fd629979567a26376f95bf93e191481\"><strong>Bertemu Penghuni Asli Tangkoko:</strong> Jelajahi <strong>Cagar Alam Tangkoko</strong>, rumah bagi satwa endemik yang unik. Temukan <strong>Tarsius Tarsier</strong> (primata terkecil di dunia dengan mata besarnya yang menggemaskan) dan <strong>Yaki</strong> (Monyet Hitam Sulawesi) yang berkeliaran bebas.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e590b7f31ea3285efb6c81af2d4933b30\"><strong>Keanekaragaman Hayati:</strong> Selain Tarsius, bersiaplah untuk melihat burung Rangkong yang ikonik dan Kuskus di habitat aslinya dengan panduan dari <i>Ranger</i> (penjaga hutan) profesional.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e39003981bd5b8e1a35b7e23a73ad2821\"><strong>Perjalanan yang Menenangkan:</strong> Nikmati rute perjalanan yang melewati desa-desa kecil yang asri serta pemandangan lembah dan perbukitan yang memanjakan mata selama perjalanan menuju Bitung.</li></ul><p><strong>“A close encounter with nature – see the unique wildlife and pristine waterfalls of North Sulawesi.”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>Nature &amp; Wildlife: A Journey to Tangkoko and Tunan</strong></h2><p>Prepare your camera and your sense of adventure! This package takes you off the beaten path into the heart of one of Indonesia’s finest conservation areas and hidden waterfall wonders. From the world’s smallest primate to the roar of an 86-meter-high waterfall, this experience will be the highlight of your North Sulawesi journey.</p><h3><strong>Tour Highlights:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"eaa6145d45f7a43f48867e8b88abbee88\"><strong>The Majesty of Tunan Waterfall:</strong> Begin your adventure in Talawaan Village. Feel the cool mist from an 86-meter-high waterfall cascading in the middle of a pristine and untouched forest.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e84f905af7ed77bf929c6f8585a8dc3de\"><strong>Meet Tangkoko’s Original Inhabitants:</strong> Explore the <strong>Tangkoko Nature Reserve</strong>, home to unique endemic wildlife. Discover the <strong>Tarsius Tarsier</strong> (the world\'s smallest primate with adorable large eyes) and the <strong>Yaki</strong> (Sulawesi Black Macaque) roaming freely.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9c274daf11aafd04071821bf54a50cf5\"><strong>Rich Biodiversity:</strong> Beyond the Tarsiers, get ready to spot iconic Hornbills and Cuscus in their natural habitat, guided by professional forest Rangers.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee479cbd080a026d0b0aaaf0fc252c33c\"><strong>A Relaxing Journey:</strong> Enjoy a scenic route passing through charming small villages with soothing views of valleys and hills on the way to Bitung.</li></ul><p><strong>“A close encounter with nature – see the unique wildlife and pristine waterfalls of North Sulawesi.”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>자연과 야생동물: 탕코코 및 투난 여행</strong></h2><p>카메라와 모험심을 준비하세요! 이 패키지는 일반적인 관광지를 벗어나 인도네시아 최고의 보존 지구와 숨겨진 폭포의 경이로움 속으로 여러분을 안내합니다. 세계에서 가장 작은 영장류부터 86m 높이에서 쏟아지는 폭포의 웅장함까지, 이번 여정은 북술라웨시 여행의 하이라이트가 될 것입니다.</p><h3><strong>투어 하이라이트:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"eba7ed355572dc05652bf87a5e0aae82e\"><strong>투난 폭포의 웅장함:</strong> 탈라완 마을에서 모험을 시작하세요. 원시림 한가운데서 세차게 떨어지는 86m 높이 폭포의 시원한 물보라를 느껴보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0f43afcdb2ae34b6b3ea5b1ebb5899df\"><strong>탕코코의 야생동물과의 만남:</strong> 희귀 토착 생물의 보고인 <strong>탕코코 자연 보호구역</strong>을 탐험하세요. 커다란 눈이 매력적인 **안경원숭이(Tarsius)**와 자유롭게 숲을 누비는 **검정짧은꼬리원숭이(Yaki)**를 만나보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e154244f10901b6eb5b82a1c6ad592834\"><strong>풍부한 생물 다양성:</strong> 안경원숭이 외에도 전문 레인저의 안내에 따라 야생 상태의 코뿔새와 쿠스쿠스를 관찰할 수 있습니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec0a1778409f929d9e736f77ac8b383f6\"><strong>평화로운 여정:</strong> 비퉁으로 향하는 길목에서 아기자기한 시골 마을과 눈이 즐거워지는 계곡, 언덕의 풍경을 감상하며 여유로운 드라이브를 즐기세요.</li></ul><p><strong>“A close encounter with nature – see the unique wildlife and pristine waterfalls of North Sulawesi.”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>自然与野生动物：唐科科与图南之旅</strong></h2><p>准备好您的相机和探险精神！本行程将带您远离常规路线，深入印度尼西亚最顶级的自然保护区及隐秘的瀑布奇观。从世界上最小的灵长类动物到 86 米高瀑布的轰鸣声，这次体验将成为您北苏拉威西之旅的核心亮点。</p><h3><strong>行程亮点：</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e36ce61b0fbe6685fb5a8b0e0361e54a9\"><strong>壮丽的图南瀑布：</strong> 在塔拉万村开启您的探险。在原始森林的环抱中，感受 86 米高瀑布飞流直下的清凉水雾。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8b0a9009385679a15ba26108cc84991d\"><strong>邂逅唐科科的原住民：</strong> 探索<strong>唐科科自然保护区</strong>，这里是独特特有生物的家园。寻找有着可爱大眼睛的<strong>眼镜猴 (Tarsius)</strong> 和自由出没的<strong>黑猴 (Yaki)</strong>。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea13233c719eb2fd1e8c8d403d518e5fb\"><strong>生物多样性：</strong> 除了眼镜猴，您还可以在专业护林员的带领下，在自然栖息地中观察到标志性的犀鸟和袋貂。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e18d33b4363fa5c9a1dc32fa7129cf610\"><strong>舒心的旅程：</strong> 在前往比通（Bitung）的途中，穿过迷人的小村庄，欣赏令人心旷神怡的山谷和丘陵美景。</li></ul><p><strong>“A close encounter with nature – see the unique wildlife and pristine waterfalls of North Sulawesi.”</strong></p>', 0.00, NULL, 'daily', 1, 0, NULL, 6, 8, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e3a6d5c7a95824505fcc7169d19c68b06\">Fully air-conditioned transportation according to the number of tour participants</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec6d02de779b3cf721615c06630e5b3a2\">Ranger at Tangkoko nature reserve</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eed59092e3fde448a5e5a4fb756ab6e44\">Experienced guide and driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e1fbf9e5db829006a3fc211fef7a86ec5\">Entrance fees to tourist attractions</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec1827a81cbe7feb5e6c155dc5f41899e\">Parking fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb65edb1a96b3c032f8f825315f9c7209\">Lunch</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5971d7bd5ebcae0985b7b12074916355\">A bottle of mineral water per person</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef7e51ca1230476f54d606b374973afb1\">Tour services as per the program</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ed1003d6a37aa7b1fbafe39f48ba09598\">Airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9101a0e59598b6ff7f1e74ede3ede14f\">Airport tax</li><li data-list-item-id=\"efd4176d12238c02b80f1e80ada630810\">Porter</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea6ec6622fd640f8ae2aff46bc2e3b6e6\">Hotel,&nbsp;</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee0e2b05c5dcca53d84e69986e0eec301\">Tips for guide and driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5de631515d01a36e9bf58f056fac2003\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eebc3a63adc6760f98d268bc5875c1aac\">Any other expenses outside the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 1, 'popular', NULL, '2026-04-20 09:08:23', '2026-05-03 01:42:49'),
(17, 1, 'Mt. Lokon Volcano Trek', 'NORTH SULAWESI', 'mt-lokon-volcano-trek', '<h2><strong>Jelajahi Kawah Aktif: Pengalaman Trekking di Gunung Lokon</strong></h2><p>Rasakan pengalaman mendaki salah satu ikon vulkanik paling aktif di Sulawesi Utara. <strong>Gunung Lokon</strong> menawarkan petualangan trekking yang otentik bagi Anda yang ingin melihat lebih dekat kekuatan alam melalui kawahnya yang memukau tanpa harus melakukan pendakian yang terlalu ekstrem.</p><h3><strong>Alasan Paket Ini Menarik Bagi Anda:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e04f2ed2dbee1e739190fdd2064058656\"><strong>Eksplorasi Kawah Tompaluan:</strong> Ikuti jalur pendakian sekitar 2 jam menuju tepi <strong>Kawah Tompaluan</strong>. Di sini, Anda bisa melihat aktivitas vulkanik dari jarak yang aman namun cukup dekat untuk merasakan kemegahannya.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e74f6d2426a973e6214b6c37e8572a346\"><strong>Panorama Kota Tomohon:</strong> Nikmati pemandangan asri Kota Tomohon dari sisi lereng gunung yang memberikan perspektif berbeda akan keindahan alam Minahasa.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e63eeb9e285c1d8c6c8a7d7a82eee414f\"><strong>Tantangan yang Terukur:</strong> Dengan ketinggian 1.580 mdpl, jalur menuju kawah ini sangat cocok bagi pendaki pemula maupun berpengalaman yang mencari aktivitas fisik yang menyegarkan di pagi hari.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"edf9a49ef3745e6ee6714368b55e7f915\"><strong>Istirahat &amp; Kuliner Lokal:</strong> Setelah perjalanan trekking, kami telah menyiapkan makan siang lezat di restoran lokal untuk menutup petualangan Anda dengan sempurna.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>Explore the Active Crater: Mt. Lokon Volcano Trekking Experience</strong></h2><p>Experience the thrill of hiking one of North Sulawesi’s most iconic active volcanoes. <strong>Mount Lokon</strong> offers an authentic trekking adventure for those who want to witness the raw power of nature through its stunning crater without an overly extreme climb.</p><h3><strong>Tour Highlights:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e0dd7fab6bb74e325e05a891d16dbf906\"><strong>Tompaluan Crater Exploration:</strong> Follow a 2-hour trail leading to the rim of the <strong>Tompaluan Crater</strong>. Here, you can observe volcanic activity from a safe yet close enough distance to feel its magnificence.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef465741b3793a7917f2ce617735b5ad0\"><strong>Tomohon City Panorama:</strong> Enjoy the refreshing views of Tomohon City from the mountain slopes, offering a different perspective of Minahasa’s natural beauty.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb934ebbd073de399ec5e24c34b97d66a\"><strong>A Balanced Challenge:</strong> Standing at 1,580 meters above sea level, the path to the crater is perfectly suited for both beginners and experienced hikers looking for a refreshing morning physical activity.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eee1d0d59b466c93aae3831c37408abe7\"><strong>Rest &amp; Local Cuisine:</strong> After your trekking journey, we have prepared a delicious lunch at a local restaurant to perfectly conclude your adventure.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>활화산 분화구 탐험: 로콘산 트레킹 체험</strong></h2><p>북술라웨시에서 가장 상징적인 활화산 중 하나를 등반하는 스릴을 느껴보세요. **로콘산(Mt. Lokon)**은 너무 험난하지 않은 코스로, 압도적인 분화구를 통해 대자연의 힘을 가까이서 목격하고 싶은 분들을 위한 정통 트레킹 어드벤처를 제공합니다.</p><h3><strong>투어 하이라이트:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e5e27211adbec18ccc84e2b58e9a1391f\"><strong>톰팔루안 분화구 탐사:</strong> <strong>톰팔루안(Tompaluan) 분화구</strong> 가장자리까지 약 2시간 동안 이어지는 트레킹 코스를 따라가 보세요. 안전한 거리에서 화산 활동의 웅장함을 직접 눈으로 확인할 수 있습니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e7dbbf4e70f83ab6f89150882b800d14e\"><strong>토모혼 시내 파노라마:</strong> 산기슭에서 내려다보는 토모혼 시내의 평화로운 전경은 미나하사 자연미의 또 다른 매력을 선사합니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef716522bd4817054ca14cce61e6d0f65\"><strong>적절한 난이도의 도전:</strong> 해발 1,580m 높이의 로콘산 분화구 코스는 상쾌한 아침 운동을 즐기고 싶은 초보자나 숙련된 등산객 모두에게 적합합니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e36cc9fdcb2e4f7e4c8131fbd1f6589aa\"><strong>휴식과 현지 미식:</strong> 트레킹을 마친 후, 현지 레스토랑에서 정성껏 준비한 점심 식사로 완벽하게 하루를 마무리하세요.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>探索活性火山口：罗孔山火山徒步体验</strong></h2><p>亲身体验攀登北苏拉威西岛最著名的活性火山之一。<strong>罗孔山</strong>（Mt. Lokon）为那些希望近距离感受大自然力量，同时又不追求极端攀登难度的游客提供了一段纯正的徒步探险之旅。</p><h3><strong>行程亮点：</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"efcb66e0c38891f5340c8016ab051ec16\"><strong>探索汤帕卢安火山口：</strong> 沿着徒步路线攀登约 2 小时，抵达<strong>汤帕卢安（Tompaluan）火山口</strong>边缘。在这里，您可以在安全距离内观察火山活动，感受大自然的宏伟。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8dc6987746e29f6485db521763741243\"><strong>托莫洪市全景：</strong> 从山坡俯瞰托莫洪市的宁静美景，为您展现米那哈萨自然风光的独特视角。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebebae1bfa24177b91cb09ddb8cda7059\"><strong>适度的体力挑战：</strong> 罗孔山海拔 1,580 米，前往火山口的路线非常适合想要在早晨进行户外锻炼的初学者或经验丰富的徒步爱好者。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e879b8e2fb8ecb89648bd01aa6a445cbe\"><strong>休息与地道美食：</strong> 徒步结束后，我们为您准备了当地餐厅的美味午餐，为您的探险之旅画上完美的句点。</li></ul>', 0.00, NULL, 'daily', 1, 0, NULL, 4, 6, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e9e914bf2ff11c00c2a9db3b87ca22efe\">Fully air-conditioned transportation according to the number of tour participants</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e680c0b8aea08452cbae884c6d5e2d572\">Experienced guide and driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebca155750890997c3be20cf7a2196305\">Entrance fees to tourist attractions</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8d8fd8ee171bb996d9ee4419d568d989\">Parking fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8b60764be181f21f1778af2b47681999\">Lunch</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec2d301ad37ffc7057334aefa9fe2257e\">A bottle of mineral water per person</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e041e6dc48bc42dd9524a3df956c00c0c\">Tour services as per the program</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e97188319fb5536c010e7d1ddc597336f\">Airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e23e09bdcb623c333c317c7b6299f8759\">Airport tax</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e83a0664f8844283c0c4348456a9dfb3b\">Porter</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e1bd92c6b00cb5ea95a1c37639c97543e\">Hotel</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef148c59f0c1f718ac34fb13f0e1dbe4a\">Tips for guide and driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8cb793f90a845b4dfd6bf1f1b2b42a80\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e763128880b466113267e760ee5d194f5\">Any other expenses outside the tour program.</li></ul>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-20 09:12:28', '2026-05-03 01:42:32'),
(18, 1, 'Mt. Mahawu Volcano & Tetetana Hill', 'NORTH SULAWESI', 'mt-mahawu-volcano-tetetana-hill', '<h2><strong>Puncak Keindahan Minahasa: Mt. Mahawu &amp; Tetetana Hill Tour</strong></h2><p>Nikmati kombinasi sempurna antara petualangan ringan dan panorama alam yang luar biasa. Paket ini dirancang bagi Anda yang ingin menikmati sensasi berada di puncak gunung berapi dan perbukitan tanpa harus melewati pendakian yang melelahkan.</p><h3><strong>Mengapa Paket Ini Wajib Anda Pilih?</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e289dad6ec38ba834f6f2a17f7c5656d4\"><strong>Pendakian Ramah Wisatawan:</strong> Jelajahi <strong>Gunung Mahawu</strong> dengan akses yang mudah. Tersedia sekitar 150 anak tangga semen yang dilengkapi pagar pengaman, memudahkan siapa saja untuk mencapai puncak dan melihat kawahnya yang unik.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e33ce1e591754988ccb7195660a2e920e\"><strong>Cakrawala Tiga Dimensi:</strong> Dari puncak Mahawu, Anda akan disuguhi pemandangan spektakuler Pulau Manado Tua, Bunaken, serta hamparan Kota Manado yang membentang luas.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee76ea66ff6557456736998e1d9ecf678\"><strong>Pesona Bukit Tetetana:</strong> Kunjungi <strong>Puncak Tetetana</strong>, destinasi hits di Tomohon. Di sini, Anda bisa melihat empat wilayah Sulawesi Utara sekaligus dari satu titik, dikelilingi oleh taman bunga yang cantik dan udara yang sangat sejuk.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb1808ad47ec527b26cc7152839beef07\"><strong>Momen Foto Estetik:</strong> Setiap sudut perjalanan ini menawarkan latar belakang yang <i>Instagrammable</i>, mulai dari jalur tangga hijau hingga kebun bunga di atas bukit.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8df418b1243fc777ad9743225ecab904\"><strong>Kuliner Lokal yang Lezat:</strong> Segarkan diri setelah eksplorasi dengan makan siang menu lokal yang autentik di restoran terpilih.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>The Peaks of Minahasa: Mt. Mahawu &amp; Tetetana Hill Tour</strong></h2><p>Enjoy the perfect combination of a light adventure and extraordinary natural panoramas. This package is designed for those who want to experience the sensation of being atop a volcano and lush hills without the need for an exhausting climb.</p><h3><strong>Why Choose This Tour?</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e7a29308d5344f9ad129dc37e992a6874\"><strong>Tourist-Friendly Hike:</strong> Explore <strong>Mount Mahawu</strong> with easy access. There are approximately 150 cemented steps with safety railings, making it easy for anyone to reach the summit and see its unique crater.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec946a5f67e92c1549489222f4029b4db\"><strong>Three-Dimensional Horizon:</strong> From the top of Mahawu, you will be treated to spectacular views of Manado Tua Island, Bunaken, and the sprawling cityscape of Manado.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eabcaad3020191546daad12cc82231e8a\"><strong>The Charm of Tetetana Hill:</strong> Visit <strong>Tetetana Peak</strong>, the latest hit destination in Tomohon. Here, you can overlook four regions of North Sulawesi simultaneously from a single point, surrounded by beautiful flower gardens and cool mountain air.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e7ceb6aea4bdfaf1d53e19b908fb71876\"><strong>Aesthetic Photo Moments:</strong> Every corner of this journey offers an Instagrammable backdrop, from the lush green staircase path to the flower gardens on the hill.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e4b9761f97b0677740424573491b01eba\"><strong>Delicious Local Cuisine:</strong> Refresh yourself after the exploration with an authentic local lunch at a selected restaurant.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>미나하사의 정점: 마하우산 &amp; 테테타나 힐 투어</strong></h2><p>가벼운 모험과 환상적인 자연 파노라마의 완벽한 조화를 즐겨보세요. 이 패키지는 힘든 등산 없이도 화산 정상과 푸른 언덕의 정취를 느끼고 싶은 분들을 위해 준비되었습니다.</p><h3><strong>이 투어를 선택해야 하는 이유:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e8839200226da494b6e450628f24f50b0\"><strong>여행객 친화적인 하이킹:</strong> **마하우산(Mt. Mahawu)**을 편리하게 탐험하세요. 안전 난간이 설치된 약 150개의 시멘트 계단이 있어 누구나 쉽게 정상에 올라 독특한 분화구를 감상할 수 있습니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebdf6d63ce152d80c04da07570e111e84\"><strong>3차원 지평선:</strong> 마하우 정상에서는 마나도 투아 섬, 부나켄 섬, 그리고 넓게 펼쳐진 마나도 시내의 장관을 한눈에 담을 수 있습니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec8ce1842c18e41a0bf7ae0fa0cf1ab9e\"><strong>테테타나 힐의 매력:</strong> 토모혼의 인기 명소인 <strong>테테타나 피크</strong>를 방문하세요. 이곳에서는 북술라웨시의 4개 지역을 한곳에서 조망할 수 있으며, 아름다운 꽃밭과 시원한 공기가 여러분을 맞이합니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee549fa49300950caa4ee759e68317dd7\"><strong>인생샷 명소:</strong> 초록빛 계단 길부터 언덕 위의 꽃 정원까지, 이 여정의 모든 순간은 인스타그램에 올리기 좋은 완벽한 배경이 됩니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e55d1d05632a7b37606f8b8ec8829c61d\"><strong>현지 미식 체험:</strong> 탐험 후에는 엄선된 레스토랑에서 정통 현지식으로 활력을 되찾으세요.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>米那哈萨之巅：马哈武火山与特特塔纳山丘之旅</strong></h2><p>尽情享受轻松探险与绝美自然全景 vertical 的完美结合。本行程专为那些希望体验登顶火山与山丘的快感，却又不愿尝试艰苦攀登的游客而设计。</p><h3><strong>为什么选择这个行程？</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e28318fa7bff3ce951944e3bb96d2df7e\"><strong>游客友好型徒步：</strong> 轻松探索<strong>马哈武火山</strong>（Mt. Mahawu）。这里设有约 150 级带安全护栏的斜坡石阶，方便任何人轻松登顶并欣赏独特的火山口。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee22e04f33a8644aab5ad045e16059f77\"><strong>三维天际线：</strong> 从马哈武山顶，您可以将马纳多图阿岛、布纳肯岛以及延绵的美娜多市景尽收眼底。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0935d11766c29b6c57df72676b17aeb5\"><strong>特特塔纳山丘的魅力：</strong> 游览托莫洪的热门景点<strong>特特塔纳峰</strong>（Tetetana Peak）。在这里，您可以从同一个位置同时俯瞰北苏拉威西省的四个地区，四周环绕着美丽的花园，空气清新宜人。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9c338a78c3df5da18a7606579505edab\"><strong>绝佳拍照瞬间：</strong> 旅途中的每个角落都极具“网红”打卡潜质，从绿意盎然的阶梯步道到山顶的花海，皆是绝佳背景。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eeabff5ae5527cede429fbbe89883a301\"><strong>地道当地美食：</strong> 探险结束后，在精选餐厅享用正宗的当地午餐，补充体力。</li></ul>', 0.00, NULL, 'daily', 1, 0, NULL, 4, 5, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ee0a07c9cb24323f7ce891a99fae8befb\">Fully air-conditioned transportation according to the number of tour participants</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2294b9fea85a5bb7b3c381229d996538\">Experienced guide and driver, entrance fees to tourist attractions</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e91b0f8f940b1ae9746f796b2399f0b12\">Parking fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e68c9ac84e6c7d75451eaf1e0bd591748\">Lunch</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e1a2d571799de05d946edbf79052260d1\">A bottle of mineral water per person</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eeeb894126a0e2667e1c122b8daf2a097\">Services as per the program</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ed040cc0dd81d42e795600e22a7bf6536\">Airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb2e43bfc1813f79cdda31725bf97dbad\">Airport tax</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eec4c3bc7fb908919a5b66c97cde714e5\">Porter</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef13b7599a238bc82e6bd5620370064d9\">Hotel</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e7a50082855dcc93d44a0d8bbcef795bb\">Tips for guide and driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2a39ca8ecbefd244e7980a1f24d1bb28\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"efae7355dae9278ce19d7a043661cdfd1\">Other expenses outside the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-20 09:16:09', '2026-05-03 01:42:18'),
(19, 1, 'White Water Rafting', 'NORTH SULAWESI', 'white-water-rafting', '<h2><strong>Pacu Adrenalin di Jeram Nimanga: White Water Rafting Adventure</strong></h2><p>Siapkan diri Anda untuk petualangan air paling seru di Sulawesi Utara! Taklukkan jeram-jeram sungai yang menantang sambil menikmati keasrian alam yang memukau. Paket ini dirancang khusus bagi Anda yang mencari kombinasi sempurna antara tantangan fisik, kegembiraan, dan pemandangan hutan tropis yang hijau.</p><h3><strong>Mengapa Anda Harus Mencoba Petualangan Ini?</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"eeeedfbffcb97dbb771976347dd931905\"><strong>Jeram Sungai Nimanga yang Menantang:</strong> Rasakan sensasi mengarungi jeram sungai selama kurang lebih 90 menit. Setiap belokan sungai menawarkan kejutan dan tantangan baru yang akan membuat jantung Anda berdegup kencang.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec90c36b11ef5ad2667737faaeded3796\"><strong>Keindahan Alam Desa Timbukar:</strong> Lokasi rafting di Desa Timbukar, Sonder, menawarkan pemandangan tebing dan pepohonan rimbun yang masih sangat asri di sepanjang aliran sungai.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e607974d3ec5878257f01f2f33d074876\"><strong>Keamanan Adalah Prioritas:</strong> Sebelum memulai, Anda akan mendapatkan pelatihan singkat mengenai gerakan dasar dan prosedur keselamatan. Selama pengarungan, Anda akan didampingi oleh dua pemandu profesional yang ahli di bidangnya.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e84176559be5f0acae411c07d5365de7f\"><strong>Peralatan Standar Internasional:</strong> Kami memastikan kenyamanan dan keamanan Anda dengan menyediakan peralatan rafting (perahu, helm, pelampung) yang memenuhi standar keselamatan internasional.</li></ul><p><strong>“Defy the rapids, embrace the wild, and conquer the Nimanga River with us!”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>Conquer the Rapids: Nimanga River White Water Rafting Adventure</strong></h2><p>Get ready for the most thrilling water adventure in North Sulawesi! Navigate challenging river rapids while surrounded by breathtaking natural beauty. This package is perfectly designed for those seeking a mix of physical challenge, excitement, and lush tropical scenery.</p><h3><strong>Tour Highlights:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e6a535b7ab8464716f4bdf51a24964de5\"><strong>Challenging Nimanga Rapids:</strong> Experience the thrill of rafting for approximately 90 minutes. Every river bend offers new surprises and challenges that will get your heart racing.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea26059dfb10c41d48b33ecd7f20cefde\"><strong>Timbukar Village Scenery:</strong> Located in Sonder, the rafting route offers stunning views of steep cliffs and dense greenery along the pristine river flow.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb5b01eb29ad1bd42c634418db8d1f262\"><strong>Safety First:</strong> Before heading out, you will receive a safety briefing and basic rowing training. You will be accompanied by two professional rafting guides throughout the journey.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e201f08efdda20a113cafafe817d5e5e0\"><strong>International Standard Gear:</strong> We ensure your comfort and safety by providing high-quality rafting equipment (boats, helmets, life jackets) that meets international safety standards.</li></ul><p><strong>“Defy the rapids, embrace the wild, and conquer the Nimanga River with us!”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>급류를 정복하라: 니망가강 화이트 워터 래프팅 어드벤처</strong></h2><p>북술라웨시에서 가장 짜릿한 수상 어드벤처를 준비하세요! 숨 막히게 아름다운 자연 속에서 도전적인 급류를 정복해 보세요. 이 패키지는 체력적인 도전, 즐거움, 그리고 푸른 열대 우림의 경치를 한 번에 즐기고 싶은 분들을 위해 특별히 설계되었습니다.</p><h3><strong>투어 하이라이트:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ef541bb82a3cc49b0a1e61036db29ca13\"><strong>도전적인 니망가 급류:</strong> 약 90분 동안 이어지는 스릴 넘치는 래프팅을 경험해 보세요. 굽이치는 강줄기마다 심장을 뛰게 할 새로운 즐거움과 도전이 기다리고 있습니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed6e4ead62dbb5bf423d7ccc1025d1784\"><strong>팀부카르 마을의 자연미:</strong> 손데르(Sonder) 지역의 팀부카르 마을에서 시작되는 이 코스는 울창한 나무와 가파른 절벽이 어우러진 태초의 자연 그대로의 모습을 보여줍니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea637412ca44e9e373ff24101d9a96689\"><strong>안전 최우선:</strong> 시작 전 기본 동작과 안전 수칙에 대한 교육이 진행됩니다. 모든 여정에는 두 명의 전문 래프팅 가이드가 동행하여 안전을 책임집니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ede01249ceebd8d9b8a17098854c74487\"><strong>국제 표준 장비:</strong> 국제 안전 표준을 준수하는 고품질 래프팅 장비(보트, 헬멧, 구명조끼)를 제공하여 안심하고 즐기실 수 있습니다.</li></ul><p><strong>“Defy the rapids, embrace the wild, and conquer the Nimanga River with us!”</strong></p>', '<h2><strong>挑战急流：尼曼加河白水漂流探险之旅</strong></h2><p>准备好迎接北苏拉威西最刺激的水上冒险了吗？在绝美的自然风光中征服充满挑战的河道急流。本套餐专为追求体力挑战、狂欢乐趣与热带雨林美景的游客量身打造。</p><h3><strong>行程亮点：</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e4683ad4f2d5fcf3bd6d526db3ae2590d\"><strong>挑战尼曼加河急流：</strong> 体验约 90 分钟的惊险漂流。河道的每一个弯道都充满了惊喜与挑战，让您心跳加速。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"edbb8ba3b34908f1f5ad3d323d5d4ab74\"><strong>廷布卡村的自然美景：</strong> 漂流位于 Sonder 的 Timbukar 村，沿途您可以欣赏到原始河流两岸壮丽的峭壁与郁郁葱葱的林木。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebfc9ca5c0359cc55ace61473c4229a95\"><strong>安全至上：</strong> 开课前，您将接受关于基本动作和安全规程的简短培训。全程将由两名专业的漂流向导陪同，确保您的安全。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eea0a535db0865034d8c07d3d41500165\"><strong>国际标准装备：</strong> 我们提供符合国际安全标准的漂流设备（橡皮艇、头盔、救生衣），为您提供全方位的保护。</li></ul><p><strong>“Defy the rapids, embrace the wild, and conquer the Nimanga River with us!”</strong></p>', 0.00, NULL, 'daily', 1, 0, NULL, 6, 7, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e8f9892615252c1f7113eb1af6758e23d\">Fully air-conditioned transportation according to the number of tour participants</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea3a96d847da9f813d56ea1bf5e5091f0\">Experienced guide and driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5f704714c2138eff93abd9ef0b451e7c\">Rafting equipment and gear</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ebef7f400e0d2a286c3753c27ac6b35d5\">Entrance fees to tourist attractions</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee7e8a9cdd869251eacb4fee991736ba1\">Parking fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e51ee15f118665b0e2d33ac03bf6150d0\">1 bottle of mineral water per person</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e25c6d77eec5df59483c0f7d94f7d0753\">Services as per the program</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e64a5c48756da8949a84fc99be24bd499\">Airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0b3182e85d9f33acc157b85808347961\">Airport tax</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2cb5bdd5ecfc46fcb144d67bfbd8950f\">Meals</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef1153321326a82f3288f350ea4e12772\">Porter</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e6657bb1483ae99b0ac50275b9a92fefa\">Hotel</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e90f5a9e0c8775eae0dd396d234c2ca6e\">Guide and driver tips</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e1bc758f69c0ff547e5c8f8aca100c99e\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed4f1470355a4f65f457a776a07b216c9\">Other expenses not mentioned in the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-20 09:18:34', '2026-05-03 01:41:57'),
(20, 1, 'Minahasa Highland Tour', 'NORTH SULAWESI', 'minahasa-highland-tour', '<h2><strong>Pesona Pegunungan Minahasa: Harmoni Budaya &amp; Keajaiban Alam</strong></h2><p>Lupakan sejenak keramaian kota dan rasakan kesejukan udara pegunungan dalam perjalanan satu hari ke dataran tinggi Minahasa. Dari pasar tradisional yang unik hingga danau sulfur yang menenangkan, paket ini menawarkan perpaduan sempurna antara petualangan budaya dan relaksasi alam yang tidak akan Anda temukan di tempat lain.</p><h3><strong>Keunikan yang Menanti Anda:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e1086989b82ea87d1648d1b0594a081eb\"><strong>Warna-warni Kota Bunga:</strong> Manjakan mata di <strong>Taman Wisata Pelangi</strong>, Tomohon, yang dipenuhi hamparan bunga cantik beraneka warna.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8b1829a8f2a0f5cb39b0b2616fe7b3e9\"><strong>Pasar Ekstrem Tomohon:</strong> Lihat langsung keunikan budaya lokal di pasar tradisional yang menjual berbagai daging hewan liar, sebuah pengalaman ikonik bagi para pelancong dunia.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e08888952b5c1fa708f73bc84d109032d\"><strong>Warisan Leluhur &amp; Kuliner:</strong> Saksikan proses pembuatan kue tradisional Manado secara langsung serta pengolahan minuman lokal \'Cap Tikus\' di hutan Aren <strong>Tuur Maasering</strong> yang sangat <i>Instagrammable</i>.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e141a721ee4df47e531b829ba3be0a2b2\"><strong>Relaksasi di Danau &amp; Bukit Kasih:</strong> Nikmati makan siang di tepi <strong>Danau Tondano</strong>. Jelajahi kawah belerang di <strong>Bukit Kasih</strong>, dan tutup hari dengan kopi atau teh hangat di tepi <strong>Danau Linow</strong> yang airnya dapat berubah warna.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>Minahasa Highland Charms: A Harmony of Culture &amp; Natural Wonders</strong></h2><p>Escape the city buzz and breathe in the cool mountain air on a full-day journey through the Minahasa Highlands. From unique traditional markets to soothing sulfur lakes, this package offers a perfect blend of cultural adventure and natural relaxation that you won\'t find anywhere else.</p><h3><strong>Tour Highlights:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e60e1c7ad058afd3b95c89eee2abc7c10\"><strong>Colorful Flower City:</strong> Delight your eyes at <strong>Taman Wisata Pelangi</strong> in Tomohon, a vibrant park filled with beautiful, multicolored flowers.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8d40b47268c9fe6fed753268235ceb39\"><strong>Tomohon Extreme Market:</strong> Witness local culture firsthand at this iconic traditional market, famous for its variety of wild animal meats—a unique experience for world travelers.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e24e58be0892abdad7b7832991e2fc743\"><strong>Heritage &amp; Culinary Delights:</strong> Watch the live preparation of traditional Manado cakes and see how the local liquor \'Cap Tikus\' is processed in the Instagrammable <strong>Tuur Maasering</strong> sugar palm forest.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec227742241ba062257262e2c9d76fa86\"><strong>Lakeside Relaxation &amp; Bukit Kasih:</strong> Enjoy lunch by <strong>Lake Tondano</strong>, explore active sulfur craters at <strong>Bukit Kasih</strong>, and end your day with warm coffee or tea by the color-changing waters of <strong>Lake Linow</strong>.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>미나하사 고원의 매력: 문화와 자연의 경이로운 조화</strong></h2><p>도시의 소란함을 뒤로하고 미나하사 고원으로 떠나는 일일 투어를 통해 시원한 산바람을 느껴보세요. 독특한 전통 시장부터 마음을 차분하게 해주는 유황 호수까지, 이 패키지는 다른 어디에서도 찾아볼 수 없는 문화적 모험과 자연 속 휴식의 완벽한 조화를 선사합니다.</p><h3><strong>투어 하이라이트:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ef09196937fecaccd19a907b7df459e88\"><strong>다채로운 꽃의 도시:</strong> 형형색색의 아름다운 꽃들로 가득한 토모혼의 **타만 위사타 펠랑이(Taman Wisata Pelangi) **에서 눈을 즐겁게 해보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb8a69a481369be71324f403a67a1ddac\"><strong>토모혼 익스트림 마켓:</strong> 다양한 야생동물 고기를 판매하는 것으로 유명한 이 이색적인 전통 시장에서 현지 문화를 가까이서 경험해 보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed015670cfab71a4e6c99837e17e17ec5\"><strong>전통 유산과 미식:</strong> 마나도 전통 케이크를 만드는 과정을 직접 참관하고, 인스타그램 명소인 <strong>투우르 마세링(Tuur Maasering)</strong> 아렌 숲에서 현지 전통주 \'찹 티쿠스(Cap Tikus)\'가 만들어지는 과정을 살펴보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e7daf5b6055e29f5e3728d4bda223dc3a\"><strong>호숫가의 휴식과 부킷 카시:</strong> <strong>톤다노 호수</strong> 옆에서 점심 식사를 즐기고, **부킷 카시(Bukit Kasih) **의 활성 유황 분화구를 탐험한 후, 물빛이 변하는 <strong>리노우 호수</strong>에서 따뜻한 커피나 차와 함께 하루를 마무리하세요.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>米那哈萨高地魅力：文化与自然奇观的和谐之旅</strong></h2><p>远离城市喧嚣，在米那哈萨高地的一日之旅中呼吸清新的山间空气 。从独特的传统市场到宁静的硫磺湖，本行程将文化探险与自然放松完美结合，为您带来独一无二的体验 。</p><h3><strong>行程亮点：</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ed81d3bceeb43396daead4b7982fb3973\"><strong>色彩斑斓的花园城市：</strong> 游览托莫洪（Tomohon）的<strong>彩虹旅游公园</strong>（Taman Wisata Pelangi），欣赏满园争奇斗艳的鲜花 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e06b11eefde48170c055d3a12afcb424e\"><strong>托莫洪极端市场：</strong> 在这个极具标志性的传统市场见证当地文化，这里以售卖各种野味而闻名，是环球旅行者不可错过的奇特体验 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0f79fb1697c5c2ce9aa0ebe558bdbf1a\"><strong>传承与美食：</strong> 亲眼见证美娜多传统糕点的制作过程，并在非常适合拍照打卡的 <strong>Tuur Maasering</strong> 糖棕林观察当地特色酒 “Cap Tikus” 的酿造工艺 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e240a99a2bf5b8f872d7954a2c906391d\"><strong>湖畔放松与爱之丘：</strong> 在<strong>通达诺湖</strong>（Lake Tondano）畔享用午餐，探索<strong>爱之丘</strong>（Bukit Kasih）的活性硫磺喷火口，最后在湖水会变色的<strong>里诺湖</strong>（Lake Linow）畔品尝热咖啡或茶，结束美好的一天 。</li></ul>', 0.00, NULL, 'daily', 1, 0, NULL, 6, 8, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e3a6d5c7a95824505fcc7169d19c68b06\">Fully air-conditioned transportation according to the number of tour participants</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eed59092e3fde448a5e5a4fb756ab6e44\">Experienced guide and driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e1fbf9e5db829006a3fc211fef7a86ec5\">Entrance fees to tourist attractions</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec1827a81cbe7feb5e6c155dc5f41899e\">Parking fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb65edb1a96b3c032f8f825315f9c7209\">Lunch</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5971d7bd5ebcae0985b7b12074916355\">A bottle of mineral water per person</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef7e51ca1230476f54d606b374973afb1\">Tour services as per the program</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ed1003d6a37aa7b1fbafe39f48ba09598\">Airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9101a0e59598b6ff7f1e74ede3ede14f\">Airport tax</li><li data-list-item-id=\"efd4176d12238c02b80f1e80ada630810\">Porter</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea6ec6622fd640f8ae2aff46bc2e3b6e6\">Hotel,&nbsp;</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee0e2b05c5dcca53d84e69986e0eec301\">Tips for guide and driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5de631515d01a36e9bf58f056fac2003\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eebc3a63adc6760f98d268bc5875c1aac\">Any other expenses outside the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 1, 'popular', NULL, '2026-04-20 09:21:02', '2026-05-03 01:41:45');
INSERT INTO `manado_tours` (`id`, `category_id`, `title`, `location`, `slug`, `description`, `description_en`, `description_ko`, `description_zh`, `base_price`, `price_usd`, `tour_type`, `duration_days`, `duration_nights`, `duration_hours`, `duration_hours_min`, `duration_hours_max`, `highlights`, `inclusions`, `exclusions`, `itinerary_pdf_path`, `is_featured`, `featured_badge`, `terms_conditions`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(21, 1, 'Bunaken Island Sightseeing Tour', 'NORTH SULAWESI', 'bunaken-island-sightseeing-tour', '<h2><strong>Jelajahi Surga Bawah Laut: Paket Wisata Pulau Bunaken</strong></h2><p>Siapkan diri Anda untuk petualangan tak terlupakan di <strong>Taman Laut Bunaken</strong>, salah satu destinasi wisata bahari paling ikonik di dunia! Nikmati perpaduan sempurna antara keindahan terumbu karang yang berwarna-warni, jernihnya air laut, dan suasana pantai yang menenangkan.</p><h3><strong>Mengapa Anda Harus Mengikuti Tour Ini?</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e2ce6ef52b65a6e6c238938e3b00c1afd\"><strong>Wajah Baru Bunaken:</strong> Kunjungi <strong>Dermaga Wisata Bunaken (New Bunaken)</strong> yang kini lebih menawan dan representatif—titik terbaik untuk berburu foto dan video estetik dengan latar pemandangan pulau yang memukau.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed0d2c7a2fa2f46afa2ff3c0aff0fabfd\"><strong>Keajaiban Bawah Laut:</strong> Temukan ribuan spesies ikan tropis dan ekosistem terumbu karang yang masih terjaga melalui aktivitas <i>snorkeling</i> atau <i>diving</i>.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"efdab2f985f4c4b01fe7d05bc86fce08c\"><strong>Santai di Tepi Pantai:</strong> Nikmati waktu bebas untuk berjalan-jalan di atas pasir putih atau sekadar bersantai menghirup udara laut yang segar.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed3cd64c65f8011091c17e4689e4ecdef\"><strong>Makan Siang di Pinggir Pantai:</strong> Rasakan sensasi makan siang lezat di restoran lokal yang terletak tepat di tepi pantai.</li></ul>', '<h3><strong>Explore an Underwater Paradise: Bunaken Island Tour Package</strong></h3><p>Prepare yourself for an unforgettable adventure in the <strong>Bunaken Marine Park</strong>, one of the world\'s most iconic marine tourism destinations! Enjoy the perfect blend of vibrant coral reefs, crystal-clear waters, and a soothing beach atmosphere.</p><h3><strong>Why Should You Join This Tour?</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e5d2fd6b61a1afe756a173ea71b540a95\"><strong>The New Face of Bunaken:</strong> Visit the <strong>New Bunaken Tourism Pier</strong>, which is now more charming and representative—the best spot to capture aesthetic photos and videos with a stunning island backdrop.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e4e334f7b7596246f8fc2c1dff6d900d2\"><strong>Underwater Wonders:</strong> Discover thousands of tropical fish species and well-preserved coral reef ecosystems through optional snorkeling or diving activities.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5f1b6e898dced29e410ed0a58ff5209d\"><strong>Relax by the Shore:</strong> Enjoy free time to stroll along the beach or simply relax while breathing in the fresh sea air.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee7b39df8583e1005cb178f0444723766\"><strong>Beachfront Lunch:</strong> Experience the sensation of a delicious lunch at a local restaurant located right on the water\'s edge.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>수중 낙원 탐험: 부나켄 섬 관광 패키지</strong></h2><p>세계에서 가장 상징적인 해양 관광지 중 하나인 <strong>부나켄 해양 국립공원</strong>에서 잊지 못할 모험을 준비하세요! 화려한 산호초, 투명한 바다, 그리고 평화로운 해변의 분위기가 완벽한 조화를 이룹니다.</p><h3><strong>왜 이 투어에 참여해야 하나요?</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e239a4ba750be49443b7fd2f83070b53f\"><strong>새로워진 부나켄:</strong> 더욱 매력적이고 현대적으로 단장된 <strong>뉴 부나켄 관광 부두</strong>를 방문해 보세요. 섬의 절경을 배경으로 감성적인 사진과 영상을 남기기에 최고의 장소입니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ead9ec054b436f6638fd19c99af1e01fa\"><strong>신비로운 수중 세계:</strong> 스노클링이나 다이빙(선택 사항)을 통해 수천 종의 열대어와 보존된 산호초 생태계를 발견해 보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecc3392ea9cbaf2d36d4bbb63d44b9fff\"><strong>해변의 여유:</strong> 해변을 거닐거나 신선한 바다 공기를 마시며 자유로운 휴식을 즐겨보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ead31a4dc8747052125c5cf14c3f1cfdf\"><strong>해변에서의 점심 식사:</strong> 해변 바로 앞에 위치한 현지 레스토랑에서 맛있는 식사를 즐기는 특별한 경험을 해보세요.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>探索海底天堂：布纳肯岛旅游套餐</strong></h2><p>准备好在<strong>布纳肯国家海洋公园</strong>开启一场难忘的冒险吧！这里是全球最著名的海洋旅游胜地之一。 五彩斑斓的珊瑚礁、清澈见底的海水与宁静的海滩在这里完美交织。</p><h3><strong>为什么要参加这次旅行？</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e342d1cb12575d69d8373412508970003\"><strong>布纳肯新貌：</strong> 游览全新升级的<strong>布纳肯观光码头</strong>，这里现在更加迷人且具代表性——是拍摄以绝美海岛为背景的网红照片和视频的最佳地点。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e91c45828a7ce6420b1ec24681678faf3\"><strong>海底奇观：</strong> 通过浮潜或深潜（自选项目），探索成千上万种热带鱼类和保存完好的珊瑚礁生态系统。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0e493cb0fb7e17bd72ee5e0eedc9c2b2\"><strong>海滩慢时光：</strong> 享受自由活动时间，漫步在沙滩上或静静呼吸清新的海风。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e82aac6df185919086b95030bbb2c2c84\"><strong>海滨午餐：</strong> 在紧邻海滩的当地餐厅品尝美味佳肴，感受惬意的用餐体验。</li></ul>', 0.00, NULL, 'daily', 1, 0, NULL, 6, 8, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e756cec54195116ff096865a21781571f\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Private boat to Bunaken Island</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e00ba750ae031939e7c8465d501457022\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Experienced tour guide &amp; boatman</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed4121d16075b5d5f88c9d38af15c2a27\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Entrance fees to tourist attractions</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2332fcb6ed90ad0ae25b1e33e756583a\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Lunch at local restaurant</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec3c758171f7de84f46c858a794205a03\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">A bottle of mineral water per person</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8ced0664ba420cfbfb7f957585b5e359\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Tour services as per itinerary</p></li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e64a5c48756da8949a84fc99be24bd499\">Airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eeec1cfc460047b34d98ccaa46e7a7e79\">Land transportation (car)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0b3182e85d9f33acc157b85808347961\">Airport tax</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2cb5bdd5ecfc46fcb144d67bfbd8950f\">Meals</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef1153321326a82f3288f350ea4e12772\">Porter</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e6657bb1483ae99b0ac50275b9a92fefa\">Hotel</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e90f5a9e0c8775eae0dd396d234c2ca6e\">Guide and driver tips</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e1bc758f69c0ff547e5c8f8aca100c99e\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed4f1470355a4f65f457a776a07b216c9\">Other expenses not mentioned in the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-20 09:25:38', '2026-05-03 01:41:32'),
(22, 1, 'Manado City Tour & Lunch with Manado\'s Special Dishes', 'NORTH SULAWESI', 'manado-city-tour-luch-with-manados-special-dishes', '<h2><strong>Jelajahi Pesona Manado: Harmoni Sejarah, Kuliner &amp; Cakrawala</strong></h2><p>Nikmati perjalanan satu hari penuh makna melintasi waktu dan keindahan alam di jantung Sulawesi Utara. <strong>Manado City Tour</strong> mengajak Anda menyelami kekayaan budaya yang berpadu sempurna dengan panorama perbukitan yang megah.</p><h3><strong>Mengapa Anda Harus Memilih Paket Ini?</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e7c70f92e3cdd87164bdbdb03c30445f6\"><strong>Napak Tilas Sejarah &amp; Budaya:</strong> Kunjungi <strong>Klenteng Ban Hin Kiong</strong>, situs bersejarah berusia 300 tahun, serta <strong>Gereja Sentrum</strong> dan <strong>Monumen Perang Dunia II</strong> yang menjadi saksi bisu perjalanan kota ini.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2137f1165edfc463ea236ab9812ad744\"><strong>Keajaiban Ikonik:</strong> Saksikan langsung kemegahan <strong>Monumen Yesus Memberkati</strong>, patung Yesus melayang yang menjadi simbol berkah bagi Kota Manado.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb94fd673a95e03e7931d46bc21250e29\"><strong>Kuliner Autentik:</strong> Manjakan lidah Anda dengan makan siang menu <strong>Ikan Tuna khas Manado</strong> yang kaya rempah dan menggugah selera.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e7a7bde94928cd16e4b42e08966d34221\"><strong>Puncak Keindahan:</strong> Tutup hari Anda di <strong>Makatete Hill</strong>. Dari ketinggian 200 mdpl, nikmati pemandangan spektakuler Kota Manado, Gunung Klabat, hingga gugusan Pulau Bunaken dan Siladen yang memukau</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>Explore the Charms of Manado: A Journey of History, Flavor, and Skyline</strong></h2><p>Experience a full-day journey through time and nature in the heart of North Sulawesi. Our <strong>Manado City Tour</strong> invites you to dive into a rich cultural heritage perfectly blended with majestic hilltop panoramas.</p><h3><strong>Highlights of the Tour:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ecb138b9444e887560f70d952170d2d9d\"><strong>Historic &amp; Cultural Landmarks:</strong> Visit the <strong>Ban Hin Kiong Temple</strong>, a 300-year-old historic site , alongside the <strong>Sentrum Church</strong> and the <strong>World War II Monument</strong>.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e878863a6bf3d54d84e6c1f1e5f501e2e\"><strong>Iconic Wonders:</strong> Witness the grandeur of the <strong>Jesus Blessing Monument</strong>, a unique \"flying\" statue that serves as a symbol of the city.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5f16279c9d815f8ddada863fc8022e62\"><strong>Authentic Flavors:</strong> Treat your palate to a traditional <strong>Manado-style Tuna</strong> lunch, rich in local spices.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e3088c71b774ac172e844157df9b8aa28\"><strong>Breathtaking Heights:</strong> End your day at <strong>Makatete Hill</strong>. From 200 meters above sea level, enjoy spectacular views of Manado City, Mount Klabat, and the stunning Bunaken and Siladen islands.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>마나도의 매력을 발견하세요: 역사, 미식, 그리고 하늘의 조화</strong></h2><p>북술라웨시의 심장부에서 역사와 자연을 가로지르는 특별한 하루를 경험해 보세요. <strong>마나도 시티 투어</strong>는 풍부한 문화유산과 웅장한 언덕의 파노라마가 완벽하게 어우러진 여정으로 여러분을 초대합니다.</p><h3><strong>투어 하이라이트:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ebd0d9e91d086fd8ac29116bd5981a3f2\"><strong>역사와 문화 탐방:</strong> 300년 역사의 <strong>반힌콩 사원</strong>과 네덜란드 식민지 시대의 유산인 <strong>센트룸 교회</strong>, <strong>제2차 세계대전 기념비</strong>를 방문합니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e4e8923ee1f06832bd6eed0e61094dbf2\"><strong>상징적인 랜드마크:</strong> 마나도 시내를 굽어보며 공중에 떠 있는 듯한 형상의 <strong>예수 축복 동상</strong>의 웅장함을 감상하세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef9817681201cb2b18aa4307b79976505\"><strong>현지 미식 체험:</strong> 마나도 전통 방식으로 요리된 매콤하고 신선한 <strong>참치 요리</strong>로 점심 식사를 즐기세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e3adc68e30df448895862f684fe059d19\"><strong>환상적인 전망:</strong> <strong>마카테테 힐</strong>에서 하루를 마무리하세요. 해발 200m 높이에서 마나도 시내와 클라밧 산, 부나켄 및 실라덴 섬의 절경을 한눈에 담을 수 있습니다.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>探索美娜多魅力：历史、美食与天际线的完美融合</strong></h2><p>在北苏拉威西的心脏地带，开启一场穿越时光与自然的全日之旅 。<strong>美娜多市区游</strong>诚邀您领略深厚的文化底蕴与壮丽的山顶全景 。</p><h3><strong>行程亮点：</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e7aeeccfd4b8d16607d2cb68ed3e05c03\"><strong>历史与文化足迹：</strong> 参观拥有300年历史的<strong>万兴宫</strong>（Ban Hin Kiong），以及荷属殖民时期的<strong>中央教堂</strong>和<strong>二战纪念碑</strong> 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e40d8315e04e54740d675d210027dbdb1\"><strong>标志性奇迹：</strong> 近距离感受<strong>耶稣祝福雕像</strong>的宏伟，这座以“飞行”姿态呈现的雕像是美娜多的重要象征 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e282009f36af6f14398cda7e76c37ddfc\"><strong>地道风味：</strong> 品尝特色的<strong>美娜多式金枪鱼</strong>午餐，体验浓郁的当地香料风味 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb634301f7b564312d4050ca4eea0b2e5\"><strong>绝佳视野：</strong> 在<strong>马卡特特山</strong>（Makatete Hill）结束行程 。从海拔200米的高处，俯瞰美娜多市、克拉巴特山以及布纳肯岛和西拉登岛的迷人美景 。</li></ul>', 0.00, NULL, 'daily', 1, 0, NULL, 4, 5, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"efa0326736a93dbe5b6f2f4886719f0ae\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Air-conditioned transportation according to the number of tour participants</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e6f7c213ce63967da3a7674f798318146\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Experienced guide (English speaking guide) &amp; driver</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e31e949b88b66a13c31a285d2ea0fe01b\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Entrance fees &amp; parking fees</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5d9e0c346d759e5a38f90442bd7731c9\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Lunch at local restaurant</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e7b7a00f1ee67b67ec041223e00f34a09\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">A bottle of mineral water per person</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e364d522edd138b4fa0906d7379169caa\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Tour services according to the program</p></li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e64a5c48756da8949a84fc99be24bd499\">Airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0b3182e85d9f33acc157b85808347961\">Airport tax</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2cb5bdd5ecfc46fcb144d67bfbd8950f\">Meals</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef1153321326a82f3288f350ea4e12772\">Porter</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e6657bb1483ae99b0ac50275b9a92fefa\">Hotel</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e90f5a9e0c8775eae0dd396d234c2ca6e\">Guide and driver tips</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e1bc758f69c0ff547e5c8f8aca100c99e\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed4f1470355a4f65f457a776a07b216c9\">Other expenses not mentioned in the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-20 09:28:50', '2026-05-03 01:41:18'),
(23, 18, '6D5N Tangkoko Adventure Tour', 'NORTH SULAWESI', '6d5n-tangkoko-adventure-tour', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>The Ultimate North Sulawesi Odyssey: Petualangan 6 Hari Menembus Hutan Hujan &amp; Surga Bawah Laut</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Jelajahi sisi liar dan indah dari Sulawesi Utara dalam paket ekspedisi terlengkap kami! <strong>6D5N Tangkoko Adventure Tour</strong> bukan sekadar liburan biasa; ini adalah perjalanan epik yang menggabungkan keajaiban daratan, pegunungan, hingga pesona bawah laut Bunaken yang mendunia. Dirancang khusus untuk Anda yang mendambakan petualangan autentik tanpa batas.</p><h3 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Highlight Petualangan Anda:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e12c758ad7a3b9caef2f6c529ff8daa49\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Ekspedisi Rimba Tangkoko:</strong> Habiskan dua malam di jantung Tangkoko untuk misi pencarian satwa langka—dari <strong>Tarsier Spectrum</strong> yang menggemaskan hingga kawanan <strong>Black Crested Macaque</strong> yang eksklusif.</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e81ed621ed4ed7c8d9bb35190937d0aba\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Keajaiban Air Terjun Tunan:</strong> Rasakan kekuatan alam di air terjun setinggi 86 meter yang tersembunyi di dalam hutan yang masih sangat murni.</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e14fd76aabd03f871e1f0e8582e0b1f9f\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Pesona Dataran Tinggi Minahasa:</strong> Hirup udara sejuk Tomohon, jelajahi kawah <strong>Gunung Mahawu</strong>, dan nikmati ketenangan di <strong>Danau Linow</strong> yang airnya dapat berubah tiga warna.</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee393d8433e78a95c193c9e46680fa6dd\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Warisan Budaya Kuno:</strong> Kembali ke masa lalu dengan mengunjungi <strong>Waruga Sawangan</strong>, situs makam batu kuno zaman megalitikum yang sarat sejarah.</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecb36bff03de4ca51c75e6c0879e2718f\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Surga Bawah Laut Bunaken:</strong> Akhiri perjalanan Anda dengan relaksasi total di Pulau Bunaken. Snorkeling atau menyelamlah di antara dinding terumbu karang raksasa dan ribuan ikan tropis berwarna-warni.</p></li></ul>', '<h2><strong>The Ultimate North Sulawesi Odyssey: A 6-Day Grand Adventure through Rainforests &amp; Underwater Paradises</strong></h2><p>Explore the wild and beautiful side of North Sulawesi with our most comprehensive expedition package! The <strong>6D5N Tangkoko Adventure Tour</strong> is more than just a holiday; it is an epic journey combining terrestrial wonders, majestic highlands, and the world-renowned marine beauty of Bunaken. Designed for those seeking an authentic, boundary-pushing adventure.</p><h3><strong>Tour Highlights:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e4917dd6e2d82c2748f2467725dc34d3e\"><strong>Tangkoko Jungle Expedition:</strong> Spend two nights in the heart of Tangkoko on a mission to find rare wildlife—from the adorable <strong>Tarsier Spectrum</strong> to the exclusive troops of <strong>Black Crested Macaques</strong>.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eebe4c2b83968e3e2913ebc0dab9597c8\"><strong>Tunan Waterfall Wonder:</strong> Witness the raw power of nature at an 86-meter waterfall hidden deep within a pristine, untouched forest.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb38ca7a37681079d6f1c0f86fe2d3e1d\"><strong>Minahasa Highland Charms:</strong> Breathe in the cool air of Tomohon, explore the <strong>Mahawu Volcano</strong> crater, and find serenity at <strong>Lake Linow</strong>, famous for its three-colored changing waters.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eecfa71564e827640d4eb3dd2ddaafe28\"><strong>Ancient Cultural Heritage:</strong> Step back in time with a visit to <strong>Waruga Sawangan</strong>, an ancient megalithic stone tomb site rich in history.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e00ef5b24e4bd423e69c5356daf0ec9f1\"><strong>Bunaken Marine Paradise:</strong> Conclude your journey with total relaxation at Bunaken Island. Snorkel or dive among giant coral walls and thousands of vibrant tropical fish.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>궁극의 북설라웨시 오디세이: 열대 우림과 수중 낙원을 관통하는 6일간의 대여정</strong></h2><p>당사의 가장 포괄적인 원정 패키지를 통해 북설라웨시의 야생적이고 아름다운 면모를 탐험해 보세요! **5박 6일 탕코코 어드벤처 투어(6D5N Tangkoko Adventure Tour)**는 단순한 휴가를 넘어 지상의 경이로움, 웅장한 고원, 그리고 세계적으로 유명한 부나켄의 수중 매력을 결합한 서사시적인 여정입니다. 진정성 있고 한계가 없는 모험을 갈망하는 분들을 위해 설계되었습니다.</p><h3><strong>투어 하이라이트:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e5082fffb3f0142d32b576fa107bce9d2\"><strong>탕코코 정글 탐험:</strong> 탕코코의 심장부에서 2박을 보내며 귀여운 <strong>타르시어 안경원숭이</strong>부터 독특한 <strong>검정 짧은꼬리원숭이</strong> 무리까지 희귀 야생 동물을 찾는 미션을 수행합니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee6730ee54ede40a0f269770e6dbe93b5\"><strong>투난 폭포의 경이로움:</strong> 원시림 깊숙이 숨겨진 86m 높이 폭포에서 자연의 순수한 힘을 느껴보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e089b453ee93307e496c011dd950796c1\"><strong>미나하사 고원의 매력:</strong> 토모혼의 시원한 공기를 마시고, <strong>마하우 화산</strong> 분화구를 탐험하며, 세 가지 색으로 변하는 물빛으로 유명한 <strong>리노우 호수</strong>에서 평온함을 만끽하세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eacb65ae84f01c6b2467448edf780b567\"><strong>고대 문화 유산:</strong> 역사가 깃든 거대 석기 시대의 고대 무덤 터인 <strong>와루가 사왕안</strong>을 방문하여 과거로 시간 여행을 떠나보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eaf7967680b7c77ca181428c980f4a9bc\"><strong>부나켄 수중 낙원:</strong> 부나켄 섬에서 완전한 휴식으로 여정을 마무리하세요. 거대한 산호벽과 수천 마리의 화려한 열대어 사이에서 스노클링이나 다이빙을 즐겨보세요.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>极致北苏拉威西奥德赛：穿越热带雨林与水下天堂的六日巅峰之旅</strong></h2><p>通过我们最全面的探险套餐，探索北苏拉威西荒野与美丽的一面！<strong>“6天5晚唐科科冒险之旅” (6D5N Tangkoko Adventure Tour)</strong> 不仅仅是一次度假；它是一场结合了陆地奇观、雄伟高原和闻名世界的布纳肯水下魅力的史诗之旅。专为追求真实、挑战极限的冒险者而设计。</p><h3><strong>行程亮点：</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ef411bb95bb02cce19e8df0937e2516cb\"><strong>唐科科丛林远征：</strong> 在唐科科的核心地带度过两个夜晚，执行寻找稀有野生动物的任务——从可爱的<strong>眼镜猴</strong>到独特的<strong>黑猴</strong>族群。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9e702bc60d7e0b37246de6a5b5d6c5d3\"><strong>图南瀑布奇观：</strong> 在深藏于原始森林中的 86 米高瀑布前，感受大自然的原始力量。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e6562928cef2245b32a2a8dcbaa6dce8b\"><strong>米纳哈萨高原魅力：</strong> 呼吸托莫洪 (Tomohon) 的凉爽空气，探索<strong>马哈武火山</strong>口，并在以三色湖水闻名的<strong>林诺湖</strong>畔享受宁静。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eec665036bb1e7ee129b4dbb1695ae672\"><strong>古老文化遗产：</strong> 参观<strong>瓦鲁加沙旺安 (Waruga Sawangan)</strong>，这是一个充满历史气息的巨石阵时代古老石墓遗址，带您重返过去。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e280c44c9bc9940f3f97f556d0cff19e4\"><strong>布纳肯水下天堂：</strong> 在布纳肯岛以彻底的放松结束您的旅程。在巨大的珊瑚墙和成千上万种色彩斑斓的热带鱼之间浮潜或潜水。</li></ul>', 0.00, NULL, 'package', 6, 5, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e003cb081df381c6177f6f6ea22e70670\">Full AC transportation&nbsp;</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0d5c6e19f840ce309c7c0f35dcfac3f4\">Private Boat to Bunaken Island</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e4364960109bee572d3a8d9cae7ce2e96\">5-night hotel stay based double occupancy</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e406c6b2a303d8fc371e9e36db30336f9\">Experienced guide &amp; driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea83df9e88b4d60410713905d99b0773e\">Entrance tickets to tourist attractions &amp; parking fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea0513d38795aacb231a0d76a6e389665\">Meals as tour program</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e1d347a24ac609ef4c151d1e191962bad\">Tour services as per the program</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e03a02e72cc81325190c8b5844feec80c\">A bottle of mineral water per pax per day</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e38650055baf01af92b30e8be7c0377e6\">Handling service</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"eb5eba377a627536111f5daaf42cb875e\">Round-trip flight tickets</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9871e63b9fbb46e8e849ba04f66112b4\">Tips for guide &amp; driver</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e141f97d4f43b25648e15d80a691fd2d7\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecbb5c50e20d10d1311cd91fb730a72f6\">Additional expenses outside the package (extra meals/drinks, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed9e6b7e4a9ad9f99209d34216e79ff72\">Porter, airport tax &amp; excess baggage</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee8836b89a60e07a22d2e2038bc73b07d\">Personal expenses (laundry, minibar, room service, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5dda5c1a16091383138fef6dd26df6ee\">Travel insurace</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed1693c3ccea40a446251d042c65b75e9\">Other costs outside the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 1, 'hot', NULL, '2026-04-25 02:23:41', '2026-05-03 01:41:04'),
(24, 18, 'Tangkoko Adventure 4D3N', 'NORTH SULAWESI', 'tangkoko-adventure-4d3n', '<h2><strong>The Ultimate Tangkoko Expedition: Petualangan Hebat 4 Hari Menjelajahi Alam Liar Sulawesi</strong></h2><p>Apakah Anda siap untuk pengalaman \"National Geographic\" versi Anda sendiri? Paket <strong>Tangkoko Adventure 4D3N</strong> dari <strong>Welcome Manado Tours</strong> adalah perjalanan mendalam yang membawa Anda jauh ke dalam keasrian hutan hujan tropis untuk bertemu dengan makhluk-makhluk paling unik di bumi. Dari gemuruh air terjun hingga tatapan mata Tarsier yang ikonik, petualangan ini adalah impian setiap pencinta alam dan fotografer.</p><h3><strong>Highlight Petualangan Anda:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e497e6410589a7fcd0ed1c6e45c3c5281\"><strong>Keajaiban Air Terjun Tunan:</strong> Awali perjalanan dengan mengunjungi Air Terjun Tunan di Desa Talawan. Rasakan kesejukan air yang jatuh dari ketinggian 86 meter di tengah hutan yang masih murni dan alami.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb2e1172fb4080170363e13fd932fc43c\"><strong>Misi Mencari \"The Big Star\":</strong> Ikuti pendakian sore untuk mencari bintang utama taman nasional ini: <strong>Tarsier Spectrum</strong>, mamalia terkecil di planet bumi yang hanya aktif di malam hari.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e464e81dfa840c8d100d7fff91b0a8876\"><strong>Eksplorasi Satwa Endemik:</strong> Habiskan waktu lebih lama di Cagar Alam Tangkoko untuk mengamati <strong>Black Crested Macaque</strong> (monyet hitam Sulawesi), Kuskus Beruang, serta populasi Burung Rangkong (Hornbill) tertinggi di dunia.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e700841feeba140864f2ddd8ee4831fc4\"><strong>Ekspedisi Hutan Mendalam:</strong> Dengan durasi 4 hari, Anda memiliki kesempatan lebih besar untuk menjelajahi sudut-sudut tersembunyi hutan Tangkoko melalui ekspedisi pagi dan sore yang dipandu oleh <i>ranger</i> ahli.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecce763fd58489acc7716796636d247cc\"><strong>Kehidupan Desa yang Autentik:</strong> Nikmati keramahan lokal dengan menginap di desa Batu Putih, memberikan Anda pengalaman budaya yang tulus sembari beristirahat di tengah suara alam.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>The Ultimate Tangkoko Expedition: A 4-Day Grand Adventure into the Sulawesi Wilderness</strong></h2><p>Are you ready for your own \"National Geographic\" experience? The <strong>4D3N Tangkoko Adventure</strong> is an immersive journey that takes you deep into the pristine tropical rainforest to meet some of the most unique creatures on Earth. From the roar of hidden waterfalls to the gaze of the iconic Tarsier, this adventure is a dream for every nature lover and photographer.</p><h3><strong>Tour Highlights:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"eb42666fb6658882b4ed83b23a9dc3c87\"><strong>Tunan Waterfall Wonder:</strong> Begin your journey at Tunan Waterfall in Talawan Village. Feel the cool mist of an 86-meter cascade tucked away in a pristine, untouched forest.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"efe0de5ac78c7a7137c62a37d36444ec0\"><strong>Mission to Find \"The Big Star\":</strong> Embark on an afternoon trek to find the park\'s main star: the <strong>Tarsier Spectrum</strong>, the world\'s smallest primate, which only emerges as the sun sets.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e999e7cc2ea046f746bb40b415bbae84b\"><strong>Endemic Wildlife Exploration:</strong> Spend ample time in the Tangkoko Nature Reserve to observe the <strong>Black Crested Macaque</strong>, Cuscus Bears, and the world’s highest density of Hornbills.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e02ca0028307d12fbdb52c5a33f1f41de\"><strong>Deep Jungle Expedition:</strong> With a 4-day duration, you have the best chance to explore hidden corners of the forest through expert-guided morning and afternoon treks.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e60cf8df072b68310a40b170709506419\"><strong>Authentic Village Life:</strong> Experience genuine local hospitality with a stay in Batu Putih Village, providing a peaceful rest accompanied by the sounds of nature.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>궁극의 탕코코 탐험: 설라웨시 야생을 탐험하는 4일간의 위대한 모험</strong></h2><p>자신만의 \"내셔널 지오그래픽\"을 경험할 준비가 되셨나요? **4박 3일 탕코코 어드벤처(4D3N Tangkoko Adventure)**는 지구상에서 가장 독특한 생명체들을 만나기 위해 원시 열대 우림 깊숙이 들어가는 몰입형 여정입니다. 숨겨진 폭포의 웅장함부터 상징적인 안경원숭이의 시선까지, 이 모험은 모든 자연 애호가와 사진작가의 꿈입니다.</p><h3><strong>투어 하이라이트:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e87685bbc9992d9015cbc1d42bf014447\"><strong>투난 폭포의 경이로움:</strong> 탈라완 마을의 투난 폭포에서 여정을 시작하세요. 사람의 손길이 닿지 않은 원시림 속 86m 높이에서 떨어지는 시원한 물줄기를 느껴보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e6da37786bc5e2bfa1f9429d478b69ebd\"><strong>\"빅 스타\"를 찾아서:</strong> 해 질 녘에만 나타나는 세계에서 가장 작은 영장류인 <strong>타르시어 안경원숭이</strong>를 찾기 위해 오후 트레킹을 떠납니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb2320123ad659a4ee369c62d7ccb3b76\"><strong>토착 야생 동물 탐사:</strong> 탕코코 자연 보호구역에서 충분한 시간을 보내며 <strong>검정 짧은꼬리원숭이</strong>, 쿠스쿠스 베어, 그리고 세계 최고의 서식 밀도를 자랑하는 코뿔새를 관찰하세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"efdb008da34545fdee51e668f5a3722a1\"><strong>심층 정글 원정:</strong> 4일간의 일정으로, 전문가이드와 함께하는 오전/오후 트레킹을 통해 탕코코 숲의 숨겨진 구석구석을 탐험할 수 있는 최고의 기회를 가집니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5ccac98710674c393f39b9063ac920f3\"><strong>정겨운 마을 생활:</strong> 바투 푸티 마을에 머물며 현지의 따뜻한 환대를 경험하고, 자연의 소리를 자장가 삼아 평온한 휴식을 취해보세요.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>极致唐科科探险：穿越苏拉威西荒野的四日巅峰之旅</strong></h2><p>您准备好开启属于自己的“国家地理”频道式体验了吗？<strong>“4天3晚唐科科冒险之旅” (4D3N Tangkoko Adventure)</strong> 将带您深入原始热带雨林，邂逅地球上最独特的生物。从轰鸣的隐世瀑布到标志性眼镜猴的深情凝视，这场冒险是每一位大自然爱好者和摄影师的梦想。</p><h3><strong>行程亮点：</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ed3f8c3b34857120d6ec6a95add90edb8\"><strong>图南瀑布奇观：</strong> 在塔拉湾村的图南瀑布开启您的旅程。在原始森林的怀抱中，感受从 86 米高处坠落的清凉水汽。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e758118f7cf837c8bdbfab49fc8246452\"><strong>寻找“大明星”任务：</strong> 开启午后徒步，寻找保护区的头号明星：<strong>眼镜猴</strong>。这是世界上最小的灵长类动物，仅在黄昏时分现身。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e05d6c189213053309d9da57274edceb2\"><strong>本土野生动物探索：</strong> 在唐科科自然保护区享受充裕的时间，观察<strong>黑猴</strong>、袋貂以及世界上种群密度最高的犀鸟。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ead60552a6c99161c221c33f86105c7de\"><strong>深度丛林远征：</strong> 为期 4 天的行程让您有更多机会在专业护林员的带领下，通过早晚两次徒步深入探索唐科科森林的隐秘角落。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e026a6f02fbdcf395fd7aeb955a28437a\"><strong>地道乡村生活：</strong> 入住白石村 (Batu Putih)，感受当地人的淳朴热情，在自然的鸣响中享受宁静的休憩。</li></ul>', 0.00, NULL, 'package', 4, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ef32c0bfe5795561b9ab193cd44c60a01\">Full AC transportation according to the number of participants</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8b6758ced173cafd33eeb47088587315\">2 Nights at Tangkoko &amp; 1N at Tomohon (DBL/TWN Bed)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e3b802aad9f6aaa8677df1b6542b2b753\">Experienced Driver &amp; Guide</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0430266106efc4c83295f481a66a272e\">Ranger at Tangkoko Nature Reserve Park</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e6263d3892d15802d1cdbba1e1483fc4b\">Entrance tickets to attractions &amp; parking fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e41e80b8e04edeabc44a8949d6f46e507\">Meals according tour itinerary</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9424305b5471b1307a625f1e394473d3\">Tour services according to the program</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e5160d2919b1850eff838c550505ea428\">Mineral water 2 bottle per day</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e7c5227391081bd816bd247709adc2fb1\">Handling service</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"eab8e19d9005d7b92a3b55f83e6c406d5\">Round-trip airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec89859e61ce5257e8ce597e8b9ed8f95\">Driver Tips &amp; Guide</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eef1817701ed7d1b37d70094c2cf03414\">Optional Tour</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecc81655adf3b9e759353573a80d75f4b\">Costs outside the package (additional food/drink, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e36914624471dc30595049484fcb9c27e\">Porter, Airport Tax &amp; Excess baggage</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0d1bbfc33f8e55265033264d9643f777\">Personal expenses (laundry, mini bar, room service, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e581cc90534790d4f6be55537e1415302\">Travel insurance</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee3f094b58737eb29f43eb8a3427ef690\">And other costs outside the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-25 02:35:03', '2026-05-03 01:40:53'),
(25, 18, 'Tangkoko Adventure 3D2N', 'NORTH SULAWESI', 'tangkoko-adventure-3d2n', '<h2><strong>Wildlife &amp; Volcano Odyssey: Petualangan Epik 3 Hari Menembus Jantung Tangkoko</strong></h2><p>Siapkan jiwa petualang Anda untuk perjalanan mendalam ke salah satu cagar alam paling unik di dunia! Paket <strong>Tangkoko Adventure 3D2N</strong> dari <strong>Welcome Manado Tours</strong> dirancang bagi Anda pecinta alam sejati yang ingin melihat langsung satwa endemik langka di habitat aslinya, sembari menikmati kemegahan kawah gunung berapi dan kearifan budaya Minahasa.</p><h3><strong>Highlight Petualangan Anda:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e3d972df038201a291c14c7e243b9558b\"><strong>Puncak Kawah Mahawu:</strong> Nikmati pendakian singkat selama 10 menit menuju tepian kawah Gunung Mahawu untuk menyaksikan panorama spektakuler kota Tomohon, Manado, dan gugusan pulau di sekitarnya.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef77190fcc702f423c7d94cc8c95cec90\"><strong>Keajaiban Satwa Endemik:</strong> Masuki Cagar Alam Tangkoko untuk bertemu dengan <strong>Tarsier Spectrum</strong> (primata terkecil di dunia), monyet hitam khas Sulawesi (<strong>Black Crested Macaque</strong>), kuskus beruang, hingga beragam burung eksotis seperti Rangkong.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e09ce900d6cd2b2a3da7fce4f0bca7651\"><strong>Relaksasi di Danau Tiga Warna:</strong> Bersantai di tepi Danau Linow yang airnya dapat berubah warna, sambil menikmati suasana sore yang tenang dengan secangkir kopi atau teh.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e511e82c5b5634a4443c25a0e482dbeb6\"><strong>Jejak Sejarah Minahasa:</strong> Mengunjungi Desa Woloan yang terkenal dengan rumah panggung kayu tradisional dan melihat langsung Waruga Sawangan, situs makam batu kuno zaman megalitikum.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8e7d76ffbbd6d97f11e2f6bd4dfbca56\"><strong>Menginap di Tengah Alam:</strong> Rasakan pengalaman autentik bermalam di area Tangkoko, memberikan Anda akses lebih dekat ke kehidupan liar hutan hujan Sulawesi.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>Wildlife &amp; Volcano Odyssey: A 3-Day Epic Journey into the Heart of Tangkoko</strong></h2><p>Prepare your adventurous soul for a deep journey into one of the most unique nature reserves in the world! The <strong>3D2N Tangkoko Adventure</strong> package is designed for true nature lovers who want to see rare endemic wildlife in their natural habitat, while enjoying the majesty of volcanic craters and the cultural wisdom of Minahasa.</p><h3><strong>Tour Highlights:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e2108589b3eb1cfb4fe6aa971a08cd10c\"><strong>Mahawu Crater Peak:</strong> Enjoy a short 10-minute hike to the rim of Mount Mahawu to witness spectacular panoramas of Tomohon, Manado, and the surrounding islands.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e3c15c6d2ece719ad1c5eb6e3cb644b76\"><strong>Endemic Wildlife Wonders:</strong> Enter the Tangkoko Nature Reserve to meet the <strong>Tarsier Spectrum</strong> (the world’s smallest primate), the <strong>Black Crested Macaque</strong> (indigenous black monkey), Cuscus bears, and various exotic birds like Hornbills.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e71dc80b3642244df56fb484407d4f962\"><strong>Relaxation at the Tri-Colored Lake:</strong> Unwind by the shores of Lake Linow, famous for its changing watercolors, while enjoying a peaceful afternoon with a cup of coffee or tea.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8b1fafa84853d96c75fcbe1601ef8bbb\"><strong>Minahasa Heritage Trail:</strong> Visit Woloan Village, famous for its traditional wooden knock-down houses, and see the ancient megalithic stone tombs at Waruga Sawangan.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e73f5e640e9e16b5f70ec077eac1356ad\"><strong>Stay Amidst Nature:</strong> Experience an authentic overnight stay in the Tangkoko area, giving you closer access to the vibrant wildlife of the Sulawesi rainforest.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>와일드라이프 &amp; 볼케이노 오디세이: 탕코코의 심장부를 관통하는 3일간의 대여정</strong></h2><p>세계에서 가장 독특한 자연 보호구역 중 한 곳으로 깊은 여정을 떠날 준비를 하세요! <strong>2박 3일 탕코코 어드벤처(3D2N Tangkoko Adventure)</strong> 패키지는 화산 분화구의 웅장함과 미나하사의 문화적 지혜를 즐기면서, 자연 서식지에서 희귀한 토착 야생 동물을 직접 보고 싶어 하는 진정한 자연 애호가들을 위해 설계되었습니다.</p><h3><strong>투어 하이라이트:</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e94a44a70232bce92cc0ea43c257ba91a\"><strong>마하우 화산 분화구 정상:</strong> 마하우산 가장자리까지 10분간의 짧은 하이킹을 즐기며 토모혼, 마나도 및 주변 섬들의 장관을 감상하세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecf5e4b3e491a4efcb9001a8cee8033f6\"><strong>토착 야생 동물의 경이로움:</strong> 탕코코 자연 보호구역에서 <strong>타르시어 안경원숭이</strong>(세계에서 가장 작은 영수류), <strong>검정 짧은꼬리원숭이</strong>(설라웨시 토종 검은 원숭이), 쿠스쿠스 베어, 그리고 코뿔새와 같은 다양한 이국적인 새들을 만나보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e01fb0eca06d79bafb64c3e11cd93e61b\"><strong>삼색 호수에서의 휴식:</strong> 물빛이 변하는 것으로 유명한 리노우 호숫가에서 여유롭게 휴식을 취하며 따뜻한 커피나 차와 함께 평화로운 오후를 즐겨보세요.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed25c42c7b4cd7850a879cf957c98df69\"><strong>미나하사 유산 탐방:</strong> 조립식 전통 목조 주택으로 유명한 월로안 마을을 방문하고, 거대 석기 시대의 고대 무덤인 와루가 사왕안을 견학합니다.</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e35c68e765552245ce8c383c2703830eb\"><strong>자연 속의 하룻밤:</strong> 탕코코 지역에서의 정통 숙박 체험을 통해 설라웨시 열대 우림의 야생 생태계에 한 걸음 더 가까이 다가가 보세요.</li></ul>', '<h2><strong>野生动物与火山探秘之旅：穿越唐科科心脏地带的史诗三日游</strong></h2><p>准备好您的冒险之魂，深入探索世界上最独特的自然保护区之一！<strong>“3天2晚唐科科冒险之旅” (3D2N Tangkoko Adventure)</strong> 专为热爱大自然的您而设计，让您在领略壮丽火山和米纳哈萨文化智慧的同时，在自然栖息地亲眼目睹稀有的本土野生动物 。</p><h3><strong>行程亮点：</strong></h3><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e579bd752dea9cb9907766f3f0b82dac6\"><strong>马哈武火山之巅：</strong> 仅需 10 分钟的简短徒步即可到达马哈武火山边缘，将托莫洪、美娜多及周边岛屿的壮丽景色尽收眼底 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef918e242d7eba4403a18efe4cda527fd\"><strong>本土野生动物奇观：</strong> 进入唐科科自然保护区，寻找<strong>眼镜猴</strong>（世界上最小的灵长类动物）、<strong>黑猴</strong>（北苏拉威西特有的黑狝猴）、袋貂以及包括犀鸟在内的多种珍稀鸟类 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e042ca215cc57ab820917553918d1dcac\"><strong>三色湖畔的悠闲时光：</strong> 在以湖水颜色多变而闻名的林诺湖畔放松身心，伴着一杯咖啡或茶，享受宁静的午后 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ec6ac96950778094156fa3bd0e6569b2d\"><strong>米纳哈萨遗产追踪：</strong> 参观以传统木制装配式房屋闻名的五老安村 (Woloan Village)，并探访巨石阵时代的古老墓地——瓦鲁加沙旺安 (Waruga Sawangan) 。</li><li data-list-item-id=\"efa81e44e3a6df43930b46eae7d573dc9\"><strong>栖身自然之中：</strong> 在唐科科地区体验地道的住宿，让您更近距离地感受苏拉威西热带雨林的生命力 。</li></ul>', 1000000.00, NULL, 'package', 3, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"eb8cd28a724737ab44cc88dd97a389dbe\">Full AC transportation according to the number of participants</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e9bac968587895ffae01f8d49356df8d4\">2 Nights at Tangkoko (DBL/TWN Bed)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e48aac6bce52fc7428359e501ff729bba\">Experienced Driver &amp; Guide</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed9fed75b7d0562e8bdb0b2bc32232277\">Ranger at Tangkoko Nature Reserve Park</li><li data-list-item-id=\"efc3381224ecde3190b545ad3376102fe\">Entrance tickets to attractions &amp; parking fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e41e80b8e04edeabc44a8949d6f46e507\">Meals according to program</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e6d5acca76e2686e9f57b3b7b6aaf5f65\">Tour services according to the program</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef45128991ca24a9ae216cd6a2ce70a4a\">Mineral water 2 bottle per day</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ea837f120d87ebda8df3ec40c685d6f66\">Handling service</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e6b416fd5c6f77881ce45c46173dd1108\">Round-trip airfare</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ee0319e1248ebd87095dad0bfd8c7d9c9\">Driver Tips &amp; Guide</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb78e7ef31eabb5138ac00798e975cc2f\">&nbsp;Optional Tour</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e7da4c8edc74e8fafda56c7e6740a2611\">Costs outside the package (additional food/drink, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed04c16639d33ef42e9159fc2d3d121c5\">Porter, Airport Tax &amp; Excess baggage</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eefc6702e5083bfaff7b21c733acbf043\">Personal expenses (laundry, mini bar, room service, etc.)</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0f2b3f55047546e4fdbba7daadab0de1\">Travel insurance</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ecc2d015d15e7b1ce5bbbd590e43ce691\">And other costs outside the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-25 02:58:18', '2026-05-03 01:40:40'),
(26, 1, 'Island Hopping Paradise: Bunaken, Siladen & Nain Escape', 'NORTH SULAWESI', 'island-hopping-paradise-bunaken-siladen-nain-escape', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Island Hopping Paradise: Bunaken, Siladen &amp; Nain Escape 🌊🐠✨</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Escape ke surga tropis paling cantik di Sulawesi Utara dan rasakan pengalaman island hopping yang benar-benar unforgettable.<br>Nikmati keindahan bawah laut <strong>Bunaken Marine Park</strong> yang terkenal di dunia dengan air laut super jernih, terumbu karang warna-warni, dan ribuan ikan tropis yang berenang bebas di sekelilingmu.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Lanjut explore cantiknya <strong>Pulau Siladen</strong> dengan suasana tenang dan panorama laut biru yang relaxing, lalu nikmati momen langka di <strong>Pasir Timbul Pulau Nain</strong>—hamparan pasir putih di tengah laut yang muncul saat air surut dan jadi spot foto paling aesthetic.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Bukan cuma sightseeing, kamu juga bisa snorkeling, diving, berenang sambil memberi makan ikan langsung dari tangan, hingga menikmati vibes pulau tropis yang pure healing.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Kenapa harus pilih trip ini?<br>Karena dalam satu hari kamu bisa menikmati kombinasi terbaik:<br><strong>crystal clear water + tropical islands + underwater paradise + white sand views + unforgettable marine experience</strong> dalam satu perjalanan yang fun dan relaxing.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Perfect buat kamu yang mau:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e4561545bc4fb56c7388bfb06977d6471\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Tropical escape yang aesthetic</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e99a0c05560a619e6fddf6706aabdc9f8\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Snorkeling &amp; island-hopping experience</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e81ab33672aa4ec2e0738ded9305601d3\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Laut biru jernih dan vibes healing maksimal</p></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Blue water. White sand. Endless tropical vibes.</strong> 🌴✨</h3><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Siap explore surga laut paling cantik di Manado?</p>', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Island Hopping Paradise: Bunaken, Siladen &amp; Nain Escape 🌊🐠✨</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Escape to North Sulawesi’s tropical paradise and experience an unforgettable island-hopping adventure.<br>Discover the world-famous beauty of <strong>Bunaken Marine Park</strong> with its crystal-clear waters, colorful coral reefs, and thousands of tropical fish swimming around you.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Continue exploring the peaceful beauty of <strong>Siladen Island</strong>, surrounded by stunning blue ocean views and relaxing tropical vibes.<br>Then experience the unique beauty of the <strong>Nain Sandbank</strong>—a hidden white sand paradise in the middle of the sea that appears during low tide and becomes the perfect aesthetic photo spot.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">More than just sightseeing, you can also enjoy snorkeling, diving, swimming while feeding fish directly by hand, and soaking in the ultimate tropical island atmosphere.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Why choose this trip?<br>Because in one journey, you’ll experience the perfect combination of:<br><strong>crystal clear water + tropical islands + underwater paradise + white sand views + unforgettable marine experiences</strong> all in one relaxing and exciting escape.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Perfect for you if you want:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e097cb199bca8defc04d44f1ce60e9f9e\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">An aesthetic tropical getaway</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"eceea21172fc9b6fc0577c17ef5fc8b08\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Snorkeling &amp; island-hopping experiences</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"edb3c81fd96111773c1bc68f523641ae1\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Clear blue ocean and ultimate healing vibes</p></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Blue water. White sand. Endless tropical vibes.</strong> 🌴✨</h3><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Ready to explore the most beautiful marine paradise in Manado?</p>', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>아일랜드 호핑 파라다이스: 부나켄, 실라덴 &amp; 나인 여행 🌊🐠✨</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">북술라웨시의 아름다운 열대 낙원에서 잊지 못할 아일랜드 호핑 여행을 경험해보세요.<br>세계적으로 유명한 <strong>부나켄 해양공원</strong>에서 수정처럼 맑은 바다, 형형색색의 산호초, 그리고 수많은 열대어가 펼치는 환상적인 수중 세계를 만날 수 있습니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">이어지는 <strong>실라덴 섬</strong>에서는 조용하고 평화로운 분위기 속에서 아름다운 바다 풍경과 힐링 가득한 트로피컬 감성을 즐길 수 있습니다.<br>또한 썰물 때만 나타나는 특별한 장소인 <strong>나인 샌드뱅크</strong>에서는 바다 한가운데 펼쳐진 새하얀 모래사장을 배경으로 인생 사진을 남길 수 있습니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">단순한 관광이 아니라, 스노클링, 다이빙, 직접 물고기에게 먹이를 주며 수영하는 특별한 경험까지 즐길 수 있습니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">왜 이 여행인가요?<br>한 번의 여행으로<br><strong>맑고 푸른 바다 + 열대 섬 + 환상적인 바닷속 세계 + 하얀 모래사장 + 특별한 해양 체험</strong>을 모두 경험할 수 있기 때문입니다.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">이런 여행을 찾고 있다면:</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"ee989543866ba510a6195f251e9749daa\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">감성적인 열대 휴양지</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef18a9d396b1e202ca793c7643b4a2375\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">스노클링 &amp; 아일랜드 호핑</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"efc419d44b1e84aa3e585312c2873d89f\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">맑은 바다와 완벽한 힐링 분위기</p></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>푸른 바다, 하얀 모래, 끝없는 트로피컬 감성.</strong> 🌴✨</h3><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">마나도의 가장 아름다운 바다를 탐험할 준비 되셨나요?</p>', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>海岛跳岛天堂：布纳肯、Siladen 与 Nain 之旅 🌊🐠✨</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">逃离城市，前往北苏拉威西最美的热带海岛，开启难忘的跳岛之旅。<br>探索世界著名的 <strong>布纳肯海洋公园（Bunaken Marine Park）</strong>，感受清澈见底的海水、五彩缤纷的珊瑚礁，以及成群热带鱼在身边自由游动的梦幻海底世界。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">接着前往宁静优美的 <strong>Siladen岛</strong>，享受蔚蓝海景与轻松惬意的热带氛围。<br>随后打卡特别的 <strong>Nain沙洲（Nain Sandbank）</strong>——退潮时才会出现的白色沙滩秘境，绝对是最梦幻的拍照地点。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">不仅能观光，你还可以体验浮潜、潜水、亲手喂鱼游泳，真正感受热带海岛的疗愈魅力。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">为什么选择这个行程？<br>因为一次旅行就能体验：<br><strong>清澈海水 + 热带岛屿 + 海底天堂 + 白色沙滩 + 难忘海洋体验</strong> 的完美组合。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">如果你想要：</p><ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e75409af863957e730362f17b4c43586f\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">高颜值热带海岛度假</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"effc1c93ed77cef7c06882a65d71c8c2a\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">浮潜与跳岛体验</p></li><li data-list-item-id=\"e1749dd83c560be2b48dbf56f51a563fa\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">纯净蓝海与满满疗愈氛围</p></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>蓝色海洋，白色沙滩，无尽热带氛围。</strong> 🌴✨</h3><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">准备好探索万鸦老最美的海洋天堂了吗？</p>', 0.00, NULL, 'daily', 1, 0, NULL, 6, 7, NULL, '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e873d778fd1724e641963f19753bd7153\">Private boat to 3 islands</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e7f8a545844508ac34789fff54c3bf4ec\">Experienced tour guide &amp; boatman</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e837639ed702b4b3d563d754b9784f201\">Entrance fees to tourist attractions</li><li data-list-item-id=\"eb3047ce26dd07cba53731a349833c934\">Parking fees</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e17952c91bc59d3bf5bd394db5c31eba2\">Lunch</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8b809428954656d954fcd1a9e186a600\">1 bottle of mineral water per person</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e8b6d227b6ff4563e99f57d10b0c0fa1b\">tour services as per itinerary</li></ul>', '<ul><li data-list-item-id=\"e8b156627fb0192d631973d4400759fd2\">Land transportation (car)&nbsp;</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e64a5c48756da8949a84fc99be24bd499\">Round-trip plane tickets</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e0b3182e85d9f33acc157b85808347961\">Airport tax</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e2cb5bdd5ecfc46fcb144d67bfbd8950f\">Meals</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ef1153321326a82f3288f350ea4e12772\">Porter</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e6657bb1483ae99b0ac50275b9a92fefa\">Hotel</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e90f5a9e0c8775eae0dd396d234c2ca6e\">Guide and driver tips</li><li data-list-item-id=\"e1bc758f69c0ff547e5c8f8aca100c99e\">Optional tours</li><li data-list-item-id=\"ed4f1470355a4f65f457a776a07b216c9\">Other expenses not mentioned in the tour program</li></ul>', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-05-28 11:33:43', '2026-05-28 11:34:24');
